customized visual solutions. We provide customers worldwide with a variety of complex visual perception applications, offering high-quality, high-performance, efficient, and low-cost products and services.','Langrong',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(134,'Foshan Huayuxi CO. LTD','foshan-huayuxi-co-ltd','manda@janssong.com','+86 185 6602 6999','$2b$10$Tatme0iZr9Nhv9RE3pKb4uLG4EdXRcw7mcI0vM2z67kn4T9RhqCxK','supplier','FOSHAN HUYUXI CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/4dabb300-eeab-421f-bb5c-a72d696b90ea.png',NULL,'JANSSONG Building,Kangping South Road, Xiajiang Industrial Zone, Jiujiang Town, Nanhai District, Foshan City.','Since 2016, Janssong has been synonymous with luxury outdoor\r\nfurniture. We’re a global\r\n\r\nleader in luxury outdoor manufacturing and design.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Foshan','Main Office','manda@janssong.com','+86 185 6602 6999',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-01-29 19:06:58','2026-01-30 15:48:17',NULL,0.00,0,0,10,10,25,2016,NULL,NULL,'JANSSONG was established in 2016, specializing in the design and manufacturing of highend outdoor furniture. We offer a wide range of furniture made from various materials such as teak, aluminum, rattan, rope, and plastic wood.','Xiajiang',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(135,'XI\'AN  PERSONAL PROTECTIVE EQUIPMENT CO. LTD','xian-personal-protective-equipment-co-ltd','bettybing@ppe-plus.com',' +86-29-87215814','$2b$10$nRm.TBmjuy9w/AL5Tpy9yOdK2YN4Fg62sxHeam32uAP1i2/ODy9fC','supplier','XI\'AN  PERSONAL PROTECTIVE EQUIPMENT CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/5e29aa08-0ac7-484a-9143-589ba6430d08.jpg','https://www.ppe-plus.com/','ADDRESS: No.217, St Dongda, Xi\'An, Shaanxi Province, China','We Can Give You much more than others',NULL,NULL,'China','Shaanxi','Main Office','bettybing@ppe-plus.com',' +86-29-87215814',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-01-30 16:06:35','2026-01-30 16:11:29','We Can Give You much more than others',0.00,0,0,15,15,30,2011,NULL,NULL,'Xi\'an PPE PLUS Co., Ltd was founded in 2011. Located in Xi\'an, which is one of the four ancient capitals of China. It is located in Xi\'an, one of the four ancient capitals of China. Xi\'an is also the starting point of the ancient Silk Road and the birthplace of oriental civilization. \r\n\r\n\r\nAs one of the well-known suppliers of P P E products in China, we are an integrated solution provider with the support of our research, manufacture and sales departments.\r\n\r\nWe have cooperated with foreign brands such as 3M, Honeywell, M S A (Mesian), Lakeland and Delta for many years, and have built strategic relations with domestic famous brands such as Jingzhou Strong, Tianjin Shuang\'an, Haimen Baojian, etc... We have many years experience in providing a full range of PPE products solutions for the world\'s top 500 enterprises in China, such as Samsung Electronics, Xi\'an Aircraft Industry, C N P C, B Y D Auto, etc., and have received very good evaluation and recognition.\r\n\r\nParticipated in the professional industry A+A German exhibition, established close cooperation with many foreign customers, and annual sales reached 10 million US dollars.\r\n\r\nSo we have the ability to serve global workers and provide safe and reliable P P E products solutions. Our aim is to promote occupational health and to facilitate global harmony. ','Dongda',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(136,'WENZHOU SUNNY ELECTRICAL CO. LTD','wenzhou-sunny-electrical-co-ltd','sale@sunnyele.com','+86-577-85828301','$2b$10$/WlOVctjKsUheMyGhyY46uYlcWgXsL1lsK8D86zyqMqB3X0jOPxuS','supplier','WENZHOU SUNNY ELECTRICAL CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/347b7662-d1c9-4b73-9e00-2e02fd847bb9.png','https://www.klasssunny.com/','No. 738, Binhai Road 12, Wenzhou, Zhejiang, China','If you want to find a good and powerful supplier in China, we are your best choice. We offer high quality and competitive products and hope to develop business with you together.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Wenzhou','Main Office','sale@sunnyele.com','+86-577-85828301',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-01-30 18:06:44','2026-01-31 15:49:35',NULL,0.00,0,0,26,26,151,2000,NULL,NULL,'Established in 2000,Wenzhou Sunny Electrical Co., Ltd. is a professional electrical appliance manufacturer. With over 21 years experience and strong R&D ability, our products have proven popular all over the world, with our high quality, competitive prices, fast delivery and efficient service welcomed by all clients. we provide products such as wall switches, sockets, led light,extension socket and so on, Especially as we start to develop smart products.In 2021, our sales volume has exceed one billion usd. we exporting our various lines to clients throughout the international market, we now have customers in 60 countries in Europe, South America, the Middle East and Southeast Asia,Africa.We now have 500 employees, including 50 engineers and technicians. Boasting magnificent office and production buildings, we are also equipped with comprehensive testing instruments,Having received ISo9001 certification for our management system, we also hold CB, CE, and IEC product approvals.','Zhejiang',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(137,'WEMET LIFT MACHINERY CO. LTD','wemet-lift-machinery-co-ltd','info@wemetlift.com','+86 19963481610','$2b$10$yGtzthdXZihUEdF4qq2OOOzRvRLJPMuVFCVNhphHqsxB7RCWA5qVO','supplier','WEMET LIFT MACHINERY CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/ecd556d3-0473-4a94-b141-0702b5ef2cfb.jpeg','https://wemetlift.com/','Building 24, Jigao Intelligent Park, Jinan City, Shandong Province, China','Wemet is a Chinese high-tech enterprise integrating R&D, design, manufacturing, sales and service of intelligent lifting equipment.\r\n\r\nView all products\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Jinan','Main Office','info@wemetlift.com','+86 19963481610',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-02 20:13:31','2026-02-07 16:28:06',NULL,0.00,0,0,12,12,80,2014,NULL,NULL,'Wemet Lift Machinery Co., Ltd. was founded in 2014, have trademark brands: Wemet®、力千钧® and Parli, which is a Chinese high-tech enterprise integrating R&D, design, manufacturing, sales and service of intelligent lifting equipment.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are committed to providing global users with safer, more convenient and efficient one-stop intelligent lifting solutions.','Shandong',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(138,'ZHONGSHAN  SENHO HARDWAREE PRODUCTS CO. LTD','zhongshan-senho-hardwaree-products-co-ltd','sales@senholock.com','+86-760-22285701','$2b$10$fCfkJ62abxG5XGPHHYMY4.V21hzDSUZ.jjNlNgeCfbR9.k0KzVUvC','supplier','ZHONGSHAN  SENHO HARDWAREE PRODUCTS CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/547e1a18-5b46-43a4-ba15-7cf2f247eb67.png','http://www.senholock.com/','NO.56, Qingfeng 1st Road, Jixi, Xiaolan Town, Zhongshan City, Guangdong Province, China.','Senho locks factory has focused on top quality door locks products for over 15 years.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Zhongshan','Main Office','sales@senholock.com','+86-760-22285701',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-05 20:54:35','2026-02-05 21:00:29',NULL,0.00,0,0,16,16,80,2026,NULL,NULL,'1. Our History\r\n\r\nSenho locks factory has focused on top quality door locks products about 15 years. Senho hardware has gradually become one of the most famous lockset manufacturers in China.\r\n\r\nIn 2003, we built a new modern plant with area 5,000 square meters, staff is about 100 persons and production capability of 500,000 sets per month.\r\n3. Our service\r\n\r\nBesides our existing molded products, Senho also offer the OEM products service. We control the product quality critically for every step during the manufacturing from material parts to the whole structure. We offer technical support that is second to none.…\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Our Factory\r\n\r\nSenho is located in the Zhongshan city of Guangdong province. As a global supplier in the hardware products, All of our products have met ANSI Grade 3 standard. Nowadays, SENHO and GUJU, our two brands have been to create added value for customers around the world.\r\n\r\n','Guangdong',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(139,'PHILIAHOME FURNITURE CO. LTD','philiahome-furniture-co-ltd','sue@philiahome.com','+254741963386','$2b$10$w440c2MslZwIQgG1MTt6w.a4vYHsCO/k/7.kam46OGDAskJ/G/RDW','service_provider','PHILIAHOME FURNITURE CO. LTD','storage/company/logos/3f556bf6-8cec-4206-a63e-e9ed46b0eb77.jpeg','http://www.philiahome.com/','Westlands','Where you make your house a \"HOME\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Nairobi','Main Office','sue@philiahome.com','+254741963386',0,'approved',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-07 16:13:29','2026-02-07 16:27:28','Where you make your house a \"HOME\"',0.00,0,0,10,10,20,2016,NULL,NULL,'PHILIAHOME FUNITURE is a cutting-edge furniture company in Kenya, providing high-quality customized furniture, creatively designed furniture, and fully furnished furniture. We firmly believe that furniture is not just a commodity, it is also an important basic element that turns your house into a home. In addition, our passion for providing high-quality furniture, excellent customer service, and dedication to excellence truly sets us apart.\r\n\r\nWe have extraordinary and unique designs and professional knowledge and skills. Our motivation is not to \'complete sales\', but to provide you with the best advice so that you can make wise and thoughtful choices according to your taste, from browsing to delivery, we are always ready to assist you.\r\n\r\nFrom materials to accessories, from design to production and processing, every detail is the driving force behind our continuous pursuit of improvement.\r\n\r\nWe believe that high-quality furniture does not necessarily have to be expensive. Our goal is to provide fashionable and high-quality furniture at reasonable prices.\r\n\r\nWe are constantly seeking new ways of expressing art and life, striving to transform its abstract beauty into concrete reality as much as possible.','Karen',NULL,NULL,'[]','[]','[]','[]',NULL,'admin',13,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
