INSERT INTO `challenges_achievements` VALUES (57,86,'challenge','1. Continuous postponements of my scheduled site visits.\n2. Sourcing for the right properties that fits my leads\' enquiries.\n3. Getting quality rentals in Parklands and Kileleshwa.'),(60,94,'challenge','1. Sourcing for a house in Kiambu road for Mr Jack who has a budget of Kshs25M.\n2. Sourcing for a ready 1bedroom for Mr Wilson.'),(61,96,'achievement','The website is ok,  i am looking forward to getting clients from the website'),(63,104,'challenge','1. Getting agency consent with Purple Haze for sale or for rent so that I can take my lead to view the apartments.\n2. Sourcing the right properties that fits my hot leads.'),(64,106,'challenge','Today\'s Challenge was making sure the necessary supplies  are restocked and arrived at the office on time and ready for the team to use'),(65,106,'achievement','Completed sourcing assignment  successfully '),(66,106,'adjustment','Will have to manage my time better and make the  most of my time at BEKE'),(67,106,'achievement','Got W.SQ to agree for us to represent them. \n'),(68,106,'achievement','Managed to get a group of  Muslim investors (that i have been following up from; this year August) to let me represent BEKE as their solo agent.\n'),(69,106,'challenge','Challenge today was submitting my daily report'),(70,112,'achievement','1.	I successfully shared Luminara details with all my Village Market clients and have already received positive feedback from two of them. I’ll be following up with the remaining clients tomorrow.\n	2.	I also contacted one lead referred by Rashid, it’s a hot lead who will be back in Nairobi later this week or early next week. I plan to call him again on Friday to schedule a viewing.\n'),(71,115,'achievement','Managed to get a second project as a listing '),(72,115,'achievement','Sent out all daily reports'),(73,115,'achievement','Followed up with one agent and one client for Luminara waiting on their confirmation. '),(74,115,'achievement','Managed to get started on joint collaboration agreement\'s , adjusted a sub - agent contract to benefit BEKE\'S agent\'s and the following up agency agreed (W.SQ)'),(75,115,'achievement','Got another listing that I would like to dedicate to the Administration team and have all of them on board as Sole Agent\'s. '),(76,116,'challenge','Timing with a client.. '),(77,119,'achievement','Our Google business account has been verified by Google,I will be sharing with my team and also alot of people to give their reviews as well.'),(78,123,'achievement','1. I am able to follow up with my previous BEKE leads and managed to convert them to scheduled viewing on this weekend, and hopefully a closure.\n2. I am now getting the right sourcing for my leads especially furnished apartments for rent and investment units for sale.'),(79,124,'challenge','Colliding with fellow work mates listings '),(80,124,'adjustment','Will find another listing to add '),(81,124,'challenge','Multi tasking various duties'),(82,124,'achievement','Sent out all daily reports '),(83,125,'achievement','1. Managed to view Riverside One with my old BEKE lead after consistent follow up.\n2. Another property viewing tomorrow with a lead looking out for 1BR that is ready.'),(84,125,'challenge','1. Most of my leads would like an Indian or a local developer\'s project.\n2. Sourcing the right property that fits my lead\'s enquiry.'),(85,127,'achievement','The Google business account is set up ,I have been sharing the link with people so that they can give their reviews '),(86,129,'challenge','Getting a lease property is proofing to be difficult.'),(87,130,'challenge','I had initially planned a viewing today with Sala, who is interested in Diplomat Residences, but he requested to postpone. He wanted to first review some of the developers’ past projects before proceeding. I shared photos and videos of their previous works, although he raised concerns about the finishing quality. I assured him that Diplomat 