ey show up to the event as promised.'),(151,278,'achievement','1. I now have 3 confirmed leads attending the Luminara Clients Open day this Saturday.\n2. My old leads are responding and 2 of them are set to view Capital Gardens next week.'),(152,278,'challenge','1. Leads who keep on postponing our scheduled viewings.'),(153,278,'adjustment','1. My focus is now on Luminara this week for the Saturday Open day.'),(154,279,'achievement','Got done with Primary office responsibilities '),(155,279,'achievement','Have managed to complete 2 out of the assignments I was given '),(156,288,'achievement','Secured confirmations for Saturday’s Luminara client event\nProvided support on active listings and client cases'),(157,291,'achievement','1. More leads are scheduling site visits. \n2. I have 3 confirmed leads for Luminara tomorrow.'),(158,291,'adjustment','1. I have to keep inviting leads for viewing Luminara tomorrow. '),(159,300,'challenge','Handing in assignments on time'),(160,301,'challenge','Submitting the \"about us \" project on time \n'),(161,302,'challenge','Writing my daily report and submitting the result on time'),(162,302,'adjustment','Time monitoring'),(163,302,'achievement','Sending out reports '),(164,302,'achievement','Getting done with the BRK assignment\n'),(165,303,'achievement','Sending out all reports on time'),(166,303,'achievement','Finding an agent to collaborate with'),(167,304,'achievement','Managed to follow up with an agent'),(168,304,'challenge','Following up with clients/ agents '),(169,304,'achievement','My client maintain contact with me'),(170,305,'achievement','Sending out daily tasks\n'),(171,305,'achievement','Followed up with clients /agents feedback was positive.'),(172,305,'adjustment','Following up with clients'),(173,306,'achievement','Managed to follow up with clients/ agents'),(174,306,'achievement','Managed to assist on a personal win '),(175,306,'challenge','Following up with daily reports'),(176,307,'achievement','Smashing all goals'),(177,307,'challenge','Closing a deal'),(178,308,'adjustment','Finding clients outside of the office'),(179,308,'achievement','Managed to follow up with pending assignments '),(180,308,'achievement','Followed up with agents'),(181,312,'challenge','Following up with my client'),(182,312,'achievement','Successful Agency - to agent collaboration launch with another agent '),(183,312,'achievement','Sent out the necessary reports'),(184,313,'achievement','Today I was able to finish the tasks I had planned to finish today'),(185,315,'challenge','My phone unfortunately broke on Saturday, and as a result I have been unable to access WhatsApp. This has made it difficult for me to share my live location as needed.'),(186,320,'achievement','1. My leads are able to create time to view properties as we are heading for the holidays.\n2. Leads are more interested with pur listings and for more'),(187,320,'challenge','1. Leads are super cautious on thier property choices and would pay attention to details which are not easy to source for.'),(188,326,'achievement','Sent out daily reports'),(189,326,'achievement','Followed up with clients and agents first,'),(190,326,'challenge','Finding a client to commit.'),(191,327,'challenge','We still haven\'t completed the new changes, we are still working '),(192,330,'achievement','Went for one viewing with a client in Karen'),(193,333,'achievement','1. There are more hot and serious leads from our social media.\n2. This week, 4 leads have confirmed for viewing.'),(194,333,'challenge','1. Rentals are stoa challenge.'),(195,338,'achievement','Followed up with pending work and got done with it.'),(196,338,'adjustment','Time management for projects.'),(197,339,'achievement','I was able to get some few details about developers and I uploaded them.'),(198,342,'achievement','1. I have a viewing tomorrow in Kitisuru with Faith to view Eternity apartments at 11am. '),(199,342,'adjustment','1. I wasn\'t able to update my CRM today. Tomorrow is a 