e unwilling to share information. Additionally, the two properties I visited had already sold out all their units, and since sales had closed, the teams were not open to providing further details.'),(215,392,'achievement','My Viewing with Mr Luo went really well, expecting a closure'),(216,396,'achievement','I was able to add some data for four developer profiles that I  created previously.'),(217,397,'achievement','1. My hot lead who will close a sale before 20th December has confirmed that he is coming to our office on the same day with his wife to pick their preferred project and book.'),(218,408,'achievement','Today I was able to achieve my target of the day,I finished the pending work that I had planned to do today '),(219,411,'achievement','1. Able to reach out to over 20 leads and have 2 scheduled viewings with two serious leads.'),(220,412,'achievement','1. My leads preferred Emaar Residence and they are awaiting our feedback on their enquiry on the available units especially the 4-bedrooms.'),(221,413,'adjustment','1. Tomorrow is a holiday and looking to report back to work on 2nd January 2026.'),(222,414,'achievement','My lead, Joyce, who viewed Emaar Residence this past Tuesday has given an offer of Kshs28M for the 4-bedroom apartment.'),(223,416,'achievement','1. There are more viewings for this week. A total of 4 viewings.'),(224,417,'challenge','Team expressed concern regarding the deducted amount of airtime claiming even while on holiday they were still making follow up calls.'),(225,421,'challenge','Network connectivity was low.'),(226,423,'achievement','1. I got an offer from one of my leads who viewed Emaar Residence on the 30th of December 2025. She would like to buy the 4-bedroom for Kshs28M. It is under consideration.\n2. Another diaspora lead would like to view a ready 1- to 2-bedroom apartment in Westlands today.'),(227,424,'challenge','Paddy helped to resize several photos using the correct dimensions of different landing pages but the photos still were not very clear as they are still appearing stretched, we had to talk to the developer and shared our new strategy which would bring a change in the quality of the photos once he has worked on what we agreed on.'),(228,428,'achievement','1.My offer for the Emaar Residence apartment unit has been accepted by the owner. The buyer is ready to pay 20% deposit and the balance via a mortgage. The buyer is waiting for the apartment documents for perusal. My fingers are crossed.\n2.A hot lead from the website is set and ready to view VAAL Real Estate projects tomorrow at 12pm and take her to the office for more orientation.'),(229,431,'challenge','The unit in Escada is available from 19th June wants immediate occupancy '),(230,433,'achievement','I managed to achieve my target for today.'),(231,440,'achievement','1.The offer for the Emaar Residence 4-bedroom apartment is going on well. The buyers have requested for a sample sale agreement to look at as they prepare the 20% deposit payment.\n2.Khadija who has viewed DIVINE suites today has given an offer for the 1-bedroom of 64SqM.\n3.More scheduled viewings are being arranged for this week.'),(232,440,'challenge','1.The rentals sourcing is a challenge especially within Parklands, Westlands, and Kileleshwa.\n2.Also, rentals for Villas are a challenge too.'),(233,444,'achievement','1. My Emaar Residence offer has progressed into a meeting with the owners on Monday next week.'),(234,445,'achievement','I was able to complete the tasks that had planned to do today.'),(235,452,'achievement','I was able to revive one of my old clients and they will be available tomorrow for site visit. '),(236,453,'achievement','1. We are getting more serious leads who are interested in rentals which are in our listings and also units for purchase.'),(237,454,'adjustment','I need to finish data entry so that the new website changes can be uploaded to the server.'),(238,468,'achievement','I  was able to achieve my target for today.'),(239,469,'achievement','1. The offer of Sam and Joyce has been accepted only that Amina and the apartment owners are following up if a mortgage can be secured.'),(240,477,'challenge','The network was unstable, I was not able to work well in the afternoon'),(241,478,'achievement','1. My leads\' offer for the Emaar apartment has been accepted and my leads are waiting for feedback from the owners on whether they accept mortgage payment.\n2. The leads we are being allocated are hot and serious and they are looking to buy or rent.'),(242,478,'challenge','1. Our internet has been very slow today. It needs to be looked at.'),(243,484,'challenge','The landlord for the standalone in Kileleshwa still has\'nt responded to the email we sent on Saturday. Here response will determine the client next steps'),(244,485,'challenge','We have received feedback from the owner regarding the house that the Nanchong Group was interested in. Unfortunately, the owner has decided not to proceed with them as tenants due to the nature of the work the clients intend to carry out on the property, as well as her preference not to have any structures built.'),(245,492,'achievement','1. Finally, the offer from Sam and Joyce has finally been accepted and will be delivered tomorrow at Emaar\'s office.\n2. My lead, Dishon, has finally scheduled for viewing tomorrow for the Syokimau Villa.'),(246,492,'adjustment','1. My viewings for today has been pushed to Saturday.'),(247,493,'adjustment','Getting acquinted to the system  and lack of airtime.'),(248,496,'challenge','The photos on alibaba website are in AVIF format, I still have to download them and convert them to jpg so that am able to use them, this process is slow as I am using other software for the conversion and they have a minimum number of photos I can convert in a day, I can only convert up to 10 photos yet I need more photos.'),(249,500,'achievement','Mia and I started working on the products part we are trying to move in speed.'),(250,502,'achievement','1. My customers: Sam and Joyce have filled up the booking form, and they are waiting for Emaar to confirm if it is in order and then they pay.'),(251,502,'adjustment','1. My scheduled viewings for today have been rescheduled to another day.'),(252,508,'challenge','No airtime allocated yet'),(253,508,'achievement','Managed to get one consent'),(254,508,'adjustment','To confirm and verify authorities with land owners and relevant agents'),(255,510,'challenge','Issue of airtime'),(256,511,'achievement','Mr and Mrs Sam Chasia\'s offer has been accepted by Emaar Consult and they are preparing a sale agreement on the same and then later they pay the deposit for the unit.'),(257,511,'adjustment','I have scheduled viewings for tomorrow which were postponed earlier this week.'),(258,515,'achievement','So far am on the second page of the supplier, I am remaining with 1 to achieve my target.'),(259,519,'achievement','networking'),(260,522,'achievement',' I managed to hit the target of having three pages for the suppliers, I am now working on their products .'),(261,528,'challenge','verification of legal documents'),(262,529,'achievement','1. I got an offer for the 1-bedroom in DIVINE Residency from Khadija and the family.'),(263,529,'challenge','1. Emaar Consult are yet to respond to my customer\'s offer letter. They are ready to pay a deposit.'),(264,532,'achievement','I have created , 3 supplier profiles and added data .'),(265,533,'achievement','Emaar Consult has accepted my customer\'s offer on their payment method and booking form too.'),(266,540,'adjustment','Networking'),(267,543,'achievement','Today I have started working on the products data, as I had planned'),(268,546,'achievement','Emaar Consult have accepted my leads\' offer and I am waiting for Mr Hassan to share the same with me so that I share with my leads.'),(269,555,'adjustment','I need to finish with the suppliers products  as I had planned to finish them by the end of this week.'),(270,556,'achievement','BEKE leads are getting better and better in terms of their enquiries and seriousness level of buying or renting a property.'),(271,565,'challenge','Transportation'),(272,565,'achievement','4 successful sourcing'),(273,566,'challenge','Getting properties for Lease.'),(274,568,'adjustment','I am pushing myself to achieve my targets for the month.'),(275,569,'challenge','1. Emaar Consult are still delaying with the offer letter which my customers are waiting for to progress on with the payment of 30% deposit.\n2. In our office, there is usually, a certain smoke or particles that is affecting us and makes us sneeze or have a running nose. Kindly, it should be looked at.'),(276,572,'challenge','2 clients rescheduled'),(277,575,'challenge','I had a challenge today updating my client follow up list'),(278,576,'challenge','client rescheduling.'),(279,576,'adjustment','Have client book or emphasize on visiting the office.'),(280,578,'challenge','Emaar Consult are really delaying with the offer letter and I believe they are not clear on their offer.'),(281,578,'adjustment','My viewings have been postponed to Saturday.'),(282,582,'challenge','Working with David has become a challenge. He is not following the set conducts of sourcing or viewing new listings.'),(283,586,'achievement','managed 3 sourcing and viewing'),(284,589,'challenge','Emaar Consult are still delaying with the offer letter, and I will still follow up with it tomorrow.'),(285,589,'achievement','I have a hot lead who would like to view Greenview and other options within Runda, since she wants to buy a house to buy and live-in.'),(286,592,'challenge','Today the system was having problems so I wasn\'t able to upload all the listings given to me'),(287,595,'achievement','I was able to get a townhouse for sale at Taj prestige where this landlady reached out through the ad that was running. I spoke to her and we decided to meet tomorrow at her house to discuss matters marketing her unit. This is a new listing for the company. '),(288,596,'challenge','most clients are rescheduling to weekend cause of work,but were still working our way around it for convenience'),(289,597,'achievement','I achieved my target for today.'),(290,603,'challenge','time inconvenient with most clients '),(291,606,'achievement','1. Finally, the offer of my Emaar Residence clients has been issued to them for their consideration and for starting the transaction.\n2. Ben Ireri, who came to our office today, has put an offer to the Luminara unit he has picked and is awaiting feedback on the same.'),(292,606,'adjustment','1. My viewing with Jane to view Greenview Villas has been postponed to tomorrow.'),(293,610,'challenge','Today the site was down,so I wasn\'t able to complete all the tasks I had intended to do.'),(294,614,'adjustment','outsource for more villas for sale and rentals with in runda and gigiri'),(295,615,'achievement','I completed my tasks for today.'),(296,619,'achievement','1. My Emaar leads have received their offer and have responded to the same with some clarification and awaiting feedback.\n\n2. Mr John has put an offer for the 4-bedroom at Greenview Villas and will confirm by Wednesday next week.'),(297,619,'challenge','Getting rentals is still a challenge.'),(298,622,'challenge','Transportation,at times riders refuse to get into some areas due harassment  from cops and most of the times they either cancel or end abruptly leaving one stranded but we always pull through.'),(299,622,'adjustment','Maybe in the near future the company may opt to invest in one motorbike  for convenience.'),(300,626,'challenge','My Emaar Consult offer is being frustrated by the owner of the unit as he would like the deposit to be paid before the sale agreement is executed by both parties. The buyers have scheduled another meeting with Mr. Hassan tomorrow morning at 9am. Yet to be confirmed by the developer.\n\nI wish we would be getting the airtime allowance before the month starts rather than at the end.'),(301,626,'achievement','I now have 3 offers in total right now and pushing for them to be closed within this month.'),(302,627,'adjustment','I need to push to become better everyday '),(303,633,'challenge','Still in getting the right properties that fits my clients\' specifics\n\nConvincing my Emaar leads to pay their 30% deposit after signing the offer letter and not after signing the sale agreement.'),(304,633,'achievement','We are getting serious leads from our marketing team. Kudos!'),(305,639,'challenge','The internet speed is Abit low since now we are many.'),(306,644,'challenge','•	The Brookside townhouse that had been actively marketed was taken up by a tenant the previous day. This has left several active leads interested in the same unit without alternative options to view.\n	•	Sourcing listings in high-end areas such as Spring Valley, Kitisuru, and Lower Kabete is challenging without proper mobility, as access restrictions limit movement without a vehicle.\n'),(307,644,'adjustment','•	I recommend that either Musa or Evans accompany me when sourcing listings in high-end areas, using a car to enable easier access and improve success in acquiring new listings.\n	•	As discussed during the morning meeting, we agreed to introduce physical posters in high-end areas such as Karen, Runda, Spring Valley, and Lower Kabete, targeting landlords who may be seeking assistance in securing tenants. This approach is expected to generate direct landlord contacts and increase available inventory.'),(308,645,'adjustment','To make sure i get all the required documents for every property sourced.'),(309,646,'adjustment','All my viewings today have been postponed to this weekend.'),(310,646,'achievement','We are now getting better leads, where 70% are responsive and 50% are looking to buy or rent a property.'),(311,653,'adjustment','To understand why the apartment ads are not performing and building strategies towards making them work '),(312,655,'adjustment','Everyday is learning day,I take it positively.'),(313,658,'adjustment','Emphasize more on clients physical meeting or walks in the off to be all to analyse as soon as possible.'),(314,659,'achievement','A new offer for my Emaar\'s clients has been accepted, and a new letter of offer is being drafted for my leads to execute and pay.'),(315,661,'achievement','Today I was able to complete the tasks I  had planned to do.'),(316,676,'achievement','Emaar Consult have accepted the new offer from my leads and have prepared a written offer on the same. It will be shared to them tomorrow.\n\nCharity is willing to buy a 2-bedroom for Kshs 8M and is interested in our listings.'),(317,676,'challenge','Sourcing for properties that fits my leads.'),(318,679,'achievement','sourced 3 rentals, and viewed Ineza 1 with my client.'),(319,679,'adjustment','sourcing = selling (more diversity for  potentials)'),(320,684,'achievement','My Emaar\'s Consult buyers have received their updated offer letter and are reviewing it. An update to follow.'),(321,688,'challenge','We should be able to reach out the listings and their developers and counter check if they have been receiving leads whom we refer to their projects.'),(322,688,'achievement','My offers are still under discussion with the respective developers and might be realised soon.'),(323,694,'achievement','I  was able o finish all the tasks I had planned  to do today.'),(324,698,'achievement','Emaar Consults and my leads have both signed the offer letter. My leads are sharing a few personal documents and then the deposit to be paid this week. A follow up tomorrow.\n\nI was able to get more listings for my clients and BEKE, for both rentals and for sale.'),(325,698,'challenge','My leads who have viewed their projects of interest that I shared with them are now taking time or getting cold to place an offer.\n\nI believe BEKE has the power to engage the developers of the projects we have listed and conduct a follow up on our potential leads and determine whether they are buying behind our backs.'),(326,701,'adjustment','I need to deliver my targets for the month early as this month is a very short month.'),(327,704,'challenge','Client rescheduling appointments \nClient responsiveness is also a challenge\nNo new leads'),(328,709,'achievement','Cold leads are now responding'),(329,718,'achievement','I was able to complete all my targets for today.'),(330,721,'achievement','My week is ending on a high note as I have been able to achieve most of my targets.'),(331,725,'challenge','Managed to get new listing for Ruiru\nManaged to get 1 client who is positively considering a rental that we viewed\nManaged to revive previous leads and 1 is viewing Greenview tomorrow and another one on Saturday afternoon'),(332,726,'achievement','Productive day with full client attendance, strong engagement, and one rental transaction at advanced negotiation stage.'),(333,732,'challenge','Managed to take a client for viewing and secure 3 more for tomorrow.'),(334,735,'achievement','All my meetings for today were successful.'),(335,741,'achievement','I achieved my target for the day.'),(336,744,'achievement','1. More leads are responsive and scheduling viewings.\n2. My Emaar Consults clients will pay their deposit within this week.'),(337,744,'adjustment','1. Some leads have changed from their initial preferred project to another one and they would like to view this weekend.'),(338,754,'adjustment','My viewings for today have been postponed to a later date.'),(339,755,'achievement','I managed to do a follow up with my previous client as I had planned to.'),(340,760,'achievement','Closed on a rental in Kilimani'),(341,760,'achievement','An offer letter was given for a one bedroon at Oasis Metricon (going for 6.5M)'),(342,764,'challenge','- I have had a laptop challenge to be honest the available option is not conducive for the job I am supposed to be doing. '),(343,766,'challenge','My colleague still needs a good laptop as the one she was given is not working properly, we are still waiting for it to be repaired as we need it as soon as possible.'),(344,768,'achievement','My Emaar Consult clients have stated they will be paying their deposit on Friday.'),(345,771,'challenge','Client rescheduling viewings');
