INSERT INTO `contractor_portfolio` VALUES (5,40,'decoration_company','designer','Logo Design','Graphics designs','Robnet Wings','Westlands',2025,'3 months','3000','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/robnetlogo-horizontal-removebg-preview-1765623342414.png','designed','\"\\\"\\\\\\\"[]\\\\\\\"\\\"\"',1,'2025-12-13 08:43:53'),(6,89,'construction_company','other','Loan Management System','Simu Loan is a comprehensive loan management system designed to support iPhone financing operations. The system manages all daily business activities, from customer onboarding and loan application to approval, repayment tracking, and account management. It is fully integrated with M-Pesa to enable seamless loan disbursements and real-time repayment processing, ensuring fast and secure transactions. Additionally, SMS integration allows automatic notifications for loan approvals, payment confirmations, reminders, and overdue alerts, improving customer communication and follow-ups. Overall, Simu Loan streamlines operations, enhances efficiency, and provides better control and visibility over the entire loan lifecycle.','Simu Loans Limited','CBD,Nairobi',2025,'4 weeks','150000 - 250000','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/simu-loans-logo-1768211083426.png','The implementation of the Simu Loan system significantly improved operational efficiency by automating daily loan processing, repayments, and customer management. Manual paperwork and errors were greatly reduced, resulting in faster loan approvals and accurate real-time tracking of customer accounts. The M-Pesa integration enabled seamless and timely disbursements and repayments, improving cash flow visibility and financial control.\r\n\r\nCustomer satisfaction increased due to quick service delivery, transparent loan records, and timely SMS notifications for approvals, payment confirmations, and reminders. Clients experienced a smoother and more reliable financing process, leading to improved trust and repeat business.\r\n\r\nKey achievements of the project include successful integration of M-Pesa payments, automated SMS communication, centralized loan data management, and improved collection rates through timely reminders and follow-ups. Overall, the system strengthened Simu Loan’s ability to scale its iPhone financing operations while maintaining efficiency, compliance, and high customer satisfaction.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-12 09:44:43'),(7,89,'design_company','designer','BEKE WEB DEVELOPMENT','BEKE is a digital transformation project where we designed and developed a modern website hosted at afbeke.com, alongside a robust CRM system, and later expanded the platform with a mobile application to support business growth and customer engagement. The website serves as BEKE’s official online presence, showcasing its services, strengthening brand credibility, and enabling seamless customer inquiries. The CRM system centralizes customer data, manages leads, tracks interactions, and streamlines internal workflows, allowing the team to efficiently handle sales, customer support, and daily operations. The mobile app development further enhanced accessibility by enabling users and staff to interact with the system on the go, providing real-time updates and improved responsiveness. Together, the website, CRM, and mobile app form a scalable and integrated digital ecosystem that enhances efficiency, visibility, and overall customer experience for BEKE.','BEKE','Parklands, Nairobi',2025,'12 weeks','600k - 850k','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/beke-1768211838851.png','The BEKE project successfully transformed an existing platform by redesigning and enhancing the company’s website and CRM system. The redesigned website at afbeke.com delivered a more modern, user-friendly, and responsive interface, improving brand image and online engagement. The upgraded CRM streamlined customer and lead management by improving data organization, workflow efficiency, and reporting accuracy, enabling the team to work faster and more effectively.\r\n\r\nAs a result, operational efficiency increased, customer interactions became more structured, and response times improved. Building on these improvements, the project later expanded into mobile app development, extending system access and functionality beyond the web. Overall, the project strengthened BEKE’s digital infrastructure, improved user experience for both customers and staff, and positioned the business for scalability and future growth.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-12 09:57:18'),(8,89,'design_company','other','EVI VENTURES LOAN MANAGEMENT SYSTEM','EVI Ventures Limited is a business loan provider, and this project focused on digitizing and streamlining their operations. Initially, the company relied on manual processes using paper records and Excel sheets to manage customers, loans, and daily activities. We designed and developed a modern website to establish a strong online presence, improve credibility, and make it easier for clients to learn about and apply for business loans. In addition, we built a comprehensive CRM system that fully replaced the manual processes by centralizing customer data, loan applications, approvals, repayments, and follow-ups in one secure platform. The CRM automated key workflows, reduced errors, improved record accuracy, and provided real-time visibility into operations, enabling EVI Ventures Limited to manage their business loans more efficiently and scale their operations with confidence.','EVI VENTURES LIMITED','Thika, Nairobi',2025,'4 weeks','100k - 150k','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/evi-ven-1768212196084.jpeg','The implementation of the website and CRM system at EVI Ventures Limited led to a complete digital transformation of their operations. Manual processes that relied on paper and Excel were eliminated, resulting in faster loan processing, improved data accuracy, and better record management. The CRM centralized all customer and loan information, enabling the team to track applications, approvals, repayments, and follow-ups in real time.\r\n\r\nOperational efficiency significantly improved, staff productivity increased, and errors associated with manual data entry were greatly reduced. Customer satisfaction improved due to quicker response times, better communication, and a more professional service experience. Overall, the project provided EVI Ventures Limited with a scalable and reliable system that supports growth, enhances control over business loan operations, and strengthens decision-making through organized and accessible data.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-12 10:03:16'),(9,99,'design_company','other','Fumigation Services','The project involved the provision of comprehensive cleaning services for the client\'s  premises, aimed at maintaining  a clean, safe and healthy environment.','ABC Place','Westlands',2026,'2 Days','30-50K','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/best-pest-control-servicesin-nairobi-kenya-1024x512-1768295095404.jpg','The cleaning services project was successfully completed in accordance with the agreed scope ,schedule and quality standards. All designated areas were thoroughly cleaned and sanitized resulting in a visibly improved and hygienic environment.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-13 09:04:55'),(10,99,'design_company','designer','Sofa cleaning services','Sofa cleaning services to one of our clients.','Residential home','Kasarani',2025,'1 Day','10-70K','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/sofa-cleaning-service-in-nairobi-kenya-1768296125706.png','The services we offered this client left them smiling as we were able to meet their standards of having a clean house on time as agreed, with the agreed budget as well. We  also fulfilled from our clients satisfaction as our main aim is to see our clients satisfied.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-13 09:22:05'),(11,99,'law_firm','other','Office cleaning services','This office hired our cleaning services for 3 Months which was like our probation period. They needed office cleaning services, cleaning of their desks, walls  and floors.',' Upperhill office suites','Upperhill',2024,'3 Months','80-100k','[]','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/portfolio/covers/cleaning-office-1768303764882.jpg','Our customer was satisfied and gave us a new contract as we kept time and gave the best cleaning services to them. This was a promotion to us as we got even more referrals.','\"[]\"',1,'2026-01-13 11:29:24');
