INSERT INTO `customers` VALUES (31,11,'Bakari Mwasengeza','+254723140643','','+254723140643','','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','Mr. Bakari is looking for a house to buy around the coastal area, he is also looking for a development that can also finance him or a financer that can also finance the apartment as he does not have the cash. i will be talking to one of my contacts in Mombasa to see how we can help this client.','2025-11-09 19:50:03','2025-11-09 19:50:03'),(36,23,'Ronald','0706143295','desmond@afbeke.com','0706143295','N/A','event','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','customer is a source from Village market activation. Interested in 3 bedrooms apartment for sale with a budget of 15M-20M in kitisuru area. Shared Angani Gardens along Kirawa road . waiting to confirm availability to view.','2025-11-10 12:25:23','2025-11-10 12:25:23'),(37,23,'Jemimah','0728594106','desmond@afbeke.com','0728594106','N/A','event','Kenya','individual','land','B','Interested in land in Migaa Golf course so that she can build. Doesnt want a ready house. I have a land from a previou client that I have shared information about land and Jemimah wants to view the piece of land on Sunday. Value of the land is at 6.5 Million.','2025-11-10 13:06:54','2025-11-19 07:16:29'),(38,23,'Aiko Mbarak','0723123051','desmond@afbeke.com','0723123051','N/A','other','Kenya','individual','villa','B','Interested in Garden Villas in Lavington.  We did a virtual viewing but once he is back in town, he will confirm so that he can view in person.','2025-11-10 13:20:34','2026-02-06 07:43:04'),(39,23,'Dominic Mutua','0757403260','desmond@afbeke.com','0757403260','N/A','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','D','Not serious client.','2025-11-10 13:41:02','2025-11-10 13:56:32'),(40,13,'Noble','1.860.881.6994','','','','other','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','Noble wanted a 4-5 Bedroom house in Kileleshwa or Lavington though she was travelling back to the USA .She allowed her brother who is in Kenya to view the options I had sourced for her. Am still in contact with the brother, he is not the one to make the decision , am  still doing follow ups slowly to see if i can close the deal. Hopefully she will consider one of the options i shared .','2025-11-10 13:54:46','2025-11-10 13:54:46'),(41,13,'Mellie','0717183908','','0717183908','','event','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','she requested if i cold source for her a 4 bedroomed house in ;spring valley, Kitisuru, Nyari and Rosslyn. I have shared several options with her and she gave a feedback that i should get back to her in December.I have this in my reminder','2025-11-10 13:59:16','2025-11-10 13:59:16'),(42,11,'Steve','+24700925348','','+24700925348','','event','Kenya','individual','apartment','D','Met Steve at Village Market, he showed interest in Luminara. He has asked me to share photos and more details of the project. I have already shared details. I will call him again tomorrow to follow up.','2025-11-10 14:31:52','2026-02-06 08:48:24'),(43,11,'Yama','+4254438413','','+4254438413','','event','USA','individual','apartment','B','I haven\'t spoken to Yama yet. His phone number is not on whatsapp, he share his wife\'s phone number which is also not on whatsapp. He also shared his mum\'s phone number (her line was going through but didn\'t pick up. i will try again tomorrow. during the expo he showed very high interests in the luminara project to a point where they wanted to go view it the same day. i still think they are serious despite not getting through to them','2025-11-10 14:40:28','2025-11-10 14:45:23'),(44,11,'Salah','+254769970747','','+254769970747','','event','Kenya','individual','apartment','B','He showed very high interest in Luminara , he requested for more details which i have already shared i will be following up with him again tomorrow','2025-11-10 14:45:07','2025-11-10 14:45:07'),(45,11,'Stellah','+254729709046','','+254729709046','','event','Kenya','individual','apartment','C',