,'individual','apartment','D','will be back in two months. interested in an apartment(off-plan).','2026-02-17 07:06:10','2026-02-17 07:06:10'),(1086,50,'alnur Gabow','0746369174','','0746369174','','other','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','share details of morvara on whatsapp','2026-02-17 07:16:43','2026-02-17 07:16:43'),(1087,50,'Jude Gaya','0722224347','','0722224347','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','Looking to rent in Ruiru. shared availables in Ruiru via whatsapp','2026-02-17 08:00:01','2026-02-17 08:00:01'),(1088,50,'Nancy','0722869399','','0722869399','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','looking to view the Ruiru project tentatively friday or saturday. to call on thursday to confirm.','2026-02-17 09:42:23','2026-02-17 09:42:23'),(1089,23,'Hector','0725966964','desmond@afbeke.com','0725966964','N/A','social','Kenya','individual','rental','B','Interested in Rental around Ruiru and has a budget of 70k. I have an option that I have shared. Pushing for a viewing.','2026-02-17 13:10:47','2026-02-17 13:10:47'),(1090,23,'Elizabeth','0725567955','desmond@afbeke.com','0725567955','N/A','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','Client asked to share details via WhatsApp including photos so that they can have a look then later confirm availability on when they can view. Subject to follow up and pushing for a viewing','2026-02-17 13:11:39','2026-02-17 13:15:40'),(1091,23,'Felix','0718372381','desmond@afbeke.com','0718372381','N/A','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','Interested in apartment in Westlands for sale 3 bedroom that is ready for occupation. I have shared option and pushing for a viewing','2026-02-17 13:19:48','2026-02-17 13:19:48'),(1092,12,'Steve ','+254724266020','brianzachary76@gmail.com','0724266020','','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','He\'s looking for a 3br apartment with a budget of 7-13M','2026-02-17 13:54:11','2026-02-17 13:54:11'),(1093,27,'Philjones Odiyo Agent','+254717964903','','+254717964903','','