ourt in Ruiru so that she can share with the husband she can confirm when they can be available for viewing.','2026-02-18 11:37:36','2026-02-18 11:37:36'),(1101,11,'Salma Ahmed','+254728111667','','+254728111667','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','D','She had inquired about a the 5 bedroom villa for sale in Ruiru, she even gave me her husbands number to discuss further. Upon discussing with her husband, he mentioned that they are looking for a development that allows rent to own payment plan (which is a challenge to find) . He wants options close to Westlands with a budget of 25 million. I do not have options in this creteria.','2026-02-18 12:46:30','2026-02-18 12:46:30'),(1102,11,'Beffon Otieno','+254724164971','','+254724164971','','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','B','this client is looking for a 2 bedroom to buy in Westlands ,Kileleshwa and Lavington. He is interested in buying to live there. We have scheduled to meet in the office Next week on Monday to discuss further on options that will be suitable for him.','2026-02-18 13:06:12','2026-02-18 13:06:12'),(1103,46,'Constant Simiyu','+254745404425','rosemary@afbeke.com','+254745404425','Businessman','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','D','-Client is looking for a one bedroom apartment .\n-He will update on his finances in 3 months time.\n','2026-02-18 13:49:50','2026-02-18 13:49:50'),(1104,46,'Ms.Norenaz','+254706385968','rosemary@afbeke.com','+254706385968','Businesswoman','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','-Client is interested in  a 5 bedroom villa at Ruiru , have shared what\'s available on what\'s app.\n-Following up .','2026-02-18 13:54:02','2026-02-18 13:54:02'),(1105,46,'Dennis Kyener\'s','+254700363214','rosemary@afbeke.com','+254700363214','businessman','social','Kenya','individual','villa','D','-Client  already  got what he was looking for a villa but have suggested on investing on land as well.\n-Will be following up on him.','2026-02-18 14:00:37','2026-02-18 14:00:37'),(1106,23,'Racheal','0727231337','desmond@afbeke.com','0727231337','N/A','social','Kenya','individual','villa','B','Inquiry was for Greenview villas, I suggested that they view palm court in Ruiru. they asked for details via WhatsApp so that they can have a look. Pushing for a viewing','2026-02-18 14:04:08','2026-02-18 14:04:08'),(1107,46,'Lucy sueng','+254724794614','rosemary@afbeke.com','+254724794614','Businesswoman','referral','Kenya','individual','apartment','C','-Client was looking for land along Thika road .\n-Have given her an option of investing on  an apartment as well with in Westland and she\'s weighing the options.\n-Following on it','2026-02-18 14:06:14','2026-02-18 14:06:14'),(1108,46,'Lewis Wambugu','+254101793455','rosemary@afbeke.com','+254101793455','businessman','social','Kenya+254101793455','individual','apartment','C','-Client phone is off.\n-Will keep trying .','2026-02-18 14:09:58','2026-02-18 14:09:58'),(1119,11,'Tobias Akaja','+254723066297','','+254723066297','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','D','Tobias is looking for a villa or land to buy on behalf of his aunt. From the conversation he doesn\'t seem like he is aware of exactly what he is looking for, does not have a budget, no preferred location hence why i have put him in the D category.','2026-02-18 14:52:15','2026-02-18 14:52:15'),(1120,11,'Joan','+254780167269','','+254780167269','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','B','Joan had inquired about the Ruiru townhouses, she is already familiar with the area and would like to come view at the end of the month with her husband. i will reach out to them towards the end of next week to schedule an appointment.','2026-02-18 15:06:27','2026-02-18 15:06:27'),(1121,11,'Mutemi','+254722251700','','+254722251700','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','B','Mutemi is looking for a one bedroom for investment , ideally in upmarket areas. i have shared options with him and we have scheduled for a viewing next week once he is in Nairobi.','2026-02-18 15:18:33','2026-02-18 15:18:33'),(1122,11,'Thomas Aul','+254700858592','','+254700858592','','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','B','Thomas is looking for a studio or one bedroom for investment in Westlands, Kileleshwa or Kilimani. I have shared some options with him awaiting response.','2026-02-18 15:28:05','2026-02-18 15:28:05'),(1123,51,'Philip','0723688856','','','','social','Kenya','individual','apartment','B','Interested in apartment 2 bedroom at 35M in Riverside or Westlands (sent options) \nAlso wanted to view townhouses that are worthy to be considered. Looking to get feedback from client','2026-02-18 15:48:02','2026-02-18 15:50:25'),(1124,51,'Joseph Ndegwa','0721812257','','','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','D','Looking for a townhouse for rent 20k. No options for this ','2026-02-18 15:50:05','2026-02-18 15:50:05'),(1125,51,'Norenaz Q','0706385968','','','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','Client did not pick up, left a message ','2026-02-18 15:52:51','2026-02-18 15:52:51'),(1126,51,'Israel','0704658267','','','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','B','I sent available options and he will revisit after ','2026-02-18 16:02:51','2026-02-18 16:02:51'),(1127,51,'x','0733940396','','','','social','Kenya','individual','villa','C','Line busy, left a message','2026-02-18 16:07:51','2026-02-18 16:07:51'),(1128,12,'Muthoni','+254723833750','brianzachary76@gmail.com','0723833750','','social','Kenya','individual','rental','C','She\'s looking for a villa to rent in Ruiru or Kamiti road ,I\'m sourcing more options for her ','2026-02-18 17:37:30','2026-02-18 17:37:30');
