-bedroom unit through mortgage financing. I shared a resale option at Capital Heights, and he is planning to create time for a site visit.\n\nI also followed up with Pamela regarding the 1-bedroom apartment she intends to buy for her daughter. She confirmed that she will schedule time to view the options I had previously shared.\n\nI checked in with Mr. Georges as well, and he mentioned that they are considering Luminara and will give their final decision by the weekend.\n\nLater, I took Albi for a viewing at the Luminara project. She was very impressed and noted that she will discuss the option with her son before giving her final decision. She showed interest in a unit on the 12th floor ','2025-11-25','Follow up with Mr Maurice concerning his viewing appointment for syokimau 5 br mansionatte \nFollow ups with pending previous clients ','2025-11-25 18:49:30','2025-11-25 18:49:30'),(211,22,'-Attended the office morning meeting\n- Made some follow up calls with clients and landlords which I updated on my customer list.\n-Later went to Karen met Mr Thugii he showed me his 2acre land ready for sale as soon as he get the title by mid next week where he will also sign the consent. ','2025-11-25','','2025-11-25 20:09:28','2025-11-25 20:09:28'),(212,29,'Finished up on the remaining locations site shoot','2025-11-25','','2025-11-25 23:47:00','2025-11-25 23:47:00'),(213,20,'i went to raphta road for a viewing of 0.5acres with a client micheal where he liked the place  but he requested for the land owner and document to be available in the next meeting\nlater i went  meeting on a law farm in kilimani regards to the 0.5acres in parklands where both advocates meet and made the requrements be done by wednesday morning','2025-11-25','','2025-11-26 06:26:00','2025-11-26 06:26:00'),(215,20,'i went to raphta road for a viewing of 0.5acres with a client micheal where he liked the place  but he requested for the land owner and document to be available in the next meeting\nlater i went