ays in the afternoon.','2025-12-10','All is good for now. ','2025-12-10 17:00:39','2025-12-10 17:00:39'),(343,22,'Attended the office morning meeting.\n-Made follow up calls with leads from meta and TikTok and also clients.\n-Updated CRM clients\n-Met a client interested in Luminara and planned for viewing early next year 2026.\n- Took a Client for a site visit to Ruiru behind Spur mall for 5acres.. We planned to meet the owner tomorrow 11th Dec 2025 9:30 Am.','2025-12-10','','2025-12-10 17:11:40','2025-12-10 17:11:40'),(344,29,'Started with our marketing team morning meeting; discussed the day\'s work plan. After our meeting we then had a joint meeting with the sales department to bring our heads together on diverse strategies we can implement for our content to stand out more. After the meeting I started editing a talking video of the Marina Bay 2 project. In the afternoon we attended the Hephe Launch event where I took some clips which I\'ll compile and edit a video out of.','2025-12-10','','2025-12-10 17:25:44','2025-12-10 17:25:44'),(345,17,'Meetings and Tasks:\n\n- Attended morning meeting at the office to discuss ongoing projects and strategies, aligning with team goals and objectives.\n- Prepared and shared the leads Excel sheet with the team, ensuring everyone is informed and up-to-date on progress.\n- Attended the Hephe\' Palace project site in Westlands and recorded footage of the new development, capturing key aspects of the project','2025-12-10','','2025-12-10 18:24:39','2025-12-10 18:24:39'),(346,23,'ChatGPT said:Daily Report:\n\n\nLeads Assigned (by Rashid):\n4 leads received today.\n\n\nResponsive Leads: 2\n\n\nLead 1: Interested in a 3-bedroom duplex in Riverside for rent. Currently, we don’t have this type of property, only simplexes available. Still sourcing options.\n\n\nLead 2: Interested in Kitisuru duplexes. I shared available details with them and will follow up to schedule a viewing.\n\n\n\n\n\n\nFollow-Up with Previous Clients:\n\n\nUtsav: 