ious kitchen',2,2,115.00,'sqm',13000000.00,'Ksh','available','apartment','storage/company/units/a651abc2-d8a8-486c-830d-e50fbe87cda1.png',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-06','3rd parklands',NULL,NULL,'[\"Gym\", \"Swimming pool\", \"Kids play\", \"High speed lifts\"]','{}',0,0,1,'2026-02-06 11:57:14','2026-02-06 11:57:14'),(71,91,'Spacious All Ensuite 4 Bedroom Apartment + SQ on Githunguri Road, Kileleshwa – 272 SQM','COMFY RESIDENCE','Property Description:\r\n\r\nOverview Comfy Residency is a residential development located on Githunguri Road, Kileleshwa. The project comprises 133 units, with each apartment offering a spacious floor area of 272 Square Meters.\r\n\r\nUnit Specifications:\r\n\r\nAll Ensuite Bedrooms: 4 Bedrooms, each featuring its own private bathroom.\r\n\r\nServant Quarter (SQ): A dedicated ensuite SQ with a separate entrance.\r\n\r\n8-Meter Balcony: An expansive 8-meter wide balcony accessible from the main living area.\r\n\r\nSolar System: Individual Solar Water Heating system for every unit.\r\n\r\nEssential Utilities & Backup:\r\n\r\nWater Supply: On-site Borehole providing a consistent water supply to supplement the municipal water system.\r\n\r\nPower Backup: Standby Generator installed to provide electricity to both common areas and individual apartments during power outages.\r\n\r\nBuilding Facilities:\r\n\r\nFitness: Separate gym rooms for men and women, featuring a selection of cardio and strength training hardware.\r\n\r\nSwimming Pool: An outdoor swimming pool with a surrounding deck area.\r\n\r\nElevators: High-speed lift access to all floors.\r\n\r\nSecurity: 24-hour manned gate, CCTV monitoring, and electric perimeter fencing.\r\n\r\nLocation: Situated on Githunguri Road, offering proximity to Kasuku Centre, Lavington Mall, and various international schools.',4,5,272.00,'sqm',21999999.98,'KES','available','apartment','storage/company/units/78ca671e-a3fd-4f4f-842d-dc69f37a0210.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-11','GITHUNGURI ROAD, KILELESHWA, NAIROBI',NULL,NULL,'[]','{}',0,1,1,'2026-02-11 06:20:30','2026-02-11 06:20:30');
