INSERT INTO `properties` VALUES (1,'PINECREST RESIDENCE','pinecrest-residence',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,145535,1,'Kindaruma rd.',-1.30023501,36.79445511,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250704/e7e3d344dd002f2435bef0c4a2456a9942136b4d.jpg',NULL,70000.00,NULL,NULL,53.00,53.00,'001','<p><strong><u>PINCREST RESIDENCE UNITS FOR RENT</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Situated in a serene and secure environment, this unit offers:</p><p>Space&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Security</p><p>Privacy </p><p>Excellent road access</p><p>Location- Kilimani along Kindaruma road</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features and amenities</strong></p><p><br></p><p>● Heated swimming pool</p><p>● Steam sauna</p><p>● Fully fitted gym</p><p>● Fully fitted kitchen </p><p>● Full backup generator </p><p>● Ample parking </p><p>● High speed lifts </p><p>● Smart lock door</p><p>● Borehole </p><p><br></p><p>Pincrest residence is in close proximity to these important facilities;</p><p><br></p><p>Top schools</p><p>Hospitals</p><p>Shopping malls and restaurants</p><p>Excellent road access</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices</strong></p><p>1 bedrooms - all sold out</p><p>2 bedrooms - 112 sqm</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,12,0,1454,'2025-10-22 19:59:09','2026-02-03 08:39:58','<p>A beautifully appointed home offering modern comfort, timeless design and exceptional livability.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'70000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"floorNumber\":\"1\",\"interiorArea\":\"53\",\"orientation\":\"15\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"70000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(2,'THE LOFTS','the-lofts',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,5,5,'Kilimani location',-1.28998794,36.79939270,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250704/7c1a8ba311370634e7468b04eb58d86a3ff485fe.jpeg',NULL,285000.00,285000.00,285000.00,55.00,70.00,'23','<h2><u>The Lofts At Wood Avenue - Kilimani Apartment</u></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\">Located about 10 minutes by car from Uhuru Park, The Lofts At Wood Avenue - Kilimani Apartment Nairobi gives access to a number of tourist attractions in the area.</span></p><p><strong>The Lofts At Wood Avenue - Kilimani Apartment</strong> comprises a balcony and a seating area featuring a sofa set, and modern comforts like a multi-channel television. Bathrooms come with a separate toilet and a shower. Additionally, you\'ll find dryers and towels.</p><p>There are a refrigerator, an oven, and kitchenware provided for guests at the apartment. This accommodation is only a stone\'s throw from the pub Jiweke Tavern.</p><p>This apartment lies at a moderate distance from Shifteye Gallery. David Sheldrick Wildlife Trust is within a 10-minute drive of the property. The nearest airport is Wilson, 10 km from this apartment, and Prestige Plaza bus station is only 350 metres away.</p><h3><u>Features and amenities</u></h3><h3>General</h3><ul><li>Wi-Fi</li><li>Safe deposit box</li></ul><h4>Dining</h4><ul><li>Dryer</li><li>Cookware/ Kitchen utensils</li><li>Outdoor dining area</li></ul><h4>Room Amenities</h4><ul><li>Sitting area</li><li>Dining table</li><li>Washing machine</li><li>Flat-screen TV</li><li>Alarm clock</li><li>Carpeted floor</li></ul><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>2 Bedrooms 55sqm at Ksh 285,000</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,13,0,1482,'2025-10-22 19:59:11','2026-01-10 14:50:32','<p>Located about 10 minutes by car from Uhuru Park, The Lofts At Wood Avenue - Kilimani Apartment Nairobi gives access to a number of tourist attractions in the area.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'285000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"floorNumber\":\"18\",\"interiorArea\":\"55\",\"orientation\":\"10\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(3,'SUNSTONE GENERAL MATHENGE','sunstone-general-mathenge',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,1,69,'General Mathenge Westlands',-1.25083980,36.79289448,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250704/b7a79e33da51ba7b0f7eb9b97ed63058933293a4.jpg',NULL,145000.00,NULL,NULL,158.00,158.00,'10','<p><br></p><p>Discover comfort and convenience in these beautifully maintained house units located in General Mathenge.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Amenities included with the unit:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Spacious main kitchen and a separate preparation kitchen</li><li>Dedicated laundry area</li><li>Large lounge and dining spaces</li><li>Smart home finishes</li><li>2 high-speed elevators</li><li>Heated swimming pool and kids’ play area</li><li>Café, yoga studio, control room</li><li>CCTV surveillance, borehole water, backup generator</li><li>Mini shop on-site</li><li>High-quality modern finishes and ample parking, including visitor slots</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>The summary below outlines available apartments categorized by type, floor, parking spaces, size, and rental amount:</strong></p><p><br></p><ol><li>2-Bedroom + DSQ Apartments Located on Floors 4, 7 to 12. Each unit has 1 parking space. Size: 1,700 sqft (158 sqm). Monthly rent ranges from 145,000 to 155,000.</li><li>4-Bedroom + DSQ Apartments Located on Floors 13 to 15. Each unit has 3 parking spaces. Size: 3,400 sqft (316 sqm). Monthly rent ranges from 325,000 to 350,000.</li><li>5-Bedroom + DSQ Apartments Located on Floors 13 and 14. Each unit has 3 parking spaces. Size: 4,800 sqft (446 sqm). Monthly rent: 425,000.</li></ol><p><br></p><p>This home is just moments away from the following key facilities:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Excellent road access</li><li>Hospitals</li><li>Top schools</li><li>Shopping malls and dinning areas</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,15,0,1396,'2025-10-22 19:59:11','2026-02-12 12:50:24','<p>Refined urban living at Sunstone General Mathenge ,one of Westland\'s most sought after residential addresses.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'145000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"floorNumber\":\"2\",\"interiorArea\":\"158\",\"orientation\":\"11\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"145000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(5,'KENZI RESIDENCE','kenzi-residence',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,1,25,'Westlands,Nairobi',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250708/978f7d5e9c0cb5a32137f1e4138bdaa4c801f3f7.jpg',NULL,70000.00,70000.00,70000.00,55.00,55.00,'7','<p><br></p><p>Welcome to Kenzi residence offering a perfect blend of privacy, space, and easy access to essential amenities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Apartment features and amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Clever, contemporary layouts with high-end finishes:</li><li>Floor-to-ceiling sliding windows</li><li>Granite countertops, high-pressure rain showers</li><li>Built-in wardrobes, MDF kitchen cabinets, gypsum bulkheads</li><li>Unit amenities include private balconies (in some units), in‑unit laundry setups, and modern intercom systems .</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Building Amenities</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Residents enjoy upscale facilities such as:</p><p>Heated resort-style swimming pool</p><p>Full gym, steam room &amp; sauna, Yoga/Juice bar</p><p>Rooftop garden lounge and social house (movie/meeting room, billiards)</p><p>24‑hour CCTV, access control, borehole water supply, backup generator</p><p>High-speed lifts and landscaped garden areas .</p><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and price:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Studio sqm (34–35) 80K – 120K (unfurnished est.)</li><li>Deluxe Studio sqm( 49) 150k</li><li>1-Bedroom sqm( 53–61)&nbsp;120K – 150K+ (furnished est.)</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Sale','rental',0,0,15,0,1060,'2025-10-22 19:59:12','2026-02-12 12:39:41','<p>Welcome to Kenzi residence offering a perfect blend of privacy, space, and easy access to essential amenities.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'70000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"floorNumber\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"55\",\"orientation\":\"11\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"120000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(6,'LE MAC','le-mac',NULL,2,2,55,1,1,1,25,'Westlands , Matundu Lane',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250718/030331c948f0f56261c7eef91ee85eb370174eb3.jpg',NULL,150000.00,150000.00,150000.00,127.00,127.00,'001','<p><strong><u>1 Bedroom for rent in Westlands</u></strong></p><p>Le’Mac is a statement of impeccable architecture with immense attention to detail and a fine blend of spaces to allow functional flows with ensuring utmost privacy.</p><p><strong>Apartment&nbsp;features:</strong></p><ul><li>Avant grade finishes</li><li>Floor to ceiling windows</li><li>Spacious kitchen</li><li>Spacious dinning area</li><li>Balcony with ample space</li><li>Spectacular views</li></ul><p><strong>Prime location</strong></p><p>Le mac is moments away from key facilities:</p><p>Top schools</p><p>Hospitals</p><p>Excellent road access</p><p>Shopping malls and restaurants</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and price</strong></p><p>127 SQM at Ksh 150,000 per month</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,13,0,0,'2025-10-22 19:59:12','2025-12-08 09:23:58','<p>Le’Mac is a statement of impeccable architecture with immense attention to detail and a fine blend of spaces to allow functional flows with ensuring utmost privacy.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'150000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"floorNumber\":\"15\",\"interiorArea\":\"127\",\"orientation\":\"14\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(7,'VOLAIRE','volaire',NULL,2,2,56,1,1,1,25,'Matundu Lane, Westlands',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250716/172c3d4fb4965f17a66754d17217f203e0131ab5.jpg',NULL,250000.00,250000.00,250000.00,84.00,84.00,'2','<p><br></p><p>Discover this beautifully maintained 2 bedroom located in Westlands .</p><p>This unit offers a perfect blend of privacy ,space , security and access to essential amenities.</p><p>Each apartment features:</p><p>terrace</p><p>balcony</p><p>washing machine</p><p>fully equipped kitchen</p><p>TV</p><p><strong>Essential Facilities:</strong></p><p>Guests enjoy free WiFi, free on-site private parking, and a private pool. The property provides a relaxing environment with a terrace and balcony.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Convenient Location:</strong> Located 5.6 mi from Wilson Airport, the apartment is close to attractions such as Nairobi National Museum (2.5 mi), Kenyatta International Conference Center (3.1 mi), and Nairobi Botanic Garden (2.5 mi).</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Local Surroundings:</strong> A restaurant is available in the surrounding area, offering diverse dining options.</p><p><strong>Unit size and price :</strong></p><p>2 Bedroom 84sqm at Ksh 250,000</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,13,0,1414,'2025-10-22 19:59:13','2026-02-16 08:10:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'250000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"floorNumber\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"0\",\"orientation\":\"13\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(8,'LE MAC','le-mac-1761163154168-1',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,1,25,'Westlands',-1.26802076,36.77553177,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250721/8e33b4bd405fd21ebf5b0313c82a18d7379525d4.jpg',NULL,250000.00,250000.00,250000.00,142.00,142.00,'19','<p><strong><u>2 Bedroom for rent in Westlands</u></strong></p><p>Le’Mac is a statement of impeccable architecture with immense attention to detail and a fine blend of spaces to allow functional flows with ensuring utmost privacy.</p><p><br></p><p>Apartment&nbsp;features:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Avant grade finishes</li><li>Floor to ceiling windows</li><li>Spacious kitchen</li><li>Spacious dinning area</li><li>Balcony with ample space</li><li>Spectacular views</li></ul><p><strong>Prime location:</strong></p><p>Le mac is moments away from key facilities:</p><p>Top schools</p><p>Hospitals</p><p>Excellent road access</p><p>Shopping malls and restaurants</p><p>Unit sizes and price:</p><ul><li>142 sqm at Ksh 250,000 per month</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','Lease','rental',0,0,13,0,1163,'2025-10-22 19:59:14','2026-02-15 07:24:25','<p>Le’Mac is a statement of impeccable architecture with immense attention to detail and a fine blend of spaces to allow functional flows with ensuring utmost privacy.</p><p><br></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'250000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"floorNumber\":\"2\",\"interiorArea\":\"142\",\"orientation\":\"10\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(10,'KRESTONE APARTMENTS','krestone-apartments',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,1,25,'Westlands, School lane',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250723/74741c80d3f9e795e9ee0da38bd04ecbf03c3b43.jpg',NULL,75000.00,75000.00,75000.00,45.00,45.00,'3','<p><strong><u>1 BEDROOM FOR RENT</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Located in Westland\'s along School Lane, this modern newly built apartment block is conveniently located within walking distance to shopping centers, offices and entertainment spots.</p><p>Newly built 1bedroom units with master ensuite and good lighting. Open floor plan with a seamless flow between the dining and living area. Quality finishes throughout the building with large windows and a balcony for every unit.</p><p>Located in the upscale Westlands area close to key shopping centres including Sarit Centre, Westgate Mall, commercial offices, restaurants and entertainment hot spots.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Full backup generator</p><p>High speed lifts</p><p>Ample Parking space</p><p>Electric fence</p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>Good security with CCTV