 166 sqm Ksh 15.5M</li><li>3 Bedroom 180 sqm Ksh 19 M</li><li>3&nbsp;Bedroom+ Study + Dsq 208 sqm 21.5 M</li><li>3 Bedroom + Dsq Ksh 212 sqm 20.5 M</li><li>3 Bedroom + Dsq 226 sqm Ksh 21.5 M</li><li>3 Bedroom+ Study + Dsq&nbsp;236 sqm Ksh 22M</li><li>4 Bedroom +Study + Dsq 251 sqm Ksh 24M</li><li>4 Bedroom + Study + Dsq 260 sqm Ksh 24.6M</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Seamlessly blends luxury, convenience, and an unbeatable location. Secure your unit today! Completion Date: Q1 2027, PAYMENT PLAN; – Minimum deposit of 20%, with the balance payable within the remaining construction period</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,13,1,1207,'2025-10-22 20:00:14','2026-02-10 12:26:37',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'102564.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"4\",\"bathrooms\":\"4\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"260\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"102564\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(131,'CAPITAL HEIGHTS','capital-heights','CAPITAL HEIGHTS',2,1,NULL,1,1,1,1,'Matundu Lane',37.27556090,112.77926310,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250702/69f6c4911befe60d0a9cbe7dd6f9f000b7eccf6a.jpg',NULL,110000.00,7150000.00,18900000.00,65.00,173.00,'2','<p><strong><u>CAPITAL HEIGHTS</u></strong></p><p>Capital Heights Apartments is a premier high-rise residential development located in the prestigious Westlands area along School Lane, Matundu Close. Spanning 21 floors across 2 blocks, this project redefines modern living in Nairobi, offering luxury, functionality, and unmatched convenience.</p><p>Developed by the team behind the successful Capital Rise and Capital Garden in Kilimani, Capital Heights combines strategic location with strong investment value.</p><h3>World-Class Amenities:</h3><ul><li>Heated Rooftop Swimming Pool with City Views</li><li>Fully Equipped Gym</li><li>Steam Room &amp; Sauna</li><li>Children’s Play Area</li><li>Ample Parking for Residents &amp; Guests</li><li>Full Backup Generator</li><li