dustrial, and commercial buildings.The construction of the development is estimated to be completed in 2026 and will offer studio and 1-bedroom units.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>These apartments will be served by facilities and amenities including: </strong></p><p><br></p><p>•• Spa - (Massage rooms, steam &amp; sauna)</p><p>•• Outdoor swimming pool.</p><p>•• Rooftop yoga garden</p><p>•• Children’s play area.</p><p>•• Gym</p><p>•• Rooftop lounging gazebos</p><p>•• Shopping complex on the ground floor.</p><p>•• Outdoor courtyard.</p><p>•• Ample parking spaces.</p><p>•• Valet parking &amp; concierge services.</p><p>•• Full power backup generator</p><p>•• Borehole</p><p>Hotel units available</p><p><br></p><p>•Studio hotel apartments - Starting from $60,000</p><p>•One Bedroom hotel apartments - Starting from $90,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>•1.5 years payment plan - 0% interest</p><p>•Reservation - 15% interest</p><p>•During Construction - 50% spread in 18 months</p><p>•Before or upon Hand Over - 20%</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Hotel unit sizes:﻿</strong></p><p>•Standard Studio - 33 sqm</p><p>•King Studio - 44 sqm</p><p>•Standard One Bedroom - 49 sqm</p><p>•King One Bedroom - 53 sqm</p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>(<strong>Note</strong>: Offering flexible payment plans over the remaining construction period after placing a 30% deposit to reserve. On the below prices, we offer high discounts for high deposits and full cash buyers)</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,13,60,1479,'2025-10-22 20:00:16','2026-02-11 07:01:13',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'239200.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"33\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"239200\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(133,'LUCKINN IVY','luckinn-ivy','LUCKINN IVY',2,1,NULL,1,1,1,1,'MOGOTIO RD',28.69305300,115.81535600,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default