n the vicinity, Riara Schools, Makini School, Braeburn, and Rusinga School to name just a few.</p><p>Set on Kingara road close to one of the most exclusive and serene parts of Kileleshwa, this is an exceptional and unique development presenting a magnificent opportunity to own or invest in one of Nairobi’s most sought-after suburbs.</p><p>The apartment is 2 minutes walk to The Junction Mall and boasts some of Nairobi’s best schools within walking distance.</p><p>The development has&nbsp;54 units of 3 and 10 units of 4 bedrooms all ensuite apartments with DSQ complete with luxurious amenities and finishing of the highest standards.</p><p>All the units have a generous size and are designed ergonomically to ensure comfortable yet functional living. The workmanship of the development and finishes are of the highest standard possible.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Our project comes with modern finishes and amenities such as;</p><p>Heated Swimming pool</p><p>Gym</p><p>CCTV cameras</p><p>Full back up generator</p><p>Jogging track</p><p>Mini Mart</p><p>Kids Play Area</p><p>Laundry area</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Apartment Prices&nbsp;and size :</strong></p><p>Unit 1: 2 bed 123.6 sqm</p><p>Unit 2: 2 bed 126.4 sqm</p><p>Unit 3: 3 bed 237.8 sqm</p><p>Unit 4: 3 bed 250.9 sqm</p><p>Unit 5: 3 bed 267.6 sqm</p><p>Unit 6: 4 bed 345.6 sqm</p><p>2 Bed – 123.6 sqm – Ksh: 19,017,000</p><p>3 Bed + SQ – 237.8 sqm – Ksh: 36,575,397</p><p>4 bed + SQ – 345.6 sqm – Ksh: 51,000,000</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,12,1,1369,'2025-10-22 20:00:18','2026-02-11 08:39:36',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'147826.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"4\",\"bathrooms\":\"5\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"345.6\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(154,'COVO ABORATUM','covo-aboratum','COVO ABORATUM',2,1,NULL,1,1,6,1,'Ring Road Kileleshwa',-1.27420532,36.79933582,'https://ap