p, conference rooms &amp; banquet hall</p><p>Rooftop entertainment terrace</p><p><br></p><p> <strong>Unit Types,sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>)</p><p>1 Bedroom (Standard) 73 m² / ~786 ft² Neighbourhood $100,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type A 111 m² / ~1,195 ft² Karura Forest $140,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type B 97 m² / ~1,044 ft² Neighbourhood $130,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type C 104 m² / ~1,120 ft² Karura Forest $140,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type D 91 m² / ~980 ft² Muthaiga / local schools $130,000</p><p>3 Bedroom (Standard) 162 m² / ~1,744 ft² 6th Avenue Parklands View $180,000</p><p><br></p><p>Surroundings &amp; Accessibility</p><ul><li>Located in Parklands, just 5 km from Nairobi’s CBD, Asili Hills benefits from:</li><li>Natural setting next to Karura Forest, providing lush greenery and peaceful views.</li><li>Nearby major amenities including Aga Khan Hospital, MP Shah Hospital, Diamond Plaza, Oshwal Centre, and the Parklands Sports Club offering sports and leisure facilities.</li><li>Close proximity to public transport options (matatus, buses, rideshares), good internet connectivity, several schools and restaurants in walking distance&nbsp;.</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,15,0,1156,'2025-10-22 20:00:21','2026-02-16 20:43:24',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'143677.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"73\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(165,'CASA RINA HEIGHTS','casa-rina-heights','CASA RINA HEIGHTS',2,1,NULL,1,1,1,1,'Westlands,Mvuli road',28.60032480,116.45013860,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/1cbbbad1dc0ac1add83eb6e1728595978957f20f.jpg',NULL,102500.00,8200000.00,15200000.00,80.00,145.00,'4','<p><br></p><p>Casa Rina Heights comprises of a variety of&nbsp;tastefully designed 1 and 2 bedroom apartments for sale along Mvuli Road in the prime serene Westlands Area. Come and experience the ep