ur living experience.</p><p>It consists of a total of 18 floors, with 95 units, 131 parking slots and 13 visitors parking slots.</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Property Features and Amenities:</strong></p><p>East and West Sky Gardens</p><p>Infinity heated swimming pool</p><p>Steam room</p><p>Modern fitted gym</p><p>Reception lobby and management office</p><p>2 High speed lifts</p><p>Ground level manicured and landscaped</p><p>courtyard garden</p><p>Ample parking</p><p>Full backup generator</p><p>24 Hr security services at the gate and on property</p><p>Intercom</p><p>Perimeter electric fence</p><p>Borehole</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li>1 Bedroom unit From 77 sqm ( 829sqft ) – From Ksh 15.7M SOLD OUT</li><li>2 Bedroom unit From 132 sqm ( 1421 sq ft ) – From Ksh 25M</li><li>3 Bedroom unit From 218 sqm ( 2347 sqft )- From Ksh39M</li><li>4 Bedroom Duplex Penthouse&nbsp;From 623 sqm ( 6706 sqft ) – From Ksh 93.2M</li></ul><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>Standard payment plan</p><p>10% booking fee, 10% upon signing of the sale agreement, 70% payable in 7 equal quarterly instalments over the construction period and 10% on project completion (non-refundable).</p><p><strong>Alternative payment plan:</strong></p><p>a) Mortgage Buyers:</p><p>For mortgage financing, there is a price premium of 20%. The payment plan would be as follows: 30% deposit, balance of 70% at completion</p><p>b) Other Payments:</p><p>If a buyer wishes to make upfront payments, a discounted price may be considered.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,13,100,1478,'2025-10-22 20:00:21','2026-02-12 11:44:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'203869.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"77\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"203869\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(167,'ROYAL LEGEND','royal-legend','ROYAL LEGEND',2,1,NULL,1,1,5,1,'Ndemi road',2