ional Schools: Brookhurst School (4 mins), Braeside School (7 mins), Strathmore School (6 mins), Nairobi International School (6 mins), Makini School (9 mins), Riara Group of Schools (7 mins), and Hekima University (7 mins).</li><li>Leading Hospitals: Coptic Hospital (10 mins), Nairobi Hospital (10 mins), Gertrude Children’s Hospital (3 mins), and Aga Khan Hospital (5 mins).</li><li>Major Shopping Malls: Yaya Centre (6 mins), Lavington Mall (6 mins), Valley Arcade Mall (5 mins), Junction Mall (10 mins), Sarit Centre (14 mins), and Westgate Mall (17 mins).</li><li>Recreational &amp; Sports Clubs: Nairobi Jaffery Sports Club (5 mins), Space Playground (11 mins), Nairobi Polo Club (12 mins), and Parklands Sports Club (19 mins).</li></ul><h3>Property Types &amp; Unit Features:</h3><p>AYA Luxury Residence offers a wide selection of modern apartments and villas tailored to diverse lifestyle needs:</p><h4>1. Sky Villas – The Ultimate Penthouse Experience</h4><ul><li>5-Bedroom Triplex Sky Villa + DSQ (580sqm, 418sqm, 360sqm)</li><li>6-Bedroom Duplex Sky Villa + DSQ (503sqm, 488sqm)</li><li><strong>&nbsp;Features:</strong></li><li>Private rooftop garden with patio shade</li><li>Double-volume ceiling</li><li>Fully fitted Turkish kitchen &amp; kitchenette</li><li>Walk-in closets in master bedrooms</li><li>His &amp; hers vanity sinks</li><li>Expansive balconies &amp; terraces</li></ul><h4>2. Duplex &amp; Garden Villas – A Private Sanctuary</h4><ul><li>6-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (740sqm)</li><li>4-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (609sqm, 347sqm, 255sqm)</li><li>3-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (347sqm, 255sqm)</li><li><strong>Features:</strong></li><li>Private landscaped garden</li><li>Spacious living &amp; dining areas</li><li>Smart home features</li><li>High-end Turkish finishes</li><li>All ensuite bedrooms</li></ul><h4>3. Duplex &amp; Standard Apartments – Luxury Redefined</h4><ul><li>4-Bedroom Duplex + DSQ (400sqm, 262sqm)</li><li>3-Bedroom Duplex + DSQ (280sqm, 265sqm, 221sqm)</li><li>2-Bedroom Apartments (125sqm)</li><li>Studio Apartments (49sqm)</li><li><strong> Features:</strong></li><li>Private balconies &amp; terraces</li><li>Fully fitted kitchen with premium appliances</li><li>Modern staircase with elegant grills</li><li>Spacious TV room &amp; lounge area</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,12,3,1087,'2025-10-22 20:00:23','2026-02-11 09:10:56',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'173460.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"6\",\"bathrooms\":\"8\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"740\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"173460\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(171,'ASTRA BAY','astra-bay','ASTRA BAY',2,1,NULL,1,1,1,14,'Westlands',-0.15988430,36.78471820,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250704/fcad0732e3cb281e2b67230dbbf9d622cd6fc6b9.jpg',NULL,72874.00,1800000.00,4300000.00,24.70,51.48,'9','<p><br></p><p>Welcome to <strong>Astra Bay Residence</strong>, where contemporary design meets urban convenience. This sophisticated development offers a range of modern living spaces perfect for young professionals, first-time homeowners, and savvy investors. Strategically located in Lower Kabete, Astra Bay Residence provides seamless connectivity to key areas of Nairobi while offering a tranquil, stylish lifestyle.</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Lower Kabete</p><p><strong>Property Type:</strong> Studios and 1-Bedroom Apartments</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Exceptional Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><h3> Backup Generator: Uninterrupted power supply for all areas.</h3><h3>✅ Fully Equipped Gym: Maintain an active lifestyle.</h3><h3>✅ 24-Hour CCTV Surveillance: Enhanced security for your peace of mind.</h3><h3>✅ Social Corridor: Perfect for community interactions.</h3><h3>✅ Borehole Water Supply: Reliable and clean water access.</h3><h3>✅ Jogging Track: Stay active in a safe environment.</h3><h3>✅ High-Speed Lifts: Quick and convenient access to all fl