inment Area</p><p>• Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>• High-Speed Lifts</p><p>• Backup Generator</p><p>• Borehole Water Supply</p><p>• 24/7 Security &amp; CCTV Surveillance</p><p>• Intercom &amp; Access Control</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,15,10,1464,'2025-10-22 20:00:35','2026-02-18 11:30:33',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'109091.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"110\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(209,'ENKANG APARTMENTS','enkang-apartments','',2,1,NULL,1,1,60,59,'Ng\'ong\' road',-1.33915290,36.68163397,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/f7c7ce8306f9fdcea952584db9aea061406b86bc.jpg',NULL,110000.00,5500000.00,10500000.00,50.00,105.00,'14','<p><strong><u>ENKANG APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Enkang Apartments is a premier residential development project along Ngong Road. The project is located near the modern Talanta Stadium. Enkang continues to grow with the exciting progress of Phase 3. Following the successful completion and handover of Phase 1 in 2021 and Phase 2 in 2024, the construction of Phase 3 began in 2024. Designed to provide modern, community-oriented living spaces, this new phase is set to deliver spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments within a 14-floor complex. Ravi Homes is excited to share the latest milestones in the construction of Phase 3 and explain why this development remains a top choice for homebuyers and investors in Kenya’s real estate market.</p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>High speed WIFI connectivity</p><p>Reliable borehole water supply</p><p>Back up generator</p><p>Ample parking space</p><p>Modern , spacious lifts</p><p>Back up power generator</p><p>Code access security system at the main entrance</p><p><br></p><p><strong><u>Unit sizes and prices</u></strong></p><p><strong>1-Bedroom Unit</strong> (50SqM)- 5.5 Million</p><p><s