>2‑Bedroom</p><p>Booking-type short-stay apartments with standard two-bedroom layout of ~120 sqm (1,292 ft²); typical night rates ~$79 (~KES 10,000+ per night) on travel platforms&nbsp;.</p><p>For sale pricing not explicitly listed for 2‑beds—but rental market context suggests 2‑beds in Kilimani often ask KSh 80k–120k/month unfurnished, with higher rates for furnished Airbnb options&nbsp;.</p><p>✅ Summary Table</p><ol><li>3‑Bedroom + DSQ ~135 sqm ~13.0 M ~140,000/month Sauna, pool, generator, borehole, solar water heating, inverter, AC units, parking, gardens&nbsp;</li><li>2‑Bedroom ~120 sqm (Not listed for sale) ~80,000–120,000/month (*) Kitchenette, balcony, flat-screen TV, patio, parking, AC, pool, generator</li></ol>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,15,0,1393,'2025-10-22 20:00:38','2026-02-11 11:31:45',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'104000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"3\",\"bathrooms\":\"3\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"135\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"104000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(211,'PHENOM PARK','phenom-park','PHENOM PARK',11,1,NULL,1,1,2,1,'Lang\'ata',-1.36204764,36.73712254,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250918/e7f3194741a7857a151d9b87c1b1aeddea01cda7.jpg',NULL,161290.00,35000000.00,35000000.00,217.00,217.00,'15','<p><strong><u>PHENOM PARK</u></strong></p><p>Phenom Park will have 10 unique clusters of 20-24 Townhouses, an Apartment Block and a Community Center with Club House. The clusters are set around the spine road which facilitates free flow of traffic within the estate.</p><h3><strong>Features:</strong></h3><ul><li>Access Gate</li><li>Backup generator</li><li>Banking Services</li><li>Basketball, Tennis and badminton court</li><li>Borehole</li><li>Children’s playgrounds</li><li>Jogging track</li><li>Ol Pejeta Conservancy</li><li>Outdoor yard</li><li>Resort</li><li>Rooftop Relaxing Gazebo</li><li>Scenic views of Mt. Kenya</li><li>Smart parking</li><li>Spa, Salon and Gym</li><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Top Notch Security</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Moments away from amazing key facilities:</p><p>Excellent roads</p><p>Best academic institutions</p><p>Shopping malls and chill spots</p><p>Top health facilities</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>4 Bedroom 217 sqm at Ksh 35,000,000</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,15,15,1144,'2025-10-22 20:00:38','2026-02-18 06:32:28',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'161290.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"4\",\"bathrooms\":\"4\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"217\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"161290\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(212,'MARINA BAY 1','marina-bay-1','MARINA BAY 1',11,1,NULL,1,1,1,1,'Sports road,Westlands',-1.26365392,36.80067064,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250714/38cf5efd5e11a5091cc265762f99d5505d620eca.jpeg',NULL,114285.00,8000000.00,21200000.00,70.00,198.00,'32','<p><strong><u>MARINA BAY SQUARE</u></strong></p><p>MARINA BAY SQUARE is located in the heart of Westland, on the junction of David Oseli and Sports road. Just behind Park Inn by Radisson Blu. With proximity to commercial hubs, shopping malls, medical and education centers. The property is premium for both investors and residents. The development comprises of 2 blocks offering 1 and 2 bedrooms.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;Features:</strong></p><p>– Swimming pool and fully equipped gym</p><p>– Children’s play area</p><p>– Sauna room</p><p>– Restaurant Cafe</p><p>– Conference room</p><p>– Visitor reception and lobby</p><p>– Main power and full Back-up generator</p><p>– Water borehole</p><p>– 24-hour security with CCTV surveillance</p><p>– Four elevators</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom (67 sqm) – From Kshs 7.8M – 8.2M</p><p>1 Bedroom (70 sqm) – From Kshs 8M – 8.4M</p><p>2 Bedroom plus DSQ (130 sqm) – From Kshs 13.55M – 14.15M</p><p>2 Bedroom plus DSQ (135 sqm) – From Kshs 14.65M – 15.25M2 Bedroom plus DSQ (145 sqm) – From Kshs 15.55M – 16.15M</p><p>3 Bedroom plus DSQ (198 sqm) – From Kshs 21.25M – 22.25M</p><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><p>Occupation Dec 2026</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,12,32,1053,'2025-10-22 20:00:38','2026-02-06 00:52:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'114285.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"3\",\"bathrooms\":\"3\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"198\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"114285\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(213,'MARBLE WEST','marble-west','MARBLE WEST',2,1,NULL,1,1,1,1,'Mogotio road,Westlands',-1.26430484,36.81399299,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250714/7d1e45b1186f9351079f657ed614eb7d05bd9e21.jpeg',NULL,146660.00,6600000.00,10900000.00,45.00,130.00,'33','<p><br></p><p>Located on Muthithi Road, just a 5-minute walk to Sarit Centre, GTC Mall, and Westgate Mall, this property offers a perfect blend of modern living and convenience. Designed with luxury in mind, the units are ideal for homeowners or investors looking for prime urban real estate in a secure and accessible location.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul><li>Rooftop Infinity Swimming Pool</li><li>Fully Fitted Gym</li><li>Sky Lounge &amp; Barbecue Area</li><li>Sauna &amp; Yoga Studio</li><li>Executive Rooftop Restaurant</li><li>Landscaped Zen Garden</li><li>Borehole Water Supply</li><li>Full Backup Generator</li><li>High-Speed Lifts</li><li>CCTV &amp; Biometric Security</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Furnished Studio</strong> (45sqm): From KSh 6.6M</li><li><strong>One Bedroom</strong> (64sqm): From KSh 7.85M</li><li><strong>Two Bedroom</strong> (97-130sqm): From KSh 10.95M</li></ul><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><ul><li>10% deposit balance within 3 years with 0% Interest.</li></ul><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><ul><li>Project estimated completion December 2027</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,12,33,1495,'2025-10-22 20:00:39','2026-02-12 12:27:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'146660.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"45\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"146660\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(214,'KINGS COURTYARD','kings-courtyard','KINGS COURTYARD',2,1,NULL,1,1,5,1,'Kilimani, Lenana rd.',-1.28883048,36.79565125,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250702/caedc2f6a3bd67becf1155b659b5f2c83ab68a42.jpg',NULL,119631.00,13000000.00,19500000.00,111.00,163.00,'0','<p><br></p><p>Situated along Lenana Road in the Kilimani neighborhood of Westlands Sub‑county, about 5 km west of Nairobi’s CBD&nbsp;.</p><p>Easily accessible — just 5 minutes from Kilimani Police Station, 10 minutes to the city center, and 8 minutes from Nairobi Arboretum&nbsp;.</p><p>Close to Yaya Centre, cafés, schools, hospitals, embassies, and banks&nbsp;.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></p><p>Kings Courtyard offers a host of upscale features geared toward comfortable and modern urban living:</p><ul><li>Recreational &amp; Community Facilities: Rooftop leisure pool, fitness &amp; recreation centre, children’s play area, community hall&nbsp;.</li><li>Security &amp; Access: Secured boundary walls, controlled entry/exit with automatic barriers, CCTV coverage of key areas, high‑speed elevators in each block&nbsp;.</li><li>Utilities: Backup generator for common areas, solar lighting in shared spaces, borehole water supply, inverter backup capability, anti‑termite foundation, cabro‑paved driveways&nbsp;.</li><li>Apartment Interiors: All bedrooms ensuite, branded bathroom fittings, designer sanitary ware, provision for gas cylinder in kitchen yard, TV points, fibre/Wi‑Fi readiness, balconies offering views&nbsp;.</li><li><br></li></ul><p><strong> Unit Types &amp; Pricing