nd children</p><p>Leisure gathering lawns</p><p>Children’s Art Playground</p><p>Jogging Loop</p><p>Sky private club</p><p>State-of-the-art Gym</p><p>SPA</p><p>Hair &amp; nail salon</p><p>Café</p><p>Mini-cinema</p><p>Boutique Mall</p><p>Card access system</p><p>24 Hour CCTV</p><p>Intrusion Alarm system</p><p>Connected Parking solution</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>One Bedroom ( 82sqm)&nbsp;– From Ksh. 28340000</p><p>Two Bedroom (105-110sqm) - From Ksh. 36400000</p><p>Three Bedroom (137sqm-175sqm) - From Ksh.45,500000</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,12,38,1395,'2025-10-22 20:00:49','2026-02-16 20:31:59','<p>A modern and elegant development designed for comfort, convenience and contemporary living.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'260000.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"82\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"260000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(243,'GITANGA DUPLEXES','gitanga-duplexes','',2,1,NULL,1,1,7,19,'Gitanga Road,Lavington',-1.28526274,36.74850767,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250721/2af5a71650d36bc1869b879a579b8e8ab7ffb5d7.jpg',NULL,161049.00,33000000.00,43000000.00,248.00,267.00,'0','<p><strong><u>GITANGA DUPLEXES</u></strong></p><p>Gitanga Duplexes (Lavington, off Gitanga Road):</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Heated swimming pool &amp; fully equipped gym</p><p>Solar water heating, borehole, and backup generator</p><p>High-speed lifts, 24/7 security, CCTV &amp; intercom</p><p>2-car parking per unit</p><p>Landscaped gardens, cabro driveways, underground tanks</p><p>Smart cabling: internet/fiber, TV, intercom Prices ready</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Price:</strong></p><p>KES 33M – 43M</p><p>Depends on unit type, size, floor level, and view.</p><p>Mortgage payment plans available with some agents.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></