cal movement across floors for resident convenience.</p><p>Borehole Water Supply – Reliable source of water regardless of municipal supply interruptions.</p><p>Children\'s Playground – Safe, dedicated recreation area for little ones.</p><p>Ample Parking – Designated parking for both residents and visitors.</p><p>Backup Generator – Ensures uninterrupted power during outages.</p><p>CCTV &amp; 24/7 Security – Round-the-clock monitoring and access control for peace of mind.</p><p>Social Hall &amp; Rooftop Garden – Communal spaces for socializing, events, and relaxation.</p><p>Modern Finishes – Stylish interiors and high-quality materials throughout the building.</p><p>Close Proximity to Shopping &amp; Dining – Just meters from Yaya Centre, and near Prestige Plaza, Java House, Art Café, Junction Mall, Nairobi Hospital, Aga Khan Clinic, and more.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><ol><li>1 Bedroom Deluxe&nbsp;53 sqm 6 million – 7 million</li><li>1 Bedroom Executive / Premium 55‑64 sqm&nbsp;6.5 million – 7.5 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Compact&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;86 sqm 9 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Standard&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;92 sqm&nbsp;9.5 million – 10 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Deluxe&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;95 sqm&nbsp;10 million – 11 million</li></ol>','show',NULL,1,'yes','On sale','sale',0,0,15,0,1437,'2025-10-22 20:00:51','2026-02-12 12:44:38',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'115789.00',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"53\",\"decorationStatus\":\"2\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"115789\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(247,'GICHUGU APARTMENTS','gichugu-apartments','GICHUGU APARTMENTS',2,1,NULL,1,1,6,1,'Gichugu Rd,Kileleshwa',-1.27580444,36.79298095,'https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250721/579ce6183bb22f32702daee4f6ef3c55f270a5b6.jpg',NULL,91133.00,9000000.00,18500000.00,148.00,203.00,'0','<p><br></p><p>Gichugu Apartments is situated off Gichu