/strong></p><p>Located in Thindigua just off Kiambu Road, this 1-acre parcel offers an exceptional opportunity for residential development or investment in one of Kiambu county\'s fastest- growing suurbs. The neighborhood is becoming highly sought after due to its strategic proximity to Nairobi\'s business districts, improved road access and expanding amenities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Land and site features:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>The plot is gently sloping and features</li><li>Power and water connections available in the area</li><li>Flexible land use</li><li>Established amenities are nearby ((Schools, hospitals, shopping malls and restaurants)</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Acres and price:</strong></p><p><strong>1 Acre at ksh 210,000,000</strong></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,24,0,1243,'2025-11-12 12:52:20','2026-02-06 00:18:06','<p><br></p><p>Located in Thindigua just off Kiambu Road, this 1-acre parcel offers an exceptional opportunity for residential development or investment in one of Kiambu county\'s fastest- growing suburbs. The neighborhood is becoming highly sought after due to its strategic proximity to Nairobi\'s business districts, improved road access and expanding amenities.</p><p><br></p>','','','[]','210000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"1\",\"landUse\":\"\",\"zoning\":\"\",\"price\":\"210000000\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[],\"titleDeed\":\"\"}'),(311,'SYNINA RESIDENCE','synina-residence',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,6,16,' Kileleshwa',1.99900000,2.34500000,'/storage/property/covers/synina1-1763116159388.jpg','2025-11-14 13:21:00',134529.00,30000000.00,41400000.00,NULL,NULL,'84','<p><strong><u>SYNINA RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Synina Residency comprises 3, 4, 5 and 6 Bedroom plus DSQs all en-suite luxury apartments strategically located on Tinderet Avenue, Kileleshwa. Encircled in a haven of scenic views, Synina Residence is conveniently situated in the highly sought after, private and secure neighborhood of Kileleshwa, Nairobi. This development comprises 77 opulent residences thoughtfully constructed with separate domestic living quarters.</p><p><strong>Features and Amenities</strong></p><ul><li>Fully-equipped Gym Dedicated Fitness Center for Ladies</li><li>Infinity Swimming Pool</li><li>Spacious Rooftop Entertainment Lounge</li><li>Serene Garden</li><li>Spacious Lounge and Dining Area</li><li>Fully Fitted Modern Kitchen with Pantry</li><li>High Speed Elevators</li><li>2 Parking Spaces Per Unit and extra for visitors</li><li>Borehole and Back Up Generator</li><li>CCTV Surveillance and 24-hour Security</li><li>Kids Play Zone</li></ul><p>Designed with meticulous attention to the needs of the occupier, Synina Residency spares no expense on the sizes of the rooms. Households today have evolving spatial needs to cater for their growing families and this development’s key merit is the ample sizes of the rooms in each unit. The spacious living area boasts soaring ceilings with full-height windows bathing the house with natural light and breathtaking views. The dining area and sitting room opens out to a large terrace with spectacular views of Nairobi’s Cityscape. The closed kitchen is both stylish and functional.</p><p>3 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (223 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 30M&nbsp;RENTAL: 180,000 per month</strong></p><p>4 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (298 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 38.5M&nbsp;RENTAL: 250,000 per month&nbsp;</strong></p><p>5 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (325 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 41.4M</strong></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1382,'2025-11-14 10:29:19','2026-02-09 10:30:24','<h3>Synina Residency comprises 3, 4, 5 and 6 Bedroom plus DSQs all en-suite luxury apartments strategically located on Tinderet Avenue, Kileleshwa. Encircled in a haven of scenic views, Synina Residence is conveniently situated in the highly sought after, private and secure neighborhood of Kileleshwa, Nairobi.</h3><h3><br></h3><h3><br></h3>','','','[]','134529',NULL,NULL,11,'{\"bedrooms\":\"4\",\"bathrooms\":\"3\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"223\",\"decorationStatus\":\"2\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(312,'BEACON BY SYNINA','beacon-by-synina',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,6,16,'Kileleshwa',1.87650000,2.09870000,'/storage/property/covers/beacon4-1763118481463.jpg','2025-11-14 13:56:00',117948.00,29900000.00,58000000.00,253.50,463.10,'84','<p><strong><u>BEACON BY SYNINA</u></strong></p><p>Rising gracefully on Mandera Road,&nbsp;<em>Beacon by Synina</em>&nbsp;is an architectural masterpiece redefining luxury living in Nairobi’s upscale Kileleshwa neighborhood. This striking high-rise offers a collection of expansive 3- and 4-bedroom residences with DSQs, alongside lavish 5-bedroom simplex and duplex penthouses, designed for the modern homeowner who values timeless elegance and superior craftsmanship.</p><p>Set in a serene yet well-connected location, Beacon by Synina ensures residents enjoy unmatched convenience. From top schools like Kenton College and The Kenya High School, to vibrant retail hubs such as Yaya Centre, Junction Mall, and ABC Place, everything you need is within minutes. Easy access to the Nairobi Arboretum, Nairobi Hospital, Westlands, Nairobi CBD, and the Expressway makes this residence as practical as it is prestigious.</p><p>With skyline views and an abundance of premium amenities, Beacon by Synina promises not just a home, but a lifestyle.</p><p><br></p><h4><strong>A</strong>menities;</h4><ul><li>Infinity rooftop swimming pool, baby pool &amp; sun deck</li><li>SkyView His &amp; Hers gym, aerobics studio &amp; sauna</li><li>Rooftop gazebo, BBQ zone &amp; firepit</li><li>Multi-purpose hall for exclusive gatherings</li><li>Welcome concierge reception lounge</li><li>Borehole water supply &amp; full backup generator</li><li>High-speed elevators</li><li>Manned gatehouse, 24/7 CCTV &amp; electric fence</li><li>Two parking bays per unit + ample visitor parking</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ (Type A, 2,728 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 29.9M</li><li><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ (Type B, 2,431 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 29M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type A, 3,685 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 40M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type B, 3,960 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 46M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type C, 3,707 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 40M</li><li><strong>5 Bedroom Simplex PH (Types A, B, C, 4,972–5,258 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 55M</li><li><strong>5 Bedroom Duplex PH (4,994 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 58M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><h4><strong>C</strong>ompletion Date</h4><p>Estimated Completion:&nbsp;<strong>Q4 2026</strong></p><h4><strong>P</strong>ayment Plan</h4><ul><li>Initial Deposit: 30%</li><li>Next 6 Months: 30%</li><li>Following 6 Months: 30%</li><li>On Handover: 10%</li></ul>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1089,'2025-11-14 11:08:02','2026-02-13 09:49:46','<p><br></p><h3>Rising gracefully on Mandera Road,&nbsp;Beacon by Synina is an architectural masterpiece redefining luxury living in Nairobi’s upscale Kileleshwa neighborhood.</h3><h3><br></h3><p><br></p><h4><br></h4>','','','[]','117948',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"3\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"253.5\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(313,'LILYDALE','lilydale',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,12,13,'Brookside',-1.25623350,36.79172380,'/storage/property/covers/lilydale1-1763378883848.jpg','2025-11-17 14:10:00',115724.00,8500000.00,14800000.00,73.45,129.45,'84','<p><strong><u>LILYDALE RIVERSIDE</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Discover contemporary urban living at Lilydale Riverside, a premier high-rise development offering elegant 1 and 2-bedroom apartments in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious neighborhoods. Whether you’re a homeowner seeking modern comfort or an investor aiming for strong rental yields, this 17-story twin-tower project combines luxury, convenience, and outstanding investment potential.</p><p>Designed with attention to detail, Lilydale at Riverside features premium amenities that prioritize comfort, security, and leisure—making it the perfect residence for professionals, families, and discerning buyers alike.</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities:</p><ul><li>Fully Equipped Gym for an active lifestyle</li><li>&nbsp;Rooftop Swimming Pool with breathtaking views</li><li>Children’s Playground for family-friendly living</li><li>Recreation Club &amp; Lounge for social gatherings</li><li>&nbsp;24/7 Security with CCTV &amp; Intercom for peace of mind</li><li>&nbsp;Borehole Water Supply ensuring uninterrupted water access</li><li>&nbsp;Backup Generator for continuous power supply</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><ul><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom Apartment (73.45sqm) – From KSh 8.5M to 9M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom Apartment (105.58sqm) – From KSh 12.5M to 12.8M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom + DSQ (124.33sqm) – From KSh 14M to 14.8M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom + DSQ (129.45sqm) – From KSh 14.35 M to 14.8 M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h4>completion period:</h4><h5>Project completion period September 2027</h5><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment plans:</strong></p><ol><li>&nbsp;20% Down Payment to reserve your unit</li><li>10% Quarterly Installments for affordability</li><li>Spread Over 36 Months for flexibility</li></ol>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1267,'2025-11-17 11:28:04','2026-02-17 01:23:59','<p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>Discover contemporary urban living at Lilydale Riverside, a premier high-rise development offering elegant 1 and 2 bedroom apartments in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious neighborhoods.</h3><h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p