an and available</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,46,0,1027,'2026-01-21 06:57:00','2026-02-12 11:59:15','<p>Land like this doesnt just hold vale-it creates it. Secure your place in Katani\'s growth story today.</p>','','','[]','12500000',2,NULL,2,'{\"plotSize\":\"0.5\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(340,'0.035 HECTARES IN KAWAIDA FOR SALE','0035-hectares-in-kawaida-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,47,48,'Tigoni',-1.12969020,36.68458360,'/storage/property/covers/kawaida-1768980327510.jpeg','2026-01-21 10:06:00',3500000.00,3500000.00,3500000.00,0.04,0.04,'101','<p>Hidden within the misty green landscape that defines Tigoni, this 0.035-hectares parcel offers more than land- it offers a way of life. Waking up to crisp air, birdsong and uninterrupted views of rolling greenery becomes pat of everyday living here.</p><p>The plot sits on rich , well -drained red soil, ideal for building a cozy home or a refined weekend escape. It\'s size is perfectly balanced - generous enough for privacy, gardens and outdoor living yet manageable for effortless maintenance.</p><p>Located within reach of Limuru road and essential amenities, the property blends rural calm with modern convenience. The surrounding neighborhood is established, secure and quietly prestigious ,making this a smart choice for both lifestyle buyers and long-term investors.</p><p><br></p><p>This is a rare chance to own a personal retreat in Tigoni, where nature ,value and tranquility meet.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,46,0,1261,'2026-01-21 07:25:28','2026-02-05 08:36:18','<p>This is a rare chance to own a personal retreat in Tigoni, where nature ,value and tranquility meet.</p>','','','[]','3500000',2,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(341,'0.035 HECTARES IN KAMAKIS FOR SALE ','0035-hectares-in-kamakis-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,80,73,'Kamakis',-1.16906270,36.96980330,'/storage/property/covers/kama