omens- 4 mins</p><p>Getrudes children hospital- 5 mins</p><p>Coptic hospital- 10mins&nbsp;</p><p>Airports&nbsp;</p><p>JKIA- 25mins</p><p>Wilsons Airport- 15mins</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,11,0,1222,'2026-01-23 10:25:40','2026-02-18 13:06:56','<p>Luna Oak Residency is an exclusive, contemporary master-planned community located in the prestigious Kilimani neighborhood, along Kilungu Road, at the heart of Nairobi City.</p>','','','[]','100000',1,1,2,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"115\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(355,'4 BEDROOM TOWNHOUSE  IN BROOKSIDE','4-bedroom-townhouse-in-brookside',NULL,14,2,58,1,1,1,25,'Brookside drive',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'/storage/property/covers/carol-t-1769167328507.jpeg','2026-01-23 14:07:00',400000.00,400000.00,400000.00,295.00,295.00,'111','<p>Secure, Spacious 4-Bedroom Townhouse with Garden &amp; Pool in Westlands – Westlands (Off Brookside Drive)</p><p><br></p><p>This elegant 4-bedroom all-ensuite townhouse is located in a secure and serene neighborhood off Brookside Drive, offering spacious living areas, premium finishes, and excellent outdoor amenities—ideal for families or executives seeking upscale living in Westlands.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>* 5 spacious bedrooms, all en-suite</p><p>* Master bedroom with shower cubicle and Jacuzzi</p><p>* Private lawn and swimming pool</p><p>* Beautifully landscaped gardens</p><p>* Mahogany wood parquet flooring</p><p>* Sliding UPVC windows for enhanced insulation and durability</p><p>* Paneled main entrance door</p><p>* Internal flush doors</p><p>* In-house intercom system</p><p>The house is all ensuite and has a family room and a rooftop terrace</p><p><br></p><p>*Security Features:*</p><p><br></p><p>* Perimeter security wall</p><p>* Electric fencing</p><p><