 4 -acre parcel of land presents an opportunity for investors, developers or buyers seeking space and exclusivity within close proximity to Nairobi.</p><p>The area is well serviced with essential utilities available nearby and continues to experience steady appreciation due to ongoing residential and infrastructure development.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Development potential:</strong></h3><p>Ideal for residential homes, gated estate development or boutique housing projects</p><p>The neighborhood is growing rapidly with quality developments nearby ,making this a smart long-term investment</p><p>Good road access from Limuru road</p><p>Close to transport links, shops ,schools and social amenities</p><p>Basic utilities are accessible nearby</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></h3><p>4 Acres at Ksh 25,000,000 /Acre</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,46,0,1111,'2026-01-24 08:34:03','2026-02-11 18:25:59','<p>Build your vision on four acres of space ,privacy and prestige in Redhill.</p>','','','[]','25000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(359,'12 ACRES IN REDHILL  TIGONI FOR SALE ','12-acres-in-redhill-tigoni-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,47,48,'Redhill Tigoni',-1.16882450,36.70674410,'/storage/property/covers/redhill-12-acres-1769245218783.jpeg','2026-01-24 11:44:00',35000000.00,35000000.00,35000000.00,12.00,12.00,'120','<p>Enjoy breathtaking panoramic views of surrounding tea farms ,hills and open countryside- a signature feature of the Tigoni area. The serene environment fresh air and natural beauty create an ideal setting for high-end homes or lifestyle- focused projects.</p><p><br></p><p>The property is well accessible via established road networks and is conveniently located near Tigoni town, reputable schools, healthcare facilities , shopping centres and social amenities. Nairobi is easily reachable making this an attractive option for both investment and residential p