eded</p><p>Strong potential for rental income or capital appreciation</p><p>Close to schools, shops hospitals and other key amenities</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,46,0,1460,'2026-01-27 10:36:02','2026-02-15 04:52:35','<p>A rare quarter-acre in the heart of Ngara-secure this prime piece today and build where demand never fades.</p>','','','[]','120000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"0.25\",\"landUse\":\"\",\"zoning\":\"\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[],\"titleDeed\":\"\"}'),(365,'DIAMOND MANGO','diamond-mango',NULL,2,1,56,1,1,5,17,'Kilimani',-1.28744220,36.78452250,'/storage/property/covers/2-front-diamond-mango-1-1769602324851.png','2026-01-28 13:08:00',115000.00,6500000.00,11500000.00,65.00,100.00,'133','<p>Diamond mango is a premier 24-storey mixed use development project strategically positioned in Nairobi\'s high -growth Kilimani district. The project integrates residential, commercial and hospitality components with state -of the -art security and luxury amenities.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>World class amenities:</strong></h3><ul><li>&nbsp;Fully Equipped Gym – modern fitness center for a healthy lifestyle</li><li>&nbsp;Elegant Swimming Pool – perfect for relaxation and recreation</li><li>&nbsp;Landscaped Gardens &amp; Green Spaces – serene outdoor areas for calm living</li><li>&nbsp;Children’s Play Area – safe and fun environment for kids</li><li>&nbsp;Full Backup Generator – uninterrupted power supply</li><li>&nbsp;Borehole Water Supply – reliable water throughout the year</li><li>&nbsp;Ample Secure Parking – convenience and peace of mind</li><li>&nbsp;High-Speed Lifts – efficient vertical mobility</li><li>&nbsp;24/7 CCTV Surveillance &amp; Manned Security – enhanced safety</li><li>&nbsp;Commercial Spaces on Ground &amp; First Floors – ideal for shops, cafés, or offices</li></ul><h3><strong>Available Units &amp; Prices</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>1 Bedroom Apartment (65 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;— From&nbsp;<strong>