ty</li><li><strong>Convenient On-Site Shop</strong></li><li><strong>2 Heated Swimming Pools</strong>&nbsp;(for adults and kids)</li><li><strong>Gentlemen &amp; Ladies Public Toilets</strong></li><li><strong>Shower Locker Rooms</strong>&nbsp;for post-swim convenience</li><li><strong>Elegant Reception Area</strong>&nbsp;to welcome guests</li><li><strong>Rooftop View Restaurant</strong>&nbsp;for scenic dining</li></ul><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>1 Bedroom (67.19sqm-72.6sqm) Kes 7.6M-7.9M</strong></li><li><strong>1 Bedroom + Study (76.9sqm-81.6sqm) Kes 8.5M-9M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom (103.5sqm) Kes 11M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom + Study (114.2sqm) Kes 12,5M</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1331,'2026-01-30 11:23:19','2026-02-14 06:25:15','<p>Amto Residence-where everyday living feels effortlessly right.</p>','','','[]','113110',1,1,12,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"interiorArea\":\"114.2\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(368,'0.5 ACRES IN RIDGEWAYS FOR SALE','05-acres-in-ridgeways-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,1,11,20,'Muthaiga',-1.25309070,36.83010360,'/storage/property/covers/ridgeways1-1769778629060.jpeg','2026-01-30 15:29:00',50000000.00,50000000.00,49999998.00,0.50,0.50,'138','<p>Discover your perfect canvas for building your your dream home or investment property in one of Nairobi\'s most sought-after neighborhoods.</p><p>Why This Land?</p><p>Set in a tranquil and secure locale, this half -acre parcel offers an exceptional opportunity to build with flexibility and privacy. Ridgeways is known for its blend of upscale residential living and convenient access to major transport links, schools ,shopping and recreational  facilities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Property highlights:</strong></p><ul><li>Location : Ridgeways ,Nairobi - a serene and prestigious address close to key ameenities</l