he building offers fully furnished residences tailored for corporate executives:</p><p>•	Executive: Studio, 1, 2, and 3-bedroom layouts.</p><p>•	Executive Plus: Elevated 1, 2, and 3-bedroom units (floors 34-38).</p><p>•	Sky Suites: Feature 3.25m ceilings and private balcony Jacuzzis.</p><p>•	Penthouses: Located on the 40th floor and above, featuring 4m ceilings and private swimming pools.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>•	Sky-High Leisure: A 21-meter heated infinity pool on the 34th floor and a sunset deck.</p><p>•	Fitness &amp; Wellness: 24/7 gym, private spa suites, and Turkish baths.</p><p>•	Business &amp; Dining: Branded 150-seat restaurant, resident bars, co-working space, and meeting rooms.</p><p>•	Convenience: Private helipad, 518 parking spaces, and valet services.</p><p>•	High-Speed Lifts: Seven passenger Schindler lifts and one service elevator.</p><p>•	Standards: Built to EU and UN security and fire safety standards.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Apartment prices at 88 Nairobi vary significantly based on the unit type, floor level, and furnishing status. As of February 2025, starting prices for these luxury condominiums are as follows:&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Sales Prices (Off plan &amp; Current)</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•	Studio Units (33–35 sqm): Starting from $105,000 to $108,000 (approx. KSh 13.5M–14M).</p><p>•	1-Bedroom Units (48–55 sqm): Starting from $187,845. Some listing sites quote entry-level one-bedroom units from KSh 13,400,000.</p><p>•	2-Bedroom Units (99–102 sqm): Starting from $212,600 to $281,400.</p><p>•	3-Bedroom Units: Starting from $462,895.</p><p>•	Executive Plus &amp; Sky Suites: Prices for these units, located on floors 34 and above, are typically higher and often available upon request.</p><p>•	Penthouses: The most exclusive units (40th floor and above) can exceed KSh 100 million ($1M+).</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1141,'2026-02-09 09:58:38','2026-02-16 12:35:38','<p>A timeless address, exceptional returns and unmatched prestige- welcome to 88 Nairobi</p>','','','[]','500000',1,3,13,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"102\",\"decorationStatus\":\"3\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(380,'BAYSTAR RESIDENCE','baystar-residence',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,5,NULL,'Kilimani',-1.28425610,36.78699770,'/storage/property/covers/baystar-1-1770634120975.jpeg','2026-02-09 13:12:00',85714.29,3000000.00,9500000.00,35.00,98.00,'148','<p><br></p><p>Rising elegantly along George Padmore Road in Kimani, this 22-floor residential tower redefines urban living in one of Nairobi’s most connected and vibrant neighbourhoods, placing residents minutes from key business, lifestyle and social amenities.</p><p><br></p><p>With commanding views over the Nairobi skyline, the State House’s lush greenery and the Ngong Hills’ glowing sunsets, the development blends luxury finishes, everyday convenience and rare serenity into a singular address for homeowners and investors alike.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Premium Amenities:</strong></p><p>The development includes a wide range of lifestyle and productivity facilities:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Wellness: Infinity pool, rooftop jogging track, fully equipped gym, yoga centre, and spa/sauna.</p><p>•	Leisure: Private cinema, rooftop lounge and garden, kids\' playroom, and a residents\' games hall.</p><p>•	Productivity: Dedicated co-working spaces, creatives\' studio, and laundry/concierge services.</p><p>•	Security &amp; Tech: Smart access systems, 24/7 security, high-speed lifts, and backup power/water.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Units are designed for both modern living and high-return investment (Airbnb-friendly) with the following starting prices:</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Studio Apartments:    35 Sqm  From Ksh 3 Million.</p><p>•	1 Bedroom Apartments: 55 Sqm From Ksh 5 Million.</p><p>•	2 Bedroom Apartments:   98 Sqm    From Ksh 9.5 Million.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•	Deposit: Typically 20% to 30% down payment.</p><p>•	Payment Plan: Flexible 3-year plan with 0% interest spread over the remaining construction period.</p><p>•	Occupation Date: Expected completion in Q2 2028.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1032,'2026-02-09 10:48:41','2026-02-13 08:33:43','<p>Rising elegantly along George Padmore Road in Kimani, this 22-floor residential tower redefines urban living in one of Nairobi’s most connected and vibrant neighbourhoods, placing residents minutes from key business, lifestyle and social amenities.</p>','','','[]','85714.285',1,1,16,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"interiorArea\":\"55\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(381,'PORINI POINT','porini-point',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru',-1.17745740,36.98242910,'/storage/property/covers/modern-kitchen-1770716621753.jpg','2026-02-09 15:40:00',138888.88,7500000.00,16200000.00,54.00,145.00,'148','<p>Porini Point is a new, premium residential development in Tatu City that launched in November 2025. Designed as a sanctuary-facing enclave, it features 570 modern apartments spread across 24 low-rise blocks (Ground + 4 floors). Construction is scheduled to commence in January 2026, with the first units expected to be ready by Q1 2027 and full completion by September 2029.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The development is centered around a landscaped courtyard and is situated just 200 metres from the 160-acre Tatu Wildlife Sanctuary.&nbsp;</p><p>•	Lifestyle: Includes a residents\' clubhouse, a swimming pool with a sun deck, a fully equipped gym, and a dedicated barbecue area.</p><p>•	Family-Friendly: Features safe children’s play zones, football pitches, and basketball courts.</p><p>•	Security: Gated entry with 24/7 CCTV surveillance and professional security management.</p><p>•	Convenience: Within walking distance of Tatu Central (CBD), international schools like Nova Pioneer and Crawford International, and various retail hubs.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Unit Type Size (sqm)	Starting Price (KES):</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom	54 – 60	7,500,000</p><p>2 Bedroom	90 – 92	10,070,000</p><p>3 Bedroom	145	16,200,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment Plans &amp; Investment:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Tatu City offers flexible financing options intended for both homeowners and investors, with projected rental yields of up to 18%–19%.&nbsp;</p><p>•	Installment Plan: A 24-month flexible payment plan is available.</p><p>•	Booking Fee: KES 200,000 (or USD 1,550) to reserve a unit, followed by a 10% deposit within 14 days.</p><p>•	Cash Discount: Discounts of up to 10.7% are available for outright cash purchases.</p><p>•	Financing: Sharia-compliant financing options are also supported.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1150,'2026-02-09 12:55:17','2026-02-17 10:52:16','<p>Porini Point is a new, premium residential development in Tatu City that launched in November 2025. Designed as a sanctuary-facing enclave, it features 570 modern apartments spread across 24 low-rise blocks (Ground + 4 floors). Construction is scheduled to commence in January 2026, with the first units expected to be ready by Q1 2027 and full completion by September 2029.</p>','','','[]','138888.88',1,1,13,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"54\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(382,'JABALI TOWERS','jabali-towers',NULL,2,1,57,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru',-1.17745740,36.98242910,'/storage/property/covers/jabali1-1770644522518.jpeg','2026-02-09 16:13:00',141860.00,6100000.00,42770000.00,43.00,258.00,'150','<p>Jabali Towers is a premier high-rise, mixed-use development by Rendeavour located in the heart of Tatu Central, the business and living district of Tatu City. Launched in July 2025, the project is designed as a sustainable \"City in a Forest\" that integrates residential, office, and retail spaces.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Project Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>The development features two residential towers of 20 and 31 storeys. Units range from studios to lavish penthouses with contemporary interiors inspired by Kenyan heritage.&nbsp;</p><p>Project Features</p><p>•	Mixed-Use Facilities: The complex includes 3,000 sqm of Grade-A office space, a 150-room 4-star hotel, and a retail district with 35 shops and 15 restaurants (including an \"Eat Street\").</p><p>•	Smart &amp; Green Living: Apartments feature smart home technology (keyless entry, intercom), floor-to-ceiling windows, and eco-friendly systems like solar lighting and rainwater harvesting.</p><p>•	Exclusive Amenities: Residents have access to an infinity pool, a fully equipped gym, steam and sauna, a business lounge, a gaming room, and private gardens.</p><p>•	Connectivity: Located 30 minutes from Nairobi CBD and JKIA, within walking distance of international schools (Nova Pioneer, Crawford) and the 100-acre Tatu Wildlife Sanctuary.&nbsp;</p><p>Investment &amp; Timeline</p><p>•	Completion Date: The estimated completion for Jabali Towers is December 2028.</p><p>•	ROI Potential: Investors can expect a projected Return on Investment (ROI) of up to 16% due to high rental demand in the Special Economic Zone (SEZ).</p><p>•	Payment Plan: Typical plans include a 25% down payment, with the balance spread over three years. Parking bays can be purchased separately for approximately KES 1.4M ($10,800).</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Residential Configuration &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Unit Type 	Typical Size	Starting Price (KES)	Price Range (USD)</p><p>Studio	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;43 sqm	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Fr