er 1, 2025, and an ambitious completion date of October 1, 2028, IVY PARK is set to become a beacon of sophisticated urban living.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>World-Class Amenities:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>IVY PARK is designed to offer a holistic and enriching living experience, with a comprehensive suite of amenities that cater to every aspect of modern life. These state-of-the-art facilities are meticulously curated to provide residents with comfort, convenience, and opportunities for relaxation and recreation. The amenities include:</p><p><br></p><p>* Heated Swimming Pool: A luxurious, heated pool perfect for year-round swimming, relaxation, and wellness.</p><p>* Lush Garden: A beautifully landscaped garden offering a tranquil retreat from the urban bustle, ideal for leisurely walks and quiet contemplation.</p><p>* Fully Equipped Gym: A modern fitness center with the latest equipment, providing residents with everything they need for their health and wellness routines.</p><p>* Indoor Children\'s Playground: A safe and engaging space where children can play and socialize in a secure, indoor environment.</p><p>* Co-working Space: A dedicated, professionally designed co-working space that offers a quiet and productive environment for remote work and business activities.</p><p>* Coffee Bar: A stylish on-site coffee bar where residents can enjoy their favorite beverages and socialize with neighbors.</p><p>* Rooftop Garden: A serene rooftop garden with panoramic city views, providing a unique space for relaxation and social gatherings.</p><p>* Rooftop Lounge: An elegant rooftop lounge designed for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the breathtaking skyline.</p><p>* Yoga Studio: A tranquil and well-appointed studio for yoga, meditation, and other mindfulness practices.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><p><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>62 sqm – Cash: KES 6.82M | Installment: KES 7.32M</li><li>66 sqm – Cash: KES 7.26M | Installment: KES 7.76M</li><li>67 sqm – Cash: KES 7.37M | Installment: KES 7.87M</li><li>69 sqm – Cash: KES 7.59M | Installment: KES 8.09M</li><li>73 sqm – Cash: KES 8.03M | Installment: KES 8.53M</li><li>76 sqm – Cash: KES 8.36M | Installment: KES 8.86M</li></ul><p><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>98 sqm – Cash: KES 10.78M | Installment: KES 11.28M</li><li>110 sqm – Cash: KES 12.10M | Installment: KES 12.60M</li><li>114 sqm – Cash: KES 12.54M | Installment: KES 13.04M</li><li>115 sqm – Cash: KES 12.65M | Installment: KES 13.15M</li><li>108 sqm + DSQ – Cash: KES 11.88M | Installment: KES 12.38M</li><li>128 sqm + DSQ – Cash: KES 14.08M | Installment: KES 14.58M</li></ul><p><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ</strong></p><ul><li>142 sqm – Cash: KES 15.62M | Installment: KES 16.12M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,11,0,1150,'2026-02-11 13:47:35','2026-02-16 12:34:52','<p>Developed by a trusted team with a strong track record that includes&nbsp;<strong>Nandwa Ivy, Diamond Homes, Diamond Ivy, Blossom Ivy, and Luckinn Ivy</strong>, Ivy Park Residence delivers more than just a home—it’s a smart investment in one of Nairobi’s most dynamic neighborhoods.</p>','','','[]','109677.41',1,1,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"3\",\"bathrooms\":\"3\",\"interiorArea\":\"142\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(390,'4 BEDROOM STAND ALONE ','4-bedroom-stand-alone',NULL,7,1,58,1,3,47,NULL,'Tigoni',-1.03639500,36.84313120,'/storage/property/covers/rosemary-villa-1770888955544.jpeg','2026-02-12 12:18:00',128571.42,45000000.00,45000000.00,310.00,350.00,'160','<p>Experience refined countryside living in this beautifully designed 4-bedroom townhouse nestled within an exclusive gated compound in the heart of Tigoni. Surrounded by rolling tea plantations and fresh highland air, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy, security, and modern comfort.</p><p>Thoughtfully crafted with spacious interiors and elegant finishes, the home features a bright, open-plan living and dining area that flows seamlessly into a contemporary fitted kitchen — ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Large windows flood the home with natural light while framing breathtaking green views.</p><p>All four bedrooms are generously sized, with the master suite offering a tranquil retreat complete with ample closet space and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. The private garden provides the perfect setting for family gatherings, quiet relaxation, or outdoor dining.</p><p>Located in a secure, well-managed gated community, residents enjoy peace of mind while remaining conveniently close to top schools, shopping centers, Limuru Road, and Nairobi’s CBD.</p><p>Where serenity meets sophistication — your Tigoni sanctuary awaits.</p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"> Unique Features</span></h3><p>✔️ Located in an exclusive gated compound with 24/7 security</p><p>✔️ Scenic views of Tigoni’s lush tea plantations</p><p>✔️ Spacious bedrooms</p><p>✔️ Private landscaped garden</p><p>✔️ Expansive windows for natural lighting</p><p>✔️ Modern fitted kitchen with premium finishes</p><p>✔️ Ample parking space</p><p>✔️ High ceilings enhancing light and airflow</p><p>✔️ Quiet, low-density development for enhanced privacy</p><p>✔️ Cool highland climate all year round</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,46,0,1281,'2026-02-12 09:35:56','2026-02-17 10:50:08','<p>Where serenity meets sophistication — your Tigoni sanctuary awaits.</p><p><br></p>','','','[]','128571.42',2,1,12,'{\"bedrooms\":\"4\",\"bathrooms\":\"4\",\"interiorArea\":\"350\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(391,'SEVENTY SEVEN APARTMENTS','maestro-homes',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,5,NULL,'Kilimani',-1.28423520,36.78706970,'/storage/property/covers/maestro-1770902279461.jpeg','2026-02-12 16:00:00',100000.00,11600000.00,18500000.00,116.00,182.00,'162','<p>A modern residential development comprising 2 &amp; 3 Bedroom Apartments, some with DSQ&nbsp;located along Argwings Kodhek Road, Hurlingham.</p><p>Project Overview:</p><p>* 2 Blocks: A &amp; B</p><p>* 20 Floors</p><p>* 4 Units per Floor in Each Block</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>* Spacious Living Lounge</p><p>* Backup Generator</p><p>* Smart Access Control</p><p>* High-Speed Lifts</p><p>* Modern Swimming Pool</p><p>* Ample Parking</p><p>* Masjid</p><p>* Rooftop Terrace</p><p>* Near Masjid Rahma, Hurlingham</p><p>* Segregated Gym for Ladies &amp; Gents</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> Unit Sizes &amp; Prices:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Price (KES)</p><p>2 Bedroom All Ensuite</p><p>116 sqm</p><p>11.6M</p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ</p><p>149 sqm</p><p>14.9M</p><p><br></p><p>3 Bedroom All Ensuite</p><p>180 sqm</p><p>18.0M</p><p><br></p><p>3 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ</p><p>185 sqm</p><p>18.5M</p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong> Payment Plan</strong></h3><p>* 30% Deposit</p><p>* 70% Balance payable within 2 years</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,51,0,1034,'2026-02-12 13:17:59','2026-02-16 13:35:14','<p>A modern residential development comprising 2 &amp; 3 Bedroom Apartments, some with DSQ&nbsp;located along Argwings Kodhek Road, Hurlingham.</p>','','','[]','99999',1,1,14,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"148\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(392,'WAREHOUSE FOR RENT','warehouse-for-rent',NULL,15,2,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru',-1.03639500,36.84313120,'/storage/property/covers/warehouse-1771234255451.jpeg','2026-02-16 12:18:00',7800000.00,665000.00,7800000.00,850.00,10000.00,'163','<p>The Link is Kenya\'s first SME-focused warehousing and logistics park, situated within Phase 2 of the Tatu Industrial Park. Developed as a KES 2.5 billion joint venture, it is specifically designed to provide high-quality, affordable space for small and medium-sized enterprises.&nbsp;</p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong>Warehousing &amp; Capacity:</strong></h3><p>As of early 2026, the development is nearing its final full-scale capacity following the launch of its second phase in March 2025.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Phase 1: Fully sold out and operational as of 2025, housing companies such as Bakels East Africa and Novis PLC.</p><p>•	Phase 2: Currently in the final stages of development or newly completed (scheduled for completion in late 2025).</p><p>•	Unit Sizes: Flexible spaces ranging from 850 sqm to 10,000 sqm.</p><p>•	Lease Rates: Historically listed from USD 6 per sqm, with some early-bird incentives offering rates as low as USD 5.7 per sqm.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Businesses at The Link benefit from the robust, \"future-proofed\" infrastructure characteristic of Tatu City.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Logistics Design: Wide internal roads (up to 29 metres), generous truck turning radii, and advanced fire safety systems.</p><p>•	Utilities: Guaranteed 24/7 power and water, supported by a 135MVA substation and high-speed fibre optic connectivity.</p><p>•	Integrated Facilities: Units include integrated office spaces and modern ablution facilities.</p><p>•	Security: Features a secure perimeter with an electric fence, CCTV surveillance, and 24-hour access control.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Special Economic Zone (SEZ) Benefits:</strong></h3><p>Companies operating within The Link enjoy significant tax incentives that lower operational costs:&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Corporate Tax: Reduced to 10% for the first 10 years and 15% for the subsequent 10 years (compared to the standard 30%).</p><p>•	Exemptions: VAT zero-rating on goods and services, and exemptions from import duty and stamp duty.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','rental',0,0,27,0,1241,'2026-02-16 09:30:55','2026-02-16 14:22:49','<p>The Link is Kenya\'s first SME-focused warehousing and logistics park, situated within Phase 2 of the Tatu Industrial Park. Developed as a KES 2.5 billion joint venture, it is specifically designed to provide high-quality, affordable space for small and medium-sized enterprises.&nbsp;</p>','','','[]','782.3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"bedrooms\":\"0\",\"bathrooms\":\"0\",\"floorNumber\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"0\",\"orientation\":\"\",\"decorationStatus\":\"\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"leasePeriod\":\"\",\"renewable\":false}'),(393,'PLOTS FOR SALE  IN JUJA /KIAMBU ','855-acres-in-kiambu-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru',-1.03639500,36.84313120,'/storage/property/covers/zuri-1771237058392.jpeg','2026-02-16 13:00:00',3000000.00,3000000.00,10900000.00,0.13,0.50,'165','<p>Zuri Springs is an 855-acre mixed-use development located in Juja, Kiambu County. It is developed by Rendeavour, the same owner and developer behind Tatu City and Oaklands. As of early 2026, it is marketed as a satellite development that offers more affordable land options compared to the core Tatu City precinct while maintaining similar master-planning standards.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Types &amp; Pricing (2026)</strong></h3><p>Prices for plots depend on the intended land use and current availability. As of early 2026, standard pricing is as follows:</p><p>Plot Type Size	Starting Price (KES)</p><p>Residential (Legacy)	1/8 Acre	3,000,000</p><p>High Density (Apartments)	1/4 Acre	7,300,000</p><p>Industrial	1/2 Acre	10,900,000</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The development is designed as a \"live-work-play\" community with a focus on natural serenity.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Infrastructure: Includes on-site power (with transformer points), water supply from natural springs, and a picturesque dam fed by the Ndarugo River.</p><p>•	Environment: The site features mature eucalyptus and pine trees, 15km of nature trails, and green open spaces.</p><p>•	Social Amenities: Includes the Kia-Ora Primary School within the development and a planned dispensary, police post, and retail areas.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Location &amp; Accessibility</p><p>•	Proximity: Situated approximately 40km north of Nairobi and 15km from Tatu City.</p><p>•	Access: Located 7–9km from the Thika Superhighway (Exit 15) via the tarmacked Juja-Gatundu Road.</p><p>•	Nearby Hubs: Close to JKUAT University, Juja City Mall, and Gatundu Level 5 Hospital.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Investment &amp; Ownership</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Buyers typically pay a 10% deposit and clear the balance over a flexible 3-year (36-month) period.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1237,'2026-02-16 10:17:38','2026-02-17 06:57:16','<p>Zuri Springs is an 855-acre mixed-use development located in Juja, Kiambu County. It is developed by Rendeavour, the same owner and developer behind Tatu City and Oaklands. As of early 2026, it is marketed as a satellite development that offers more affordable land options compared to the core Tatu City precinct while maintaining similar master-planning standards.&nbsp;</p>','','','[]','3000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"0.13\",\"landUse\":\"\",\"zoning\":\"\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[],\"titleDeed\":\"\"}'),(394,'COMMERCIAL/INDUSTRIAL LAND IN RUIRU (SEZ) ','land-for-sale-in-kiambu',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru',-1.26681942,36.74789429,'/storage/property/covers/tatu-industrial-1771239337555.jpeg','2026-02-16 13:39:00',22500000.00,22500000.00,22500000.00,0.25,0.25,'166','<p>Tatu Industrial Park is the largest private light industrial and logistics zone in East Africa. It is a core component of the 5,000-acre Tatu City Special Economic Zone (SEZ), designed to provide a \"live, work, play\" environment that decongests Nairobi.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Project Scope &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p>•	Size: The park is divided into phases; Phase 1 covers 457 acres (over 90% sold), and Phase 2 adds another 450 acres to meet rising demand.</p><p>•	Location: Situated 24km from Nairobi CBD at Exit 11 on the Thika Superhighway and 2km from the Northern/Eastern Bypasses.</p><p>•	Utilities: Features world-class infrastructure including 99.7% power reliability via a dedicated substation, 24/7 water supply with 30 million liters of storage, and 90km of underground fibre optic cable.</p><p>•	Security: Managed by a centralized command center monitoring all infrastructure and security 24/7.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Special Economic Zone (SEZ) Benefits:</strong></h3><p>Businesses operating within the park receive significant fiscal incentives under Kenya\'s SEZ framework:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Corporate Tax: Reduced to 10% for the first 10 years and 15% for the next 10 years (vs. the standard 30%).</p><p>•	Tax Exemptions: Zero-rated VAT on all supplies, and exemptions from import duties, excise duties, and stamp duty on property transfers.</p><p>•	One-Stop Shop: Fast-tracked processing for work permits, business licenses, and construction approvals.&nbsp;</p><p>Major Tenants &amp; Businesses</p><p><br></p><p>Over 100 local and global companies are already operational or under development:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Manufacturing &amp; FMCG: Unilever East Africa, Heineken, Chandaria Industries, Bidco Africa, and Kim-Fay.</p><p>•	Logistics: Africa Logistics Properties (ALP), Emirates Logistics, and Freight Forwarders Solutions.</p><p>•	Tech &amp; Services: CCI Global (Kenya\'s largest contact centre) and Davis &amp; Shirtliff.</p><p>•	Retail &amp; Food: Naivas, Dormans Coffee (global HQ), and the Tamarind Group.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Investment Opportunities:</strong></h3><p>•	Land Sales: Serviced plots are available for purchase, starting at approximately KSh 22.5 million per ¼-acre for commercial/industrial use.</p><p>•	Warehousing: Premium grade-A warehousing is available for lease for businesses not looking to build their own facilities.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1418,'2026-02-16 10:55:38','2026-02-17 06:55:13','<p>Tatu Industrial Park is the largest private light industrial and logistics zone in East Africa. It is a core component of the 5,000-acre Tatu City Special Economic Zone (SEZ), designed to provide a \"live, work, play\" environment that decongests Nairobi.&nbsp;</p>','','','[]','22500000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"landUse\":\"\",\"zoning\":\"\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[],\"titleDeed\":\"\"}'),(395,'8 BEDROOM FURNISHED TOWNHOUSE ','8-bedroom-furnished-townhouse',NULL,14,2,NULL,1,1,8,NULL,'Runda',-1.21821190,36.80898870,'/storage/property/covers/rental-2-1771245844750.jpeg','2026-02-16 15:32:00',700000.00,700000.00,700000.00,520.00,520.00,'166','<p>Set within the tranquil, tree-lined avenues of Runda, this exceptional 8-bedroom townhouse offers an unmatched blend of space, elegance, and privacy. Designed for refined living, the home delivers expansive interiors and seamless indoor-outdoor flow in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious residential addresses.</p><p>From the moment you step inside, you’re welcomed by grand, light-filled living spaces with high ceilings and sophisticated finishes. The generous lounge opens onto a beautifully landscaped private garden — ideal for entertaining, family gatherings, or simply enjoying peaceful afternoons in a serene setting.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Property Highlights:</strong></h3><p>8 generously sized bedrooms, all en-suite for maximum comfort and privacy</p><p>Lavish master suite with walk-in closet and spa-style bathroom</p><p>Expansive formal lounge and separate family/TV room</p><p>Elegant dining area perfect for hosting</p><p>Contemporary, fully fitted kitchen with ample cabinetry and workspace</p><p>Private landscaped garden ideal for outdoor relaxation</p><p>Domestic staff quarters (DSQ)</p><p>Ample parking and secure compound</p><p><br></p><p>Located in a quiet, secure, and highly sought-after neighborhood</p><p>This residence is perfectly suited for ambassadors, corporate executives, large families, or organizations seeking a prestigious address with generous accommodation capacity.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','rental',0,0,51,0,1499,'2026-02-16 12:44:05','2026-02-18 13:24:32','<p>Schedule your viewing today and discover elevated living at its finest.</p>','','','[]','700000',2,3,1,'{\"bedrooms\":\"8\",\"bathrooms\":\"8\",\"interiorArea\":\"520\",\"orientation\":\"1\",\"decorationStatus\":\"3\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"renewable\":false}'),(396,'1 ACRE FULLY SERVICED PLOTS FOR SALE','1-acre-fully-serviced-plots-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,1,2,NULL,'Karen',-1.32521151,36.69817150,'/storage/property/covers/karen-hill-1-1771248050969.jpeg','2026-02-16 15:52:00',110000000.00,110000000.00,150000000.00,1.00,1.00,'167','<p>Karen Hills is a premier, master-planned gated community developed by Lordship Africa. Located in the lush suburb of Karen, it serves as the company\'s pilot project in Kenya and is designed for high-net-worth individuals seeking a \"signature lifestyle\" in a serene, controlled environment.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3>Development Overview:</h3><p>•	Concept: A low-density residential estate consisting of 60 fully serviced one-acre plots.</p><p>•	Infrastructure: The project features world-class infrastructure that is already completed, including:</p><p>o	Roads: Heavy-duty cabro-paved internal roads with attractive street lighting.</p><p>o	Utilities: Reliable borehole water with a large underground reservoir, electricity, and IT/telecommunications conduits provided to every plot.</p><p>o	Security: A dry-stone perimeter …</p><p><br></p><h3>On-Site Amenities:</h3><p>•	Sports Facilities: Includes a tennis court, basketball court, and a 7-aside football field.</p><p>•	Leisure: A Gazebo club for social gatherings and entertainment, plus dedicated children\'s play areas.</p><p>•	Landscape: Extensive indigenous landscaping designed to preserve the natural \"leafy\" character of Karen.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Pricing &amp; Investment:</strong></p><p>•	Plot Sales: Serviced one-acre plots have been listed starting from KSh 110 million, depending on the location within the estate.</p><p>•	Management: The estate is professionally managed to ensure value preservation and consistent service quality.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1092,'2026-02-16 13:20:51','2026-02-17 06:36:38','<p>Karen Hills is a premier, master-planned gated community developed by Lordship Africa. Located in the lush suburb of Karen, it serves as the company\'s pilot project in Kenya and is designed for high-net-worth individuals seeking a \"signature lifestyle\" in a serene, controlled environment.&nbsp;</p>','','','[]','110000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"1\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(397,'PLOTS FOR SALE IN RUIRU.','1400-acre-land-for-sale-in-kambu',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru, Kiambu.',-1.17745740,36.98242910,'/storage/property/covers/whatsapp-image-2026-02-16-at-124807-1771318449085.jpeg','2026-02-17 11:45:00',2800000.00,2800000.00,12900000.00,0.13,0.50,'164','<p>Oaklands is a 1,400-acre master-planned, mixed-use development located in Ruiru, Kiambu County. It is a sister project to Tatu City, situated just 800 metres from the Tatu City boundary and approximately 7 km from the Thika Superhighway. As of early 2026, it continues to offer serviced plots for residential, commercial, and light industrial use in a controlled environment.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing :</strong></h3><p>Pricing varies by plot size and intended use (e.g., single dwelling vs. high-density apartments).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Plot Type Size	Starting Price (KES)	3-Year Installment Price (KES)</p><p>Residential (1/8 Acre)	50 x 100 ft	2,800,000	~3,700,000</p><p>Residential (1/4 Acre)	100 x 100 ft	4,900,000	~5,600,000</p><p>Apartment Plots (1/4 Acre)	High Density	5,500,000	7,600,000</p><p>Apartment Plots (1/2 Acre)	High Density	10,400,000	12,900,000</p><p>Note: Some premium listings for 1/8-acre plots are priced up to KES 4.3 million depending on location and proximity to amenities.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Sub-Communities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>Oaklands is divided into several distinct gated precincts:</p><p>•	Taratibu: Offers 1/8-acre plots designated for single-dwelling residential homes.</p><p>•	The Springs: An 8-acre gated community featuring 1/4-acre plots and a private 5-acre park.</p><p>•	Utulivu: Features larger 1/4 and 1/2-acre plots situated by a magnificent lake with a jetty and indigenous trees.</p><p>•	Pazuri Park: A 46-acre community with completed infrastructure, including borehole water and elevated storage tanks.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Amenities &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></p><p>•	Education: Home to the Oaklands Primary School and the upcoming Catholic Archdiocese of Nairobi day school.</p><p>•	Utilities: Fully serviced with all-weather murram roads, permanent beacons, piped water, and reliable electricity.</p><p>•	Environment: Includes 15km of nature trails, green open spaces, and a scenic dam fed by the Ndarugo River.</p><p>•	Security: Features perimeter fencing, gated entries, and professional security management.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment &amp; Contact Information:</strong></p><p>•	Payment Plan: Requires a 10% deposit, with the balance payable over flexible periods ranging from 3 months to 3 years (36 months).</p><p>•	Title Deeds: Over 1,800 clean title deeds have already been issued for the project.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1198,'2026-02-17 08:54:09','2026-02-17 09:17:46','','','','[]','2800000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"1400\",\"landUse\":\"\",\"zoning\":\"\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[],\"titleDeed\":\"\"}'),(398,'PRIME RESIDENTIAL PLOTS FOR SALE.','prime-residential-plots-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Ruiru, Kiambu.',-1.17745740,36.98242910,'/storage/property/covers/whatsapp-image-2026-02-17-at-121142-1771320284223.jpeg','2026-02-17 12:20:00',22400000.00,22400000.00,48000000.00,0.25,0.50,'168','<p>Kijani Ridge is the flagship residential neighborhood of the Tatu City Special Economic Zone, a 5,000-acre master-planned city in Ruiru. Spanning approximately 350 to 400 acres of undulating land, it is designed for a \"live, work, play\" lifestyle.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Project Scope &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p>•	Controlled Development: Managed by a Development Control Company to ensure architectural uniformity and protect property value.</p><p>•	Fully Serviced Plots: Every plot includes underground utilities: power, water (from a 10M-litre reservoir), waste management, and ICT fibre.</p><p>•	Current Status: Over 90–95% sold, with hundreds of families already residing in the community.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>Prices vary based on plot location (e.g., proximity to the dam or green areas) and current market rates.&nbsp;</p><p>•	1/4 Acre (approx. 1,000 sqm): Starting from KES 22.4 million.</p><p>•	1/2 Acre (approx. 2,000 sqm): Starting from approximately KES 42 million to 48 million.</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Tatu City typically offers a flexible 24-month payment plan with a booking fee.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>•	Health &amp; Wellness: Features 15km of exercise trails and jogging tracks designed by Olympian Lornah Kiplagat.</p><p>•	Recreation: Includes a large stunning lake/dam, over 75 acres of green space, and a planned clubhouse.</p><p>•	Education: Within walking distance of international schools like Nova Pioneer and Crawford International School.</p><p>•	Security: A gated community with 24/7 manned security and patrol walkways.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>House Designs:</strong></p><p>While buyers can bring their own dream home designs for approval, Tatu City provides 12 pre-approved architectural designs for 3-, 4-, and 5-bedroom villas and bungalows.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1162,'2026-02-17 09:24:44','2026-02-17 10:49:47','','','','[]','22400000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"5000\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(399,'APARTMENT FOR SALE ','apartment-for-sale',NULL,2,1,NULL,1,1,5,NULL,'Kilimani',-1.29601460,36.78177910,'/storage/property/covers/kilimani-1771321513567.jpeg','2026-02-17 12:22:00',120000.00,7800000.00,7800000.00,65.00,65.00,'168','<p><br></p><p><br></p><p>A contemporary, high-return residential development strategically located in Kilimani, ideal for buy-to-let investors seeking strong rental demand and capital growth.</p><p>Welcome to this stylish and modern 1-bedroom apartment located in the heart of the sought-after Kilimani neighborhood. Perfectly blending comfort, convenience and  urban living ,this unit offers an ideal space for investors, couples or singles .</p><p><br></p><p>? Prime Location</p><p>• 1-minute walk to Adlife Plaza</p><p>• 500 metres to Yaya Centre✨ Features &amp; Amenities</p><p>✔ On-site Restaurant</p><p>✔ Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>✔ Controlled Access</p><p>✔ High-Speed Lifts</p><p>✔ Borehole</p><p>✔ Water Purification System</p><p>✔ Backup Generator</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>? Available Unit</p><p>• 1 Bedroom (65 sqm) – KES 7.8M</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,11,0,1153,'2026-02-17 09:45:14','2026-02-17 12:54:55','<p>A contemporary, high-return residential development strategically located in Kilimani, ideal for buy-to-let investors seeking strong rental demand and capital growth.</p><p><br></p>','','','[]','120000',2,1,15,'{\"bedrooms\":\"1\",\"bathrooms\":\"1\",\"interiorArea\":\"65\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(400,'37 BY INEZA','37-by-ineza',NULL,1,1,59,1,3,86,NULL,'Runda',-1.23496005,36.71275629,'/storage/property/covers/ineza-cover-1771332120531.png','2026-02-17 15:13:00',196883.85,69500000.00,79500000.00,353.00,353.00,'169','<p>Quietly tucked behind Runda, just off Kiambu Road along Kwaheri Road, and moments from Sabis International School, 37 By Ineza reveals itself the way nature intended unforced, calm, and deeply rooted in its surroundings.</p><p><br></p><p>Set within one of Nairobi’s most prestigious low-density residential neighbourhoods, this exclusive development introduces a new rhythm of life guided by greenery, light, and intentional design.</p><p><br></p><p>Only 37 expansive luxury residences, elegantly positioned across 5 acres of verdant land. Each home sits on approximately 1/8 of an acre, preserving rare openness where nature is not an afterthought, but a constant companion.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Lifestyle &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>* Residents enjoy a carefully curated lifestyle offering:</p><p>* Exclusive Residents’ Clubhouse</p><p>* Heated Swimming Pool</p><p>* Paddle Court</p><p>* Half Basketball Court</p><p>* Landscaped Green Lawns</p><p>* Children’s Play Areas</p><p>* CCTV Surveillance</p><p>* Controlled Entry Gate</p><p>* Perimeter Wall with Electric Fencing</p><p>* Intercom Access</p><p>* Borehole &amp; Mains Water Supply</p><p>* Underground Water Storage</p><p>* Backup Generator</p><p>* Wide Internal Roads</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Prime Location Advantage:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>* Positioned next to Ineza Estate on Kwaheri Road, within a renowned blue-zone neighbourhood reserved for low-density luxury living, the development guarantees privacy, security, exclusivity, and long-term value.</p><p>* Runda</p><p>* Off Kiambu Road</p><p>* Near Sabis International School</p><p>* Easy access to Gigiri, UN Avenue &amp; Westlands</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> Investment Highlights:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>* 5-Bedroom Ultra-Luxury Villas</p><p>* Prices from Ksh. 69.5 Million</p><p>* Limited to only 37 homes</p><p>* Ideal for owner-occupiers &amp; high-end investors</p><p>* Every residence at 37 BY INEZA is a 5-bedroom, all-ensuite townhouse with DSQ, meticulously planned across approximately 353 sqm.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,50,0,1485,'2026-02-17 12:42:01','2026-02-18 06:45:07','<p>Quietly tucked behind Runda, just off Kiambu Road along Kwaheri Road, and moments from Sabis International School, 37 By Ineza reveals itself the way nature intended unforced, calm, and deeply rooted in its surroundings.</p>','','','[]','196883.85',1,1,13,'{\"bedrooms\":\"5\",\"bathrooms\":\"5\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"356\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(401,'ARIA CAPITAL RESIDENCY','aria-capital-residency',NULL,2,1,56,1,1,5,17,'Kilimani, Nairobi.',-1.29601460,36.78177910,'/storage/property/covers/whatsapp-image-2026-02-17-at-154101-1771333527760.jpeg','2026-02-17 15:55:00',112857.14,7900000.00,22000000.00,70.00,194.62,'170','<p><br></p><p>Located along Nairobi, Kilimani area.</p><p>Consists of 1,2 and 3 bedroom all units ensuite plus an extra guest washroom.</p><p><br></p><p>2 Blocks, A and B</p><p>24 Floors</p><p>2 lifts per block&nbsp;</p><p>2 Basement levels&nbsp;</p><p>5 units per floor</p><p>200 units in total&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>AMENITIES.</strong></p><p>✔️Rooftop heated swimming pool</p><p>✔️Fully equipped gym</p><p>✔️Steam and Sauna</p><p>✔️Children play area</p><p>✔️Ample parking</p><p>✔️Full back up generator</p><p>✔️Shopping Mart</p><p>✔️Public reading room</p><p>✔️CCTV&nbsp;</p><p>✔️2 lifts per block</p><p>✔️Party room</p><p>✔️Inter come</p><p>✔️24hrs security</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and Prices.</strong></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite of size 70sqm</p><p>Price from- 7.9M</p><p><br></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite of size 80sqm</p><p>Price from 9M</p><p><br></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite + study of 92sqm&nbsp;</p><p>Price from 10.4M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 113sqm</p><p>Price from 12.8M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 126sqm</p><p>Price from 14.2M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 129.8sqm</p><p>Price from 14.6M</p><p><br></p><p>3 bedroom all ensuite of size 174.83sqm</p><p>Price from 19.8M</p><p><br></p><p>3 bedroom all ensuite + Dsq of size 194.62sqm&nbsp;</p><p>Price from 22M</p><p><br></p><p><strong>PAYMENT PLAN.</strong></p><p>?Installments:- 20% deposit, balance paid in installments. Monthly or quarterly up to completion</p><p><br></p><p>?Cash payment:- 20% deposit,balance shall be done within 2 weeks.</p><p><br></p><p>?Morgage:-at least 20% within 7 days, balance shall be financed and secured by financiers and professional undertakings after completion.</p><p><br></p><p>Completion is December 2027.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,46,0,1502,'2026-02-17 13:05:28','2026-02-18 06:23:01','','','','[]','112857.14',1,1,13,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"113\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"2\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(402,'SERENE MANOR','serene-manor',NULL,2,1,57,1,1,5,17,'Kilimani, Nairobi.',-1.31246978,36.75973892,'/storage/property/covers/whatsapp-image-2025-10-03-at-130349-1-1771405159093.jpeg','2026-02-18 11:29:00',42857.14,6000000.00,20000000.00,140.00,140.00,'172','<p>Serene Manor Apartments&nbsp;is a premium residential development offering&nbsp;modern apartments for sale in Kilimani, Nairobi. Designed for both homeowners and savvy investors, the project blends smart layouts, quality finishes, and lifestyle-enhancing amenities in one of Nairobi’s most desirable neighborhoods.</p><p>Whether you’re buying your first home, upgrading your lifestyle, or investing in a high-demand rental area,&nbsp;Serene Manor Kilimani&nbsp;delivers exceptional value and long-term returns.&nbsp;</p><h2><br></h2><h2>Amenities</h2><ul><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Fully equipped gym</li><li>Landscaped gardens &amp; circular relaxation area</li><li>Children’s play area</li><li>On-site community shop</li><li>High-speed elevators</li><li>Full backup power generator</li><li>Borehole water supply</li><li>CCTV surveillance</li><li>24/7 professional security</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Apartment Options And Pricing</h2><p>Serene Manor offers a diverse range of apartment options to suit different budgets and lifestyle needs:</p><ul><li>1 Bedroom Apartments (56 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 6,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (60 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 7,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (80 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 9,500,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (98 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 12,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom + Master Ensuite (110 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 13,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (125 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 13,500,000</li><li>3 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (140 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 15,800,000</li><li>4 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (180 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 20,000,000.</li></ul><h2><br></h2><h2>Payment Plan.</h2><ul><li>20% deposit on booking</li><li>Balance payable through&nbsp;monthly or quarterly installments&nbsp;up to project completion</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Project Completion and handover is scheduled for December 2027.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1191,'2026-02-18 08:59:19','2026-02-18 09:21:26','','','','[]','42857.14',1,1,15,'{\"bedrooms\":\"3\",\"bathrooms\":\"3\",\"plotSize\":\"0\",\"interiorArea\":\"140\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"parking\":\"0\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"ownership\":\"\",\"paymentPlan\":\"\"}'),(403,'GOLDEN MANGO HEIGHTS.','golden-mango-heights',NULL,2,1,56,1,1,5,17,'Kilimani, Nairobi.',-1.29067441,36.76660538,'/storage/property/covers/gh-1-1771406644572.webp','2026-02-18 12:08:00',90000.00,7000000.00,9000000.00,55.00,100.00,'173','<p>These beautifully designed 1 and 2-bedroom apartments are ideal for both homeowners and investors looking for a luxury lifestyle in a prime location. Located in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious neighborhoods, The Golden Mango Heights offers a blend of modern architecture, spacious living, and top-tier amenities. The apartments are designed to allow maximum natural light and provide optimal space for comfort.</p><p><br></p><h3>Amenities:</h3><ul><li>Two dedicated parking spaces per unit</li><li>Standby backup generator</li><li>Reliable water supply with storage tanks per apartment</li><li>High-speed elevators for all floors</li><li>Intercom system for easy communication</li><li>24/7 manned security gate and electric fencing</li><li>High-speed internet and connectivity</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>Apartment Features:</h3><ul><li>Modern and spacious layouts</li><li>Bright living rooms with large windows</li><li>Stylish open-plan kitchen with pantry</li><li>Dining area with guest washroom</li><li>DSQ (Domestic Servant Quarter) with private entrance through the kitchen</li><li>High-quality fittings and finishes for long-lasting comfort</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Pricing:</h3><ul><li><br></li><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom (55 sqm) – KES 7,000,000</li><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom (88 sqm) – KES 9,000,000</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom (100 sqm on 8th floor) – KES 11,000,000</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>Flexible Payment Plan</h3><ul><li>Pay just 30% deposit on booking</li><li>Settle the balance on occupation</li></ul><p>This flexible plan makes it easy to own your dream apartment in one of Nairobi’s most desirable locations.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,27,0,1362,'2026-02-18 09:24:05','2026-02-18 09:28:08','','','','[]','90000',1,1,17,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"interiorArea\":\"100\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}'),(405,' RESIDENTIAL PLOTS FOR SALE','residential-plots-for-sale',NULL,9,1,NULL,1,3,45,NULL,'Kiambu',-1.03639500,36.84313120,'/storage/property/covers/whatsapp-image-2026-02-18-at-122853-1-1771413560652.jpeg','2026-02-18 14:04:00',90000000.00,90000000.00,100000000.00,1.00,3.00,'170','<p>Kofinaf Tatu Residences is the most exclusive residential neighborhood within Tatu City, specifically designed as a low-density \"legacy\" estate. Launched in January 2023, it spans over 200 acres of mature landscape, including century-old indigenous trees and a 32-acre lake (Comte de Beaumont Dam).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Unlike other developments in Tatu City that offer apartments, Kofinaf primarily provides serviced plots for buyers to build custom, high-end homes.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The estate is defined by its \"lakeside living\" and integrated nature reserve.&nbsp;</p><p>Tatu City</p><p>•	Private Nature Reserve: Exclusive access to the Comte de Beaumont Dam, which serves as a sanctuary for diverse wildlife.</p><p>•	Estate Amenities: Includes gatehouses with 24/7 security, CCTV, electric fencing, private jogging tracks, and picnic sites.</p><p>•	Infrastructure: Fully serviced with reliable power, water, and high-speed fibre optic connectivity.</p><h3><br></h3><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing:</strong></h3><p>Plots at Kofinaf are significantly larger than those in the neighboring Kijani Ridge, emphasizing privacy and exclusivity.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Plot Sizes: Typically range from 1 to 2 acres (approximately 0.7 to 3.0 acres).</p><p>•	Pricing: Prices are generally available on application. As of early 2026, specific re-sale or premium listings for 4-bedroom luxury residences on smaller nearby parcels (1/4 acre) have been priced around KES 90 million, while the primary large-acreage plots require direct inquiry.</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Tatu City typically offers flexible 2-year payment plans for its residential plots, with financing available through partners like Stanbic Bank.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>Location &amp; Connectivity:</h3><p>•	Proximity: Situated in the \"secluded heart\" of Tatu City, it is minutes away from Tatu Central (the CBD), Grade A offices, and the Business Bay Square (BBS) expansion.</p><p>•	Education: Close to international schools including Crawford International School and Nova Pioneer.</p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','land',0,0,27,0,1121,'2026-02-18 11:19:21','2026-02-18 14:40:09','<p>Kofinaf Tatu Residences is the most exclusive residential neighbourhood within Tatu City, specifically designed as a low-density \"legacy\" estate. Launched in January 2023, it spans over 200 acres of mature landscape, including century-old indigenous trees and a 32-acre lake (Comte de Beaumont Dam).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>','','','[]','90000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"plotSize\":\"2\",\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\",\"infrastructure\":[]}'),(406,'MOGOTIO OASIS','mogotio-oasis',NULL,2,1,55,1,1,1,NULL,'Westlands',-1.24652810,36.78607590,'/storage/property/covers/mogotio-oasis-1771416946533.jpeg','2026-02-18 14:37:00',146341.46,6000000.00,18500000.00,41.00,158.70,'171','<p>Designed for modern urban lifestyles, Mogotio Oasis features&nbsp;<strong>studio, 1, 2, and 3 bedroom luxury apartments</strong>, finished with premium materials and hotel-grade detailing. Every element of the development is crafted to offer comfort, elegance, and long-term value for homeowners and investors alike. </p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>Mogotio Oasis offers world-class activity facilities designed to enhance everyday living and overall happiness:</p><ul><li>Golf club</li><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Fully equipped gym</li><li>Children’s play area</li><li>Yoga room</li><li>Landscaped relaxation spaces</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Mogotio Oasis Apartments Types &amp; Prices:</h3><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Studio Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 5.8M</strong></li><li><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 7.8M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 12.3M</strong></li><li><strong>3 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 18.3M</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Prime Westlands Location:</h3><p>Situated in a highly accessible and secure part of Westlands, residents enjoy proximity to:</p><ul><li>Global Trade Centre (GTC)</li><li>Shopping malls, offices, and restaurants</li><li>Top schools and hospitals</li><li>Major roads and business hubs</li></ul><p><br></p><p>The completion is scheduled for&nbsp;<strong>June 2028</strong>, making this project an ideal off-plan investment opportunity in Westlands.</p><p><br></p>','show',NULL,1,'yes','available','sale',0,0,11,0,1143,'2026-02-18 12:15:47','2026-02-18 13:07:32','<p>Designed for modern urban lifestyles, Mogotio Oasis features&nbsp;<strong>studio, 1, 2, and 3 bedroom luxury apartments</strong>, finished with premium materials and hotel-grade detailing. Every element of the development is crafted to offer comfort, elegance, and long-term value for homeowners and investors alike.</p><p><br></p>','','','[]','146341.46',1,1,16,'{\"bedrooms\":\"2\",\"bathrooms\":\"2\",\"interiorArea\":\"96.81\",\"decorationStatus\":\"1\",\"amenities\":[],\"price\":\"0\",\"currency\":\"KES\"}');
