INSERT INTO `report_replies` VALUES (12,89,11,NULL,'Thank you for your detailed weekly report Dennis, it’s well-structured and clearly highlights your efforts and progress throughout the week. I appreciate how thorough you’ve been in documenting your targets, follow-ups, and achievements.\n\nI especially want to commend you for the excellent job you’re doing with follow-ups it’s great to see that some of your previously cold leads have now revived and are actively engaging again. This shows consistency and persistence in your client handling, which is key in our line of work.\n\nAs you continue managing your hot leads, I’d like to emphasize the importance of also prioritizing the Luminara project this week. Let’s focus on driving as much traffic as possible both to the office and the site. We need to sell this project.\n\nKeep up the great work and maintain this same level of effort and structure moving forward.','2025-11-09 17:44:26','2025-11-09 17:44:26'),(13,92,11,NULL,'Hi Desmond, this report is for Friday and Saturday?','2025-11-10 08:44:59','2025-11-10 08:44:59'),(14,89,27,12,'Thank you, Manager Caroline, for your feedback. As stated, before I have to close a sale or a rental this month.','2025-11-10 10:55:49','2025-11-10 10:55:49'),(15,92,23,NULL,'Thats the weekly report.\n','2025-11-10 12:29:24','2025-11-10 12:29:24'),(16,98,9,NULL,'Brian, I didn\'t see you schedule any client meetings yesterday. This needs to change. You need to meet with at least one client every day to have a chance of closing a deal. Also, you didn\'t specify the time and place for the client meeting on the 11th today; you need to add that.','2025-11-11 05:47:24','2025-11-11 05:47:24'),(17,89,9,NULL,'Well done, keep it up!','2025-11-11 07:01:04','2025-11-11 07:01:04'),(18,91,24,NULL,'Dominic,\nFrom your report you seem to have had a busy week and quite productive. Keep up the good work.\nKindly note:\nYou\'ve to include the project visited on your daily report-Use the icon for Project visited.\nAll the customers you have contacted ensure you upload them into the system.','2025-11-11 07:18:34','2025-11-11 07:18:34'),(19,100,24,NULL,'Dominic,\nKindly indicate the location of your site visit.','2025-11-11 07:41:52','2025-11-11 07:41:52'),(20,101,24,NULL,'David.\nKindly update your project visited using the Icon provided on your daily report.','2025-11-11 09:29:02','2025-11-11 09:29:02'),(21,98,12,NULL,'noted ,will correct\nthe client had view over the weekend on saturday ,in syokimau along mombasa road  ,he wanted to revisit the project for some payment plan claifications ,in the morning he gave me a call to reschedule for friday','2025-11-11 12:37:52','2025-11-11 12:37:52'),(22,107,9,NULL,'Get your Google account up and running as soon as possible, and your website will generate traffic and leads.','2025-11-11 18:12:07','2025-11-11 18:12:07'),(23,108,9,NULL,'Okay, your daily report should include at least the number of leads and who they have been sent to. Then, compile a weekly report for me.','2025-11-11 18:14:22','2025-11-11 18:14:22'),(24,105,24,NULL,'Dominic,\n\nI am glad your interaction with clients has increased. Push to close on one.\nI will have a training tomorrow on how to enter the projects visited.\nRemember to send me 60Bob for the failed Luminara client office/site visit.\n\nRegards,','2025-11-11 18:58:07','2025-11-11 18:58:07'),(25,109,24,NULL,'David,\n\nYour report is too shallow, the timelines doesn\'t capture the entire 8working hours provided for. Kindly rectify on that.\n\nAlso we\'ll have a training tomorrow on how to properly use this CRM tomorrow morning meeting.\n\nKeep up the good work with client interactions and update them on the CFL.','2025-11-11 19:09:02','2025-11-11 19:09:02'),(26,110,11,NULL,'Hi Brian, you didn\'t manage to meet your client in the morning?  Also, the client named Brian, is he the client or the agent? How many clients did you call today and what were their responses? Especially those from Village market? ','2025-11-11 20:25:16','2025-11-11 20:25:16'),(27,104,11,NULL,'Hi Dennis, how many clients did you follow up with today? And did you receive any clients from Rashid? ','2025-11-11 20:28:54','2025-11-11 20:28:54'),(28,103,11,NULL,'Hey Desmond, please include the number of leads you followed up with from the Village Market, as well as the number of clients you received from Rashid. This will help me keep track of your client list.\n\nI also haven’t received the weekly report I requested, kindly make sure to share it tomorrow without fail.\n\nGood job on securing tomorrow’s client for Luminara, and I hope they show up for the viewing!\n','2025-11-11 20:36:43','2025-11-11 20:36:43'),(29,107,13,NULL,'Ok sir I am working on that.','2025-11-12 06:12:44','2025-11-12 06:12:44'),(30,105,22,NULL,'This is well noted ','2025-11-12 16:07:38','2025-11-12 16:07:38'),(31,108,15,NULL,'Noted ','2025-11-12 16:45:39','2025-11-12 16:45:39'),(32,104,27,NULL,'Hi. Yesterday I followed up with 15 plus leads, with 5 of Luminara.\nNo, I didn\'t get any leads from Rashid.','2025-11-13 06:14:01','2025-11-13 06:14:01'),(33,116,24,NULL,'Dominic,\n\nThe maximum you can give is 1hour, more that shows you that a client is not serious. Dont be too generous with your time.\nKeep pushing to close atleast one deal.','2025-11-13 18:45:50','2025-11-13 18:45:50'),(34,120,24,NULL,'David,\nThere is a slight improvement of your report. Keep it up. Let the report transform into an A client. \nInclude more details on your work plan.','2025-11-13 18:50:25','2025-11-13 18:50:25'),(35,100,22,NULL,'Sure, i will moving forward ','2025-11-14 05:40:22','2025-11-14 05:40:22'),(36,91,22,NULL,'Sure, i will ','2025-11-14 05:41:02','2025-11-14 05:41:02'),(37,159,9,NULL,'Domnic,Your work schedule should include specific details, such as the actual time and place for the invitation.','2025-11-19 07:06:41','2025-11-19 07:06:41'),(38,158,11,NULL,'Hi Brian, thank you for the detailed report. For todays report, include details on how far you are with Luminara Clients.','2025-11-19 07:12:28','2025-11-19 07:12:28'),(39,156,11,NULL,'Hi Desmond, thank you for the detailed report. All the best with your viewing today','2025-11-19 07:14:13','2025-11-19 07:14:13'),(40,157,10,NULL,'Find more ways to get more leads. All in all, keep up the good work. ','2025-11-19 07:24:57','2025-11-19 07:24:57'),(41,153,10,NULL,'Keep up the good work. update on the progress of the website and learn more about Google Ads','2025-11-19 07:26:41','2025-11-19 07:26:41'),(42,161,11,NULL,'Noted','2025-11-19 08:22:05','2025-11-19 08:22:05'),(43,157,15,NULL,'Sure thing ','2025-11-19 18:04:22','2025-11-19 18:04:22'),(44,159,22,NULL,'Sure, i will -moving forward','2025-11-20 06:44:34','2025-11-20 06:44:34'),(45,215,24,NULL,'David,\nI have seen great improvement in terms of details. Keep it Up!\nHowever, the activities are so little to counter the 8-hours provided for our official working hours. In your next report, I expect you to account for every hour how it was spent and activities carried on.\nAlso this week we had set a target of atleast one offer letter, PUYS.\nRegards.','2025-11-26 13:36:58','2025-11-26 13:36:58'),(46,213,24,NULL,'Dominic,\nI have seen great improvement in terms of details for your report. Keep it Up!\nHowever, the activities are so little to counter the 8-hours provided for our official working hours. In your next report, I expect you to account for every hour how it was spent and activities carried on.\nAlso this week we had set a target of at least one offer letter, PUYS.\nRegards.','2025-11-26 13:39:13','2025-11-26 13:39:13'),(47,217,11,NULL,'Noted','2025-11-26 18:54:23','2025-11-26 18:54:23'),(48,252,11,NULL,'Noted. I appreciate your detailed report. Wishing you all the best with your Luminara client as well. Keep up the great work on your follow-ups..','2025-12-01 19:49:41','2025-12-01 19:49:41'),(49,246,11,NULL,'Hey Dennis, how many old leads did you follow up with today? How many new leads did you receive today from Rashid and how many are responsive? ','2025-12-01 20:00:07','2025-12-01 20:00:07'),(50,245,11,NULL,'What was the outcome of the calls you made today?\nDid you also follow up with your previous clients?','2025-12-01 20:20:16','2025-12-01 20:20:16'),(51,246,27,NULL,'Hi. I followed 9 old leads today, and 2 new leads today.','2025-12-02 09:33:28','2025-12-02 09:33:28'),(52,261,11,NULL,'Hey Desmond, your report is so shallow. Kindly give a more detailed report especially when talking about leads and the follow ups done. ','2025-12-02 21:16:41','2025-12-02 21:16:41'),(53,257,11,NULL,'Hey Dennis, how many leads did you get from Rashid today? if any, are there any that are responsive. How many leads did you follow up with today?','2025-12-02 21:20:09','2025-12-02 21:20:09'),(54,265,11,NULL,'Hey Brian, did you receive any leads today? If yes, what were the outcomes of those leads? \nYour rental client, what\'s her budget?','2025-12-02 21:23:10','2025-12-02 21:23:10'),(55,278,11,NULL,'Noted. ','2025-12-04 20:51:24','2025-12-04 20:51:24'),(56,282,11,NULL,'Desmond, I’ve mentioned before that your reports are lacking in detail and this needs to be improved. Ensure your reports are comprehensive because they are not viewed by me alone.\nFor example, when you state that you’re meeting a client tomorrow, kindly specify which client and what they are looking for. Also, when you mention follow-ups, please include the names so that I can verify them on the CRM.\nKindly update and rectify this moving forward.','2025-12-04 21:01:10','2025-12-04 21:01:10'),(57,278,11,NULL,'Here’s a polished and professional version of your message:\n\n---\n\nAs you share the follow-ups you’ve done, I’d appreciate it if you could include the names of the clients you followed up with. That way, I can easily check on your CRM and confirm the follow-ups made. Thank you.\n','2025-12-04 21:06:44','2025-12-04 21:06:44'),(58,276,11,NULL,'Here’s a polished and professional version of your message:\n\n---\n\nAs you share the follow-ups you’ve done with the leads provided, I’d appreciate it if you could include the names of the clients you followed up with. That way, I can easily check on your CRM and confirm the follow-ups made. Thank you.','2025-12-04 21:09:24','2025-12-04 21:09:24'),(59,316,11,NULL,'Good job Brian. All the best with your clients','2025-12-08 17:31:03','2025-12-08 17:31:03'),(60,318,27,NULL,'Here is my Saturday weekly report. I was overwhelmed during the weekend and could only write it today.','2025-12-08 17:36:32','2025-12-08 17:36:32'),(61,319,11,NULL,'Good job on the follow ups, all the best with your clients','2025-12-08 17:52:17','2025-12-08 17:52:17'),(62,318,11,NULL,'noted','2025-12-08 17:52:31','2025-12-08 17:52:31'),(63,315,9,NULL,'Well done. I haven\'t received your weekly report from last week yet.','2025-12-09 06:06:58','2025-12-09 06:06:58'),(64,314,9,NULL,'Well done! I haven\'t received your weekly report from last week yet.','2025-12-09 06:09:05','2025-12-09 06:09:05'),(65,336,24,NULL,'Dominic,\nClear your afternoon of 11th Dec for us to go through your clients in the CRM system.','2025-12-10 14:43:42','2025-12-10 14:43:42'),(66,360,45,NULL,'Well done Dennis! \nI love your Q&A version of report , keep it up. ','2025-12-15 13:17:55','2025-12-15 13:17:55'),(67,363,45,NULL,'Well done Brian!  \nJust keep pushing.','2025-12-15 13:36:17','2025-12-15 13:36:17'),(68,361,45,NULL,'Well done Desmond!\nKeep following up. ','2025-12-15 13:38:11','2025-12-15 13:38:11'),(69,360,27,66,'Thank you. Pushing for a sale or rental before 20th December 2025.','2025-12-15 14:04:16','2025-12-15 14:04:16'),(70,361,23,NULL,'Thank you','2025-12-15 19:38:34','2025-12-15 19:38:34'),(71,381,11,NULL,'This is Noted. \nContinue pushing for a closure this week','2025-12-16 22:27:25','2025-12-16 22:27:25'),(72,378,11,NULL,'This is noted. \nContinue pushing for a closure this week','2025-12-16 22:28:37','2025-12-16 22:28:37'),(73,375,11,NULL,'This is Noted. Continue pushing for a closure this week','2025-12-16 22:30:11','2025-12-16 22:30:11'),(74,381,23,NULL,'Will do','2025-12-18 06:55:06','2025-12-18 06:55:06'),(75,417,9,NULL,'Joy,Keep up the good work! We look forward to you being the team\'s first sale in 2026.','2026-01-06 04:17:21','2026-01-06 04:17:21'),(76,418,9,NULL,'Mia, keep up the good work! Doing your job well while also boosting sales is definitely possible.','2026-01-06 04:19:25','2026-01-06 04:19:25'),(77,419,9,NULL,'Desmond, remember to follow up well with your Category A potential clients from 2025, and keep in touch with your Category B clients regularly! Convert new leads as soon as possible; if that doesn\'t work, immediately move on to the next one. Don\'t waste too much time on clients who aren\'t interested. You have potential; give yourself more time to work hard, and look forward to doing even better in 2026.','2026-01-06 04:26:20','2026-01-06 04:26:20'),(78,420,9,NULL,'Yes, Paddy can help you with the images on your website; you can ask him for help. Alternatively, you can contact the development team. We need to ensure the new website content is online as soon as possible before developing the app; time is tight, so let\'s work hard!','2026-01-06 04:31:00','2026-01-06 04:31:00'),(79,418,17,NULL,'Thank you sir.','2026-01-06 05:30:13','2026-01-06 05:30:13'),(80,429,9,NULL,'Brian, congratulations! Was this transaction paid for last year, or is it a new order?','2026-01-07 01:54:08','2026-01-07 01:54:08'),(81,428,9,NULL,'Dennis, you need to understand the client\'s needs in advance and find suitable properties beforehand. If you can\'t find any, you can post them to the team for inquiry. Your current job-hunting method is very inefficient.','2026-01-07 01:58:49','2026-01-07 01:58:49'),(82,426,9,NULL,'David ，Are the number of clients you schedule to meet each day acceptable? Are these clients your existing clients, or are they newly found by you?','2026-01-07 02:02:54','2026-01-07 02:02:54'),(83,419,23,NULL,'Will do. Thank you. Looking forward to a productive 2026.','2026-01-07 06:18:24','2026-01-07 06:18:24'),(84,429,12,NULL,'thank you  Mr. Ken  ,it is the one we started following as from last month .','2026-01-07 12:36:23','2026-01-07 12:36:23'),(85,417,24,75,'I am close enough. I will close one this month.','2026-01-07 16:20:52','2026-01-07 16:20:52'),(86,428,27,81,'Hi Mr. Ken. First, I was allocated the lead on the same day and was supposed to show them a certain given property and also the client\'s needs that were relayed to me were not accurate. The information given to me is that I was supposed to show them a certain property, not to source for them. What encountered was miscommunication from one end.\n\nIt Zhu Yi who later after viewing a specified property clearly informed me of what the client\'s needs were because he speaks English. Totally not my fault.','2026-01-07 18:53:29','2026-01-07 18:53:29'),(87,426,20,NULL,'Newly found,it\'s connection to my colleagues ','2026-01-07 19:13:12','2026-01-07 19:13:12'),(88,444,11,NULL,'All the Best with your Emaar client Dennis. We are hopeful for a closure this month. ','2026-01-08 20:44:18','2026-01-08 20:44:18'),(89,452,9,NULL,'Carol, good job. You take the lead in closing deals with clients quickly and set an example for the team with your performance, so that the team can learn from your approach.','2026-01-09 02:15:24','2026-01-09 02:15:24'),(90,444,27,88,'Thank you','2026-01-09 11:04:06','2026-01-09 11:04:06'),(91,452,11,NULL,'Thank you. i am working towards that','2026-01-09 15:11:37','2026-01-09 15:11:37'),(92,469,9,NULL,'Dennis, your daily report is very detailed. Good job.','2026-01-13 06:26:02','2026-01-13 06:26:02'),(93,469,27,92,'Thank you Mr Ken. I am working to be better every day.','2026-01-13 13:21:10','2026-01-13 13:21:10'),(94,496,9,NULL,'Okay, Mia and Paddy can help with some of the work.','2026-01-14 17:37:06','2026-01-14 17:37:06'),(95,495,9,NULL,'How did the sales interview go? Let me know if there\'s a second interview.','2026-01-14 17:39:13','2026-01-14 17:39:13'),(96,494,9,NULL,'The record is very detailed, good job. We must pay attention to the quality of LEADS.','2026-01-14 17:42:27','2026-01-14 17:42:27'),(97,493,9,NULL,'Rosemary, a warm welcome to the BEKE family! Your work plan is very well organized, and I hope you will achieve new successes.','2026-01-14 17:46:42','2026-01-14 17:46:42'),(98,493,24,NULL,'Rosemary,\nIt was a great start today.\nRemember to come with the documents requested by the accounts department to enable you sign the contract.\nAlso pick the consent letters while going out to get new pieces of land.\nAll the best!','2026-01-14 18:01:39','2026-01-14 18:01:39'),(99,492,9,NULL,'Maureen, would like to view Eternity。\nDeniss,Is this a LEADS customer? Did the customer specifically request this project, or did you recommend it to the customer?','2026-01-14 18:02:29','2026-01-14 18:02:29'),(100,486,9,NULL,'Paddy,Keep up the good work!','2026-01-14 18:08:22','2026-01-14 18:08:22'),(101,496,13,NULL,'Ok ,I will let them know','2026-01-14 18:47:02','2026-01-14 18:47:02'),(102,493,46,97,'Thankyou sir.','2026-01-15 08:43:35','2026-01-15 08:43:35'),(103,493,46,98,'noted,thankyou.','2026-01-15 08:45:09','2026-01-15 08:45:09'),(104,492,27,99,'Hi. Yes. She would like to view after I shared the Eternity project details to her. She is yet to pick a day and time of viewing the Eternity apartments. Once she does, we will take her for viewing.','2026-01-15 13:56:17','2026-01-15 13:56:17'),(105,494,17,NULL,'noted sir','2026-01-15 16:02:00','2026-01-15 16:02:00'),(106,486,29,NULL,'Of course sir. Thank you.','2026-01-15 17:05:57','2026-01-15 17:05:57'),(107,503,9,NULL,'Carol,OK, help the team achieve their goals based on their potential clients.','2026-01-15 18:58:24','2026-01-15 18:58:24'),(108,492,9,NULL,'okay','2026-01-15 19:00:31','2026-01-15 19:00:31'),(109,503,11,NULL,'Okey','2026-01-16 03:05:19','2026-01-16 03:05:19'),(110,506,11,NULL,'Hey Desmond, continue focusing on the serious clients. ','2026-01-16 05:24:18','2026-01-16 05:24:18'),(111,502,11,NULL,'This is noted','2026-01-16 05:28:12','2026-01-16 05:28:12'),(112,506,23,NULL,'will do','2026-01-16 12:13:25','2026-01-16 12:13:25'),(113,523,9,NULL,'Joy, didn\'t you client in HK schedule a meeting for today?','2026-01-19 17:09:58','2026-01-19 17:09:58'),(114,523,24,NULL,'Yes.\nThe HK Team was ready to have a meeting but the Board of the 11acres were held up in the New Year planning. They requested we postpone to next week same time. ','2026-01-20 04:37:59','2026-01-20 04:37:59'),(115,553,11,NULL,'This is noted. Have you updated the viewings you had on the CRM?','2026-01-22 04:51:45','2026-01-22 04:51:45'),(116,551,11,NULL,'Hey Brian, did you have any Viewings yesterday? Desmond mentioned that you were to take his client for a viewing in Westlands the one who was looking for a commercial space.','2026-01-22 04:54:50','2026-01-22 04:54:50'),(117,546,11,NULL,'All the best with your Emaar Client','2026-01-22 04:56:21','2026-01-22 04:56:21'),(118,551,12,NULL,'Yes,I did facilitate the viewing \n\nThe client did not consider that location ','2026-01-22 05:53:26','2026-01-22 05:53:26'),(119,553,23,NULL,'Yes I have','2026-01-23 17:45:43','2026-01-23 17:45:43'),(120,595,9,NULL,'Carol,Good, keep up the good work!','2026-01-28 03:33:09','2026-01-28 03:33:09'),(121,603,24,NULL,'Rosemary,\nKindly give more accurate details of your whereabouts in the report. Share the time frame, location name, client name and next course of action.','2026-01-29 05:52:17','2026-01-29 05:52:17'),(122,603,46,121,'noted','2026-01-29 20:31:30','2026-01-29 20:31:30'),(123,622,24,NULL,'Rosemary,\nKindly adhere to the simple steps I gave you earlier regarding sourcing for land.\n1. Identify a property(within the locations I assigned you).\n2.Visit the property.\n3.Ensure you get the necessary documents of the property i.e the deed plan and pin location.\n4.Ensure that you have met with the landowner or the POA of the property not an agent, before submitting any of the property to the marketing team.\n5.Get the consent signed or an acknowledgement email or chat from the landowner before we start marketing the property.\n6.Lastly be strategic. Source on request/lead/enquiry and focus more on clients.\n\nOtherwise you\'re doing great. Keep up the good work. Your CRM is to be emulated. If you continue with the daily follow ups, your 1st sale is getting closer and closer. Bravo!','2026-02-02 16:16:44','2026-02-02 16:16:44'),(124,626,11,NULL,'Dennis, I’ve noticed the effort you’ve been putting into your follow-ups. Keep pushing great work ?','2026-02-02 20:09:38','2026-02-02 20:09:38'),(125,637,9,NULL,'James，Keep up the good work!','2026-02-04 02:30:15','2026-02-04 02:30:15'),(126,636,9,NULL,'Isaiah，Keep up the good work! I also need to write down you  plans for the next day.','2026-02-04 02:34:41','2026-02-04 02:34:41'),(127,634,9,NULL,'Tasha,Familiarize yourself with the company\'s sales process as soon as possible and align your work habits with the company\'s.I hope you a goal to achieve 1 closure this month.When everything is ready, the company will help you build a team.','2026-02-04 02:47:07','2026-02-04 02:47:07'),(128,622,46,NULL,'Hello,working on consents and will share with Diana.','2026-02-04 05:51:52','2026-02-04 05:51:52'),(129,659,11,NULL,'This is noted. Now that leads coming in are not many, focus on your A and B clients to see if you can get another offer from those clients. ','2026-02-05 15:46:29','2026-02-05 15:46:29'),(130,665,24,NULL,'Rosemary,\nIf you don\'t have clients you are taking to site, ensure you are out sourcing for new properties. We cannot afford to relax in the office the whole day without having meetings in the office.','2026-02-05 17:11:53','2026-02-05 17:11:53'),(131,660,24,NULL,'James,\nYour report has improved greatly. Keep up.\nImprove on the Schedules, give them timelines. \nAlso note that you are expected to be viewing with clients or sourcing for new listings. Hence, I don\'t expect you to be seated in the office the whole day.\nBear in mind you\'re expected to be having atleast 20Viewings with clients per month. Wishing you all the best as you settle in.\n\nRegards,','2026-02-05 17:20:46','2026-02-05 17:20:46'),(132,665,46,NULL,'Had two scheduled meeting in the office which were postponed ,but the point is well noted.','2026-02-06 05:52:36','2026-02-06 05:52:36'),(133,673,24,NULL,'I visited Muthithi 56 and Reliable Towers but the system didn\'t pick up the location.','2026-02-06 15:05:32','2026-02-06 15:05:32'),(134,685,24,NULL,'Rosemary,\nI have a great improvement on your report and schedule. Keep up the good work. Keep pushing more on the client interactions also. Together as a team we will achieve greater heights.','2026-02-09 16:53:36','2026-02-09 16:53:36'),(135,686,24,NULL,'James,\nYour report is still lacking. Let\'s purpose  tomorrow morning meeting to do a training on the same.','2026-02-09 17:06:47','2026-02-09 17:06:47'),(136,685,46,NULL,'Thankyou','2026-02-10 05:40:31','2026-02-10 05:40:31'),(137,709,11,NULL,'This is good news for the Emaar clients. There is hope for a closure this month. Keep pushing ','2026-02-11 15:39:03','2026-02-11 15:39:03'),(138,716,9,NULL,'Desmond,You did a very good job.That\'s how it was; I visited clients every day and invited them to meet the next day.','2026-02-11 17:46:54','2026-02-11 17:46:54'),(139,715,9,NULL,'Mia，The video shot in the Westlands this week was great; we need to find ways to improve the quality of the lyrics. Keep it up!','2026-02-11 17:52:22','2026-02-11 17:52:22'),(140,715,17,NULL,'Thank you for your acknowledgement sir, we are currently working on that sir.','2026-02-12 17:10:51','2026-02-12 17:10:51'),(141,716,23,NULL,'Thank you very much','2026-02-12 19:54:19','2026-02-12 19:54:19'),(142,725,11,NULL,'You\'re plans for tomorrow aren\'t stated. ','2026-02-12 21:31:52','2026-02-12 21:31:52'),(143,725,23,NULL,'Kindly check on the work plan','2026-02-13 14:06:14','2026-02-13 14:06:14'),(144,757,9,NULL,'Remember, focus first on Morvara\'s leads.','2026-02-17 18:31:43','2026-02-17 18:31:43'),(145,763,45,NULL,'Well done! I like your remarks','2026-02-18 13:35:28','2026-02-18 13:35:28');
