9 10:32:03','2026-01-29 10:32:03'),(99,133,'Wide angle TOF Camera - B0028','wide-angle-tof-camera-b0028-1769683455013','Wide Field of View (FoV): Typically around 108° x 78°, providing roughly four times the viewable area of standard ToF cameras at the same distance.\r\nApplications: Ideal for palettizing, large-area 3D inspection, and autonomous mobile robot (AMR) navigation.\r\nComponents: Often utilize Sony DepthSense sensors (e.g., IMX556PLR) with specialized wide-angle M12/S-mount lenses.\r\nPerformance: While offering a wider view, they may have slightly reduced accuracy compared to narrower FOV cameras due to light dispersion.\r\nData Types: Available as standalone depth cameras or integrated modules that include RGB data (e.g., Sunny Aiot and Arducam). ','others','others','new','A','','','',20990.00,'piece',20,'in_stock',11000,0,NULL,'/storage/products/covers/20240625203716-1769683455011-3l4ybh.png','{}',0,'active','2026-01-29 10:44:15','2026-01-29 10:44:15'),(100,133,'Development Kit - VM2401','development-kit-vm2401-1769683682085','Jinghong Technology\'s smart box (AIBox) is a smart box developed based on high-performance AI chip chips. It can provide multi-computing power, high value, low-power edge computing intelligent hardware, support deep learning algorithms, and corresponding AI processing modules. It has the characteristics of lightweight, high performance, low power consumption, and easy access. It can enable the product to connect the end, cloud, edge, etc., thereby realizing more intelligent automated operations. Therefore, it is widely used in various fields such as smart industry, smart manufacturing, industrial automation, smart agriculture, smart transportation, and the Internet of Things.\r\n\r\n','others','others','new','A','','','',4017.00,'piece',15,'in_stock',1900,0,NULL,'/storage/products/covers/20240527164451-1769683682083-6eo0ft.jpg','{}',0,'active','2026-01-29 10:48:02','2026-01-29 10:48:02'),(101,103,'Dinning Table, Adjustable Size