operty',128,'zh','alternative_name','RIARA OASIS'),(2245,'property',128,'zh','detailed_address','Riara路'),(2246,'property',128,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>RIARA OASIS</u></strong></p><p>Riara Oasis, a landmark residential development located along the tranquil and leafy <a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/A4UUWoAvzqMw2h9y5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Riara Road</a> in Lavington, Nairobi. Spanning 0.83 acres, this visionary project features three magnificent 22-floor towers offering a curated collection of 1, 2, and 3-bedroom modern apartments for sale, all crafted for sophisticated urban living.</p><h2>Lifestyle Amenities That Elevate Everyday Living:</h2><p>Riara Oasis is fully equipped to deliver comfort, convenience, and community through a suite of top-tier amenities:</p><ul><li>Fully Equipped Gym</li><li>Children’s Play Area</li><li>Swimming Pool</li><li>Borehole Water Supply &amp; Water Purifier</li><li>4-Level Ample Parking</li><li>CCTV Surveillance &amp; Visual Conversational Systems</li><li>High-Speed Lifts</li><li>Integrated Security Systems with Professional Guards</li></ul><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom Units</p><ul><li>Sizes: 50m² – 68m</li><li>Types: 6 unique layouts</li><li>Price Range: From KSh 5.5M to KSh 7M</li></ul><p>2 Bedroom Units</p><ul><li>Sizes: 88m² – 95m²</li><li>Types: 2 configurations</li><li>Price Range: From KSh 9.5M to KSh 10M</li></ul><p>3 Bedroom Units</p><ul><li>Sizes: 120m² – 135m²</li><li>Types: 3 expansive designs</li><li>Price Range: From KSh 13.5M to KSh 15M</li></ul><h2>Prime Location in Lavington:</h2><p>Riara Oasis is located in the prestigious Lavington suburb, offering excellent connectivity to:</p><ul><li>Top international schools</li><li>Shopping malls (The Junction, Yaya Centre)</li><li>Hospitals, restaurants, and entertainment hubs</li><li>Quick access to Ngong Road, Gitanga Road &amp; Nairobi CBD</li></ul><p><strong>Expected Completion</strong>: December 2027</p><p><strong>Flexible Payment Plans:</strong></p><ul><li>20%, 30%, or 50% deposit</li><li>Balance payable in easy installments up to December 2027</li></ul>'),(2247,'property',129,'zh','property_name','翡翠府'),(2248,'property',129,'zh','alternative_name','JADE RESIDENCE'),(2249,'property',129,'zh','detailed_address','Kindaruma路， Kilimani'),(2250,'property',129,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>JADE RESIDENCY</u></strong></p><p>The Jade Residency offers luxury living within the city. Offering luxury apartments that are centrally located in Kilimani area in Nairobi. Close proximity to major shopping malls, schools. Hospitals and other amenities, all within a 2 km radius. The boutique development comprising 2, 3 and 4 bed luxury apartments has been tastefully designed with world class finishes. 114 units in total</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provision for gym space</li><li>Roof top gym facility,</li><li>Roof top social hall with kitchenette</li><li>Roof top open terrace lounge</li><li>Sky bridge connecting both blocks</li><li>High speed lifts,</li><li>Dedicated parking spots,</li><li>Generator for common areas</li><li>Provision for intercom, internet and satellite TV,</li><li>Private balconies</li><li>Provision for an inverter in each apartment,</li><li>Perimeter wall with electric fence,</li><li>Solar water heating system e</li></ul><p>The well thought out spaces allow for natural light and air circulation and the interior design has been designed by an on board professional designer. Modern interiors with tasteful selection of finishes and colours to provide maximum flexibility. The light, airy spaces are a breath of fresh air; large windows for maximum light, private balcony, fully fitted kitchen with appliances</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>2 bedroom master en-suite (107.6 sq.m) From Kes. 13M</p><p>2 bedroom including open terrace (211 sq.m) – Kes. 17M (offer)</p><p>2 bedroom including open terrace (231 sq.m) – Kes. 18M (offer)</p><p>3 bedroom master en-suite plus DSQ (155 sq.m) – Kes. 20M (offer)</p><p>3 bedroom plus DSQ including open terrace (287 sq.m) – Kes. 24M (offer)</p><p>4 bedroom master en-suite plus DSQ (222.6 sq.m) – Kes. 24M (offer)</p><p>4 bedroom plus DSQ and family room – Penthouse (310 sq.m) – Kes. 45M</p>'),(2251,'property',130,'zh','property_name','BLOSSOM IVY'),(2252,'property',130,'zh','alternative_name','BLOSSOM IVY'),(2253,'property',130,'zh','detailed_address','Othaya路， Kileleshwa'),(2254,'property',130,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>BLOSSOM IVY RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>Blossom Ivy Residence is a luxurious apartment complex located in Kileleshwa, Nairobi, offering 1 to 4-bedroom apartments with amenities like a gym, indoor heated pool, and children\'s play areas. It features modern architecture, ample parking, and is designed to provide a comfortable and convenient urban lifestyle. The development emphasizes high-end finishes, smart home features, and a range of amenities, including a coffee bar, gardens, and leisure spaces.</p><p>Key features of Blossom Ivy Residence:</p><p>Variety of apartment sizes: Offers 1, 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments, some with DSQ (Domestic Staff Quarter) and study areas. Prime location: Situated on Gatundu Road in Kileleshwa, providing easy access to Westland, the CBD, schools, hospitals, and shopping centers. Modern amenities: Includes a gym, indoor heated swimming pool, children\'s play areas, a coffee bar, and well-manicured gardens. High-end finishes and smart home features: Features include fitted kitchens, decorative interiors, water purifiers, and smart home technology. Security and convenience: Offers 24/7 security, ample parking, dual generators, and backup power. Flexible payment plans: Flexible payment plans are available.</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>– ?️‍♀️ Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>–&nbsp;Children’s Playground/Leisure Space</p><p>– ?‍♀️ Heated Swimming Pool</p><p>– ? Office Space and Conference Room</p><p>– ⁠? Con