illance &amp; 24/7 Security</li></ul><p><strong>Interior finishes:</strong></p><p>Granite Countertops</p><p>Imported Ceramic Tiles</p><p>Custom Cabinetry</p><p>Modern Sanitary Fittings</p><p>Spacious Balconies</p><p>High Ceilings &amp; Ample Natural Light</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ol><li>Studio&nbsp;36.11 sqm&nbsp;4,900,000</li><li>Studio&nbsp;37.06 sqm&nbsp;5,000,000</li><li>1 Bedroom 61.22 sqm 7,800,000</li><li>1 Bedroom 69.62 sqm&nbsp;8,800,000</li><li>2 Bedroom + DSQ&nbsp;122.86 sqm 14,900,000</li><li>2 Bedroom +DSQ&nbsp;125.35 sqm 15,100,000</li><li>2 Bedroom +DSQ&nbsp;129.30 sqm 16,000,000</li><li>3 Bedroom +DSQ 180.89&nbsp;sqm&nbsp;22,000,000</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment flexibility:</strong></p><p><strong> </strong>20% deposit followed by monthly/quarterly installments, cash plan (balance within two weeks), mortgage option (20% down in 7 days), and post-completion financing available&nbsp;.</p>'),(2259,'property',132,'zh','property_name','DG JKIA'),(2260,'property',132,'zh','alternative_name','DG JKIA'),(2261,'property',132,'zh','detailed_address','肯尼亚内罗毕Msa路Jkia机场'),(2262,'property',132,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>DG JKIA RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>DG JKIA is an upcoming luxury residential project by SSS Developers on Mombasa Road, opposite the Jomo Kenyatta International Airport (JKIA), Nairobi. The neighbourhood is a popular commercial and industrial district in Nairobi, majorly dominated by residential, industrial, and commercial buildings.The construction of the development is estimated to be completed in 2026 and will offer studio and 1-bedroom units.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>These apartments will be served by facilities and amenities including: </strong></p><p><br></p><p>•• Spa - (Massage rooms, steam &amp; sauna)</p><p>•• Outdoor swimming pool.</p><p>•• Rooftop yoga garden</p><p>•• Children’s play area.</p><p>•• Gym</p><p>•• Rooftop lounging gazebos</p><p>•• Shopping complex on the ground floor.</p><p>•• Outdoor courtyard.</p><p>•• Ample parking spaces.</p><p>•• Valet parking &amp; concierge services.</p><p>•• Full power backup generator</p><p>•• Borehole</p><p>Hotel units available</p><p><br></p><p>•Studio hotel apartments - Starting from $60,000</p><p>•One Bedroom hotel apartments - Starting from $90,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>•1.5 years payment plan - 0% interest</p><p>•Reservation - 15% interest</p><p>•During Construction - 50% spread in 18 months</p><p>•Before or upon Hand Over - 20%</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Hotel unit sizes:﻿</strong></p><p>•Standard Studio - 33 sqm</p><p>•King Studio - 44 sqm</p><p>•Standard One Bedroom - 49 sqm</p><p>•King One Bedroom - 53 sqm</p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>(<strong>Note</strong>: Offering flexible payment plans over the remaining construction period after placing a 30% deposit to reserve. On the below prices, we offer high discounts for high deposits and full cash buyers)</p>'),(2263,'property',133,'zh','property_name','LUCKINN常春藤'),(2264,'property',133,'zh','alternative_name','LUCKINN IVY'),(2265,'property',133,'zh','detailed_address','MOGOTIO RD'),(2266,'property',133,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>LUCKINN IVY</u></strong></p><p>Luckinn Ivy Residence is a modern, high-rise apartment development located in Westlands, Nairobi, offering 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments with options including a DSQ (Domestic Staff Quarter). It\'s situated on Mogotio Road, behind GTC, and features expansive, open-plan layouts with high-quality finishes and city views. The development is designed for both homeowners and investors, emphasizing a blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience.</p><p>Whether you’re a homebuyer looking for a modern residence or an investor seeking high returns, these luxury apartments in Nairobi provide exceptional value in the heart of the city.&nbsp;</p><h3>Unmatched Features &amp; Amenities:</h3><ul><li>Swimming Pool – Enjoy a refreshing swim in a luxurious pool</li><li>Fully E