ccess to a multitude of commercial establishments, shopping centers, hotels, and dining options.</p><p>Investors can anticipate not only attractive rental returns but also long-term appreciation in property value. </p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Swimming Pool</li><li>Kids Play Area </li><li>Fully-equipped Gym</li><li>Back-up Generator </li><li>Borehole Water Supply</li><li>CCTV Surveillance</li><li>Intercom</li><li>High-speed Elevators &amp; Ample Parking </li><li>24/7 Manned Security</li><li>Landscaped Zen Garden</li><li>Facilities for management staff</li><li>Access control facilities</li></ul><p><strong> Unit sizes and prices :</strong></p><p>1-bedroom (60 sqm, 645 sqft) – From Kes. 7M</p><p>1-bedroom + study room (75 sqm, 808 sqft) – From Kes. 8.5M</p><p>2-bedroom - type 1 (95 sqm, 1023sqft) – From Kes. 10.5M </p><p>2-bedroom - type 2 (95 sqm, 1023sqft) – From Kes. 10.5M</p><p>EARLY-BIRD DISCOUNT AVALIABLE, CONTACT US FOR MORE INFO!!</p><p><br></p><p>Completion date</p><p>June 2026</p>'),(2287,'property',139,'zh','property_name','王国塔'),(2288,'property',139,'zh','alternative_name','KINGDOM TOWERS'),(2289,'property',139,'zh','detailed_address','4th Parklands, Avenue.'),(2290,'property',139,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>KINGDOM TOWER</u></strong></p><p>Kingdom Tower in 4th Parklands, Nairobi refers to a residential building with 4, 2, and 1 bedroom luxurious apartments. It\'s a 17-story building, nearing completion by July 2027, with prices starting from 7.8 million KES, according to a real estate Instagram account. The location is within the Parklands area of Nairobi.</p><p>Key Details:</p><p>Name: Kingdom Towers 1Location: 4th Parklands, Nairobi Type: Residential apartments Features: 4, 2, and 1 bedroom units Status: Under construction, completion expected by July 2027 Starting Price: 7.8 million KES</p><p><strong> Amenities include;</strong></p><p>Religious Facilities:A mosque and a madarasa (religious school) cater to the spiritual needs of re