><p>KSH. 22,000,000</p><p>Right in the heart of Kilimani along George Padmore road is an</p><p>exquisite new addition to its rustic enclave, Cicada Crest apartments</p><p>The visualization for this development is a blend of comfort, space and</p><p>contemporary lifestyle to create a perfect home for you. 3 Bedroom All en-</p><p>suite plus a DSQ with plinth areas of 206 and 218 sqm on a 2-year payment plan at 0% interest rate.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(2363,'property',158,'zh','property_name','格罗夫纳住宅'),(2364,'property',158,'zh','alternative_name','GROSVENOR RESIDENCE'),(2365,'property',158,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰'),(2366,'property',158,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><strong><u>GROSSVENOR RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>Welcome to Grosvenor Residences Apartments, a visionary project redefining investment in Westlands. It offers an unparalleled living experience, seamlessly blending luxury with a prime location.</p><p><strong>Why Invest In Grosvenor Residences Apartments.</strong></p><p><strong>✅ </strong>Low Site Coverage ensuring ample green space.</p><p>✅ Full Lighting for optimal illumination and ambiance.</p><p>✅ Sky-high Pool offering unparalleled views.</p><p>✅ Iconic Location commanding attention in the city’s skyline.</p><p>✅ Prime Positioning at the center stage of urban living.</p><p>✅ Artistic Design showcasing architectural excellence.</p><p>✅ Luxurious Reception with soaring high ceilings</p><p>✅ Convenient Surroundings with easy access to amenities<strong>.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong> Features and Amenities:</strong></p><p>Two heated pool one on ground floor another one at the rooftop.</p><p>4000sqm fully equipped gym.</p><p>Residence coffee house.</p><p>Meeting and conference hall.</p><p>Beautiful landscape art garden.</p><p>Full back up generator.</p><p>High speed lift.</p><p>Barbecue area.</p><p>Spacious big kids play area.</p><p>Ample parking.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit Types And Prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom Apartmen