 Ridge Court, 3rd Avenue Park sits in the heart of the Parklands neighborhood, offering convenient access to shopping malls, eateries, and the CBD .</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Smart door locks and enhanced security</p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>High-speed elevators</p><p>Rooftop air garden</p><p>Children’s play area</p><p>Coffee shop within the premises</p><p>Ample parking for residents and guests</p><p>Borehole and city council water access</p><p>Full backup generator for uninterrupted power</p><p><br></p><p> <strong>Unit Types, Sizes &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>3rd Avenue Park (Serviced Apartments)</p><ul><li>1‑Bedroom fully furnished serviced apartments</li></ul><p>Price: Starting from 11000000 million</p><ul><li>2‑Bedroom fully furnished serviced apartments</li></ul><p>Price: Starting from 15,517,090 Million</p><p>Includes high ceiling, open kitchen, balcony, laundry area, en‑suite master bedroom&nbsp;.</p>'),(2383,'property',163,'zh','property_name','现代都市房源'),(2384,'property',163,'zh','alternative_name','MODERN CITY HOMES'),(2385,'property',163,'zh','detailed_address','Kindaruma路'),(2386,'property',163,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Situated in one of Nairobi’s most vibrant and accessible neighborhoods, Modern City Apartment places you close to:</p><p>✅ Top schools and international learning institutions</p><p>✅ Premier shopping centers like Yaya Centre and Prestige Plaza</p><p>✅ Quality healthcare facilities</p><p>✅ A variety of cafes, restaurants, and social amenities</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Swimming Pool</strong>: Enjoy relaxation and scenic views.</li><li><strong>Fully Equipped Gym</strong>: Stay fit with state-of-the-art equipment.</li><li><strong>Kids’ Play Area</strong>: A safe and fun space for children.</li><li><strong>Relaxation Area</strong>: Perfect for unwinding after a long day.</li><li><strong>Ample Parking</strong>: Sufficient space for residents and visitors.</li><li><strong>