-up zone</p><p>His &amp; Hers gyms, heated swimming pool, gaming room, meditation area</p><p>Restaurant/Coffee bistro, tuck shop &amp; grocery market, dry cleaning &amp; laundry</p><p>Beauty salon &amp; barber shop, conference rooms &amp; banquet hall</p><p>Rooftop entertainment terrace</p><p><br></p><p> <strong>Unit Types,sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>)</p><p>1 Bedroom (Standard) 73 m² / ~786 ft² Neighbourhood $100,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type A 111 m² / ~1,195 ft² Karura Forest $140,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type B 97 m² / ~1,044 ft² Neighbourhood $130,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type C 104 m² / ~1,120 ft² Karura Forest $140,000</p><p>2 Bedroom Type D 91 m² / ~980 ft² Muthaiga / local schools $130,000</p><p>3 Bedroom (Standard) 162 m² / ~1,744 ft² 6th Avenue Parklands View $180,000</p><p><br></p><p>Surroundings &amp; Accessibility</p><ul><li>Located in Parklands, just 5 km from Nairobi’s CBD, Asili Hills benefits from:</li><li>Natural setting next to Karura Forest, providing lush greenery and peaceful views.</li><li>Nearby major amenities including Aga Khan Hospital, MP Shah Hospital, Diamond Plaza, Oshwal Centre, and the Parklands Sports Club offering sports and leisure facilities.</li><li>Close proximity to public transport options (matatus, buses, rideshares), good internet connectivity, several schools and restaurants in walking distance&nbsp;.</li></ul>'),(2391,'property',165,'zh','property_name','CASA RINA HEIGHTS'),(2392,'property',165,'zh','alternative_name','CASA RINA HEIGHTS'),(2393,'property',165,'zh','detailed_address','Westlands, Mvuli路'),(2394,'property',165,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Casa Rina Heights comprises of a variety of&nbsp;tastefully designed 1 and 2 bedroom apartments for sale along Mvuli Road in the prime serene Westlands Area. Come and experience the epitome of upscale living. Experience elevated living at Casa Rina Heights, as you step outside into your own personal oasis. (20 floor development)</p><p><br></p><h3>Amenities:</h3><p>– Roof Top Garden</p><p>– Fully Equipped GYM</p><p>– Club House</p><p>– Children’s Play Ground</p><p>– Borehole &amp; Ample Water Storage Tanks</p><p>– Generator Backup</p><p>– CCTV &amp; Electrical Fence</p><p>– DSTV &amp; Internet Provision</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> Varieties&nbsp;and Price:</strong></h3><p>1-Bedroom (55 sqm) starts from KES 6.2M</p><p>1-Bedroom + Laundry area (80 sqm) starts from KES 8M</p><p>1-Bedroom&nbsp;+ Study room (80 sqm) starts from KES 8.2M</p><p>2-Bedroom&nbsp;master en-suite (100 sqm) starts from KES 11.5M</p><p>2-Bedroom all en-suite plus detached studio (145 sqm) starts from KES 15.2M</p>'),(2395,'property',166,'zh','property_name','SARUNI公寓'),(2396,'property',166,'zh','alternative_name','河畔搁浅'),(2397,'property',166,'zh','detailed_address','Saruni, Riverside'),(2398,'property',166,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>The Saruni, is a unique contemporary development that is the embodiment of a luxurious lifestyle secluded from the hustle and bustle of the fast-paced urban life.The development provides a luxurious refuge away from the high paced energy of city life with an extensive list of amenities specifically curated for an environment of leisure, serenity and rejuvenation. With uninterrupted views from each apartment.</p><p>The Saruni , is a modern interpretation of contemporary luxury specifically designed to enhance your living experience.</p><p>It consists of a total of 18 floors, with 95 units, 131 parking slots and 13 visitors parking slots.</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Property Features and Amenities:</strong></p><p>East and West Sky Gardens</p><p>Infinity heated swimming pool</p><p>Steam room</p><p>Modern fitted gym</p><p>Reception lobby and management office</p><p>2 High speed lifts</p><p>Ground level manicured and landscaped</p><p>courtyard garden</p><p>Ample parking</p><p>Full backup generator</p><p>24 Hr security services at the gate and on property</p><p>Intercom</p><p>Perimeter electric fence</p><p>Borehole</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Uni