120 sqm (All Ensuite From Ksh 12.5M) | Cash Price: Ksh 11.8M</li></ul><p>3-Bedroom + DSQ (160 sqm, All Ensuite)</p><ul><li>From: Ksh 17M</li><li>Cash Price: Ksh 16M</li><li>Mortgage Price: Ksh 18M</li></ul><p>4-Bedroom + DSQ + Study Room</p><ul><li>260 sqm (All Ensuite From Ksh 28M) | Cash Price: Ksh 26M | Mortgage: Ksh 30M</li><li>269 sqm (All Ensuite From Ksh 28.8M) | Cash Price: Ksh 26.8M | Mortgage: Ksh 30.8M</li></ul><p>? <strong>Completion Date</strong>: December 2027</p>'),(2407,'property',169,'zh','property_name','钻石湾'),(2408,'property',169,'zh','alternative_name','DIAMOND BAY'),(2409,'property',169,'zh','detailed_address','Westlands Road, Westlands内罗毕'),(2410,'property',169,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>DIAMOND BAY RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>Diamond Bay Residence an exclusive high-rise development in the heart of Westlands, along Westlands Road. This architectural marvel features 1 and 2-bedroom all en-suite apartments across two 23-story towers, with each floor comprising 7 thoughtfully designed units and 3 basement levels for parking.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> World-Class Amenities:</strong></h3><ul><li>High-Speed Lifts: 2 per block for seamless movement</li><li>Heated Swimming Pool: Enjoy year-round luxury</li><li>Kids’ Play Area: Safe and fun for children</li><li>Café: Relax and unwind</li><li>Yoga Studio: Wellness at your doorstep</li><li>CCTV Surveillance: 24/7 security monitoring</li><li>Smart Home Features: Advanced face scan technology</li><li>Water Borehole: Reliable water supply</li><li>Mini Shop: Convenience within the residence</li><li>Control Room: Enhanced security and monitoring</li><li>Modern, High-Quality Finishing: Crafted for luxury</li><li>Ample Parking: Dedicated resident slots and separate visitor parking</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong> Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>1 bedroom (60 sqm) – Kes. 8M1-bedroom ProMax (78 sqm) – (SOLD OUT)</p><p>2 bedrooms (125 sqm) – (SOLD OUT)</p><p>2 bedrooms (144 sqm) – Kes. 14M2 bedrooms p