10 mins), Gertrude Children’s Hospital (3 mins), and Aga Khan Hospital (5 mins).</li><li>Major Shopping Malls: Yaya Centre (6 mins), Lavington Mall (6 mins), Valley Arcade Mall (5 mins), Junction Mall (10 mins), Sarit Centre (14 mins), and Westgate Mall (17 mins).</li><li>Recreational &amp; Sports Clubs: Nairobi Jaffery Sports Club (5 mins), Space Playground (11 mins), Nairobi Polo Club (12 mins), and Parklands Sports Club (19 mins).</li></ul><h3>Property Types &amp; Unit Features:</h3><p>AYA Luxury Residence offers a wide selection of modern apartments and villas tailored to diverse lifestyle needs:</p><h4>1. Sky Villas – The Ultimate Penthouse Experience</h4><ul><li>5-Bedroom Triplex Sky Villa + DSQ (580sqm, 418sqm, 360sqm)</li><li>6-Bedroom Duplex Sky Villa + DSQ (503sqm, 488sqm)</li><li><strong>&nbsp;Features:</strong></li><li>Private rooftop garden with patio shade</li><li>Double-volume ceiling</li><li>Fully fitted Turkish kitchen &amp; kitchenette</li><li>Walk-in closets in master bedrooms</li><li>His &amp; hers vanity sinks</li><li>Expansive balconies &amp; terraces</li></ul><h4>2. Duplex &amp; Garden Villas – A Private Sanctuary</h4><ul><li>6-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (740sqm)</li><li>4-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (609sqm, 347sqm, 255sqm)</li><li>3-Bedroom Duplex Garden Villa + DSQ (347sqm, 255sqm)</li><li><strong>Features:</strong></li><li>Private landscaped garden</li><li>Spacious living &amp; dining areas</li><li>Smart home features</li><li>High-end Turkish finishes</li><li>All ensuite bedrooms</li></ul><h4>3. Duplex &amp; Standard Apartments – Luxury Redefined</h4><ul><li>4-Bedroom Duplex + DSQ (400sqm, 262sqm)</li><li>3-Bedroom Duplex + DSQ (280sqm, 265sqm, 221sqm)</li><li>2-Bedroom Apartments (125sqm)</li><li>Studio Apartments (49sqm)</li><li><strong> Features:</strong></li><li>Private balconies &amp; terraces</li><li>Fully fitted kitchen with premium appliances</li><li>Modern staircase with elegant grills</li><li>Spacious TV room &amp; lounge area</li></ul>'),(2415,'property',171,'zh','property_name','阿斯特拉湾'),(2416,'property',171,'zh','alternative_name','阿斯特拉湾'),(2417,'property',171,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(2418,'property',171,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Welcome to <strong>Astra Bay Residence</strong>, where contemporary design meets urban convenience. This sophisticated development offers a range of modern living spaces perfect for young professionals, first-time homeowners, and savvy investors. Strategically located in Lower Kabete, Astra Bay Residence provides seamless connectivity to key areas of Nairobi while offering a tranquil, stylish lifestyle.</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Lower Kabete</p><p><strong>Property Type:</strong> Studios and 1-Bedroom Apartments</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Exceptional Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><h3> Backup Generator: Uninterrupted power supply for all areas.</h3><h3>✅ Fully Equipped Gym: Maintain an active lifestyle.</h3><h3>✅ 24-Hour CCTV Surveillance: Enhanced security for your peace of mind.</h3><h3>✅ Social Corridor: Perfect for community interactions.</h3><h3>✅ Borehole Water Supply: Reliable and clean water access.</h3><h3>✅ Jogging Track: Stay active in a safe environment.</h3><h3>✅ High-Speed Lifts: Quick and convenient access to all floors.</h3><h3>✅ Access Control System: Secure entry for residents.</h3><h3><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;<strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>✅ <strong>Outdoor Refreshing Area:</strong> Ideal for relaxation and socializing.</p><p>✅ <strong>Convenience Store:</strong> On-site shopping for daily essentials.</p><p>✅ <strong>Gaming Room:</strong> Entertainment for all ages.</p><p>✅ <strong>Green Area:</strong> Beautifully landscaped for a refreshing environment.</p><p>✅ <strong>Indoor Activity Space:</strong> Multi-purpose area for residents.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>&nbsp;Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p> <strong>Prices Starting From:</strong> Ksh 1.8M</p><ul><li><strong>Studio (24.7 sqm)