d long-term investment. Nestled on 1.1 acres along Mbaazi Road, this stunning high-rise community features three 17-floor towers offering 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments for sale. Whether you’re a homeowner or an investor looking for a high-value property in Nairobi, this project delivers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience.</p><h3>Why Invest in Metricon Oasis Apartments?</h3><ul><li>Strategic Location: Situated in Lavington, one of Nairobi’s most sought-after residential neighborhoods, with easy access to shopping malls, international schools, and key business hubs.</li><li>Modern Design &amp; Spacious Units: Choose from various apartment layouts ranging from 60m² to 150m², all featuring elegant interiors, high-end finishes, and contemporary designs.</li><li>Flexible Payment Plan: Secure your dream home today with just a 20% deposit and spread the balance in convenient installments until December 2025.</li></ul><h3>Premium Apartment Features:</h3><ul><li>Each unit is fitted with:</li><li>Modern Kitchen: This kitchen comes with 2 fitted burners, an exhaust fan, and a light belt for added convenience.</li><li>Elegant Lighting – Beautiful chandeliers to elevate your living space.</li><li>Extra Storage – The 3-bedroom units include a spacious pantry.</li></ul><h3>Apartment Prices &amp; Sizes:</h3><p>1-Bedroom Apartments (5 types) – 60m² to 70m² | KES 7.6M – 8.8M</p><p>2-Bedroom Apartments (4 types) – 85m² to 95m² | KES 10.6M – 11.8M</p><p>3-Bedroom Apartments (3 types) – 110m² to 150m² | KES 13.6M – 17.8M</p>'),(2431,'property',175,'zh','property_name','钻石常春藤'),(2432,'property',175,'zh','alternative_name','DIAMOND IVY'),(2433,'property',175,'zh','detailed_address','内罗毕Kileleshwa的Mandera路'),(2434,'property',175,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>DIAMOND IVY APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p>Diamond ivy apartments are located in Kileleshwa, along Mandera road. In a prime location with close proximity to educational, social, religious and recreational amenities