Design:The development emphasizes the preservation of existing mature trees and incorporates abundant greenery.</li><li>Privacy and Exclusivity:The development consists of only five villas, ensuring a sense of privacy and tranquility.</li><li>Modern Amenities:Features include a private lift in each home, a top-floor entertainment lounge with panoramic views, and 4-car parking with additional visitor spaces.</li><li>Quiet and Secure Location:, Located in a quiet and safe area on Jacaranda Avenue, known for its beautiful landscaping.</li><li>Community and Convenience:</li><li>Close to international schools, shopping malls, and other amenities.</li><li>Location:</li><li>Verde Vista is situated on Jacaranda Avenue, a tree-lined street in Lavington</li><li>Verde Vista is marketed towards families, entertainers, and those seeking refined tranquility. The development aims to provide a peaceful and nature-rich living environment while still offering convenient access to urban amenities.</li></ul><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>5 Bedroom 145 sqm 22,000,000</p>'),(2439,'property',177,'zh','property_name','芬斯伯里高地'),(2440,'property',177,'zh','alternative_name','FINSBURY HEIGHTS'),(2441,'property',177,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(2442,'property',177,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>FINSBURY HEIGHTS</u></strong></p><p>Finsbury Heights is a residential development in Nairobi, Kenya, offering spacious 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments with luxurious amenities. It\'s located off Parklands Road in Westlands, near the border with Parklands. Finsbury Heights is known for its blend of modern living, convenience, and community atmosphere.</p><p><strong>Key features of Finsbury Heights:</strong></p><ul><li>Location:Prime location in Nairobi, specifically in the Westlands area, situated between Parklands and Westlands.</li><li>Apartment types:Offers a range of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments, including some with servant\'s quarters (DSQ).</li><li>Amenities:Includes a rooftop pool, mosque, gym, children\'s play area, on-site supermarket, and ample parking.</li><li>Security:Features 24/7 CCTV and manned security, ensuring a safe living environment, accor&nbsp;ding to Instagram posts by UrbanGlow Real Estate.</li><li>Modern living:Highlights fully fitted kitchens, and a sustainable borehole for water supply.</li><li>Community:Promotes a vibrant community atmosphere</li></ul>'),(2443,'property',178,'zh','property_name','独立房屋'),(2444,'property',178,'zh','alternative_name','STANDALONE HOUSE'),(2445,'property',178,'zh','detailed_address','Loresho'),(2446,'property',178,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>STAND ALONE HOUSE</u></strong></p><p>Discover comfort and convenience in this beautifully maintained 4-bedroom house located in Loresho,one of Nairobi\'s&nbsp;most sought- after residential neighborhoods.</p><p>This property offers a perfect blend of privacy, space and easy access to essential amenities.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p>En-suite bedrooms</p><p>Spacious living area</p><p>Garden</p><p>Staff quarters (DSQ)</p><p>Gated community</p><p><strong> Additional Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Clubhouse</li><li>Gym</li><li>Back up generator</li></ul><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>4 Bedroom 790 sqm at Ksh 108,000,000</p>'),(2447,'property',179,'zh','property_name','法拉杰高地'),(2448,'property',179,'zh','alternative_name','FARAJ HEIGHTS'),(2449,'property',179,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(2450,'property',179,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>FARAJ HEIGHTS</u></strong></p><p><strong>Prime location:</strong> Situated in the heart of Kilimani, Farah Heights offers the perfect blend of tranquillity and easy access to the city’s pulse.</p><p><strong>Walkable distance:</strong> Enjoy the convenience of being within walking distance of the esteemed Masjid Adam’s, the popular Yaya Mall for all your shopping needs, and the renowned CJ’s Restaurant for delightful meals.</p><p><strong>Quick commute: