l tiles</li><li>Particle laminated wardrobes</li><li>Shower cubicles with toughened glass</li><li>Modern fitted kitchens with granite tops</li><li>High quality sanitary-wares and fittings</li></ul><p>Moments away from the property comes the following important facilities</p><p><strong>Top schools</strong></p><ul><li>Consolata school</li><li>Olive crescent international school</li><li>Herald international school</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Hospitals</strong></p><ul><li>MP Shah hospital</li><li>Westlands medical center</li><li>Westlands laser eye hospital</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Shopping and dinning</strong></p><ul><li>Sarit Centre</li><li>Westgate mall</li><li>The mall</li><li>Quick mart</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Excellent road access</strong></p><ul><li>Waiyaki way</li><li>Nairobi express way</li><li>General mathenge road</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit typology and pricing:</strong></p><ol><li>3 Bed | 200 Sqm. – Ksh. 22,200, 000</li><li>3 Bed | 220 Sqm. – KS. 23,000, 000</li><li>3 Bed | 260 Sqm. plus DSQ – KS. 28,000, 000 <em> (Sold out)</em></li><li>4 Bed | 270 Sqm. – KS. 28,700, 000<em> (Sold out)</em></li><li>Duplex – 4 Bed | 320 Sqm. – KS. 35,000, 000</li></ol>'),(2486,'property',189,'zh','property_name','威尔玛塔'),(2487,'property',189,'zh','alternative_name','WILMA TOWER'),(2488,'property',189,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani ， Elgeyo Marakwet路。'),(2489,'property',189,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><strong><u>WILMA TOWER</u></strong></p><p>In the scenic and serene environment of Kilimani along</p><p>Elgeyo Marakwet Road with easy access to the best</p><p>shopping malls, schools, and recreational centers.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Landscaped Gardens</p><p>Borehole</p><p>Full Backup Generator</p><p>Heated Swimming Pool</p><p>Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>Outdoor Walking/Running Track</p><p>Basketball Court</p><p>Steam and Sauna</p><p>Children’s Games Room (indoor)</p><p>Children’s Play Area (outdoor)</p><p>Barbeque Area</p><p>Solar Water