operty is located along Loiyangalani road, Lavington.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Spacious 6-Bedroom Triplex</p><p>DSQ for added convenience</p><p>Private BBQ Zone for entertaining</p><p>2 Car Parking + Guest Parking</p><p>Tranquil Private Garden</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Top Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Modern Gym &amp; Exercise Facilities</p><p>Safe Kids’ Playground</p><p>Full Power Backup</p><p>CCTV and security personnel with walled electric perimeter fencing</p><p>Well maintained landscapes and common areas provide a luxury feel</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and prize:</strong></p><p>6 Bedrooms 852 sqm at Ksh 90,000,000</p>'),(2522,'property',198,'zh','property_name','RIARA ONE'),(2523,'property',198,'zh','alternative_name','RIARA ONE'),(2524,'property',198,'zh','detailed_address','Riara路， Kilimani'),(2525,'property',198,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Located in Kilimani area, opposite The Junction Mall. Has luxurious amenities and best quality finishing including 1050 sqm of entertainment center, 1150 sqm open floor garden.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities;</strong></p><p>Heated swimming pool</p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>Open floor garden</p><p>Children’s paradise</p><p>Business center</p><p>CCTV and 24 hour security</p><p>Backup generator</p><p>Ample parking</p><p>Borehole</p><p>Riara one residency is moments away from key facilities:</p><ul><li>Top schools</li><li>Hospitals</li><li>Shopping malls and restaurants</li></ul><p><strong>Unit size and prize:</strong></p><p>2BR 95Sqm&nbsp;Ksh. 12.5M</p>'),(2526,'property',199,'zh','property_name','皇家维斯塔'),(2527,'property',199,'zh','alternative_name','ROYAL VISTA'),(2528,'property',199,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(2529,'property',199,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><strong>Royal Vistaa Residence Apartments</strong>, an epitome of luxury living nestled in the heart of Westlands, Nairobi, A short walk from the renowned Villa ROSA Kempinski.</p><p>These 29 