strong> is your perfect choice.</p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>Minimum of 20% deposit, balance to be paid in monthly, quartely or semi annual installments upto completion date.</p><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><p>Project completion period June 2027</p>'),(2530,'property',200,'zh','property_name','GRAND PREMIER'),(2531,'property',200,'zh','alternative_name','GRAND PREMIER LAVINGTON'),(2532,'property',200,'zh','detailed_address','Argwings Kodhek'),(2533,'property',200,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Grand Premier (Along Argwings Khodhek, Lavington): Complete Project</p><p>A luxurious two block apartment with 1,2 and 3Bdr with DSQ, all with modern Turkish finishes, fully fitted kitchen and smart home features.</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Other Amenities:</strong></p><p> Swimming pool</p><p> Ample parking</p><p> Solar water heaters</p><p> Fitted Gym</p><p> Multiple balconies</p><p> Rooftop lounge deck and Bbq area</p><p> Borehole</p><p> Electric fence</p><p> Full backup generator</p><p> 24Hr security</p><p> Supermarket</p><p> Café and Restaurant</p><p> Laundry Services</p><p> VIP Lounge</p><p> 4 High speed lifts</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom: 73.1SQM:&nbsp;KES 10M 8.5m</p><p>2 Bedroom: 139.8SQM:&nbsp;KES 17M</p><p>3 Bedroom plus DSQ: 183.1SQM:&nbsp;KES 24M</p><p>8 Bedroom penthouse: KES 89M</p><p> Few units left</p>'),(2534,'property',201,'zh','property_name','山谷拱廊别墅'),(2535,'property',201,'zh','alternative_name','VALLEY ARCADE VILLAS'),(2536,'property',201,'zh','detailed_address','山谷拱廊'),(2537,'property',201,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>VALLEY ARCADE VILLA</u></strong></p><p>The villas are located in valley arcade along othaya road&nbsp;just a walking distance to valley arcade&nbsp;shopping mall.</p><p>It includes 4 bedroom + dsq</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Luxurious reception</p><p>Rooftop view club</p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>Childrens play area and facilities</p><p>A