>•Professional Reception &amp; Management Office for seamless services</p><p>•Meeting Room for business and private discussions</p><p>•Barbecue Area for outdoor entertaining</p><p>•Gaming &amp; TV Room for leisure and recreation</p><p>•Dedicated Prayer Room for spiritual reflection</p><p>•Borehole with Filtration System for a reliable water supply</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Prime Location Benefits:</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;Strategically situated in <strong>Riverside Drive</strong>, Pavo Residence offers proximity to:</p><p><strong>Embassies &amp; Diplomatic Missions</strong> – Netherlands, Philippines, Germany, Japan</p><p><strong>Leading Educational Institutions</strong> – Strathmore University, Pink Towers, Montessori</p><p><strong>High-End Retail &amp; Dining Destinations</strong></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>&nbsp;Unit Types &amp; Pricing:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Studio Apartments (38 sqm)</strong> – Starting from <strong>$60,500</strong></li><li><strong>1-Bedroom Apartments (50–61 sqm)</strong> – Starting from <strong>$77,900</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Location:</strong> Riverside Drive, Nairobi</p><p><strong>Completion Date:</strong> December 2027</p>'),(2542,'property',203,'zh','property_name','米兰草地'),(2543,'property',203,'zh','alternative_name','MILAN MEADOWS'),(2544,'property',203,'zh','detailed_address','Kitengela'),(2545,'property',203,'zh','description','<p><strong><u> MILAN MEADOWS</u></strong></p><p>A gated community project that comprises of eight well-designed all-Ensuite 3 Bedroom plus DSQ bungalows each occupying a full 50 by100 plot.</p><p>It\'s located in Kitengela only 900 meters from tarmac within Muiga\'s estate.</p><p>Selling at an introductory price of 12.5M - slightly negotiable.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>&nbsp;Key Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>All Ensuite plus Dsq</p><p>Spacious lounge with large windows</p><p>American design kitchen with quartz countertops.</p><p>Fully fitted kitchen(hood, microwave, oven,cooker, breakfast table).</p><p>Solar water-heater system</p><p>Bio-digester system</p><p>Intercom</p><p>Sliding gates programmed with App operating system for residents</p><p>Solar lighting for common areas.</p><p>No service charge for residents.</p><p>Total of 8 units.</p><p>Controlled development area.</p><p>1000litre water tank for each unit.</p><p>Ample parking space</p><p>Spacious backyard for barbeque</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>Cash or Mortgage</p><p>✅Deposit/Down payment 10-20% balance through bank finance.</p><p>✅ Completion: June-2025.</p>'),(2546,'property',204,'zh','property_name','AJMAL TWIN TOWER'),(2547,'property',204,'zh','alternative_name','AJMAL TWIN TOWER'),(2548,'property',204,'zh','detailed_address','Othaya路， Kileleshwa'),(2549,'property',204,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Ajmal Twin Towers offers a premium living experience in the heart of Kileleshwa, Nairobi. Our modern 2, 3, 4, and 5-bedroom apartments are designed with comfort, style, and convenience in mind. Enjoy world-class amenities such as a fully-equipped gym, sauna, high-speed lifts, kids’ play area, backup power, ample parking, and more. Located close to schools, hospitals, malls, and with easy access to the CBD, Ajmal Twin Towers is the perfect place to call home. Book a viewing today and step into your dream home!</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Fully equiped gym</li><li>sauna</li><li>High speed lifts</li><li>Kids play area</li><li>Back-up generator</li><li>Swimming pool</li><li>4 level parking</li><li>Library</li><li>Borehole</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>2BR&nbsp;125 SQM&nbsp;$90000&nbsp;</p><p>3BR 200 SQM&nbsp;$170000</p><p>4BR 270 SQM&nbsp;$190000</p><p>5BR 313 SQM $238000</p>'),(2550,'property',205,'zh','property_name','ELITZ RESIDENCE'),(2551,'property',205,'zh','alternative_name','ELITZ RESIDENCE'),(2552,'property',205,'zh','detailed_address','南C'),(2553,'property',205,'zh','description','<h2><br></h2><p>Elitz Residency is a premium off-plan residential development offering thoughtfully designed 2, 3 &amp; 4-bedroom apartments, ideal for both homeowners and investors.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></p><p>Rooftop leisure area</p><p>High-speed elevators</p><p>Backup generator</p><p>Borehole and county water</p><p>Ample parking</p><p>24/7 security with cctv</p><p>Modern finishes and spacious</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom: From Ksh 9 Million</p><p>3 Bedroom with Dsq: From Ksh 14.5 Million</p><p>3 Bedroom without Dsq From Ksh 13Million</p><p>4 Bedroom with Dsq: From Ksh 16 Million</p><p>Cash Price 4 bedroom with Dsq – Ksh 13M till 27th July 2025</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment Plan:</strong></p><p>Flexible 3-Year Payment Plan</p><p>0% Interest</p>'),(2554,'property',206,'zh','property_name','黑斑羚棕榈'),(2555,'property',206,'zh','alternative_name','IMPALA PALMS'),(2556,'property',206,'zh','detailed_address','龍蓋'),(2557,'property',206,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Impala Palms is a modern residential development located in the serene Laiser Hill area of Rongai. Designed to offer comfort and functionality, it features spacious 2 and 3-bedroom apartments with contemporary interiors, including American-style open-plan kitchens, abundant natural light, and master ensuite bedrooms. The property boasts thoughtful amenities such as a gaming room, rooftop gym, children’s play area, and a walking path for relaxation. With a secure gated environment, ample parking, and proximity to key recreational, educational, and shopping facilities, Impala Palms is the perfect blend of urban convenience and tranquil living. Completion is set for September 2025.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><p>Well-Planned Interiors:</p><p>• American-Style Open-Plan Kitchen</p><p>• Spacious Living Rooms</p><p>• Master Bedroom Ensuite</p><p>• Dedicated Laundry Area</p><p>• Abundant Natural Light in All Rooms</p><p>• Fitted Wardrobes for Efficient Storage</p><p><br></p><p>Moments away from Impala Palms Rongai comes the following</p><ul><li>Top schools</li><li>Hospitals</li><li>Excellent road access</li><li>Shopping malls and restaurants</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong> Unit sizes and price:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>2 Bedroom: KSh 6.675M (Offer Price: KSh 5.95M)</li><li>• 3 Bedroom: KSh 7.75M</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Total Units: 102 Apartments</p>'),(2558,'property',207,'zh','property_name','ASDA居留'),(2559,'property',207,'zh','alternative_name','ASDA RESIDENCY'),(2560,'property',207,'zh','detailed_address','Parklands'),(2561,'property',207,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Asda residency 3RD Parklands, adjacent to doctors park</p><p><br></p><p>25 Floors:</p><p><br></p><p>1st to 4th Commercial Floors</p><p>5th to 25th Residential</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Commercial area: 10,000 KES/SQM</p><p>Asda Tower, an upcoming development that features tasteful finishes and bespoke interiors. 1,2,3 and 4 bedroom apartments designed for those who seek a peaceful way of life and where convenience and security are a top priority. Amenities: Ample parking Backup generator Borehole Kids play Area CCTV Surveillance cameras High Speed lifts ASDA Mosque Madarasa Super Market Gym (Man and Woman) High Speed internet 5 star Restaurant</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities Available:</strong></h3><p>•Master Ensuite</p><p>•Parking</p><p>•Servant Quarters (DSQ)</p><p>•Pets Allowed</p><p>•Open kitchen</p><p>•Backup Generator</p><p>•Elevator/ Lift</p><p>•Gym</p><p>•CCTV surveillance</p><p>•Borehole</p><p>•Restaurant</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1. 250 Sqm : 4Bedroom + DSQ - 18,100,000 Ksh</p><p>2. 200 Sqm :3 Bedroom + DSQ - 15,500,000 Ksh</p><p>3. 140 Sqm: 2 Bedroom - 9,600,000 Ksh</p><p>3. 90 Sqm : 1 Bedroom - 6,500,000 Ksh</p>'),(2562,'property',208,'zh','property_name','光线视图'),(2563,'property',208,'zh','alternative_name','RAYS VIEW'),(2564,'property',208,'zh','detailed_address','Parklands'),(2565,'property',208,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><br></p><p>introduction Discover Rays View, a stunning new development nestled in the heart of Parklands</p><p>along the prestigious 6th A venue. Where luxury meets location, Rays View is more than just a</p><p>residence - it\'s a lifestyle statement. With breathtaking views, elegant architecture, and unmatched</p><p>con­venience, this is your chance to own a piece of Nairobi\'s most sought-after neighborhood.</p><p>Whether you\'re looking for a new home or a high-potential investment, Rays View offers the perfect</p><p>blend of comfort, class, and connectivity. Don\'t just dream it-live it.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Amenities at Rays View:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>• Secure Parking</p><p>• Children\'s Play Area</p><p>• Balconies with Scenic Views</p><p>• Landscaped Garden Spaces</p><p>• Fire Safety Systems</p><p>• Fibre-Ready Internet Connection</p><p>• Rooftop Swimming Pool</p><p>• Rooftop Lounge &amp; Entertainment Area</p><p>• Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>• High-Speed Lifts</p><p>• Backup Generator</p><p>• Borehole Water Supply</p><p>• 24/7 Security &amp; CCTV Surveillance</p><p>• Intercom &amp; Access Control</p>'),(2566,'property',209,'zh','property_name','恩康公寓'),(2567,'property',209,'zh','detailed_address','昂路'),(2568,'property',209,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>ENKANG APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Enkang Apartments is a premier residential development project along Ngong Road. The project is located near the modern Talanta Stadium. Enkang continues to grow with the exciting progress of Phase 3. Following the successful completion and handover of Phase 1 in 2021 and Phase 2 in 2024, the construction of Phase 3 began in 2024. Designed to provide modern, community-oriented living spaces, this new phase is set to deliver spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments within a 14-floor complex. Ravi Homes is excited to share the latest milestones in the construction of Phase 3 and explain why this development remains a top choice for homebuyers and investors in Kenya’s real estate market.</p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>High speed WIFI connectivity</p><p>Reliable borehole water supply</p><p>Back up generator</p><p>Ample parking space</p><p>Modern , spacious lifts</p><p>Back up power generator</p><p>Code access security system at the main entrance</p><p><br></p><p><strong><u>Unit sizes and prices</u></strong></p><p><strong>1-Bedroom Unit</strong> (50SqM)- 5.5 Million</p><p><strong>2- Bedroom Unit </strong>( 85Sqm)-8.5 Million</p><p><strong>3-Bedroom Unit </strong>(105SqM)-10.5 Million</p>'),(2569,'property',210,'zh','property_name','檀香木公寓'),(2570,'property',210,'zh','alternative_name','SANDALWOOD APARTMENTS'),(2571,'property',210,'zh','detailed_address','Argwings kodhek, Hurlingham'),(2572,'property',210,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>SANDALWOOD APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p>Situated off Lenana Road near Yaya Centre, in a quiet, secure compound with easy access to shops, schools, hospitals, and transport corridors&nbsp;.</p><p>14‑storey development with modern finishes, efficient layouts, and strong appeal for long-term rentals and corporate stays&nbsp;.</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Full‑size pool</li><li>Jacuzzi</li><li>Gym/garden lounge area</li><li>Solar water heaters</li><li>Backup generator</li><li>Borehole supply</li><li>High-speed lifts</li><li>CCTV, electric fencing, 24/7 security</li><li>Inbuilt wardrobes</li><li>Private balconies</li><li>Kitchenette</li><li>Marble‑tiling</li></ul><p><strong> Unit Types &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>3‑Bedroom (with DSQ)</p><p>Approx. 135 sqm (1,458 ft²): Price from ~KES 13.0 million&nbsp;.</p><p>Also available to rent: ~KSh 140,000/month unfurnished (~USD 1,000 +), with features including air conditioning, solar water heating, inverter, 24‑hour electricity, hot water, built‑in wardrobes, swimming pool, backup generator and borehole water supply. This listing mentions the 3‑bed size as ~102 sqm, so there may be variation between units or blocks&nbsp;.</p><p>2‑Bedroom</p><p>Booking-type short-stay apartments with standard two-bedroom layout of ~120 sqm (1,292 ft²); typical night rates ~$79 (~KES 10,000+ per night) on travel platforms&nbsp;.</p><p>For sale pricing not explicitly listed for 2‑beds—but rental market context suggests 2‑beds in Kilimani often ask KSh 80k–120k/month unfurnished, with higher rates for furnished Airbnb options&nbsp;.</p><p>✅ Summary Table</p><ol><li>3‑Bedroom + DSQ ~135 sqm ~13.0 M ~140,000/month Sauna, pool, generator, borehole, solar water heating, inverter, AC units, parking, gardens&nbsp;</li><li>2‑Bedroom ~120 sqm (Not listed for sale) ~80,000–120,000/month (*) Kitchenette, balcony, flat-screen TV, patio, parking, AC, pool, generator</li></ol>'),(2573,'property',211,'zh','property_name','凤凰公园'),(2574,'property',211,'zh','alternative_name','PHENOM PARK'),(2575,'property',211,'zh','detailed_address','Lang \'ata'),(2576,'property',211,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>PHENOM PARK</u></strong></p><p>Phenom Park will have 10 unique clusters of 20-24 Townhouses, an Apartment Block and a Community Center with Club House. The clusters are set around the spine road which facilitates free flow of traffic within the estate.</p><h3><strong>Features:</strong></h3><ul><li>Access Gate</li><li>Backup generator</li><li>Banking Services</li><li>Basketball, Tennis and badminton court</li><li>Borehole</li><li>Children’s playgrounds</li><li>Jogging track</li><li>Ol Pejeta Conservancy</li><li>Outdoor yard</li><li>Resort</li><li>Rooftop Relaxing Gazebo</li><li>Scenic views of Mt. Kenya</li><li>Smart parking</li><li>Spa, Salon and Gym</li><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Top Notch Security</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Moments away from amazing key facilities:</p><p>Excellent roads</p><p>Best academic institutions</p><p>Shopping malls and chill spots</p><p>Top health facilities</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>4 Bedroom 217 sqm at Ksh 35,000,000</p>'),(2577,'property',212,'zh','property_name','滨海湾1号'),(2578,'property',212,'zh','alternative_name','MARINA BAY 1'),(2579,'property',212,'zh','detailed_address','Sports road, Westlands'),(2580,'property',212,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>MARINA BAY SQUARE</u></strong></p><p>MARINA BAY SQUARE is located in the heart of Westland, on the junction of David Oseli and Sports road. Just behind Park Inn by Radisson Blu. With proximity to commercial hubs, shopping malls, medical and education centers. The property is premium for both investors and residents. The development comprises of 2 blocks offering 1 and 2 bedrooms.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;Features:</strong></p><p>– Swimming pool and fully equipped gym</p><p>– Children’s play area</p><p>– Sauna room</p><p>– Restaurant Cafe</p><p>– Conference room</p><p>– Visitor reception and lobby</p><p>– Main power and full Back-up generator</p><p>– Water borehole</p><p>– 24-hour security with CCTV surveillance</p><p>– Four elevators</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom (67 sqm) – From Kshs 7.8M – 8.2M</p><p>1 Bedroom (70 sqm) – From Kshs 8M – 8.4M</p><p>2 Bedroom plus DSQ (130 sqm) – From Kshs 13.55M – 14.15M</p><p>2 Bedroom plus DSQ (135 sqm) – From Kshs 14.65M – 15.25M2 Bedroom plus DSQ (145 sqm) – From Kshs 15.55M – 16.15M</p><p>3 Bedroom plus DSQ (198 sqm) – From Kshs 21.25M – 22.25M</p><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><p>Occupation Dec 2026</p>'),(2581,'property',213,'zh','property_name','MARBLE WEST'),(2582,'property',213,'zh','alternative_name','MARBLE WEST'),(2583,'property',213,'zh','detailed_address','Mogotio路， Westlands'),(2584,'property',213,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Located on Muthithi Road, just a 5-minute walk to Sarit Centre, GTC Mall, and Westgate Mall, this property offers a perfect blend of modern living and convenience. Designed with luxury in mind, the units are ideal for homeowners or investors looking for prime urban real estate in a secure and accessible location.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul><li>Rooftop Infinity Swimming Pool</li><li>Fully Fitted Gym</li><li>Sky Lounge &amp; Barbecue Area</li><li>Sauna &amp; Yoga Studio</li><li>Executive Rooftop Restaurant</li><li>Landscaped Zen Garden</li><li>Borehole Water Supply</li><li>Full Backup Generator</li><li>High-Speed Lifts</li><li>CCTV &amp; Biometric Security</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Furnished Studio</strong> (45sqm): From KSh 6.6M</li><li><strong>One Bedroom</strong> (64sqm): From KSh 7.85M</li><li><strong>Two Bedroom</strong> (97-130sqm): From KSh 10.95M</li></ul><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><ul><li>10% deposit balance within 3 years with 0% Interest.</li></ul><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><ul><li>Project estimated completion December 2027</li></ul>'),(2585,'property',214,'zh','property_name','国王庭院'),(2586,'property',214,'zh','alternative_name','KINGS COURTYARD'),(2587,'property',214,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani, Lenana rd.'),(2588,'property',214,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Situated along Lenana Road in the Kilimani neighborhood of Westlands Sub‑county, about 5 km west of Nairobi’s CBD&nbsp;.</p><p>Easily accessible — just 5 minutes from Kilimani Police Station, 10 minutes to the city center, and 8 minutes from Nairobi Arboretum&nbsp;.</p><p>Close to Yaya Centre, cafés, schools, hospitals, embassies, and banks&nbsp;.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></p><p>Kings Courtyard offers a host of upscale features geared toward comfortable and modern urban living:</p><ul><li>Recreational &amp; Community Facilities: Rooftop leisure pool, fitness &amp; recreation centre, children’s play area, community hall&nbsp;.</li><li>Security &amp; Access: Secured boundary walls, controlled entry/exit with automatic barriers, CCTV coverage of key areas, high‑speed elevators in each block&nbsp;.</li><li>Utilities: Backup generator for common areas, solar lighting in shared spaces, borehole water supply, inverter backup capability, anti‑termite foundation, cabro‑paved driveways&nbsp;.</li><li>Apartment Interiors: All bedrooms ensuite, branded bathroom fittings, designer sanitary ware, provision for gas cylinder in kitchen yard, TV points, fibre/Wi‑Fi readiness, balconies offering views&nbsp;.</li><li><br></li></ul><p><strong> Unit Types &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>Unit Type Size Price (KES)</p><p>2 Bedroom (all ensuite) ~102 m² (1,100 ft²) ~13.5M (SOLD OUT)&nbsp;</p><p>3 Bedroom (all ensuite) ~162 – 163 m² (1,750 ft²) From ~18.5–19.5M</p><p>2 bed units priced around KES 13.5M — quickly sold out.</p><p>3 bed units start around KES 19.5M, with some listings showing KES 18M (depending on size and timing)&nbsp;.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><p>Developed by Kings Developers Limited, this is a deluxe‑grade residential tower expected for completion between Q3 2025 and December 2027&nbsp;.</p>'),(2589,'property',215,'zh','property_name','MONTEBLUE'),(2590,'property',215,'zh','alternative_name','MONTEBLUE'),(2591,'property',215,'zh','detailed_address','Muthithi路， Westlands'),(2592,'property',215,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Montbleu Apartments offer luxury 1 &amp; 2 bedroom residences in the heart of Westlands, blending modern elegance with hotel-style amenities. Ideal for both living and investment, these stylish apartments feature a rooftop pool, gym, clubhouse, and more. Prices start from KSh 6.75M for 1-bedroom units and KSh 11.85M for 2-bedroom units. With flexible payment plans and a construction timeline from November 2024 to November 2027, Montbleu is your perfect urban retreat.</p><p><br></p><p>Unit Details &amp; Pricing:</p><p><br></p><p><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><p>• Standard: 60 sqm – From KSh 6.75M</p><p>• Premium: 61 sqm – KSh 6.95M</p><p><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><p>• Standard: 104 sqm – KSh 11.85M</p><p>• Premium: 116 sqm – From KSh 12.95M</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Hotel-Style Amenities</strong>:</p><p>• Rooftop Swimming Pool</p><p>• Social Clubhouse</p><p>• Rooftop Fully Fitted Gym</p><p>• Reception Lobby</p><p>• Sky Lounge</p><p>• Conference Room</p><p>• Children’s Play Area</p><p>• Spa &amp; Salon Space</p><p>• Restaurant Cafe</p><p>• Mini Mart</p><p>• Four High-Speed Lifts</p><p>• Fully Backup Generator</p><p><strong>Security &amp; Convenience</strong>:</p><p>• CCTV Surveillance</p><p>• Electric Fence</p><p>• Internet Connectivity</p><p>• Borehole Water Supply</p><p>• Ample Parking</p><p>• Solar Water-Heating System</p><p><strong>Payment Plans:</strong></p><p><strong>Cash Installment Buyer</strong>:</p><p>• 10% booking fee</p><p>• 10% upon signing of sales agreement</p><p>• 75% over construction period</p><p>• 5% on completion</p><p><strong>Mortgage Buyer:</strong></p><p>• 10% booking fee</p><p>• 20% upon signing of sales agreement</p><p>• 70% on completion through mortgage</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Construction Timeline:</strong></p><p>• Start: November 2024</p><p>• Completion: November 2027 (36 months)</p>'),(2593,'property',216,'zh','property_name','KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE'),(2594,'property',216,'zh','alternative_name','KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE'),(2595,'property',216,'zh','detailed_address','Kitisuru'),(2596,'property',216,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>KITISURU FALLS RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Welcome to&nbsp;<strong>Kitisuru Falls Residence (KFR)</strong>&nbsp;– an ultra-modern gated community nestled in the serene neighborhood of Kibichiku, right next to the prestigious New Kitisuru suburb. Overlooking the scenic&nbsp;<strong>Getathuru Falls</strong>, this development is designed to combine contemporary architecture with nature, offering a peaceful yet well-connected lifestyle.</p><p><br></p><h4><br></h4><h4><strong>Apartment Features</strong></h4><p><br></p><ul><li>Spacious open-plan kitchens with granite tops &amp; MDF cabinetry</li><li>