 estate markets, a new icon of luxury living has emerged. <strong>Kings Apollo Towers</strong> is a landmark development by <strong>Kings Developers</strong> offering a unique, all-inclusive lifestyle. For those seeking an effortless transition into a world of elegance and convenience, these fully furnished 3-bedroom apartments represent the pinnacle of modern urban living.</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Fully furnished apartments, all en-suite</p><p>Jogging track encircling the building</p><p>Heated swimming pool with changing rooms</p><p>Gym and sauna</p><p>Kids play area</p><p>Multi-purpose community hall</p><p>Theatre room</p><p>Video intercom system for security</p><p>High-speed elevators with elegant finishes</p><p>Grand entrance lobby and gate</p><p>Generator backup for the entire building</p><p>Borehole water supply and solar water heating</p><p>Firefighting system in common areas</p><p>Security cabin and visitor parking</p><p>Management office onsite</p><p>Designer suspended finishes: anti-skid balcony tiles, UPVC windows, concealed wiring</p><p>Modular kitchens with branded appliances</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes&nbsp;and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Unit Size ~242–255 m² (~2,600 ft²)</p><p>Bedrooms / Bathrooms 3-bedrooms, all en suite (plus DSQ)</p><p>Furnishing Fully furnished with Grade A decor</p><p>Kitchen Modular design, branded appliances</p><p>Price Range (estimated) KSh 28 M – KSh 30 M per unit</p>'),(2680,'property',238,'zh','property_name','白羊座住宅'),(2681,'property',238,'zh','alternative_name','ARIES RESIDENCE'),(2682,'property',238,'zh','detailed_address','Sabaki ， Signature商场后面'),(2683,'property',238,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Modern Apartments Apartments For Sale In Sabaki, Off Mombasa Road&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>This is a gated development comprising various high end apartment types for sale. Aries Residences is located in Sabaki, Mavoko behind Signature Mall and near Tamarind Meadows, Sunshine Gardens Estate, Total Petrol Station and Mombasa Road Expressway Mlolongo toll station</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Residence Amenities:</strong></p><p>Club house</p><p>Gym</p><p>Swimming pool</p><p>Kids play area</p><p>Community shop</p><p>Intercom system in house</p><p>water purifier system installed for safe drinking water</p><p>24hr security system</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Aries residence is in close proximity to :</strong></p><ul><li>Top schools</li><li>Hospitals</li><li>Shopping malls and restaurants</li><li>Excellent road access</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ol><li>3 Br + Dsq 139 Sqm @ 9.7M</li><li>3Br&nbsp;119 Sqm&nbsp;@ 8M</li><li>2Br&nbsp;99 Sqm&nbsp;@ 6.9M</li><li>2Br&nbsp;90 Sqm @ 6.5M</li><li>1Br&nbsp;61 Sqm @ 5.5M</li><li>Studio&nbsp;27 Sqm @ 3M</li></ol>'),(2684,'property',239,'zh','property_name','复古住宅'),(2685,'property',239,'zh','alternative_name','VINTAGE RESIDENCE'),(2686,'property',239,'zh','detailed_address','ngong路附近的赛马场'),(2687,'property',239,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Located off Ngong Road in Riruta, just minutes from major amenities like Junction Mall, Karen Hospital, and Lenana School .</p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></p><p>All sources highlight an impressive range of amenities for this development:</p><p>Balcony attached to a spacious lounge</p><p>Green landscaped areas and kids’ play zone</p><p>One designated parking slot per unit</p><p>Three high-speed elevators</p><p>Generator backup for common areas, with inverter provision per unit</p><p>Borehole water supply; anti-termite foundation</p><p>Cabro-paved driveways</p><p>Secured boundary wall, controlled access with automatic entry/exit barriers</p><p>CCTV surveillance; solar lights in common areas</p><p>Designer sanitary fittings, branded bath accessories</p><p>Wi-Fi and TV point provisions</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>Price: KSh 9.5 million for each 2‑bedroom, master‑ensuite unit</p><p>2-Bedroom, master ensuite apartments: approximately 950 sq ft (around 84 m²), priced at KSh 9.5 million .</p><p>Summary: Expect 2-bedroom units from roughly KSh 9M to KSh 9.5M, spanning 84–95 m²</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Completion date:</strong></p><p>Q4 2026</p>'),(2688,'property',240,'zh','property_name','LE MIRAGE'),(2689,'property',240,'zh','alternative_name','LE MIRAGE'),(2690,'property',240,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(2691,'property',240,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Le Mirage offers an exceptional lifestyle that combines modern comfort with an unparalleled location. Located in a vibrant neighborhood, you’ll have convenient access to dining, entertainment, shopping, and cultural hotspots. This prime location places you within reach of everything you need while providing a serene haven to call home.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Spacious and contemporary living spaces</li><li>Spectacular views from private balconies</li><li>Heated rooftop infinity swimming pool</li><li>State-of-the-art gym</li><li>Relaxation area with panoramic city views</li><li>Lush rooftop garden</li><li>Children’s play area</li><li>Barbecue facilities</li><li>Badminton and squash courts</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Property sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>1 BR 70.6SQM- 10.9M-11.1M(SOLD OUT)</p><p>1 BR 74.3SQM - 11.45M-11.65M(SOLD OUT)</p><p>2 BR 125.6SQM - 19.05M-21.85M</p><p>2 BR 134.9SQM - 19.85M-23.1M</p><p>3 BR +SQ&nbsp;207SQM -30.4M-34.6M</p><p>3 BR 210SQM&nbsp;-35M</p><p>3 BR 265.8SQM -44.35M</p><p>3 BR Duplex&nbsp;-65M</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(2692,'property',241,'zh','property_name','安庐居'),(2693,'property',241,'zh','alternative_name','SERENITY RESIDENCE'),(2694,'property',241,'zh','detailed_address','龍蓋'),(2695,'property',241,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Kings Serenity will feature a total of 720 two-bedroom apartments. Each apartment is designed with cross-ventilation, a well-planned layout, and a compact design. The apartments include a lounge cum dining area, a kitchen with a dry yard, separate toilet and shower, and two bedrooms. These apartments won\'t come fully furnished, giving you the freedom to customize them to your liking.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>In-Unit Features</p><p>Compact and efficient design with:</p><p>Lounge-cum-dining area</p><p>Modern kitchen with dry yard</p><p>Separate shower and toilet</p><p>Two bedrooms (each with built-in wardrobes)</p><p><strong>Community Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Lush green spaces and landscaped gardens throughout</li><li>Security via masonry boundary wall, controlled access, and security checkpoints</li><li>Parking: One parking slot per apartment and additional visitor spaces</li><li>Solar street lighting for energy-efficient illumination</li><li>Water security through a borehole and overhead storage tank</li><li>Cabro-paved driveways for better accessibility and aesthetics</li><li>Children’s play area and community hall for social events</li></ul><p><strong>Unit Sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom 84 sqm at Ksh&nbsp;4,000,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Location Advantages:</strong></p><p>Located within Rongai town, offering convenient access to many facilities</p><p>Masai Mall: 700–800 meters away</p><p>Highway access: Just 300–500 meters from the main road</p><p>Near reputable schools, institutions (e.g., NIBS, Multimedia University), shopping centers (Karen Galleria, Maasai Centre), banks, fuel stations, and public transport routes</p>'),(2696,'property',242,'zh','property_name','G.T.C RESIDENCE'),(2697,'property',242,'zh','alternative_name','G.T.C RESIDENCE'),(2698,'property',242,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(2699,'property',242,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><br></p><p>The GTC Centre stands as a transformative mixed-use development, destined to redefine Nairobi\'s skyline.</p><p>Crafted to offer a serene residence and an inspiring workspace for corporate elites, the GTC Centre boasts distinguished volumes with top-notch finishes, exuding opulence and elegance.</p><p>The residential segment comprises four towers, featuring one-bedroom, two-bedroom, three-bedroom, and four-bedroom penthouses atop each tower. Rising between 28 and 31 floors above ground, the apartments provide breath-taking views of Nairobi\'s Central Business District.</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p>Pools for adults and children</p><p>Leisure gathering lawns</p><p>Children’s Art Playground</p><p>Jogging Loop</p><p>Sky private club</p><p>State-of-the-art Gym</p><p>SPA</p><p>Hair &amp; nail salon</p><p>Café</p><p>Mini-cinema</p><p>Boutique Mall</p><p>Card access system</p><p>24 Hour CCTV</p><p>Intrusion Alarm system</p><p>Connected Parking solution</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>One Bedroom ( 82sqm)&nbsp;– From Ksh. 28340000</p><p>Two Bedroom (105-110sqm) - From Ksh. 36400000</p><p>Three Bedroom (137sqm-175sqm) - From Ksh.45,500000</p>'),(2700,'property',243,'zh','property_name','GITANGA DUPLEXES'),(2701,'property',243,'zh','detailed_address','Gitanga Road, Lavington'),(2702,'property',243,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>GITANGA DUPLEXES</u></strong></p><p>Gitanga Duplexes (Lavington, off Gitanga Road):</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Heated swimming pool &amp; fully equipped gym</p><p>Solar water heating, borehole, and backup generator</p><p>High-speed lifts, 24/7 security, CCTV &amp; intercom</p><p>2-car parking per unit</p><p>Landscaped gardens, cabro driveways, underground tanks</p><p>Smart cabling: internet/fiber, TV, intercom Prices ready</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Price:</strong></p><p>KES 33M – 43M</p><p>Depends on unit type, size, floor level, and view.</p><p>Mortgage payment plans available with some agents.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>Type 1: 248 m² – 4 bedrooms all en-suite + DSQ + 1 lounge</p><p>Type 2: 267 m² – 4 bedrooms all en-suite + DSQ + 2 lounges</p><p>Both are duplex layouts (2 floors) with private balconies and laundry areas</p>'),(2703,'property',244,'zh','property_name','MARINA BAY 2'),(2704,'property',244,'zh','alternative_name','MARINA BAY 2'),(2705,'property',244,'zh','detailed_address','Sports road, Westlands'),(2706,'property',244,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Marina Bay Phase II exclusively boasts of eye-catching and compelling view of the whole</p><p>Westlands, Karura Forest ,Nairobi’s alluring architecture and infrastructure. Just 8 minutes</p><p>drive access to the NCBD and 15 minutes drive to Kenya’s Main Airport, JKIA via the</p><p>Express way. This is also complemented with close proximity to various high end</p><p>social amenities including major shopping malls, best schools, hospitals, religious centers</p><p>and uptown recreational sport.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Resident Amenities:</strong></p><p>Rooftop Swimming Pool</p><p>Rooftop Fully Fitted Gym</p><p>Sky Lounge</p><p>Children’s Playing Area</p><p>Conference Room</p><p>Mini Mart</p><p>Restaurant Cafe</p><p>Social Club House</p><p>Reception Lobby</p><p>Four High-Speed Lifts</p><p>Borehole Water Supply</p><p>Solar Water-Heating system</p><p>Fully Back-up Generator</p><p>CCTV Surveillance</p><p>Electric Fence</p><p>Internet Conectivity</p><p>Video Intercom</p><p>Ample Parking</p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><ul><li>1Bedroom 67SQM&nbsp;From Ksh 9Million</li><li>1Bedroom&nbsp;70SQM From Ksh 9.2Million</li><li>2Bedrooms&nbsp;130SQM From Ksh 14.4Million</li><li>2Bedrooms&nbsp;135SQM From Ksh 15.1Million</li><li>2 Bedrooms 145SQM&nbsp;with&nbsp;DSQ&nbsp;From Ksh 16.75Million</li></ul><p>3 Bedrooms 198SQM with DSQ&nbsp;From Ksh. 22.55Million</p><p>Payment plan:</p><p>24 months with 0% interest</p><p>Cash Installment Buyer: 10% Deposit fee,10% on signing the sales agreement,75% spread over construction</p><p>period within 30 months, 5% on completion.&nbsp;</p><p>Mortgage Buyer: 30% Deposit,70% by Financing Bank of your choice.</p><p><strong>CONSTRUCTION PROGRESS:</strong> Construction has commenced from November 2023,with an estimated</p><p>construction period of 36 months. Expected completion date end of December 2026</p>'),(2707,'property',245,'zh','property_name','MANTAZ PLAZA'),(2708,'property',245,'zh','alternative_name','MANTAZ PLAZA'),(2709,'property',245,'zh','detailed_address','Rose Avenue, Kilimani'),(2710,'property',245,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>MANTAZ PLAZA</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Mantaz Plaza is a modern residential development situated just ~300 m from Yaya Centre, at the intersection of Cotton Avenue and Rose Avenue in Kilimani–Hurlingham, Nairobi .</p><p>The plaza offers upscale 1- and 2-bedroom apartments with spacious layouts, balconies, kitchens, and high-end finishes .</p><p><strong>Key Amenities :</strong></p><p>High-Speed Lifts – Swift vertical movement across floors for resident convenience.</p><p>Borehole Water Supply – Reliable source of water regardless of municipal supply interruptions.</p><p>Children\'s Playground – Safe, dedicated recreation area for little ones.</p><p>Ample Parking – Designated parking for both residents and visitors.</p><p>Backup Generator – Ensures uninterrupted power during outages.</p><p>CCTV &amp; 24/7 Security – Round-the-clock monitoring and access control for peace of mind.</p><p>Social Hall &amp; Rooftop Garden – Communal spaces for socializing, events, and relaxation.</p><p>Modern Finishes – Stylish interiors and high-quality materials throughout the building.</p><p>Close Proximity to Shopping &amp; Dining – Just meters from Yaya Centre, and near Prestige Plaza, Java House, Art Café, Junction Mall, Nairobi Hospital, Aga Khan Clinic, and more.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><ol><li>1 Bedroom Deluxe&nbsp;53 sqm 6 million – 7 million</li><li>1 Bedroom Executive / Premium 55‑64 sqm&nbsp;6.5 million – 7.5 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Compact&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;86 sqm 9 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Standard&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;92 sqm&nbsp;9.5 million – 10 million</li><li>2 Bedroom Deluxe&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;95 sqm&nbsp;10 million – 11 million</li></ol>'),(2715,'property',247,'zh','property_name','GICHUGU公寓'),(2716,'property',247,'zh','alternative_name','GICHUGU APARTMENTS'),(2717,'property',247,'zh','detailed_address','Gichugu Rd, Kileleshwa'),(2718,'property',247,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Gichugu Apartments is situated off Gichungu (Durham) Road in Kileleshwa—a leafy, upscale neighbourhood about 5 km west of Nairobi’s CBD .</p><p><strong> Features:</strong></p><p>Ensuite bedrooms, modern kitchens with pantries, balconies/verandahs, laundry areas, AC, laminated/tiled floors.</p><p>Security &amp; Utilities 24-hour security, electric fencing, boundary walls, backup generators (in some), fibre internet, piped water with backup tanks.</p><p>Community Amenities Swimming pools, gym, play areas, gardens, lift/elevators, gated compounds.</p><p>Lifestyle Enhancements Boreholes, solar water heating, walk-in closets, BBQ areas, wheelchair access.</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li>2bedroom plus SQ at 13.5M</li><li>3 bedrooms from 15.5M-16.5M</li><li>3 bedrooms plus SQ at&nbsp;18.5M</li></ul><p><strong>Payment plan :</strong></p><p>20% deposit .</p><p>30% after 6-8 month , balance 50% upon completion.</p><p>Showroom ready.layout size and fittings very clear</p><p><br></p>'),(2719,'property',248,'zh','property_name','GATEWAY PARK SYOKIMAU'),(2720,'property',248,'zh','alternative_name','GATEWAY PARK SYOKIMAU'),(2721,'property',248,'zh','detailed_address','Mwananchi路， Syokimau'),(2722,'property',248,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Gateway park is a&nbsp;512 residential units, spread across 8 blocks, each with 8 floors, developed in 2 phases on a ~5-acre site&nbsp;.Phase 1 began ground works in October 2018&nbsp;.Close to key infrastructure: Gateway Mall, SGR Terminus, Jomo Kenyatta International Airport, and major bypasses&nbsp;.<