om</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1 Bedroom&nbsp;58 Sqm from&nbsp;Ksh 8.12M</p><p>1 Bedroom 84 Sqm from Ksh 10.92M- <strong>sold out</strong></p><p>2 Bedroom 105 Sqm from Ksh 14.175M</p><p>3 Bedroom 150 Sqm from Ksh 19.5M</p><p><br></p><p><strong>completion date&nbsp;&nbsp;Q3 2027</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Contact us today:</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(2796,'property',269,'zh','property_name','希拉尔居住地'),(2797,'property',269,'zh','alternative_name','HILAL RESIDENCY'),(2798,'property',269,'zh','detailed_address','Parklands第三大道， Krishna广场对面。'),(2799,'property',269,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>HILAL RESIDENCY</u></strong></p><p>Hilal apartment is a lifestyle development that combines the best of contemporary design with artfully furnished interiors. Indulgent luxury abounds throughout, from the fully fitted modern kitchen to the spacious bedroom suites complete with full height windows that bathe the rooms in natural light, to the stunning en-suite bathrooms.</p><p>This signature development is strategically located on 3rd Parklands Avenue, only 3km away from Nairobi’s CBD, with easy road connectivity to its environs.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Luxurious 5-bedroom duplex apartments</p><p>Well-appointed en-suite master bedroom with walk-in closet</p><p>En suite bedrooms with spacious wardrobe storage</p><p>Spacious fully fitted kitchen with veneered cabinets</p><p>Externally accessed DSQ</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Underground and Ground Level Parking allowing 2 dedicated two parking spaces for each unit</li><li>4 High-speed elevators</li><li>Manned gatehouse with 24-hour security</li><li>Borehole</li><li>Generator</li><li>CCTV cameras</li><li>Electric fence</li></ul><p>The apartment is situated ideally a stone throw away from amenities such as Diamond Plaza I &amp; II, Parklands Mosque, The Aga khan University Hospital, MP Shah Hospital, and 2 kilometers to the UN Headquarters, Gigiri.</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>5 Bedroom duplex plus DSQ 265 sqm Ksh 30,000,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Apartment Payment plan;</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Cash installment = 30% Deposit and Balance on occupation</p>'),(2800,'property',270,'zh','property_name','CHALBI DRIVE VILLA'),(2801,'property',270,'zh','alternative_name','CHALBI DRIVE VILLA'),(2802,'property',270,'zh','detailed_address','Chalbi drive, Lavington'),(2803,'property',270,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>CHALBI DRIVE VILLA</u></strong></p><p>A boutique enclave of luxury 5‑bedroom villas&nbsp;</p><p>Property Layout: Typically 3‑storey villas (~550 sqm) with 5 ensuite bedrooms, staff quarters (DSQ), rooftop terrace, modern open-plan kitchen, and garden or outdoor living space</p><p>4-bedroom townhouses starting around KES 65 million, and 5-bedroom villas in gated Chalbi Drive developments from KES 75–85 million and above&nbsp;</p><p>A comparable 4‑bed townhouse with high-end finishes and backup generator is listed at KES 65M, while another 4‑bed townhouse listing is at KES 75M</p><p><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></p><p>Design and Layout: Spacious modern villas, rooftop terraces, lush gardens, staff quarters, dedicated parking and gardens&nbsp;</p><p>Security &amp; Utilities: Gated community with 24‑hour security, CCTV, electric fencing, backup generator, borehole or mains water connection&nbsp;</p><p>Location &amp; Surroundings: Within walking or short drive to Lavington Mall, schools, embassies and diplomatic zone; serene, leafy setting ideal for professionals and families</p>'),(2804,'property',271,'zh','property_name','SYOKIMAU 5卧室MANSIONATTE'),(2805,'property',271,'zh','alternative_name','SYOKIMAU 5 BEDROOM MANSIONATTE'),(2806,'property',271,'zh','detailed_address','Syokimau, Katani路'),(2807,'property',271,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Welcome to your perfect sanctuary in the heart of Syokimau al