-purpose hall</p><p>Barbeque area</p><p>Leisure Park with a water pan/dam</p><p>Jogging track within the wider Two Rivers</p><p>A sports recreation center with a 7-aside soccer pitch, tennis court, basketball and a children play area</p><p>Well elaborate security comprising of CCTV cameras on each floor, access control to every apartment, video door intercom and armed security within the wider Two Rivers development</p><p>Smart home provision</p><p>Reticulated LPG gas to the kitchen</p><p>Fiber Optic cable to every apartment for internet, DSTV and Telephone</p><p><br></p><p><strong><u>Unit sizes and prices</u></strong></p><ul><li>1Bedroom Ensuite 17.4M 87sqm</li><li>2Bedrooms Ensuite 25.6M 130sqm</li><li>3Bedrooms Ensuite ksh 37M 185 sqm</li></ul>'),(2819,'property',275,'zh','property_name','三叉戟公园二期'),(2820,'property',275,'zh','detailed_address','Lang \'ata'),(2821,'property',275,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>TRIDENT PARK PHASE 2</u></strong></p><p>The 3-bedroom units at Trident Park Langata Phase 2 are priced at Ksh 18,000,000. For cash buyers, there\'s a discounted price of Ksh 17,500,000. These prices are for apartments with an en-suite master bedroom and include features like a spacious lounge and dining area, open-plan kitchen, and in-built appliances</p><p><strong>&nbsp;Features:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Master Bedroom: </strong>En-suite</li><li><strong>Spacious Living Area: </strong>Lounge and dining area</li><li><strong>Open Plan Kitchen: </strong>Fully fitted with cooker, oven, and hood</li><li><strong>Security: </strong>Intercom, CCTV surveillance, and 24/7 security</li><li><strong>Other Amenities: </strong>Elevator in each block, generator, ample parking, and a perimeter wall with an electric fence</li><li><strong>Community: </strong>Gated community</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Unit size and price:</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;3 Bedroom&nbsp;164 sqm at </strong>Ksh 18,000,000 (Ksh 17,500,000 for cash buyers)</p><p><strong>&nbsp;Payment Plan:</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>A 9-month payment plan is available.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><ul><li><br></li></ul>'),(2822,'property',276,'zh','property_name','两条河流复式公寓'),(2823,'property',276,'zh','alternative_name','TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES'),(2824,'property',276,'zh','detailed_address','Gigiri'),(2825,'property',276,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES</u></strong></p><p>Modern 3 Bedroom Duplexes with DSQ in Two Rivers Nairobi.</p><p>This project is located in the Diplomatic Blue Zone of Nairobi, Two Rivers.</p><p>making it easy access to key urban nodes such as Westlands, Parklands,</p><p>Nairobi CBD and Upper hill.</p><p>This accessibility is assured with its</p><p>strategic location between the Northern Bypass and Limuru Road</p><p>It comprises of exquisite 3-bedroom duplexes with Dsq.</p><p>Each unit is set on two levels offering luxurious, exquisite and spacious</p><p>lifestyles.</p><p>This project sits on 3.86 acres of a gated community &amp; comprises of</p><p>7 detached blocks. Each block is made up of 8 duplexes.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>AMENITIES:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•Swimming pool</p><p>•Wheel Chair Access</p><p>•Jogging Track</p><p>•Club house</p><p>•Reliable power and generator back-up</p><p>•Lifts and a staircase</p><p>•Fully equipped Gym</p><p>•Sports district</p><p>•100% reliable water supply from Two Rivers Water Company</p><p>•Solar water heating for all units</p><p>•Reticulated gas for all units</p><p>•Fiber optic link to digital telephone exchange, DSTV and internet provision</p><p>•Security Intercom, CCTV, smart homes features, access control</p><p>•Internet-5G ready</p>'),(2826,'property',277,'zh','property_name','自由高地'),(2827,'property',277,'zh','detailed_address','Lang \'ata'),(2828,'property',277,'zh','description','<p><br></p><h2><strong><u>FREEDOM HEIGHTS</u></strong></h2><p>Freedom Heights Mixed Use development is located right next to Wilson Airport in Lang’ata and is directly opposite Uhuru Gardens. The development comprises of a shopping mall, residences, and a service plot. The residents can live, work, shop, and play without commuting. All the need to do is to walk down the block.</p><p>The service plot supplies power, piped gas, fresh water, and recycled water to the mall and residences.</p><p>The residences comprises of 2-, 3- and 4-Bedroom apartments.</p><p><strong>Special amenities in the development include:</strong></p><p>6 Years SERVICE CHARGE FREE PERIOD in the residences</p><p>Common Gas supply to each unit for cooking</p><p>• Covered and open parking spaces</p><p>• High speed lifts in each block</p><p>• Solar water heating System</p><p>• Full backup Generator in both the internal areas of the apartments and the common areas</p><p>• Children’s Play area</p><p>• CCTV surveillance and manned security</p><p>• GYM within the shopping mall among other amenities.</p><p>• Bore hole water supply and adequate water storage system.</p><p>• On site management office.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>The apartments are sold through three modes of payment, Cash, Mortgage and Tenant Purchase Model.</p><p>• 4 Bedroom – Kshs. 17.1 Million</p><p>• 3 Bedroom – Kshs. 14.2 Million</p><p>• 2 Bedroom – Kshs. 11.4 Million</p>'),(2829,'property',278,'zh','property_name','Loft住宅'),(2830,'property',278,'zh','alternative_name','THE LOFT RESIDENCIES'),(2831,'property',278,'zh','detailed_address','Gigiri'),(2832,'property',278,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>THE LOFT RESIDENCIES</u></strong></p><p>Modern 4 Bedroom Duplexes with DSQ in Two Rivers Nairobi.</p><p>This project is located in the Diplomatic Blue Zone of Nairobi, Two Rivers.</p><p>making it easy access to key urban nodes such as Westlands, Parklands,</p><p>Nairobi CBD and Upper hill.</p><p>This accessibility is assured with its</p><p>strategic location between the Northern Bypass and Limuru Road</p><p>It comprises of exquisite 4-bedroom duplexes with Dsq.</p><p>Each unit is set on two levels offering luxurious, exquisite and spacious</p><p>lifestyles.</p><p>This project sits on 3.86 acres of a gated community &amp; comprises of</p><p>7 detached blocks. Each block is made up of 8 duplexes.</p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Wheel chair access</li><li>•Jogging Track</li><li>•Club house</li><li>•Reliable power and generator back-up</li><li>•Lifts and a staircase</li><li>•Fully equipped Gym</li><li>•Sports district</li><li>•100% reliable water supply from Two Rivers Water Company</li><li>•Solar water heating for all units</li><li>•Reticulated gas for all units</li><li>•Fiber optic link to digital telephone exchange, DSTV and internet provision</li><li>•Security Intercom, CCTV, smart homes features, access control</li><li>•Internet-5G ready</li></ul><p><strong>Unit size and prize:</strong></p><p>4 Bedrooms 280 sqm 55,000,000</p>'),(2833,'property',279,'zh','property_name','265 ELMER ONE公寓'),(2834,'property',279,'zh','alternative_name','265 ELMER ONE APARTMENTS'),(2835,'property',279,'zh','detailed_address','内罗毕Kasarani Mwiki路'),(2836,'property',279,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>265 ELMER ONE APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>265 Elmer One Apartments, offers you an excellent opportunity to diversify your investment portfolio into Real Estate and earn a minimum return of 20-25% over a 2 year period ( based on standard unit prices and secondary market price point) and thereafter secure recurrent rental income of up to 7.5% yield. The project is located next to Stardom Hotel in Kasarani. Kasarani is the second most populated constituency in Nairobi (with approximately 708,000 residents) hence very high demand for rental units. ​265 Elmer One will be a differentiated high quality product compared to the existing stock in the area making it highly competitive in the rental market ; resulting to high and sustainable occupancy in the development. Available for sale are Studios , 1 bedroom, 1 bedroom loft and 2 bedroom apartments.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features and amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>A gated community with perimeter fencing, internet provision, CCTV surveillance, and manned security.</li><li>Upgraded internal drainage system, coordinated landscaping for greenery, 24/7 clean, potable water supply, and backup power for all common areas in the development.</li><li>Mobility-friendly development with wheelchair access and a combination of lifts and staircases.</li><li>Ample parking spaces for residents and visitors.</li><li>Rooftop lounge/garden for entertainment, mini soccer pitch and tennis court.</li><li>Harmonized interior design for easy living and maximum indoor comfort.</li><li>Unique premium house typologies, unparalleled in the affordable housing market segment e.g. executive studio and 1 bed loft apartment.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p><br></p><ol><li>Studio 21 sqm&nbsp;at Ksh 2,500,000</li><li>1 Bedroom 60 sqm&nbsp;Ksh 4,950,000</li><li>2 Bedrooms 76 sqm Ksh 6,600,000</li></ol><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><h1><strong>10% Deposit </strong> followed by flexible period to complete the payment</h1><h1>Total Units: <strong>265 </strong></h1>'),(2837,'property',280,'zh','property_name','26套MZIZI COURT公寓'),(2838,'property',280,'zh','alternative_name','26 MZIZI COURT APARTMENTS'),(2839,'property',280,'zh','detailed_address','Gigiri'),(2840,'property',280,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>26 MZIZI COURT</u></strong></p><p>The homes are located within a prime and sought- after gated community designed to satisfy your family lifestyle, and leisure needs. The estate provides quieter pockets of green parks, beautifully landscaped outdoor spaces, and a wide range of outdoor facilities. This distinguishes 26 Mzizi court and makes it a residential estate of choice for many of Nairobi residents.</p><p>Modular Courtyard Approach?</p><p>This Phase 2 of 26 Mzizi court boasts of stylishly designed apartments that shall be develope