imize noise and smoke pollution</li><li>A convenience retail section at the ground floor</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong> Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;Located within Two Rivers Development</p><p>Executive Studio (35sqm) from Kes 5,960,000 (sold out)</p><p>1 bedroom (48sqm) from Kes 6,500,000</p><p>1bedroom Loft (55sqm) from Kes 8,100,000</p><p>2 bedroom (73sqm) from Kes 9,700,000</p>'),(2845,'property',282,'zh','property_name','斯瓦拉乡村小屋'),(2846,'property',282,'zh','alternative_name','SWARA COTTAGES'),(2847,'property',282,'zh','detailed_address','Redhill, Lower Kabete'),(2848,'property',282,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>SWARA COTTAGES</u></strong></p><p>A three-bedroom modern design bungalow set on 170sq metres,</p><p>With:</p><p>A sprawling lounge</p><p>Dining area dressed with large windows.</p><p>The interiors are of high quality and include a large kitchen with pantry,</p><p>Indoor and outdoor washing areas.</p><p>Beautifully landscaped gardens with a live hedge and 2 car park.</p><p><strong>Facilities around:</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent road access</li><li>Top schools</li><li>Hospitals</li><li>Shopping malls and chill spots</li><li>Hospitals</li></ul><p><strong> Unit size and price</strong></p><p>3 Bedroom 170 sqm 15,000,000</p><p><em>Hurry and book a slot today!!</em></p>'),(2849,'property',283,'zh','property_name','A-ONE PANDORA RESIDENCE'),(2850,'property',283,'zh','alternative_name','PANDORA RESIDENCY'),(2851,'property',283,'zh','detailed_address','Muthangari Drive'),(2852,'property',283,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>A- ONE PANDORA RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>A-One Pandora is more than just a residence—it’s a lifestyle</p><p>designed to elevate everyday moments. Located on Muthangari</p><p>Drive, this premium development offers 2, 3, and 4-bedroom</p><p>homes, perfect for young and growing families who value space,</p><p>connection, and convenience.</p><p>With expansive layouts, floor-to-ceiling windows, and seamless</p><p>