&nbsp;along Peponi Road, crafted for modern, upscale urban living.</p><p><strong>Premium Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Rooftop infinity pool and panoramic skyline lounge</li><li>Fully equipped gym, yoga studio, spa &amp; wellness center</li><li>Concierge, hotel-style lobby &amp; co-working/business center</li><li>Landscaped sky gardens, courtyard areas, and children’s play zone</li><li>Retail outlets, café, laundry services, and recreational spaces</li><li>Tennis, padel, and other sports facilities</li><li>Smart access control, CCTV surveillance &amp; 24/7 security</li></ul><p><strong>Apartment Options &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>1-Bedroom Units*</p><ul><li>Type A (43 sqm)* – From Ksh 5M</li><li>Type B (52 sqm)* – From Ksh 6.1M</li><li>Type C (76 sqm)* – From Ksh 9M</li><li>Type D (88 sqm)* – From Ksh 10.3M</li></ul><p>2-Bedroom Units*</p><ul><li>Type E (113 sqm) – From Ksh 13.2M</li><li>Type E (142 sqm) – From Ksh 16.7M</li><li>Type F (139 sqm) – From Ksh 19.46M</li></ul><p>Enjoy excellent connectivity and convenience with top-tier shopping, schools, offices, and hospitals just minutes away:</p><ul><li>2 minutes to Westgate &amp; Sarit Centre</li><li>5 minutes to UN Avenue &amp; Parklands</li><li>Quick access to Gigiri, CBD, and key international schools</li></ul><p>Flexible Payment Plan*</p><ul><li>20% deposit to reserve</li><li>Balance spread over 3 years</li><li>Ideal for off-plan buyers looking for structured, affordable terms</li></ul>'),(3026,'property_category',4,'zh','name','TEST4'),(3028,'property_category',5,'zh','name','苔丝'),(3037,'property',27,'zh','detailed_address','Parklands'),(3040,'property',19,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa ， Othaya路'),(3043,'property',2,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani位置'),(3052,'property',23,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani位置'),(3055,'property',26,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(3059,'property',306,'zh','property_name','5+ 卧室'),(3060,'property',306,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(3061,'property',306,'zh','short_description','<p>入住这栋令人惊叹的5卧室房源，体验舒适和便利，该房源位于宁静且广受欢迎的Kileleshwa街区。非常适合寻求充足空间和便利的家庭或专业人士。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(3062,'property',307,'zh','property_name','金陵大厦'),(3063,'property',307,'zh','detailed_address','22 Muthithi Road'),(3064,'property',307,'zh','short_description','<p>坐落在内罗毕首屈一指的商业、生活方式和投资区Westlands繁华中心的Muthithi路和Crossway路交汇处。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(3065,'property',308,'zh','property_name','出售LOWER KABETE 2英亩土地'),(3066,'property',308,'zh','detailed_address','Lower Kabete'),(3067,'property',308,'zh','short_description','<p><strong><u>2 ACRES IN LOWER KABETE FOR SALE</u></strong></p><p>Discover this exceptional 2-ace parcel nestled in the serene and highly sought-after neighborhood of Lower Kabete. Perfectly positioned just a short drive from Westlands and spring valley, this property offers the ideal blend of tranquility and and convenience.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Property features:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>2 </strong>Acres (flat and well drained land)</li><li>Easily accessible via well maintained tarmac road</li><li>Water and electricity are available on-site</li><li>Quiet ,green and secure area with stunning views of the lush Kabete landscape</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>Acres and price:</strong></p><p>2 Acres at Ksh 180,000,000</p>'),(3068,'property',309,'zh','property_name','瑞鲁1英亩待售'),(3069,'property',309,'zh','detailed_address','Kiambu县Ruiru'),(3070,'property',309,'zh','short_description','<h2><br></h2><p>This exceptional 1 -acre parcel located in the fast growing and highly sought- after Ruiru area .The land is ideal for both residential and commercial development, with easy access to amenities.</p>'),(3084,'property',303,'zh','detailed_address','华兰路 18 号'),(3085,'property',303,'zh','short_description','<p>San Remo Heights公寓是一个位于内罗毕Westlands的25层豪华住宅开发项目，在Westlands提供现代化公寓出售，旨在提供舒适、时尚和长期投资。</p><p><br></p>'),(3097,'property',301,'zh','short_description','<p>卡地亚伦达别墅（ Cartier Villas Runda ）是奈奥比（ Naiobi ）仅出售的16栋超豪华别墅的罕见系列。位于著名的润达庄园（ Runda Estate ）。这些别墅将精致优雅与现代便利相结合。这座封闭式飞地提供安全、独特和精致的生活方式。</p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3>'),(3106,'property',297,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>STALLION&nbsp;VILLAS</u></strong></p><p>Welcome to Stallion Villas, an exclusive gated gated community nestled in the heart of Karen, along Kuwinda road. This is more than just a home- Its a sanctuary of elegance, tranquility and&nbsp;prestige.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li><em>Spacious Main Lounge</em>&nbsp;and a cozy&nbsp;<em>Mini Lounge</em>&nbsp;for family gatherings.</li><li><em>Home Office/Study Room</em>&nbsp;for productivity and work-from-home flexibility.</li><li><em>Modern Kitchen</em>&nbsp;with a pantry and a convenient utility area.</li><li><em>Home Gym</em>&nbsp;and a private&nbsp;<em>Movie Theatre</em>&nbsp;for entertainment.</li><li><em>Rooftop Terrace Lounge</em>&nbsp;offering breathtaking views and relaxation.</li><li><em>Walk-in Closets</em>&nbsp;for ultimate comfort and storage.</li><li><em>Kitchen Yard</em>&nbsp;for additional utility.</li><li><em>Patio/Outdoor Dining Area</em>&nbsp;for alfresco dining experiences.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>&nbsp;Unit size and price:</strong></p><p>5 Bedrooms 750 sqm at Ksh 150,000,000</p>'),(3107,'property',310,'zh','property_name','KIAMBU Thindigwa 1英亩待售'),(3108,'property',310,'zh','detailed_address','Thindigua, Kiambu'),(3109,'property',310,'zh','short_description','<p>这块占地1英亩的地块位于Kiambu路附近的Thindigua ，为基安布县发展最快的郊区之一的住宅开发或投资提供了绝佳的机会。由于该街区毗邻内罗毕的商业区，道路交通便利，便利设施不断扩大，因此备受追捧。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(3113,'property',311,'zh','property_name','SYNINA RESIDENCE'),(3114,'property',311,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(3115,'property',311,'zh','short_description','<h3>Synina Residency包括3间卧室、4间卧室、5间卧室和6间卧室，加上DSQ ，所有套房豪华公寓均位于Kileleshwa的Tinderet大道上，地理位置优越。Synina Residence坐落在内罗毕Kileleshwa这个备受追捧、私密和安全的街区，周围环绕着风景秀丽的天堂。</h3><h3><br></h3><h3><br></h3>'),(3116,'property',312,'zh','property_name','BEACON BY SYNINA'),(3117,