ing modern, stylish home&nbsp;just minutes from Nairobi CBD and Jomo Kenyatta International Airport (JKIA). Designed with elegance and functionality in mind, Mara groove is perfect for families ,young professionals or investors looking for comfort, convenience and value.</p><p>Property features:</p><ul><li>Spacious 1,2 and 3-bedroom&nbsp;apartments with master ensuite</li><li>Modern open-plan kitchen with granite countertops</li><li>Elegant ceramic tile flooring and quality fittings</li><li>Ample natural light and ventilation</li><li>Balconies with scenic views</li></ul><p><strong>Estate amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>24/7 security with perimeter wall and electric fence</li><li>CCTV Surveillance and manned entry gate</li><li>Ample cabro-paved parking for residents and visitors</li><li>Children\'s&nbsp;play area and landscaped gardens</li><li>Borehole water supply and storage tanks</li><li>Onsite management office</li></ul><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom 56 sqm at ksh 4,400,000</p><p>2 Bedroom&nbsp;95 sqm at ksh 7,400,000</p><p>3 Bedroom&nbsp;136 sqm at Ksh 10,500,000</p><p>3 Bedroom&nbsp;145 sqm at Ksh 11,000,000</p><p>3 Bedroom 166 sqm at Ksh&nbsp;12,500,000</p><p>Completion time:</p><p>2028</p>'),(3601,'property',294,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>BUTTERFLY PALACE</u></strong></p><p>Discover an oasis of tranquility in the heart of Westlands at Butterfly palace-where nature meets elegance for unforgettable experiences. Perfect for families, couples, photo lovers and those looking to unwind in a serene, inspiring setting.</p><p>Key features:</p><p>Onsite borehole</p><p>Swimming pool</p><p>High speed lifts</p><p>Bio metric access</p><p>Highspeed lifts</p><p>Children\'s play area</p><p>Ample residents/Visitor parking</p><p>Full power back up</p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li>2 Bedrooms 169 sqm at Ksh 23,400,000</li><li>3 Bedrooms 236 sqm at Ksh 32,200,000</li><li>4 Bedrooms 378 sqm at Ksh 52,400,000</li></ul><p><strong>Payment plan:</strong></p><p>20% Deposit upon signing the offer letter</p><p>70% eaqual monthly/quarterly installments</p><p>10% on handover</p><p><strong>Completion:</strong></p><p>April 2028</p>'),(3604,'property',293,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>EVEREST COURT </u></strong></p><p>Welcome to Everest&nbsp;Court , a modern residential development located in the heart of Kileleshwa, Nairobi. Designed for comfort and contemporary living ,Everest Court offers spacious, well-finished apartments ideal for families, professionals or investors seeking a prime address in a serene yet central location.</p><p>Apartment highlights</p><p>Spacious&nbsp;open-plan living and dinning areas</p><p>Large windows offering ample natural light</p><p>Fully fitted modern kitchen with high-quality cabinetry</p><p>En-suite master bedroom+ build- in wardrobes</p><p>Self contained DSQ with separate entrance</p><p>Laundry area</p><p>Two dedicated parking spots per unit</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities and lifestyle:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>24/7 security and CCTV surveillance</li><li>High-speed lifts</li><li>Backup generator</li><li>Borehole and ample water storage</li><li>Beautiful views of the green Kileleshwa surroundings</li></ul>'),(3610,'property',292,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>LUMINARA APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p>Luminara Westlands is a new 24 floor development offering stylish 1 and 2 bedroom luxury apartments for sale on Mogotio Road, just off Ojijo Road in Westlands near GTC. Available as an exclusive off-plan project, these residences combine bold architecture with hotel-inspired elegance. With launch prices available for a limited time, this is your chance to lock in a high-value home or investment before units sell out.</p><p><br></p><h4>Inside the Apartments:</h4><p><br></p><ul><li>1 and 2 Bedroom residences (56 sqm – 113 sqm)</li><li>Open-plan living, dining &amp; kitchen layouts</li><li>Floor-to-ceiling windows for natural light</li><li>Spacious balconies with skyline views</li><li>Premium modern finishes &amp; fitted kitchens</li><li>Smart space planning for style &amp; comfort</li></ul><p><br></p><h4><strong>Lifestyle Amenities:</strong></h4><ul><li>Rooftop infinity pool with sweeping Nairobi views</li><li>Sky lounge and signature rooftop dining club</li><li>Fully equipped gym and wellness studio</li><li>Stylish café and business lounge</li><li>Concierge reception with hotel-inspired design</li><li>Secure parking with 24/7 CCTV &amp; controlled access</li><li>Four high-speed lifts</li><li>Reliable backup power and water supply</li></ul><h3>Special Offer Launch Prices at Luminara Westlands Apartments</h3><h3>1 Bedroom Comfort (56 sqm)</h3><ul><li><strong>100% Price from:</strong> KES 6.83M</li><li>(Original: KES 8.12M | 20% deposit: KES 7.42M | 50% deposit: KES 7.22M)</li></ul><h3>1 Bedroom Premium (65 sqm)</h3><ul><li><strong>100% Price from:</strong> KES 7.23M</li><li>(Original: KES 9.42M | 20% deposit: KES 7.82M | 50% deposit: KES 7.62M)</li></ul><h3>1 Bedroom Luxury (82 sqm)</h3><ul><li><strong>100% Price from:</strong> KES 8.23M</li><li>(Original: KES 10.66M | 20% deposit: KES 8.82M | 50% deposit: KES 8.62M)</li></ul><h3><a href=\"https://commercialpropertykenya.com/properties/apartment-for-sale-off-ojijo-road-westlands/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">2 Bedroom Luxury (113 sqm)</a></h3><ul><li><strong>100% Price from:</strong> KES 11.23M</li><li>(Original: KES 13.56M | 20% deposit: KES 11.82M | 50% deposit: KES 11.62M)</li></ul><p>⚡ <strong>Urgency Tip:</strong> Buyers who pay 100% upfront secure the <strong>lowest prices and highest ROI.</strong> With units selling fast and prices set to rise, acting now guarantees the best deal. Offer Valid till 31 December 2025.</p><h4>Location Highlights – Westlands Connections</h4><ul><li>Sarit Centre – 3 mins</li><li>Westgate Shopping Mall – 4 mins</li><li>Carrefour Market GTC – 5 mins</li></ul>'),(3613,'property',291,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>RAFILAND APARTMENTS</u></strong></p><p>Located just a 5-min walk from JKUAT gate B in Juja,Rafiland apartments (Rafi Studios) offer fully furnished studio and one bedroom units ideal for students, young professionals or investors looking for high demand rental property.</p><p>Apartment features:</p><p>Fully furnished with bed,study desk,wardrobe</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Gym</li><li>Rooftop study area</li><li>Lounge</li><li>24/7 Hrs CCTV surveillance /security</li><li>Backup generator</li><li>Borehole</li><li>Ground floor commercial shops/supermarket</li><li>Fast elevators</li><li>Ample parking</li><li>Fitted kitchen</li></ul><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><p>Studio 25sqm at Ksh 2,400,000 (double bed studio)</p><p>Studio 25 sqm at Ksh 2,400,000 (single bed studio)</p><p>1 Bedroom 48 sqm at Ksh 4,200,000</p>'),(3616,'property',290,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>CRESCENT SERENITY</u></strong></p><p>Welcome to CRESCENT RESIDENCY, an esteemed 18-story development in Kileleshwa offering spacious one and two-bedroom apartments. Ideally situated on Gatundu Road, it’s just minutes from Yaya Center, Prestige Plaza, and other major shopping destinations. Close proximity to Artcaffe and renowned schools like Kenya High School enhances the appeal of this exceptional residential enclave. Discover excellence with CRESCENT SERENITY DEVELOPERS LIMITED, trusted since 2005. We’re committed to crafting affordable, comfortable homes that exceed expectations, ensuring a living experience that’s truly exceptional.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Coffee Lodge for Residents</p><p>Swimming Pool</p><p>Hotel-Style Reception Lobby</p><p>Borehole Water Supply</p><p>Back-up Generator</p><p>Fully Equipped Gym Electrical Fence and CCTV Surveillance</p><p>Kids Play Area</p><p>DSTV and Internet Provision</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>1 Bedrooms</strong></p><p>690 sq.ft- Kes 6.6M</p><p>715 sq.ft- Kes 6.7M</p><p>726 sq.ft- Kes 6.9M</p><p>823 sq.ft Kes 7.7M</p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom Units</p><p>1173 sq.ft- Kes 11M plus utility room</p><p>1215 sq.ft- Kes 11.3M</p><p>1270 sq.ft with study room – Kes 12M</p>'),(3686,'property',265,'zh','short_description','<h3>这些双卧室套房公寓设计现代都市生活，在舒适便利和隐私之间取得完美平衡。</h3>'),(3694,'property',266,'zh','short_description','<p>在这个美丽的地方探索舒适和便利</p><p>维护的<strong>5卧室房屋位于Runda市中心</strong>，</p><p>内罗毕最受欢迎的住宅区。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(3702,'property',298,'zh','short_description','<p>&nbsp;位于Peponi路Westlands的豪华1卧室和2卧室公寓。</p>'),(3705,'property',319,'zh','description','<h2><u>LAISER PLACE</u></h2><p>In&nbsp;the serene suburbs of Rongai town, overlooking Ngong hills stands Laiser place an amazing apartment ideal for families. Comes with a swimming pool, a pool deck, and a children\'s play area. The units feature spacious ,well lit interiors , stylish finishes and a thoughtfully designed layout perfect for singles ,couples or small families .</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities</strong></p><ul><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Ample parking</li><li>Borehole</li><li>Pool Deck</li><li>Kids play area</li><li>24/7 Security</li></ul><p><br></p><p>This property offers easy access to to :</p><p><br></p><p>Major roads</p><p>Shopping centers</p><p>Reputable schools</p><p>Popular social amenities</p><p><br></p><p>Unit size and price:</p><p>2 Bedrooms 60 sqm at Ksh 5,500,000</p>'),(3709,'property',318,'zh','description','<h2><strong><u>BAHARI HOMES</u></strong></h2><p><br></p><p>Bahari Homes Residency is a distinctive apartment complex strategically located at the intersection of Kilimani and Kirichwa Road, next to Quick Mart Kilimani. Spanning 1.1 acres, the development features 170 modern units, including 68 two-bedroom apartments and 102 three-bedroom apartments. Each floor is designed with two units, served by two high-speed elevators, ensuring convenience and privacy.</p><p>The two-bedroom apartments are thoughtfully designed to offer comfort and style, with ample natural light and fresh air, creating a welcoming and serene living space.</p><p>Inspired by the finest art, the aspirations of the homeowners, and the tastes of its residents, Bahari Homes blends classic and contemporary design elements. This exceptional development is built to meet diverse tastes, providing an experience where residents can truly embrace the vibrancy and luxury of life in Nairobi.</p><p><br></p><p>UNIT PRICES;</p><p><br></p><ul><li>2 bedrooms starts from (117 sqm) KES.15.65M</li><li>2 bedrooms starts from (122 sqm ) KES.16M</li><li>2 bedrooms starts from (123 sqm) KES.16.5M</li><li>2 bedrooms starts from (129 sqm) KES.17M</li><li>3 bedrooms starts from (173.55sqm) KES.23M</li><li>3 bedroom starts from (182.45sqm) KES 25M</li></ul><p><br></p><p>AMENITIES;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><ul><li>High speed Lifts&nbsp;</li><li>Heated pool</li><li>Kids cycling area</li><li>Event center</li><li>Manned security</li><li>Intercom</li><li>Fitted kitchen</li><li>Extended balconies</li><li>Large window</li></ul><p>COMPLETION DATE&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;Project completion Period AUGUST 2025</p><p>PAYMENT PLAN</p><p><br></p><p>1. 20% initial deposit, 50% next installment, 30% Upon completion period</p>'),(3713,'property',313,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>LILYDALE RIVERSIDE</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Discover contemporary urban living at Lilydale Riverside, a premier high-rise development offering elegant 1 and 2-bedroom apartments in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious neighborhoods. Whether you’re a homeowner seeking modern comfort or an investor aiming for strong rental yields, this 17-story twin-tower project combines luxury, convenience, and outstanding investment potential.</p><p>Designed with attention to detail, Lilydale at Riverside features premium amenities that prioritize comfort, security, and leisure—making it the perfect residence for professionals, families, and discerning buyers alike.</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities:</p><ul><li>Fully Equipped Gym for an active lifestyle</li><li>&nbsp;Rooftop Swimming Pool with breathtaking views</li><li>Children’s Playground for family-friendly living</li><li>Recreation Club &amp; Lounge for social gatherings</li><li>&nbsp;24/7 Security with CCTV &amp; Intercom for peace of mind</li><li>&nbsp;Borehole Water Supply ensuring uninterrupted water access</li><li>&nbsp;Backup Generator for continuous power supply</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><ul><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom Apartment (73.45sqm) – From KSh 8.5M to 9M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom Apartment (105.58sqm) – From KSh 12.5M to 12.8M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom + DSQ (124.33sqm) – From KSh 14M to 14.8M</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom + DSQ (129.45sqm) – From KSh 14.35 M to 14.8 M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h4>completion period:</h4><h5>Project completion period September 2027</h5><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment plans:</strong></p><ol><li>&nbsp;20% Down Payment to reserve your unit</li><li>10% Quarterly Installments for affordability</li><li>Spread Over 36 Months for flexibility</li></ol>'),(3721,'property',312,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>BEACON BY SYNINA</u></strong></p><p>Rising gracefully on Mandera Road,&nbsp;<em>Beacon by Synina</em>&nbsp;is an architectural masterpiece redefining luxury living in Nairobi’s upscale Kileleshwa neighborhood. This striking high-rise offers a collection of expansive 3- and 4-bedroom residences with DSQs, alongside lavish 5-bedroom simplex and duplex penthouses, designed for the modern homeowner who values timeless elegance and superior craftsmanship.</p><p>Set in a serene yet well-connected location, Beacon by Synina ensures residents enjoy unmatched convenience. From top schools like Kenton College and The Kenya High School, to vibrant retail hubs such as Yaya Centre, Junction Mall, and ABC Place, everything you need is within minutes. Easy access to the Nairobi Arboretum, Nairobi Hospital, Westlands, Nairobi CBD, and the Expressway makes this residence as practical as it is prestigious.</p><p>With skyline views and an abundance of premium amenities, Beacon by Synina promises not just a home, but a lifestyle.</p><p><br></p><h4><strong>A</strong>menities;</h4><ul><li>Infinity rooftop swimming pool, baby pool &amp; sun deck</li><li>SkyView His &amp; Hers gym, aerobics studio &amp; sauna</li><li>Rooftop gazebo, BBQ zone &amp; firepit</li><li>Multi-purpose hall for exclusive gatherings</li><li>Welcome concierge reception lounge</li><li>Borehole water supply &amp; full backup generator</li><li>High-speed elevators</li><li>Manned gatehouse, 24/7 CCTV &amp; electric fence</li><li>Two parking bays per unit + ample visitor parking</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ (Type A, 2,728 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 29.9M</li><li><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ (Type B, 2,431 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 29M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type A, 3,685 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 40M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type B, 3,960 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 46M</li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (Type C, 3,707 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 40M</li><li><strong>5 Bedroom Simplex PH (Types A, B, C, 4,972–5,258 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 55M</li><li><strong>5 Bedroom Duplex PH (4,994 Sq. Ft)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 58M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><h4><strong>C</strong>ompletion Date</h4><p>Estimated Completion:&nbsp;<strong>Q4 2026</strong></p><h4><strong>P</strong>ayment Plan</h4><ul><li>Initial Deposit: 30%</li><li>Next 6 Months: 30%</li><li>Following 6 Months: 30%</li><li>On Handover: 10%</li></ul>'),(3725,'property',311,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>SYNINA RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Synina Residency comprises 3, 4, 5 and 6 Bedroom plus DSQs all en-suite luxury apartments strategically located on Tinderet Avenue, Kileleshwa. Encircled in a haven of scenic views, Synina Residence is conveniently situated in the highly sought after, private and secure neighborhood of Kileleshwa, Nairobi. This development comprises 77 opulent residences thoughtfully constructed with separate domestic living quarters.</p><p><strong>Features and Amenities</strong></p><ul><li>Fully-equipped Gym Dedicated Fitness Center for Ladies</li><li>Infinity Swimming Pool</li><li>Spacious Rooftop Entertainment Lounge</li><li>Serene Garden</li><li>Spacious Lounge and Dining Area</li><li>Fully Fitted Modern Kitchen with Pantry</li><li>High Speed Elevators</li><li>2 Parking Spaces Per Unit and extra for visitors</li><li>Borehole and Back Up Generator</li><li>CCTV Surveillance and 24-hour Security</li><li>Kids Play Zone</li></ul><p>Designed with meticulous attention to the needs of the occupier, Synina Residency spares no expense on the sizes of the rooms. Households today have evolving spatial needs to cater for their growing families and this development’s key merit is the ample sizes of the rooms in each unit. The spacious living area boasts soaring ceilings with full-height windows bathing the house with natural light and breathtaking views. The dining area and sitting room opens out to a large terrace with spectacular views of Nairobi’s Cityscape. The closed kitchen is both stylish and functional.</p><p>3 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (223 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 30M&nbsp;RENTAL: 180,000 per month</strong></p><p>4 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (298 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 38.5M&nbsp;RENTAL: 250,000 per month&nbsp;</strong></p><p>5 bedroom plus DSQ all en-suite (325 sqm) –&nbsp;<strong>Kes. 41.4M</strong></p>'),(3729,'property',307,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>GOLDEN MANSION</u></strong></p><p>Nestled at the junction of Muthithi Road and Crossway road in the bustling heart of Westlands, Nairobi\'s premier business , lifestyle and investment zone.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities and lifestyle:</strong></p><ul><li>Rooftop heated infinity swimming pool</li><li>Sky garden with panoramic city vistas</li><li>Fully equipped gym ,sauna and wellness centre</li><li>Clubhouse</li><li>Childrens\'s play zone</li><li>Landscaped green spaces</li><li>Five-storey parking garage</li><li>High- speed elevators</li><li>24/7 CCTV surveillance</li><li>Smart access control</li><li>Backp generator</li><li>Water reserve</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1 Bedroom 64.40 sqm Ksh 6,500,000</p><p>1 Bedroom 78 .46sqm Ksh 9,022,900</p><p>1 Bedroom duplex 66..86 sqm Ksh 9,696,150</p><p>1 Bedroom duplex 91.53 sqm Ksh 12,356,550</p><p>2 Bedroom 107.57 sqm Ksh 10,757,000</p><p>Luxury 2 Bedroom duplexes 138 sqm Ksh 20,010,000</p><p>Corner 3 Bedroom duplex 155.10 sqm Ksh 21,714,000</p><p><br></p><p>Payment Plan:</p><p>200,000 reservation fee 20% downpayment within 14 days of offer letter signing</p><p>2 equal installments of the balance every 6 months</p><p>Finish last installment before May 2028</p>'),(3733,'property',305,'zh','description','<h2><strong><u>DIVINE RESIDENCES</u></strong></h2><p>Divine residence is truly a treasure waiting to be discovered. Not only is each apartment designed with international hotel standards in mind, but it is furnished with custom-made furniture created specifically for it. Every detail in design, finishing, and furnishing is directly hand-picked by our interior designers to ensure maximum elegance and comfort for future tenants.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>World class amenities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Heated swimming pool (Rooftop)</li><li>Two fully equipped gym</li><li>Rooftop Sitting Area</li><li>Kids play area</li><li>Reception zone &amp; Concierge Service</li><li>Meeting rooms</li><li>Ample parking spaces</li><li>Landscape gardens</li><li>Class A facility management service</li><li>Balconies &amp; terraces</li></ul><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><p>1 Bedroom 66 sqm 18,850,000</p><p>2 Bedroom 90 sqm 24,570,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>completion date:</strong></p><p>DECEMBER 2025</p>'),(3737,'property',304,'zh','description','<h1><u>CANTO Westlands </u></h1><p>Tucked in the leafy suburbs of Westlands along School Lane are these prestigious and luxurious developments featuring studio &amp; 1 Bedroom apartment units available for Sale. The development is designed with the highest quality materials, creating an inviting living atmosphere that fulfills all wishes.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>World class amenities:</strong></p><ul><li>Rooftop infinity pool</li><li>Co-working space</li><li>Indoor cinema lounge</li><li>Rooftop BBQ area</li><li>Sky gym</li><li>Steam and Sauna rooms</li><li>Game lounge</li><li>Sky lounge with panoramic, City views</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><ol><li>Studio 38 sqm 7,800,000</li><li>1 Bedroom 56 sqm 10,140,000</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>Flexible payment plan:</strong></p><p>30% deposit, balance payable over 36 months</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Expected completion:</strong></p><p><strong>December 2028</strong></p>'),(3738,'property',304,'zh','short_description','<p>这些久负盛名的豪华开发项目位于学校巷（ School Lane ）沿线的韦斯特兰（ Westlands ）绿树成荫的郊区，设有单间公寓和单卧室公寓，可供出售。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(3741,'property',303,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>SAN REMO HEIGHTS</u></strong></p><p>San Remo Heights apartments is a 25-floor luxury residential development in Westlands, Nairobi, offering modern apartments for sale in Westlands designed for comfort, style, and long-term investment. Rising along Westlands Road, this high-rise project presents&nbsp;unique apartments for sale in Nairobi; 1 Bedroom, 1 Bedroom + Study, and 2 Bedroom Master Ensuite apartments, blending elegant design with exceptional real estate value.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Stylish 1 Bedroom apartments for sale off Rhapta road– ideal for young professionals and first-time investors</li><li>1 Bedroom + Study units – perfect for hybrid working or home office use</li><li>Spacious 2 Bedroom Master Ensuite apartments – designed for private and comfortable homes</li><li>Open-plan living and dining areas filled with natural light</li><li>Modern fitted kitchens with premium finishes</li><li>Master ensuite in all two-bedroom units</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Exterior amenities</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Elegant clubhouse and reception lobby</li><li>Smart access control and high-level security systems</li><li>Fully equipped gymnasium and rooftop garden with panoramic views</li><li>Children’s play area for family-friendly living</li><li>Borehole and large water storage tanks for reliable supply</li><li>Backup generator for uninterrupted power</li><li>CCTV surveillance &amp; electric fencing</li><li>High-speed internet and DSTV provision</li><li>Social connectivity and community interaction spaces</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><p>1 Bedroom 55 sqm  Ksh  5,500,000</p><p>1 Bedroom +study 80 sqm  Ksh 7,500,000</p><p>2 Bedroom master En-suite 115 sqm    Ksh11,500,000</p><p><br></p>'),(3745,'property',301,'zh','description','<h3><strong><u>CATIER VILLA</u></strong></h3><p>The Cartier Villas Runda, a rare collection of only 16-ultra luxury villas for sale in Nairobi. Located in prestigious Runda Estate. These Villas combine refined elegance with modern convenience. This gated enclave offers a lifestyle defined by security, exclusivity and sophistication.</p><p><br></p><h3>Residents enjoy exclusive access to :</h3><ol><li>A clubhouse which includes: (a gym, conference room, Library, Kids play area, Cafe, heated swimming pool, chill spot)</li><li>Beautifully landscaped gardens and walking paths</li><li>24- hour security, CCTV surveillance and controlled access</li><li>Ample parking and backup power</li><li>Two lush gardens create perfect spaces for relaxation and entertainment</li><li>A private swimming pool</li><li>Smart home systems allowing effortless control of lighting, security and entertainment</li><li>Designer kitchens and high-end finishes combine functionality with elegance</li><li>Expansive living and dinning areas for family comfort</li><li>Panoramic balconies showcasing serene views and fresh air</li><li>4- Car parking spaces</li><li>Two DSQ\'s</li></ol><p><br></p><p>Location advantage:</p><p>The Cartier villas are strategically moments away from key facilities</p><p>Top schools</p><p>Good hospitals</p><p>Major roads</p><p>Shopping malls and restaurants</p>'),(3749,'property',299,'zh','description','<h3><u>OSTREA KAREN VILLAS</u></h3><p>Welcome to Ostrea Karen Villas, a private enclave of just 20 ultra-luxury 5-bedroom residences in Nairobi Karen, off Karen Ridge Road. Each villa is a bold architectural statement, combining timeless elegance with next-generation smart living. Inspired by the pearl, Ostrea Karen Villas are designed with precision, privacy, and purpose, crafted for discerning homeowners who value both lifestyle and legacy.</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities:</p><ul><li>5 Spacious Ensuite Bedrooms, including a master suite with private terrace</li><li>Private Library / Home Office</li><li>Sunken Lounge with double-height glass windows</li><li>Modern Hard Kitchen and&nbsp;Soft (Prep) Kitchen, both fully fitted</li><li>Formal Dining Area + Ground Floor Guest Suite &amp; Cloakroom</li><li>Spiral Marble Staircase flowing into upper floors</li><li>Optional Private Elevator across all levels</li><li>2 Detached DSQs with private entrances</li></ul><h4>Exterior and Lifestyle Amenities</h4><ul><li>Solar Water Heating and Water Storage Systems</li><li>Heated Private Swimming Pool + Hot Tub</li><li>Expansive Private Garden and Landscaped Grounds (over 300m²)</li><li>Elegant Rooftop Pergola and Entertainment Deck (198m²) with BBQ and rooftop kitchen</li><li>Fully Detached Guest House – customizable as office, wellness suite, or studio</li><li>8-Car Parking + Gated Community Security</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Total Built-Up Area:</strong>&nbsp;703 sqm</p><p><strong>Plot Size Per Unit:</strong>&nbsp;1,582 sqm</p><p><br></p><h4>Ostrea Karen Prices and Payment Plan</h4><p>Prices range from&nbsp;<strong>$1.3M – $1.5M</strong>, depending on villa selection.</p><p>Flexible installment options available after booking with a deposit:</p><ul><li>20% deposit – 20-month plan</li><li>25% deposit – 25-month plan</li><li>30% deposit – 30-month plan</li></ul><p><br></p><h4><br></h4>'),(3750,'property',299,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到奥斯特雷亚·卡伦别墅（ Ostrea Karen Villas ） ，这是内罗毕卡伦仅有20套超豪华5居室住宅的私人飞地，位于卡伦岭路（ Karen Ridge Road ）附近。每栋别墅都是大胆的建筑宣言，将永恒的优雅与下一代智能生活相结合。</p><h4><br></h4><p><br></p><p><br></p><h4><br></h4>'),(3754,'property',297,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到Stallion别墅，这是一个独特的门禁社区，坐落在Karen的中心，沿着Kuwinda路。这里不仅仅是一个家--这里是优雅、宁静和声望的圣地</p>'),(3757,'property',296,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>GARDEN VILLAS TOWNHOUSES</u></strong></p><p>Discover timeless elegance and modern comfort in these luxurious garden villas nestled in the heart of Lavington,one of Nairobi\'s most serene and prestigious neighborhoods.</p><p>These exclusive homes offer a perfect blend&nbsp;of contemporary design and lush, private gardens ideal for families or individuals seeking privacy, space and tranquility.</p><p>Property features;</p><p>Spacious 5 Bedroom villas (all ensuite)</p><p>Expansive living and dinning areas with natural light</p><p>Modern fitted kitchen with pantry</p><p>Master bedroom with walk-in closet and balcony</p><p>High end-finishes with quality fixtures</p><p>Private garden and outdoor seating area</p><p>Ample parking with DSQ (Domestic staff quarters)</p><p>24/7 security,CCTV surveillance and electric fencing</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Location highlights:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>Minitues away from top schools (e.g ,Braeburn, Rusinga)</li><li>Easy access to shopping malls (Lavington mall, Junction mall)</li><li>Quiet ,leafy surroundings with excellent road connectivity</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>5 Bedroom 600 sqm at Ksh 125,000,000</p>'),(3758,'property',296,'zh','short_description','<p>这些豪华花园别墅坐落在内罗毕最宁静、最负盛名的街区之一拉文顿（ Lavington ）的中心，探索永恒的优雅和现代舒适。</p><p><br></p>'),(3762,'property',295,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到Mara Grove ，这是一个宁静安全的门禁社区，提供现代时尚的房源，距离内罗毕中央商务区和乔莫·肯雅塔国际机场（ JKIA ）仅几分钟路程。MARA GROOVE以优雅和功能为设计理念，非常适合寻求舒适、便利和价值的家庭、年轻专业人士或投资者。</p>'),(3766,'property',294,'zh','short_description','<p>在蝴蝶宫（ Butterfly palace ）探索韦斯特兰（ Westlands ）中心的宁静绿洲，在这里，大自然与优雅相遇，带来难忘的体验。非常适合家庭、情侣、摄影爱好者以及希望在宁静、鼓舞人心的环境中放松身心的人。</p>'),(3770,'property',293,'zh','short_description','<p>位于内罗毕Kileleshwa市中心的现代化住宅开发项目。Everest Court专为舒适和现代生活而设计，提供宽敞、装修精良的公寓，非常适合家庭、专业人士或投资者在宁静而中心的地理位置寻找黄金地段。</p>'),(3774,'property',292,'zh','short_description','<p>Luminara Westlands是一个全新的24楼开发项目，在Mogotio路上出售时尚的1卧室和2卧室豪华公寓，就在GTC附近Westlands的Ojijo路附近。</p><p><br></p>'),(3778,'property',291,'zh','short_description','<p>Rafiland公寓（ Rafi Studios ）距离Juja的JKUAT B门仅5分钟步行路程，提供设备齐全的单间公寓和一卧室公寓，非常适合学生、年轻专业人士或寻找高需求出租房源的投资者。</p>'),(3782,'property',290,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到CRESCENT Residency ，这是位于Kileleshwa的一栋备受推崇的18层住宅楼，提供宽敞的1卧室和2卧室公寓。地理位置优越，位于加通杜路（ Gatundu Road ） ，距离亚亚中心（ Yaya Center ）、威望广场（ Prestige Plaza ）和其他主要购物目的地仅几分钟路程靠近Artcaffe和肯尼亚高中等著名学校，增强了这个独特的住宅飞地的吸引力。</p>'),(3786,'property',288,'zh','short_description','<p>Oyster Pearl是一个优质住宅开发项目，位于Westlands的General Mathenge Road沿线宁静的Spring Valley地区。这些宽敞的公寓周围环绕着绿色植物，坐落在一个宁静的街区，融合了奢华、舒适和便利，使其成为内罗毕最受欢迎的地址之一。</p>'),(3790,'property',287,'zh','short_description','<p>埃克塞特高地（ Exeter Heights ）由32套独特的三卧室公寓组成，所有公寓均设有独立的D.S.Q. ，位于Muguga Green （ Brookside Grove附近） ，这个备受追捧的地理位置确保您轻松抵达内罗毕最好的餐厅、最时尚的购物中心以及顶级医疗和教育机构。</p>'),(3794,'property',286,'zh','short_description','<p>位于基库尤卡曼古（ Kikuyu Kamangu ）的这些维护精美的五卧室别墅让您感受舒适和便利。这些别墅非常适合家庭、专业人士或投资者入住，完美融合了隐私、空间和便利的基本便利设施。</p>'),(3798,'property',285,'zh','short_description','<p>走进Hephé宫，宽敞的设计与市中心的高架生活相遇</p><p>Westlands—Nairobi最负盛名的地区。专为家庭和专业人士</p>设计<p>考虑到这一点，我们的两居室公寓在舒适性、隐私性和风格之间提供了完美的平衡。</p>'),(3802,'property',284,'zh','short_description','<p>这套公寓位于内罗毕最受欢迎的住宅区之一Kileleshwa ，维护良好，舒适方便。此房源完美融