ort_description','<p>这座庄园坐落在快速发展的Syokimau街区，可轻松前往内罗毕的主要高速公路，同时提供宁静的住宅环境。</p>'),(4103,'property',258,'zh','short_description','<p>Velvet towers提供现代化的公寓，居住在内罗毕最方便的街区之一。</p>'),(4110,'property',256,'zh','short_description','<p>JKAC花园（ JKAC Gardens ）位于兰加塔路（ Langata road ）的宁静对面，巧妙地集中在距离威尔逊机场（ Wilson airport ）、乌呼鲁花园博物馆（ Uhuru Gardens Museum ）、食肉动物博物馆（ Carnivore ）、肯尼亚博马斯（ Bomas of Kenya ）、长颈鹿中心（ giraffe center ）、Galleria购物中心（ Galleria</p>'),(4114,'property',255,'zh','short_description','<p>奈韦斯特公寓（ Naiwest Apartments ）位于内罗毕西部的甘地大道（ Gandhi avenue ） ，地理位置优越，步入现代化、便利的城市生活</p>'),(4118,'property',254,'zh','short_description','<p>这是一个现代化的住宅开发项目，提供精心设计的2卧室主套房公寓，位置宁静，交通便利，紧邻南部旁路。</p>'),(4125,'property',252,'zh','short_description','<p>Nyari是一个宁静的绿树成荫的住宅区，位于内罗毕北部，坐落在Redhill、New Muthaiga和Kitisuru之间，距离Gigiri Westlands和主要便利设施仅几步之遥。</p>'),(4129,'property',257,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到芒果树公寓-您在Syokimau的理想住所或投资！</p>'),(4133,'property',253,'zh','short_description','<p>Golden Street Residency是一个现代化的住宅开发项目，位于Nyari路沿线，位于绿树成荫的内罗毕市中心Kileleshwa街区，正对着圣三一教堂</p>'),(4141,'property',251,'zh','short_description','<p>这套位于鲁阿卡（ Ruaka ）的3卧室公寓维护精美，售价1850万欧元，让您感受舒适和便利。</p>'),(4149,'property',250,'zh','short_description','<p>这栋房源注重细节，四周环绕着郁郁葱葱的绿色植物，完美融合了舒适的风格和便利性。</p>'),(4153,'property',248,'zh','short_description','<p>盖特威公园公寓（ Gateway Park Residence ）位于蒙巴萨路（ Mombasa Road ）旁边的Syokimau ，是一座现代化、安全的庄园，舒适</p>'),(4280,'property',323,'zh','property_name','永恒之高'),(4281,'property',323,'zh','detailed_address','Kitisuru'),(4282,'property',323,'zh','description','<h2><strong><u>ETERNITY HEIGHTS</u></strong></h2><p>Discover refined living at Eternity Heights, a boutique collection of just 20 upscale units nestled in tranquil Kitisuru west . Each residence -ranging from 2- bedroom duplexes to spacious penthouse thoughtfully designed to offer comfort , elegance and value.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li>Modern open kitchen</li><li>High ceiling windows</li><li>Large balconies</li><li>Fine finishes</li><li>Designated laundry area</li><li>Cabro paved parking</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities</strong>:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>24 – hour manned gate</li><li>CCTV cameras</li><li>Gym</li><li>Ample parking</li><li>Rooftop entertainment</li><li>High Speed lift</li><li>Rooftop Sky Lounge</li><li>Well-manicured gardens</li><li>Co-Working Space</li><li>Beautiful Entrance Lobby</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>2Bedroom Duplex 112.56 sqm Ksh 12,500,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Duplex 127.44 sqm Ksh 15,850,000</li><li>3 Bedroom Penthouse 187.87 sqm Ksh 23,500,000</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Payment plan:</p><p><br></p><p>Flexible Friendly payment Terms</p><p>20% deposit</p><p>60% equal quarterly instalments</p><p>20 % on completion</p><p><br></p><p>Completion date:</p><p>March 2026</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;</p>'),(4286,'property',323,'zh','short_description','<p>Eternity Heights坐落在宁静、安全和郁郁葱葱的环境中，提供宽敞、高雅的现代生活公寓。</p>'),(4421,'property',264,'zh','short_description','<p>这套维护精美的公寓在锡卡宁静安全的地区提供温馨的生活体验。</p>'),(4485,'property',247,'zh','short_description','<p>这些单元提供现代化的装饰、出色的安全性和方便的主要便利设施-非常适合寻求舒适和隐私的家庭或专业人士。</p>'),(4492,'property',244,'zh','short_description','<p>该开发项目专为现代生活方式而设计，融合了现代建筑、精心设计的布局和度假村风格的便利设施，所有这些都可以欣赏到壮丽的水景和天际线美景。</p>'),(4499,'property',242,'zh','short_description','<p>为舒适、便利和现代生活而设计的现代和优雅的开发项目。</p>'),(4506,'property',193,'zh','short_description','<p>在宁静公寓（ Serenity Residence ）体验当代都市生活，这是一个沿着恩贡路（ Ngong Road ）的时尚而便利的开发项目</p>'),(4510,'property',241,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到宁静公寓（ Serenity Residence ） ，这是一个现代化的住宅开发项目，位于Rongai宁静便利的区域。</p>'),(4514,'property',240,'zh','short_description','<p>进入Le Mirage Residence的现代优雅，在这个设计精美的社区中，舒适与便利相结合。</p>'),(4518,'property',239,'zh','short_description','<p>在复古住宅（ Vintage residence ）体验永恒的优雅，这是一个经过精心设计的住宅开发项目，将现代舒适与经典魅力相结合。</p>'),(4525,'property',237,'zh','short_description','<p>阿波罗国王大厦（ Kings Apollo Tower ）是集现代设计、奢华和便利于一体的首屈一指的住宅开发项目，提升您的生活方式。</p>'),(4529,'property',236,'zh','short_description','<p>Syokimau时尚而安全的住宅社区。</p>'),(4533,'property',235,'zh','short_description','<p>在位于充满活力的Kilimani街区的优雅住宅区Skyline Wood Avenue体验精致的城市生活。</p>'),(4540,'property',233,'zh','short_description','<p>在Kenzi公寓探索您的理想家园，提供设计舒适便捷的现代优雅。</p>'),(4545,'property',324,'zh','property_name','FOUNTAIN RESIDENCY'),(4546,'property',324,'zh','detailed_address','kilimani, Muringa road'),(4547,'property',324,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>FOUNTAIN RESIDENCY</u></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Fountain Residency, located at the junction of&nbsp;<strong>Kirichwa Road &amp; Muringa Road in Kilimani</strong>, is your chance to own a modern home in one of Nairobi’s most sought-after neighborhoods. Just minutes from&nbsp;<strong>Yaya Centre, Junction Mall, schools, hospitals, and major transport links</strong>, it offers unmatched convenience and strong investment appeal.</p><h3>Lifestyle Amenities</h3><p>Fountain Residency is designed for comfort, wellness, and leisure:</p><ul><li>Rooftop heated swimming pool</li><li>Ultra-modern rooftop gym with Nairobi skyline views</li><li>Sauna &amp; Steam room</li><li>Game room &amp; children’s play spaces</li><li>Laundry area</li><li>Rooftop café with panoramic Nairobi views</li><li>Landscaped garden</li><li>Turkish finishes for elegant interiors</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>Unit Prices &amp; Sizes</h3><ul><li><strong>1 Bedroom (52.29 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 5M</li><li><strong>1 Bedroom (53.76 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 5.1M</li><li><strong>1 Bedroom (55.71 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 5.3M</li><li><strong>2 Bedroom (77.88 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 7.47M</li><li><strong>2 Bedroom (81.35 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 7.8M</li><li><strong>2 Bedroom (115.93 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From Ksh 11.12M</li></ul><h3>Payment Plan &amp; Completion</h3><ul><li><strong>20% deposit</strong>&nbsp;to reserve</li><li><strong>Balance payable in flexible installments during construction 0% interest</strong></li><li>Completion:&nbsp;<em>Dec 2028</em></li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3><br></h3>'),(4548,'property',324,'zh','short_description','<p>Fountain Residency –位于内罗毕Kilimani的豪华1卧室和2卧室公寓。</p>'),(4559,'property',226,'zh','short_description','<p>每套公寓均采用现代布局和高端装饰，打造完美的城市避难所。</p>'),(4566,'property',223,'zh','short_description','<p>Diamond Oak Residency是一个现代化住宅开发项目，位于Kileleshwa宁静的Othaya路沿线，可体验高档生活。</p>'),(4570,'property',220,'zh','short_description','<p>Oloitoktok路沿线的这个开发项目坐落在绿树成荫、宁静的Kileleshwa街区，在便利和舒适之间取得了完美的平衡。</p>'),(4581,'property',306,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>5 BEDROOMS FOR RENT</u></strong></p><p>Experience comfort and convenience in this stunning 5-bedroom house located in the serene and sought-after neighborhood of Kileleshwa. Perfect for families or professionals seeking ample space and convenience.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p><ol><li>Large back and front yard</li><li>Spacious fitted kitchen</li><li>Separate dinning area</li><li>Kids play area</li><li>Back up generator</li><li>24/7 security system</li><li>Ample parking space</li></ol><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and price</strong>:</p><p>5 Bedrooms 300 sqm at Ksh 330,000</p>'),(4586,'property',27,'zh','short_description','<p>悉尼公寓是一栋豪华的19层住宅开发项目，位于内罗毕公园中安静、高档的Batubatu花园。</p>'),(4590,'property',26,'zh','short_description','<p>银石公寓（ Silverstone Apartments ）位于乞力马尼（ Kilimani ）市中心，提供舒适、便利和时尚的完美融合的现代生活。</p><p><br></p>'),(4594,'property',25,'zh','short_description','<p>探索出租多功能独立商业大楼的绝佳机会，这栋大楼非常适合各种商业用途。</p>'),(4598,'property',24,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到Alpamayo别墅，这是一栋精致的现代住宅，位于Njumbi路沿线，位于内罗毕拉文顿（ Lavington ）广受欢迎的街区。这栋别墅融合了精致的建筑、舒适性和顶级安全性，非常适合家庭或挑剔的租户/买家，他们喜欢在绿色、人脉良好的环境中享受宁静的奢华。</p><p><br></p>'),(4608,'property',23,'zh','short_description','<p>丹尼斯花园公寓（ Denis Gardens Apartments ） ：丹尼斯普里特路（ Dennis Pritt Road ）上精致的1卧室、2卧室和3卧室公寓可</p>'),(4622,'property',21,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎入住这套位于乞力马尼市中心的出租公寓，价格实惠，配备现代化的必需设施，地理位置优越。</p>'),(4626,'property',20,'zh','short_description','<p>探索Nyangumi路沿线维护良好的2间卧室和3间卧室。</p>里维拉塔（<p> Rivera tower ）完美融合了空间、安全和基本便利设施。</p>'),(4638,'property',19,'zh','short_description','<p>在这些维护精美的民宅单元中发现舒适和便利。</p><p><br></p>'),(4642,'property',18,'zh','short_description','<p>位于丹尼斯·普里特路（ Dennis Pritt Road ）旁的Nyangumi路（ Nyangumi Road ）上的带家</p>'),(4654,'property',14,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到位于宁静安全环境中的Bahari房源，这里的空间、安全、隐私和便利的基本便利设施完美融合。</p><p><br></p>'),(4658,'property',11,'zh','short_description','<p>这座现代化的新建公寓楼位于学校巷（ School Lane ）沿线的韦斯特兰（ Westlands ） ，步行即可轻松抵达购物中心、办公室和娱乐场所。</p>'),(4662,'property',10,'zh','short_description','<p>位于高档Westlands地区，靠近主要购物中心，包括Sarit中心、Westgate购物中心、商业办公室、餐厅和娱乐热点。</p><p><br></p>'),(4666,'property',8,'zh','short_description','<p>Le \'Mac是一个无可挑剔的建筑宣言，非常注重细节和精细的空间融合，以实现功能流，确保最大的隐私。</p><p><br></p>'),(4670,'property',6,'zh','short_description','<p>Le \'Mac是一个无可挑剔的建筑宣言，非常注重细节和精细的空间融合，以实现功能流，确保最大的隐私。</p>'),(4674,'property',5,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到Kenzi公寓，这里完美融合了隐私、空间和便利的生活必需品。</p>'),(4682,'property',2,'zh','short_description','<p>The Lofts At Wood Avenue - Kilimani公寓距离乌胡鲁公园（ Uhuru Park ）约10分钟车程，可前往该地区的许多旅游景点。</p>'),(4686,'property',1,'zh','short_description','<p>布置精美的房源，提供现代舒适、永恒的设计和卓越的宜居性。</p>'),(4690,'property',3,'zh','short_description','<p>Sunstone General Mathenge是Westland最受欢迎的住宅区之一，拥有精致的城市生活。</p>'),(4693,'property',310,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>1 ACRE IN KIAMBU THINDIGUA&nbsp;FOR SALE</u></strong></p><p>Located in Thindigua just off Kiambu Road, this 1-acre parcel offers an exceptional opportunity for residential development or investment in one of Kiambu county\'s fastest- growing suurbs. The neighborhood is becoming highly sought after due to its strategic proximity to Nairobi\'s business districts, improved road access and expanding amenities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Land and site features:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li>The plot is gently sloping and features</li><li>Power and water connections available in the area</li><li>Flexible land use</li><li>Established amenities are nearby ((Schools, hospitals, shopping malls and restaurants)</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Acres and price:</strong></p><p><strong>1 Acre at ksh 210,000,000</strong></p>'),(4697,'property',309,'zh','description','<h2><strong><u>1 ACRE IN RUIRU FOR SALE</u></strong></h2><p>This exceptional 1 -acre parcel located in the fast growing and highly sought- after Ruiru area .The land is ideal for both residential and commercial development, with easy access to amenities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Property features:</strong></p><ol><li>Water and electricity are available on-site</li><li>Well connected to by tarmac roads and close to Thika superhighway</li><li>Ready and clean title deed</li><li>1 Acre fully serviced</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>Acres and price:</strong></p><ul><li>1 Acre at Ksh 38,000,000</li></ul>'),(4702,'property',122,'zh','short_description','<p>这块占地1.1英亩的罕见地块位于Parklands的中心地带，为住宅或混合用途开发提供了绝佳的机会。该物业地理位置优越，道路正面极佳，靠近主要设施、医院学校和购物中心。</p>'),(4706,'property',118,'zh','short_description','<p>探索这座位于韦斯特兰（ Westlands ）的顶级房源，它完美融合了隐私、空间和便利的生活必需品，是理想的投资选择。</p>'),(4714,'property',114,'zh','short_description','<p>这片土地位于拉文顿购物中心对面的詹姆斯·吉丘鲁路（ James Gichuru Road ）对面的拉文顿（ Lavington ）。</p>'),(4718,'property',111,'zh','short_description','<p>探索拥有1.81英亩黄金地段的绝佳机会。位于Kileleshwa郁郁葱葱的宁静飞地。</p>'),(4729,'property',126,'zh','short_description','<p>探索难得的机会，在快速发展的Ruiru镇拥有占地0.104英亩的战略地块，距离内罗毕中央商务区仅几步之遥，可通过Thika高速公路和Eastern Bypass到达。</p>'),(4733,'property',125,'zh','short_description','<p>探索这个占地1.2英亩的特殊地块，位于宁静且备受追捧的Lower Kabete地区。坐落在一个安静、绿色和安全的街区，这个绿色和安全的街区，这个温和的倾斜物业为建造您梦寐以求的房屋或小型封闭式社区提供了绝佳的机会。</p>'),(4737,'property',124,'zh','short_description','<p>探索帕克兰市中心的难得机会，距离中央商务区、Westlands和包括Limuru路在内的主要干道仅几分钟路程。Parklands是一个充满活力和成熟的街区，结合了便利性、个性和高需求。该地块可通过维护良好的道路网络轻松抵达，靠近主要地标、学校医院、购物中心和公共交通。</p>'),(4741,'property',123,'zh','short_description','<p>这个占地1.75英亩的地块位于Raphta路上，等待着开发商、投资者或私人业主的绝佳机会。这块地块坐落在一个独特且不断增长的区域，具有出色的访问权限和知名度，具有非凡的潜力。</p>'),(4749,'property',121,'zh','short_description','<p>这块占地0.8英亩的罕见地块位于乞力马尼（ Kilimani ）市中心，是内罗毕最受欢迎、发展最快的街区之一。</p>'),(4761,'property',325,'zh','property_name','MAYLAN PARK RESIDENC'),(4762,'property',325,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(4763,'property',325,'zh','description','<h3><strong><u>MAYLAN PARK RESIDENCE</u></strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Set along the quiet tree lined stretch of Mandera Road, the apartment stands out for delivering a calm riverside lifestyle while keeping residents close to key amenities. Schools, supermarkets, hospitals and shopping centres are all within a short drive, giving homeowners a perfect balance between privacy and daily convenience.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>The flowing Kirichwa River adds a natural touch to the neighborhood, and the projects modern planning ensures every resident enjoys comfort, serenity and reliable connectivity to the wider city.</p><p><br></p><p>UNITS PRICE:</p><p><br></p><p>1 Bedroom A1 starts from (66sqm) 6.3M&nbsp;</p><p>1 Bedroom A2 starts from (66sqm) 6.3M</p><p>1 Bedroom A3 starts from(70sqm) 6.7M</p><p>2 Bedroom B1 starts from (89sqm) 8.6M</p><p>2 Bedroom B2 starts from (89sqm) 8.6M</p><p>2 Bedroom Promax + study B5 starts from (110sqm) 10.6M</p><p>3 Bedroom B3 starts from (92sqm) 8.9M</p><p>3 Bedroom B4 starts from (100sqm) 9.5M</p><p>3 Bedroom Promax + DSQ C starts from (128sqm) 12.2M</p><p>4 Bedroom Promax + DSQ D starts from (161sqm) 15.2M</p><p><br></p><p>AMENITIES:</p><p><br></p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>Children’s play area</p><p>6 high-speed lifts</p><p>Backup generator</p><p>Borehole for consistent water supply</p><p>Ample parking</p><p>Landscaped garden</p><p>Community shop for daily essentials</p><p>Dedicated social courtyard for relaxing and socializing</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>PAYMENT PLAN:</p><p><br></p><p>20%Deposit Within 14Days,</p><p>20%Shall be Paid With in 3months</p><p>20% Shall be Paid With in 6months</p><p>20% Shall be Paid With in 8months,</p><p>10%Shall be Paid With in 12months,</p><p>10%Balance Shall be Paid On or Before the Completion Day.</p><p>Mortgage payment:&nbsp;20% Deposit in 7 Days, Balance Shall be financed and secured by financiers and professional undertakings after the Completion Day.</p><p><br></p><p>COMPLETION DATE:</p><p><br></p><p>Project completion Period Q2 2028</p>'),(4764,'property',325,'zh','short_description','<p>公寓坐落在曼德拉路（ Mandera Road ）宁静的树林中，提供宁静的河畔生活方式，同时让居民靠近主要便利设施。学校、超市、医院和购物中心都在短途车程内，让房主在隐私和日常便利之间取得完美平衡。&nbsp;</p>'),(4773,'property',326,'zh','property_name','快速查看居住地'),(4774,'property',326,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(4775,'property',326,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>EXPRESS VIEW RESIDENCY&nbsp;</u></strong></p><p>Express View Residency is a premium residential development designed to offer elegant urban living and strong investment potential in one of Nairobi’s most sought-after locations.</p><p><br></p><p>Project Highlights:</p><p>Located in Kilimani, along Riara Gardens Road, off Riara Road</p><p>Close to Makini School and The Junction Mall</p><p>Ideal for both homeowners and investors with high rental demand</p><p>Modern architecture with spacious, well-lit interiors</p><p>Flexible 3-year payment plan for convenience</p><p>Located in a secure, accessible, and serene neighborhood</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities:</p><p><br></p><p>Swimming Pool</p><p>Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>Coffee Bar</p><p>Kids Play Area</p><p>24/7 Manned Security &amp; CCTV</p><p>Borehole Water Supply</p><p>High-Speed Elevators</p><p>Intercom System</p><p><br></p><p>Available Units:</p><p><br></p><p>1 Bedroom Apartment | 52 sqm | KSh 5M</p><p>2 Bedroom Apartment | 108 sqm | KSh 10M</p><p>3 Bedroom Apartment | 168 sqm | KSh 16.5M</p><p>4 Bedroom Apartment | 195 sqm | KSh 19.5M</p><p><br></p><p>Payment Plan:</p><p>20% deposit on booking</p><p>Balance payable within 36 months (3 years)</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Project Timeline:</p><p>Groundbreaking: July 2025</p><p>Completion: December 2028</p>'),(4776,'property',326,'zh','short_description','<p>Express View Residency是一个优质住宅开发项目，旨在为内罗毕最受欢迎的地点之一提供优雅的城市生活和强大的投资潜力。</p>'),(4781,'property',327,'zh','property_name','EAST VISTA公寓'),(4782,'property',327,'zh','detailed_address','Parklands'),(4783,'property',327,'zh','description','<p><strong><u>EAST VISTA RESIDENCE</u></strong></p><p>Designed for contemporary urban living, East Vista combines comfort, intelligent home features, and a suite of lifestyle amenities to deliver exceptional value in Kenya’s real estate market.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Apartment Features:</strong></p><p>Each residence at East Vista includes thoughtfully selected interior upgrades to support enhanced daily living:</p><p><br></p><p>Spacious 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans</p><p>Intelligent entry door locks for security</p><p>Electric curtains for modern convenience</p><p>Automated smart toilets</p><p>Instant electric water heaters</p><p>Ducted ventilation systems for improved indoor air quality</p><p>Private balconies for outdoor relaxation</p><p>Lifestyle &amp; Community Amenities</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Residents benefit from a comprehensive range of shared facilities:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Two swimming pools with decorative fountains</p><p>Fully equipped gym</p><p>Children’s indoor play area</p><p>On-site café and minimart</p><p>High-speed elevators</p><p>Standby generator and well water backup</p><p>24-hour CCTV security</p><p>Controlled access with secure gate entry</p><p>Landscaped gardens and resident parking areas</p><p><br></p><p>Unit Sizes and Prices:</p><p><br></p><p>1.	1-bedroom of 60.39 SqM from Kshs 6.7M</p><p>2.	1-bedroom of 70.34 SqM from Kshs 7.7M</p><p>3.	1-bedroom of 71.17 SqM from Kshs 7.8M</p><p>4.	2-bedroom of 92.19 SqM from Kshs 10.1M</p><p>5.	2-bedroom of 104.96 SqM from Kshs 11.5M</p><p>Flexible Payment Plans:</p><p>Buyers can choose from various flexible payment options, including discounts on 20%, 30%, and 50% initial deposits or cash purchases.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(4784,'property',327,'zh','short_description','<p>East Vista专为现代城市生活而设计，融合了舒适、智能家居功能和一套生活方式便利设施，为肯尼亚的房地产市场带来非凡的价值。</p><p><br></p>'),(4785,'property',328,'zh','property_name','ZELIG别墅'),(4786,'property',328,'zh','detailed_address','Lavington Nairobi'),(4787,'property',328,'zh','description','<h3><strong><u>ZELIG VILLAS</u></strong></h3><p>Zelig villas is a premium gated community offering spacious 6-bedroom villas with upscale finishes and modern amenities, designed for families and investors seeking comfort and exclusivity in one of Nairobi\'s  most desirable suburbs.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>Spacious 6 bedrooms ideal for family living and guest comfort</p><p>Open-plan living and dinning areas designed for modern lifestyle and entertainment</p><p>Dual kitchens-a main kitchen and a wet/ spice kitchen</p><p>Private rooftop terrace /entertainment area -perfect for social gatherings</p><p>Home gym and study spaces for convenience and productivity </p><p>Ample parking and landscaped garden</p><p>Staff quarters and utility areas</p><p>Reliable utilities with backup generator and dual water supply</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"border-color: rgb(225, 231, 239); --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: 