</p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom Apartments (2 Options)</p><p><br></p><p>Luxury 2 Bedroom</p><p>Size: 110 – 129 sqm</p><p>Starting from Ksh 14.85M</p><p><br></p><p>Platinum 2 Bedroom + Study</p><p>Size: 117 – 138 sqm</p><p>Starting from Ksh 16.27M</p><p><br></p><p>? Note: Every floor features different unit sizes and pricing, enhancing exclusivity and investment appeal.</p><p><br></p><p>? Expected Completion</p><p>Mid 2028</p>'),(4792,'property',329,'zh','short_description','<p>即将在Riverside Drive推出一个标志性的住宅开发项目，位于The Cube正对面，独特地坐落在双路正面，与Riverside Drive和Kirichwa Road Grove相连，这是一个罕见且非常理想的地方。</p><p><br></p>'),(4793,'property_type',14,'zh','name','联排别墅'),(4794,'property',330,'zh','property_name','4卧室联排别墅'),(4795,'property',330,'zh','detailed_address','拉文顿'),(4796,'property',330,'zh','description','<p>Well-Maintained 4-Bedroom + DSQ Townhouse</p><p>Lavington | KSh 300,000 per month.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Only 6 units in the compound.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Enjoy comfortable family living in the heart of prime Lavington. This well-maintained townhouse offers generous living spaces and reliable amenities within a prestigious neighbourhood.</p><p><br></p><p>Property Features:</p><p><br></p><p>•	4 bedrooms plus DSQ</p><p>•	Private back yard garden</p><p>•	Spacious family living area</p><p>•	Ample water storage</p><p>•	Borehole water supply</p><p>•	Well maintained throughout</p><p>* Full back up generator&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Rent: KSh 300,000 per month</p>'),(4797,'property',330,'zh','short_description','<p>维护良好的4卧室+ DSQ联排别墅</p><p>Lavington |每月30万肯尼亚先令。</p>大<p>院里只有6个单元。</p><p><br></p>在拉文顿（<p> Lavington ）黄金地段享受舒适的家庭生活。这栋维护良好的联排别墅位于著名的街区，提供宽敞的起居空间和可靠的便利设施。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(4802,'property',331,'zh','property_name','AMANI住宅'),(4803,'property',331,'zh','detailed_address','Jalaram路'),(4804,'property',331,'zh','description','<p>Amani residence is an exclusive ,contemporary residential development in the heart of Westlands. Designed for modern urban living, this elegant 18-storey project offers premium 3 and 4 bedroom apartments with domestic staff quarters.</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities :</p><ol><li><strong>Expansive Central Garden</strong>&nbsp;for serenity and relaxation</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Fully Equipped Gymnasium</strong>&nbsp;with modern training equipment</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Convenience Store</strong>&nbsp;within the complex</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Three Heated Infinity Pools</strong>&nbsp;(two rooftop, one ground level)</li><li><strong>Children’s Playground</strong>&nbsp;for safe family fun</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Rooftop Yoga Room</strong>&nbsp;and wellness deck</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Reading Lounge / Library &amp; Co-working Space</strong></li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Coffee Bar</strong>&nbsp;and social lounge</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>24-hour Security &amp; CCTV</strong>&nbsp;with smart face recognition entry</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Borehole Water Supply with Purifier</strong></li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Full Backup Generator</strong>&nbsp;for uninterrupted power</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Five-Level Parking Structure</strong></li><li>&nbsp;<strong>Rooftop BBQ Area &amp; Outdoor Lounge</strong></li><li><strong>Jogging Track</strong>&nbsp;around the landscaped podium</li><li><strong>Sauna &amp; Spa Facilities</strong>&nbsp;on the rooftop</li></ol><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><ul><li><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ (150–156 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<em>From KES 19.5M</em></li><li><strong>4 Bedroom + DSQ (201–230 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<em>From KES 26.3M</em></li></ul><p><br></p>'),(4805,'property',331,'zh','short_description','<p>Amani RESIDENCE是一个位于Westlands市中心的独家现代住宅开发项目。这座优雅的18层公寓专为现代城市生活而设计，提供3卧室和4卧室的高档公寓，配备家政服务人员。</p>'),(4806,'property',332,'zh','property_name','舒适的住宅'),(4807,'property',332,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(4808,'property',332,'zh','description','<p>Discover comfortable city living in this charming residence located in the heart of Kileleshwa, set in a serene and secure neighborhood, the home offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and everyday comfort. The spacious interiors are thoughtfully designed with ample natural light creating a warm welcoming atmosphere.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>Solar hot water system and Water tank storage system</p><p>Four units per floor, two elevators for each block</p><p>Visitor reception room</p><p>Rooftop lounge</p><p>Gym</p><p>Children play area</p><p>Common and adequate parking slots</p><p>Fire protection system and facilities</p><p>Borehole</p><p>Standby generator</p><p>Swimming pool</p><p>24 hours CCTV surveillance system for car parking area</p><p>Vehicle access control</p><p><br></p><p>Unit sizes and prices:</p><p><br></p><p><strong>4 Bedrooms plus DSQ 272 Sqm From Ksh. 23M</strong></p>'),(4809,'property',332,'zh','short_description','<p>这座迷人的住宅位于Kileleshwa市中心，坐落在一个宁静安全的街区，探索舒适的城市生活，提供现代便利和日常舒适的完美融合。宽敞的室内设计经过精心设计，自然光线充足，营造出温馨温馨的氛围。</p>'),(4814,'property',333,'zh','property_name','LESONIA RESIDENCY'),(4815,'property',333,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa ， Tinderet大道'),(4816,'property',333,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>*Affordable 1 &amp; 2 &amp;3Bedroom Apartments for</strong></h3><h3><strong>Sale</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Unit Sizes &amp; Prices :</p><p><br></p><p>? 1 Bedroom Apartments</p><p>•	55 sqm — KSh 5.5 – 6.5M</p><p>•	65 sqm — KSh 6.5 – 7.7M</p><p>•	68 sqm — KSh 7.0 –&nbsp;8.0M</p><p>? 2 Bedroom Apartments</p><p>•	110 sqm — KSh 12.5 – 14M</p><p>•	115 sqm — KSh 13 – 15M</p><p>? 3 Bedroom Apartments</p><p>•	150 sqm — KSh 17.1– 18M</p><p>•	155 sqm — KSh 17.3 - 18.3M</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities</p><p><br></p><p>✨Heated infinity swimming pool</p><p>✨Fully equipped modern gym&nbsp;</p><p>✨Sauna room &amp; yoga studio</p><p>✨Children’s Paradise &amp; Play Area&nbsp;</p><p>✨Business Center and Meeting room</p><p>✨Hight Speed Internet Connectivity&nbsp;</p><p>✨Art Space Coffee bar &amp; restaurant</p><p>✨Rooftop lounge and leisure zone&nbsp;</p><p>✨Open floor garden&nbsp;</p><p>✨Intelligent Access Control Systems</p><p>✨Ample Secure Parking Spaces</p><p>✨Full Backup Generator</p><p>✨Water Borehole for complete self sufficiency&nbsp;</p><p>✨24/7 Advanced Security with CCTV Surveillance&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Payment Plan:</p><p>A20% down payment, with the remaining 80% payable in installments until the house is completed. The balance can be made monthly or quarterly, whichever is more convenient for you.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>? Prime Location: Intersection Gatundu Road and Tinderet Avenue</p><p>Completion: December 2028</p>'),(4817,'property',333,'zh','short_description','<p>Lesonia Residency是位于Kileleshwa中心的精致住宅，提供精心设计的1,2卧室和3卧室公寓，融合了舒适性、风格和功能性。</p>'),(4826,'property',334,'zh','property_name','5卧室联排别墅'),(4827,'property',334,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa, Mandera Road'),(4828,'property',334,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Rent: Ksh 400,000 per month</p><p>Availability: Immediate</p><p>Land Size: 1.5 Acres</p><p>Rent Includes: Service Charge</p><p><br></p><p>Property Overview</p><p><br></p><p>This elegant and spacious 5-bedroom villa is located in a quiet, secure gated community along Mandera Road, Kileleshwa. Sitting on a generous 1.5-acre plot, the home offers expansive indoor and outdoor living spaces, ideal for family living or executive residence.</p><p><br></p><p>Key Features</p><p>	•	Well-lit entrance hallway</p><p>	•	Large living room with adjacent dining area</p><p>	•	Floor-to-ceiling wall-to-wall windows offering abundant natural light</p><p>	•	Living area opening directly to the garden</p><p>	•	Spacious closed-plan kitchen with pantry</p><p>	•	Detached DSQ for two</p><p>	•	Garage accommodating two vehicles</p><p>	•	Master bedroom plus two additional bedrooms are en-suite</p><p>	•	Two spacious bedrooms sharing a common bathroom and toilet</p><p>	•	Ample wardrobe space in all bedrooms</p><p>	•	All bedrooms open onto an all-round balcony</p><p>	•	Small private office/study area</p><p>	•	Guest washroom at the entrance</p><p><br></p><p>Amenities</p><p>	•	Large landscaped garden at the back and an extra-large garden at the front</p><p>	•	Borehole and additional water storage tanks</p><p>	•	Parking space for 10–15 vehicles</p><p>	•	Enhanced security with a manned gated entrance</p><p><br></p><p>Location: Quiet, secure, and highly sought-after neighborhood in Kileleshwa.</p><p><br></p><p>For viewings or more information, please get in touch.</p>'),(4833,'property',336,'zh','property_name','舒适的出租住宅'),(4834,'property',336,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(4835,'property',336,'zh','description','<p>This comfort focused apartment offers a relaxed yet stylish living experience, ideal for families, professionals or couples seeking quality rental living in a secure ,modern setting .</p><p><br></p><h3>Property Highlights :</h3><p>Spacious and airy interiors</p><p>Comfortable bedrooms</p><p>Modern kitchen</p><p>Balcony/ scenic views</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>On-site amenities:</strong></h3><p>Solar hot water system and Water tank storage system</p><p>Four units per floor, two elevators for each block</p><p>Visitor reception room</p><p>Rooftop lounge</p><p>Gym</p><p>Children play area</p><p>Common and adequate parking slots</p><p>Fire protection system and facilities</p><p>Borehole</p><p>Standby generator</p><p>Swimming pool</p><p>24 hours CCTV surveillance system for car parking area</p><p>Vehicle access control</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit size and prize:</strong></p><p><strong>272 sqm at Ksh 200,000 Per month</strong></p>'),(4836,'property',336,'zh','short_description','<p>这套以舒适为中心的公寓提供轻松而时尚的生活体验，非常适合在安全、现代的环境中寻求优质出租生活的家庭、专业人士或情侣。</p><h3><br></h3>'),(4847,'property',337,'zh','property_name','伯克利房源'),(4848,'property',337,'zh','detailed_address','Kileleshwa'),(4849,'property',337,'zh','description','<p>The development offers a mix of unit types suitable for different needs.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Lifestyle Amenities:</strong></h3><p>Designed to offer comfort, convenience, and community living:</p>