ing manageable yet spacious landholding with strong development potential.</p>'),(4933,'property',339,'zh','property_name','SYOKIMAU 0.5英亩待售'),(4934,'property',339,'zh','detailed_address','Katani'),(4935,'property',339,'zh','description','<p>Tucked within the steadily rising Katani neighborhood of Syokimau lies this half-acre gem, offering the rare combination of space, location and future value.</p><p>The plot is naturally flat and well- drained, saving on construction costs and allowing immediate development. It surroundings strike a balance between peaceful living and urban convenience ,with established homes nearby and ongoing infrastructure growth adding to the areas appeal.</p><p>With easy access to Mombasa Road, JKIA and the Nairobi CBD, this location connects you effortlessly to the city while giving you room to breathe away from congestion.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Size</strong>: 0.5 Acre</p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Katani, Syokimau</p><p><strong>Status: </strong> Ready for development</p><p><strong>Title</strong>: Clean and available</p>'),(4936,'property',339,'zh','short_description','<p>像这样的土地不仅仅是山谷-它创造了它。立即在Katani的成长故事中占据一席之地。</p>'),(4941,'property',340,'zh','property_name','KAWAIDA 0.035公顷待售'),(4942,'property',340,'zh','detailed_address','Tigoni'),(4943,'property',340,'zh','description','<p>Hidden within the misty green landscape that defines Tigoni, this 0.035-hectares parcel offers more than land- it offers a way of life. Waking up to crisp air, birdsong and uninterrupted views of rolling greenery becomes pat of everyday living here.</p><p>The plot sits on rich , well -drained red soil, ideal for building a cozy home or a refined weekend escape. It\'s size is perfectly balanced - generous enough for privacy, gardens and outdoor living yet manageable for effortless maintenance.</p><p>Located within reach of Limuru road and essential amenities, the property blends rural calm with modern convenience. The surrounding neighborhood is established, secure and quietly prestigious ,making this a smart choice for both lifestyle buyers and long-term investors.</p><p><br></p><p>This is a rare chance to own a personal retreat in Tigoni, where nature ,value and tranquility meet.</p>'),(4944,'property',340,'zh','short_description','<p>这是在自然、价值和宁静交汇的蒂戈尼拥有私人度假胜地的难得机会。</p>'),(4949,'property',341,'zh','property_name','卡马基斯0.035公顷待售'),(4950,'property',341,'zh','detailed_address','卡马基斯'),(4951,'property',341,'zh','description','<p>Discover an excellent investment opportunity in one of the fastest-growing neighborhoods off the eastern bypass in Kamakis , Ruiru. </p><p>The land is flat, well drained and ready for immediate development , with water and electricity available nearby. It enjoys easy access via all -weather road and is surrounded  by established and upcoming residential residential developments.</p><p>Kamakis is one of the most sought-after locations due to its excellent connectivity to Nairobi, Thika Road and key amenities such as schools , shopping centres and public transport. The area continues to be a smart choice for both homeowners and investors.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key features:</strong></h3><p>Size: 0.035 hectares </p><p>Prime location in Kamakis Ruiru</p><p>Ideal for residential development</p><p>Flat and ready for construction</p><p>Utilities available </p><p>Clean title deed, ready for transfer</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(4952,'property',341,'zh','short_description','<p>不要错过这个在Ruiru发展最快的街区之一拥有一块黄金地段的机会，确保您在Kamakis的未来。</p>'),(4953,'property',342,'zh','property_name','BROOKSIDE OAK RESIDENCY '),(4954,'property',342,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(4955,'property',342,'zh','description','<p>Brookside oak residency offers refined living in a serene ,well -connected neighborhood designed for comfort and convenience .Surrounded by mature oak trees and landscaped green spaces ,this residence blends modern architecture with a calm community -focused environment.</p><p>Brookside oak residency is ideal for 