356,'zh','short_description','<p>拥有一块Tigoni无与伦比的美景-自然声望和机会相遇的地方。</p>'),(4985,'property',357,'zh','property_name','TIGONI 50英亩待售'),(4986,'property',357,'zh','detailed_address','Tigoni'),(4987,'property',357,'zh','description','<p>Seize this rare opportunity to own 50 acres of fertile land in Tigoni, a highly sought -after area known for its cool climate ,lush greenery and tranquil environment.</p><p>With easy access vial all weather roads, nearby electricity, water and proximity to Limuru Town and Nairobi ,this property offers the ideal combination of serenity and convenience. It\'s undulating terrain and scenic views make it a perfect canvas for your vision.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>50 acres in a single contiguous block</p><p>Fertile well drained land</p><p>Ideal for farming ,estates or eco-projects</p><p>Excellent road access and nearby utilities</p><p>Peaceful secure neighborhood with investment potential</p><p>Clear title ready for transfer</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Acres and price:</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>50 </strong>Acres at Ksh 27000000 per acre</p>'),(4988,'property',357,'zh','short_description','<p>像这样在Tigoni的50英亩土地不会在市场上停留很长时间-今天就宣称您的天堂</p>'),(4989,'property',358,'zh','property_name','REDHILL 4英亩待售'),(4990,'property',358,'zh','detailed_address','红山'),(4991,'property',358,'zh','description','<p>Set in the prestigious and fast- growing Redhill area off Limuru Road, this expensive 4 -acre parcel of land presents an opportunity for investors, developers or buyers seeking space and exclusivity within close proximity to Nairobi.</p><p>The area is well serviced with essential utilities available nearby and continues to experience steady appreciation due to ongoing residential and infrastructure development.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Development potential:</strong></h3><p>Ideal for residential homes, gated estate development or boutique housing projects</p><p>The neighborhood is growing rapidly with quality development