ing natural light throughout the space.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Experience unparalleled convenience and luxury with:</p><ul><li><strong>Intercom System</strong>&nbsp;for seamless communication</li><li><strong>Yoga Room</strong>&nbsp;to rejuvenate your body and mind</li><li><strong>State-of-the-Art Gym</strong>&nbsp;for fitness enthusiasts</li><li><strong>Kids’ Indoor Play Area</strong>&nbsp;for endless fun and safety</li><li><strong>Convenient On-Site Shop</strong></li><li><strong>2 Heated Swimming Pools</strong>&nbsp;(for adults and kids)</li><li><strong>Gentlemen &amp; Ladies Public Toilets</strong></li><li><strong>Shower Locker Rooms</strong>&nbsp;for post-swim convenience</li><li><strong>Elegant Reception Area</strong>&nbsp;to welcome guests</li><li><strong>Rooftop View Restaurant</strong>&nbsp;for scenic dining</li></ul><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>1 Bedroom (67.19sqm-72.6sqm) Kes 7.6M-7.9M</strong></li><li><strong>1 Bedroom + Study (76.9sqm-81.6sqm) Kes 8.5M-9M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom (103.5sqm) Kes 11M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom + Study (114.2sqm) Kes 12,5M</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(5132,'property',367,'zh','short_description','<p>Amto Residence-where everyday living feels effortlessly right.</p>'),(5133,'property',368,'zh','property_name','出售0.5英亩RIDGEWAYS'),(5134,'property',368,'zh','detailed_address','Muthaiga'),(5135,'property',368,'zh','description','<p>Discover your perfect canvas for building your your dream home or investment property in one of Nairobi\'s most sought-after neighborhoods.</p><p>Why This Land?</p><p>Set in a tranquil and secure locale, this half -acre parcel offers an exceptional opportunity to build with flexibility and privacy. Ridgeways is known for its blend of upscale residential living and convenient access to major transport links, schools ,shopping and recreational  facilities.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Property highlights:</strong></p><ul><li>Location : Ridgeways ,Nairobi - a serene and prestigious address close to key ameenities</li><li>Size: 0.5 acres</li><li>Ideal for : Luxury residence ,gated home, duplex project or a boutique deveelopment</li><li>Title: Clean and ready for transfer</li><li>Access: Good road frontage with easy access to tarmacked road</li><li>Utilities: Water and electricity available at site</li><li>Environment: Quiet, leafy neighborhood with established homes and gardens</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(5136,'property',369,'zh','property_name','LESTO RESIDENCES'),(5137,'property',369,'zh','detailed_address','Ojijo Road'),(5138,'property',369,'zh','description','<p>Discover refined urban living at Lesto Residences, an exclusive residential development tucked away on Ojijo close Westlands. This low- density development offers thoughtfully planned 1- and 2- bedroom apartments ideal for homeowners and investors alike.</p><p><br></p><h3>✨Project Highlight:</h3><p>? Low-density luxury Apartments with 96 units (14 Floor High)</p><p>? Easy access to GTC, Malls, Sport Club &amp; Hospitals</p><h3><br></h3><h3>Lifestyle &amp; Wellness Amenities:</h3><p><br></p><p>▪️Indoor Swimming Pool</p><p>▪️Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>▪️Mini Café, Mini Bar only for Resident</p><p>▪️Full Rooftop Garden</p><p>▪️Children’s play Zone&nbsp;</p><p>▪️24/7 security, CCTV &amp; full backup generator</p><p><br></p><h3>Unit Options &amp; Price:</h3><p><br></p><p>1 Bedroom | 67 sqm | From Ksh 6.90 M</p><p>1 Bedroom with Study | 83 sqm | From Ksh 8.50 M</p><p>2 Bedroom | 105 sqm | From Ksh 10.50 M</p><p><br></p><p>Payment Plan: Flexible installments available</p><p><br></p><p>Excavation Finished. Completion date April 2027.</p>'),(5139,'property',369,'zh','short_description','<p>体验宁静的生活和城市便利的完美平衡。LESTO距离城市首屈一指的便利设施仅几分钟路程，提供无与伦比的无障碍设施，同时提供宁静的度假胜地。精致生活和明智投资的绝佳机会。</p>'),(5148,'property',370,'zh','property_name','4间卧室+ DSQ'),(5149,'property',370,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(5150,'property',370,'zh','description','<p>Located in the serene and fast-growing neighborhood of Mugutha,Ruiru, this well designed 4 bedroom residence offers much more than an ordinary home.</p><p>The home features a generous living and dinning area with with ample natural light, creating warm and welcoming atmosphere. The modern kitchen is well laid out with sufficient storage and workspace making it both practical and functional for daily living.</p><p><br></p><p>Set within a quiet residential environment, the property enjoys easy access to Thika Road, Ruiru Town, schools, shopping centers, and other essential amenities, while still maintaining a calm and secure setting.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features:</strong></h3><p>4 spacious bedrooms (master ensuite)</p><p>Bright and airy living &amp; dining area</p><p>Modern kitchen with ample storage</p><p>Well-ventilated rooms with good natural lighting</p><p>Secure and family-friendly neighborhood</p><p>Ample parking space</p><p>Reliable water and electricity supply</p><p>This residence offers excellent value for homeowners or investors looking to settle in one of Ruiru’s most promising locations.</p><p><br></p>'),(5151,'property',370,'zh','short_description','<p>在安静、人脉广阔的街区中称之为家的完美场所-为veiwing todaty安排时间表</p>'),(5152,'property',371,'zh','property_name','5间卧室+ DSQ'),(5153,'property',371,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(5154,'property',371,'zh','description','<p>Welcome to your dream residence at Amari Homes, Ruiru — a stunning modern home designed for comfort, style, and family living. Built by Amari Homes, known for elegant and durable properties that support today’s lifestyle, this home offers exceptional quality and thoughtful design throughout.</p><p><br></p><p>? Prime Location:</p><p><br></p><p>Located in the desirable Ruiru Mugutha area — just off Thika Road with easy access to key amenities, major transport routes, schools, shopping centers, and business hubs within the greater Nairobi metropolitan region.</p><p><br></p><p>?️ Spacious &amp; Elegant Living:</p><p><br></p><p>* 5 generously sized bedrooms, all designed to maximize comfort and natural light — perfect for families large and small.</p><p>* Many units feature ensuite bathrooms for privacy and convenience.</p><p>* Comfortable living spaces ideal for relaxing, entertaining, or quality family time.</p><p><br></p><p>? Modern Features &amp; Finishes:</p><p><br></p><p>* Clean, contemporary architectural style with flat roof design and modern finishes.</p><p>* Open-plan concept living areas that flow seamlessly from lounge to dining.</p><p>* Well-appointed kitchen ready to handle family meals and gatherings.</p><p>* Dedicated spaces such as family room, storage, and potentially staff quarters</p><p><br></p><p>? Secure Community Living:</p><p><br></p><p>* Set within a gated community — offering enhanced privacy and peace of mind.</p><p>* Perimeter fencing and controlled access help create a safe environment for families.</p><p><br></p><p>? Practical &amp; Convenient:</p><p><br></p><p>* Ample parking space for residents and visitors.</p><p>* Easy access to public transport and major roads, putting Nairobi CBD and surrounding towns within reach.</p>'),(5155,'property',371,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到您梦寐以求的Ruiru Amari Homes住宅</p>'),(5190,'property',113,'zh','short_description','<p>探索这处位于内罗毕工业区中心、Mugumoini路沿线的黄金地段。</p>'),(5246,'property',216,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到<strong>Kitisuru Falls Residence （ KFR ）</strong>&nbsp;，这是一个超现代化的门禁社区，坐落在宁静的Kibichiku街区，毗邻著名的新Kitisuru郊区。该开发项目俯瞰风<strong>景秀丽的格塔图鲁瀑布（ Getathuru Falls</strong> ） ，旨在将当代建筑与大自然相结合，提供宁静而紧密相连的生活方式。</p>'),(5256,'property',29,'zh','short_description','<p>该物业是投资者的理想选择，完美融合了隐私、安全、空间和便利的基本便利设施。</p>'),(5456,'property',194,'zh','short_description','<p>玫瑰木公园宽敞的3卧室公寓，乞力马尼时尚的城市生活</p>'),(5474,'property',191,'zh','short_description','<p>欢迎来到Brookside One Residency Apartment For Sale In Westlands ，这是一处首屈一指的房地产开发项目，位于内罗毕最负盛名的街区之一，提供现代化、宽敞、设计优雅的公寓。无论您是在寻找梦寐以求的房源还是有利可图的投资机会，这些豪华公寓都能完美融合舒适、便利和高端生活</p>'),(5481,'property',189,'zh','short_description','<p>在风景优美、宁静的乞力马尼（ Kilimani ）沿线</p><p>Elgeyo Marakwet路，可轻松抵达最好的地方</p><p>购物中心、学校和娱乐中心。</p>'),(5485,'property',188,'zh','short_description','<p>这座现代化的开发项目位于著名的General Mathenge路沿线，提供宽敞的3卧室和4卧室单元，包括3张床和DSQ以及豪华的4床双层公寓。它拥有高品质的装饰、专业的工艺，靠近顶级便利设施，在市中心完美融合了时尚、舒适和便利。</p>'),(5536,'property',372,'zh','property_name','ROSSLYN 0.6公顷待售'),(5537,'property',372,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5538,'property',372,'zh','description','<p>Set on a generous 0.6 hectares, this rare Rosslyn property offers freedom and vision in equal measure. Whether you\'re dreaming of a private estate , an investment project or a future-forward development, this expansive parcel is a blank canvas waiting for bold ideas.</p><p><br></p><p>With its impressive land size, this property invites possibilities that smaller plots can\'t offer-room to build, expand , landscape or reimagine entirely. Tucked within Rossyln , it balances accessibility with breathing space making it ideal for those who value both convenience and potential.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Potential features and enhancements:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Expansive 0.6-hectare canvas with endless design flexibility</p><p><br></p><p>Ample space for landscaped gardens, private driveways, or green zones</p><p><br></p><p>Natural sense of privacy and exclusivity due to generous land size</p><p><br></p><p>Perfect setting for outdoor living — patios, entertainment areas, or future leisure spaces</p><p><br></p><p>Strong future value appreciation potential in the Rosslyn area</p><p><br></p><p>Easy access to main routes and key amenities while maintaining a peaceful feel</p><p><br></p><p>Opportunity for custom boundary design (walls, fencing, or natural borders)</p><p><br></p><p>Suitable for eco-friendly or modern architectural concepts</p><p><br></p><p>Rare chance to own a large, versatile parcel in a growing location</p>'),(5539,'property',372,'zh','short_description','<p>这种规模的土地并不经常出现。这不仅仅是一个情节，而是一个塑造持久事物的机会。</p>'),(5547,'property',373,'zh','property_name','0.1965 IN ROSSLYN TRIO待售'),(5548,'property',373,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5549,'property',373,'zh','description','<p>This 0.1965-hectare parcel in Rosslyn isn\'t trying to impress loudly. It doesn\'t  have to. It sits with quiet confidence, waiting for someone who understands that the most valuable spaces are the ones you shape yourself. </p><p><br></p><p>Nearly half an acre of possibility, framed by an established setting and the kind of calm that can\'t be manufactured. This is land of thinkers, builders and dreamers who want more than square meters-they want meaning in what they create.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Property Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Excellent frontage allowing flexible  architectural  layout</p><p><br></p><p>Prime Rosslyn location in a well-established neighborhood</p><p><br></p><p>Ideal for bespoke residential development or long-term investment</p><p><br></p><p>Ample space for a main residence, gardens, and outdoor living areas</p><p><br></p><p>Quiet surroundings with a sense of privacy and exclusivity</p><p><br></p><p>Flat / build-ready terrain (adjust if needed)</p><p><br></p><p>Good road access with easy connectivity to key routes</p><p><br></p><p>Strong area value retention and growth potential</p><p><br></p><p>Freedom of design — create a home that reflects your vision</p><p><br></p><p>Rare plot size for the area</p><p><br></p><h3>\"Land like this doesn\'t  announce itself -it waits for the right owner , be one.\"</h3><p><br></p>'),(5550,'property',373,'zh','short_description','<p>无论您是在建造个人避难所，还是在一个始终具有吸引力的地方保护土地，这片土地都会悄悄地说： “建造持久的东西。”</p>'),(5551,'property',374,'zh','property_name','RUIRU棕榈阁宁静别墅'),(5552,'property',374,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(5553,'property',374,'zh','description','<h3><strong>ICONIC 5-Bedroom All En-Suite Maisonette — For Sale!</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>? Location: Ruiru, near Spur Mall, along Thika Superhighway&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>?<strong> Property Overview:</strong></h3><p>* Type: 5-Bedroom Maisonette (All En-Suite)</p><p>* Plinth Area: 320 sqm</p><p>* Plot Size: 50 x 100 ft</p><p>* Parking: Ample space for up to 5 cars</p><p>* Garden: Well-manicured front garden</p><p>* Finishes: High-quality finishes with modern gypsum ceilings &amp; stylish lighting fixtures</p><p><br></p><h3>?<strong> Interior Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p><strong>Lounge &amp; Dining</strong></p><p>* Spacious lounge area</p><p>* Separate dining area overlooking the garden</p><p>* Large windows allowing plenty of natural light</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Kitchen</strong></p><p>* Modern open-plan kitchen</p><p>* Fitted with an oven, microwave, hob , extractor hood and a dishwasher&nbsp;</p><p>* Additional chef’s kitchen with a pantry</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Bedrooms</strong></p><p>* Inbuilt MDF wardrobes in all bedrooms</p><p>* Master bedroom with a walk-in closet, jacuzzi &amp; private balcony</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Bathrooms</strong></p><p>* Elegant shower cubicles</p><p>* Common cloakroom</p><p><br></p><p>?<strong> Outdoor &amp; Rooftop Features</strong></p><p>* Accessible roof terrace with two rooftop areas</p><p>* Pergola and umbrella seating area</p><p>* Kitchen setup and common washroom</p><p>* Rooftop water tank</p><p><br></p><p>? <strong>Security &amp; Utilities</strong></p><p>* Connected to the main sewer line</p><p>* Perimeter wall with electric fence and razor wire</p><p>* Water from both County supply and Borehole</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Estate Amenities</strong></p><p>* Jogging track</p><p>* Swimming pool</p><p>* Tennis &amp; basketball courts</p><p>* Clubhouse with gym, kitchenette &amp; multipurpose hall</p><p><br></p><p><strong>? Price: Ksh 25,500,000</strong></p><p><strong>(Available for cash or mortgage)</strong></p><p><strong>? Title: Ready Freehold Title Deed</strong></p>'),(5554,'property',374,'zh','short_description','<h3><strong>标志性的5卧室全套房公寓—出售！</strong></h3>'),(5563,'property',375,'zh','property_name','4卧独立式别墅'),(5564,'property',375,'zh','detailed_address','Gigiri'),(5565,'property',375,'zh','description','<p>This 4 bedroom stand-alone villa is more than a home-its a statement of space  and self-contained living. Designed for those who value privacy without isolation, the villa  stands confidently on its own, offering a rare blend of architectural  presence and everyday comfort.</p><p><br></p><p>Inside, the layout unfolds with intention. Each bedroom feels like its own sanctuary, crafted to offer quiet moments away from the rhythm of the household. </p><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\">Features&nbsp;:</strong></h3><p>Newly renovated&nbsp;</p><p>All bedrooms en-suite</p><p>2 DSQs&nbsp;</p><p>Landscaped gardens&nbsp;</p><p>Borehole&nbsp;</p><p>Water storage tanks&nbsp;</p><p>Parking space for  6-7cars</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Location advantage:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Strategic and prestigious location </p><p>Unrivalled security and privacy</p><p>World- class amenities nearby, the village market </p><p>Green and relaxed environment as it boarders Karura forest</p><p>Excellent connectivity- well connected via Limuru road and major city arteries</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Where every day feels quietly elevated-this is not just a place to live ,but a place to belong, in the heart of Gigiri.</p>'),(5566,'property',375,'zh','short_description','<p>在吉吉里（ Gigiri ）市中心，这里不仅是一个居住的地方，也是一个归属的地方，每天都能感受到宁静的高度。</p>'),(5567,'property',376,'zh','property_name','两卧室乡村民宿'),(5568,'property',376,'zh','detailed_address','利穆鲁'),(5569,'property',376,'zh','description','<p>A charming 2-bedroom country home featuring a master ensuite, high-end finishes, and a functional fireplace for cozy evenings. Enjoy outdoor living with a gazebo + fireplace and a shaded carport.</p><p><br></p><p>? Prime location near Ridge Cabin Resort, Kentmere Club, Limuru Country Club, Two Rivers Mall, St. Ruth School.</p><p><br></p><p>KES 120,000 per month (Service charge inclusive)</p><p><br></p><p> 24-hour security with controlled entry</p><p>Fully fitted kitchen with ample storage</p><p>Kids play area</p><p>CCTV Surveillance&nbsp;</p><p> Garbage collection</p><p>Private garden or backyard</p><p>Stand- alone structure offering full privacy</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>? Quiet • Secure • Lifestyle living</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Step into a home where every detail is designed for comfort, privacy and effortless living -your perfect two- bedroom  retreat awaits.</p>'),(5570,'property',376,'zh','short_description','<p>舒适的双卧室独立房源，融合了隐私、舒适和简约。房间明亮通风，布局设计便于生活，是完美的度假胜地，每个角落都像自己的一样。</p>'),(5571,'property',377,'zh','property_name','以太住宅'),(5572,'property',377,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5573,'property',377,'zh','description','<p>Modern 1 &amp; 2 Bedroom Apartments on Lantana Road, Westlands, Nairobi</p><p><br></p><p>Discover refined urban living at Aether Residences, a contemporary residential development ideally located along Lantana Road in the heart of Westlands.</p><p><br></p><p>? Limited Early-Bird Discount: KES 500,000?</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities include:</strong></h3><p>? Rooftop infinity pool with city views</p><p>? Padel Court on rooftop&nbsp;</p><p>?️ Restaurant</p><p>☕ Café</p><p>?‍♂️ Fully equipped gym</p><p>? Hotel-style lobby</p><p>? Convenience store</p><p>⚡ Fully back-up generator</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit Types:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Studio | 43-50 sqm | from KES 6M&nbsp;</p><p>One-bedroom | 57-60 sqm | from KES 6.5M</p><p>Two-bedroom with DSQ | 95-120sqm | from KES 10.5-12M&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\">Investment Highlights</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\">:</span></h3><p>High rental demand from professionals, expats &amp; embassy staff</p><p>Attractive rental yields</p><p>Strong capital appreciation potential</p><p>Prime Westlands location with easy access to CBD, Parklands &amp; Waiyaki Way</p><p><br></p><p>Book your unit today with flexible payment options.</p>'),(5574,'property',377,'zh','short_description','<p>在Aether Residences探索精致的城市生活，这是一个现代住宅开发项目，位于Westlands市中心的Lantana路沿线。</p><p><br></p>'),(5575,'property',378,'zh','property_name','牛津房源'),(5576,'property',378,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5577,'property',378,'zh','description','<p>Discover a thoughtfully designed residential development offering spacious, modern apartments in a secure and well-connected neighborhood. Ideal for both homeowners seeking comfort and investors looking for solid value.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Internal features:</strong></p><p>✨ Alarm system</p><p>⚡ Backup generator</p><p>? Fibre internet connectivity</p><p>? Walk-in closets</p><p>❄️ Air conditioning</p><p>?️ Furnished options available</p><p><br></p><p><strong>External Amenities &amp; Lifestyle Features:</strong></p><p>? Balcony spaces</p><p>? CCTV &amp; electric fence</p><p>? Borehole water supply</p><p>?️ Fully equipped gym</p><p>? Lift / elevator access</p><p>? Ample parking</p><p>♿ Wheelchair-friendly access</p><p>? Secure gated community</p><p>? BBQ area</p><p>? Pet-friendly environment</p><p>? Landscaped garden areas</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Nearby Conveniences</strong></p><p>? Bus stop</p><p>? Hospitals</p><p>? Schools</p><p>?️ Shopping centres</p><p>? Scenic views &amp; social amenities</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Available Unit Types:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•1 Bedroom – 70 sqm From Ksh 6.8M</p><p>•1 Bedroom – 90 sqm From Ksh 8M</p><p>•2 Bedroom – 110 sqm From Ksh 10.5M</p><p>•2 Bedroom – 120 sqm From Ksh 11.5M</p>'),(5578,'property',378,'zh','short_description','<p>探索精心设计的住宅开发项目，在安全、交通便利的街区提供宽敞、现代化的公寓。非常适合寻求舒适的房主和寻求坚实价值的投资者。</p><p><br></p>'),(5594,'property',379,'zh','property_name','88内罗毕公寓'),(5595,'property',379,'zh','detailed_address','Upper hill'),(5596,'property',379,'zh','description','<p>Located at the corner of 4th Ngong Avenue and Bishops Road in Upper Hill, 88 Nairobi is an iconic 47-storey luxury residential tower developed by Lordship Africa. It is designed to be the tallest residential building in Sub-Saharan Africa, standing at a height of 150 to 176 metres.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Structural &amp; General Details:</strong></p><p>•	Floors: 47 floors in total.</p><p>•	Units: Approximately 288 high-end luxury condominiums.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Apartment Types:</strong></p><p>The building offers fully furnished residences tailored for corporate executives:</p><p>•	Executive: Studio, 1, 2, and 3-bedroom layouts.</p><p>•	Executive Plus: Elevated 1, 2, and 3-bedroom units (floors 34-38).</p><p>•	Sky Suites: Feature 3.25m ceilings and private balcony Jacuzzis.</p><p>•	Penthouses: Located on the 40th floor and above, featuring 4m ceilings and private swimming pools.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>•	Sky-High Leisure: A 21-meter heated infinity pool on the 34th floor and a sunset deck.</p><p>•	Fitness &amp; Wellness: 24/7 gym, private spa suites, and Turkish baths.</p><p>•	Business &amp; Dining: Branded 150-seat restaurant, resident bars, co-working space, and meeting rooms.</p><p>•	Convenience: Private helipad, 518 parking spaces, and valet services.</p><p>•	High-Speed Lifts: Seven passenger Schindler lifts and one service elevator.</p><p>•	Standards: Built to EU and UN security and fire safety standards.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Apartment prices at 88 Nairobi vary significantly based on the unit type, floor level, and furnishing status. As of February 2025, starting prices for these luxury condominiums are as follows:&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Sales Prices (Off plan &amp; Current)</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•	Studio Units (33–35 sqm): Starting from $105,000 to $108,000 (approx. KSh 13.5M–14M).</p><p>•	1-Bedroom Units (48–55 sqm): Starting from $187,845. Some listing sites quote entry-level one-bedroom units from KSh 13,400,000.</p><p>•	2-Bedroom Units (99–102 sqm): Starting from $212,600 to $281,400.</p><p>•	3-Bedroom Units: Starting from $462,895.</p><p>•	Executive Plus &amp; Sky Suites: Prices for these units, located on floors 34 and above, are typically higher and often available upon request.</p><p>•	Penthouses: The most exclusive units (40th floor and above) can exceed KSh 100 million ($1M+).</p>'),(5597,'property',379,'zh','short_description','<p>永恒的地址，卓越的回报和无与伦比的声望-欢迎来到88内罗毕</p>'),(5602,'property',380,'zh','property_name','BAYSTAR RESIDENCE'),(5603,'property',380,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(5604,'property',380,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Rising elegantly along George Padmore Road in Kimani, this 22-floor residential tower redefines urban living in one of Nairobi’s most connected and vibrant neighbourhoods, placing residents minutes from key business, lifestyle and social amenities.</p><p><br></p><p>With commanding views over the Nairobi skyline, the State House’s lush greenery and the Ngong Hills’ glowing sunsets, the development blends luxury finishes, everyday convenience and rare serenity into a singular address for homeowners and investors alike.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Premium Amenities:</strong></p><p>The development includes a wide range of lifestyle and productivity facilities:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Wellness: Infinity pool, rooftop jogging track, fully equipped gym, yoga centre, and spa/sauna.</p><p>•	Leisure: Private cinema, rooftop lounge and garden, kids\' playroom, and a residents\' games hall.</p><p>•	Productivity: Dedicated co-working spaces, creatives\' studio, and laundry/concierge services.</p><p>•	Security &amp; Tech: Smart access systems, 24/7 security, high-speed lifts, and backup power/water.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Units are designed for both modern living and high-return investment (Airbnb-friendly) with the following starting prices:</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Studio Apartments:    35 Sqm  From Ksh 3 Million.</p><p>•	1 Bedroom Apartments: 55 Sqm From Ksh 5 Million.</p><p>•	2 Bedroom Apartments:   98 Sqm    From Ksh 9.5 Million.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>•	Deposit: Typically 20% to 30% down payment.</p><p>•	Payment Plan: Flexible 3-year plan with 0% interest spread over the remaining construction period.</p><p>•	Occupation Date: Expected completion in Q2 2028.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>'),(5605,'property',380,'zh','short_description','<p>这栋22层高的住宅大楼优雅地沿着基马尼的乔治·帕德莫尔路（ George Padmore Road ）崛起，重新定义了内罗毕最具连通性和充满活力的街区之一的城市生活，让居民距离主要的商务、生活方式和社交便利设施仅几分钟路程。</p>'),(5606,'property',381,'zh','property_name','PORINI POINT'),(5607,'property',381,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(5608,'property',381,'zh','description','<p>Porini Point is a new, premium residential development in Tatu City that launched in November 2025. Designed as a sanctuary-facing enclave, it features 570 modern apartments spread across 24 low-rise blocks (Ground + 4 floors). Construction is scheduled to commence in January 2026, with the first units expected to be ready by Q1 2027 and full completion by September 2029.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The development is centered around a landscaped courtyard and is situated just 200 metres from the 160-acre Tatu Wildlife Sanctuary.&nbsp;</p><p>•	Lifestyle: Includes a residents\' clubhouse, a swimming pool with a sun deck, a fully equipped gym, and a dedicated barbecue area.</p><p>•	Family-Friendly: Features safe children’s play zones, football pitches, and basketball courts.</p><p>•	Security: Gated entry with 24/7 CCTV surveillance and professional security management.</p><p>•	Convenience: Within walking distance of Tatu Central (CBD), international schools like Nova Pioneer and Crawford International, and various retail hubs.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Unit Type Size (sqm)	Starting Price (KES):</strong></p><p>1 Bedroom	54 – 60	7,500,000</p><p>2 Bedroom	90 – 92	10,070,000</p><p>3 Bedroom	145	16,200,000</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment Plans &amp; Investment:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Tatu City offers flexible financing options intended for both homeowners and investors, with projected rental yields of up to 18%–19%.&nbsp;</p><p>•	Installment Plan: A 24-month flexible payment plan is available.</p><p>•	Booking Fee: KES 200,000 (or USD 1,550) to reserve a unit, followed by a 10% deposit within 14 days.</p><p>•	Cash Discount: Discounts of up to 10.7% are available for outright cash purchases.</p><p>•	Financing: Sharia-compliant financing options are also supported.</p>'),(5609,'property',381,'zh','short_description','<p>Porini Point是塔图市的一个新的优质住宅开发项目，于2025年11月推出。它被设计成一个面向庇护所的飞地，拥有570套现代公寓，分布在24个低层街区（地面+ 4层）。施工计划于2026年1月开始，首批单元预计将于2027年第一季度完工，并于2029年9月全面竣工。</p>'),(5610,'property',382,'zh','property_name','JABALI TOWERS'),(5611,'property',382,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(5612,'property',382,'zh','description','<p>Jabali Towers is a premier high-rise, mixed-use development by Rendeavour located in the heart of Tatu Central, the business and living district of Tatu City. Launched in July 2025, the project is designed as a sustainable \"City in a Forest\" that integrates residential, office, and retail spaces.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Project Features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>The development features two residential towers of 20 and 31 storeys. Units range from studios to lavish penthouses with contemporary interiors inspired by Kenyan heritage.&nbsp;</p><p>Project Features</p><p>•	Mixed-Use Facilities: The complex includes 3,000 sqm of Grade-A office space, a 150-room 4-star hotel, and a retail district with 35 shops and 15 restaurants (including an \"Eat Street\").</p><p>•	Smart &amp; Green Living: Apartments feature smart home technology (keyless entry, intercom), floor-to-ceiling windows, and eco-friendly systems like solar lighting and rainwater harvesting.</p><p>•	Exclusive Amenities: Residents have access to an infinity pool, a fully equipped gym, steam and sauna, a business lounge, a gaming room, and private gardens.</p><p>•	Connectivity: Located 30 minutes from Nairobi CBD and JKIA, within walking distance of international schools (Nova Pioneer, Crawford) and the 100-acre Tatu Wildlife Sanctuary.&nbsp;</p><p>Investment &amp; Timeline</p><p>•	Completion Date: The estimated completion for Jabali Towers is December 2028.</p><p>•	ROI Potential: Investors can expect a projected Return on Investment (ROI) of up to 16% due to high rental demand in the Special Economic Zone (SEZ).</p><p>•	Payment Plan: Typical plans include a 25% down payment, with the balance spread over three years. Parking bays can be purchased separately for approximately KES 1.4M ($10,800).</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Residential Configuration &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Unit Type 	Typical Size	Starting Price (KES)	Price Range (USD)</p><p>Studio	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;43 sqm	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;From 6.1M – 8.35M	N/A</p><p>1 Bedroom	64 sqm	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;From 10.49M – 12.25M	$98,000 – $113,000</p><p>2 Bedroom	106–124 sqm	From 15.8M – 19.4M	$133,000 – $150,000</p><p>3 Bedroom	140–156 sqm	From 25.5M – 34.36M	$192,000 – $218,000</p><p>3 Bed Duplex	Up to 258 sqm	N/A	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$290,000 – $329,000</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(5613,'property',382,'zh','short_description','<p>Jabali Towers是Rendeavour的首屈一指的高层综合开发项目，位于塔图市的商业和生活区塔图中央的中心地带。该项目于2025年7月启动，旨在打造一个集住宅、办公和零售空间于一体的可持续“森林之城”。&nbsp;</p>'),(5614,'property',383,'zh','property_name','基安布0.5英亩待售'),(5615,'property',383,'zh','detailed_address','Njathaini Road'),(5616,'property',383,'zh','description','<p>An excellent opportunity to own 0.5 acres of prime land in the serene fast -growing area of Njathaini , Kiambu. The land is flat, well -drained and ready for development, making it ideal for a residential home, rental units or small -scale farming .</p><p>The property is located in a quiet ,secure neighborhood with a pleasant countryside feel ,yet conveniently close to the main access roads, schools ,shopping centers and other social amenities. Electricity and water are available nearby, ensuring easy connection.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unique features:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Flat and well-drained land-ideal for immediate development</p><p>Fertile soil ideal for farming or landscaping</p><p>Peaceful and secure neighborhood</p><p>Good access roads</p><p>Electricity and water available nearby</p><p>Close to schools, shopping centers and churches</p><p>Clean ownership with ready title deed</p><p><br></p><p>\" Invest now, build later , profit always .\"</p>'),(5617,'property',383,'zh','short_description','<p>“购买和平满足潜力的土地”</p>'),(5634,'property',384,'zh','property_name','GOLFSCAPE RESIDENCES'),(5635,'property',384,'zh','detailed_address','Ngong Road'),(5636,'property',384,'zh','description','<p>Tucked away in the lush ,tree -lined serenity of Muchai Drive yet seamlessly connected to the pulse of Nairobi through Ngong road, Golfscape residences is a new benchmark for luxury urban living. Here, the city\'s vibrance  meets tranquil exclusivity creating a live, work and play environment like no other. This iconic development presents a curated mix of boutique 1,2 and 3 bedroom apartments alongside 4-bedroom executive penthouses-each with expensive layouts, premium finishes and uninterrupted views across the Ngong Skyline , crowned by the Royal Nairobi Golf Club.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>World-Class Amenities</strong></h3><p>Golfscape Residences offers residents a luxurious and secure environment with top-tier facilities, including:</p><ul><li>Fully equipped&nbsp;<strong>fitness gym</strong></li><li><strong>Heated swimming pool</strong></li><li><strong>Backup generator</strong>&nbsp;for uninterrupted power supply</li><li><strong>24/7 manned security gate</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>CCTV surveillance</strong></li><li><strong>Rooftop communal space</strong>&nbsp;for relaxation and entertainment</li><li><strong>An intercom system</strong>&nbsp;for easy communication</li></ul><p><br></p><h3><strong>Location advantage:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Situated along&nbsp;<strong>Ngong Road</strong>, Golfscape Residences provides quick access to major business hubs, shopping centers, hospitals, and schools. Enjoy proximity to:</p><ul><li>The Junction Mall</li><li>Prestige Plaza</li><li>Nairobi Hospital</li><li>Karen and Kilimani neighborhoods</li><li>Major transport routes</li></ul><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prizes</strong></h3><p><br></p><p><strong>Type A – 1 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>5.6M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>46.15 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>6.9M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>57.91 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>7.5M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>64.55 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>9.1M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>69.54 sqm</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Type B – 2 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>10.3M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>79.05 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>10.5M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>80.65 sqm / 88.64 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>12.5M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>102.14 sqm</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>12.8M</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>102.8 sqm</strong></li></ul><p><strong>3 Bedroom Apartments (sold out)</strong></p><ul><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>13.5M | 114.00 sqm&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p><a href=\"https://ravihomes.co.ke/property/highpoint-336-residences-kilimani-nairobi/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Executive Penthouses</strong></a></p><ul><li>KES<strong>&nbsp;26.5M | 221.31 sqm&nbsp;</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>28M | 234.26 sqm&nbsp;</strong></li><li>KES&nbsp;<strong>31M | 258.79 sqm&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p><strong><span class=\"ql-cursor\">﻿</span></strong></p><p><strong>Estimated Completion:</strong>&nbsp;July 2027</p><p>?&nbsp;<strong>Payment Plan:</strong>&nbsp;Flexible installments over&nbsp;<strong>24 months</strong></p><p><br></p>'),(5739,'property',385,'zh','property_name','行政套房'),(5740,'property',385,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5741,'property',385,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Introducing Executive Suites, an exclusive new residential development nestled in the serene, prestigious, and sought-after neighbourhoods offering a full mix of 1, 2, and 3-bedroom residences FROM Kshs. 7.2M, including select units with DSQ, to cater to diverse lifestyle needs and investment strategies.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Enjoy an array of world-class features:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h3><p>Arrival concierge</p><p>Waiting lounge</p><p>Restaurant</p><p>Café</p><p>Garden/courtyard</p><p>Gym</p><p>Swimming pool</p><p>Convenient Store</p><p>Reading Area</p><p>Kid’s Play Area</p><p>Rooftop Garden/courtyard</p><p>Rooftop Sports Area</p><p>Smart access solutions offering a full mix of 1, 2, and 3-bedroom residences FROM Kshs. 7.2M, including select units with DSQ, to cater to diverse lifestyle needs and investment strategies.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><p>A1 – 3 Bedroom | Size: 174 sqm&nbsp;- From Ksh. 21M - 22.62M&nbsp;</p><p>A2 – 3 Bedroom | Size: 174 sqm&nbsp;- From Ksh. 21M - 22.62M&nbsp;</p><p>A3 – 2 Bedroom with DSQ | Size: 129 sqm&nbsp;- From Ksh. 15.48M - 16.77M&nbsp;</p><p>A4 – 2 Bedroom with DSQ | Size: 129 sqm&nbsp;- From Ksh. 15.48M - 16.77M&nbsp;</p><p>___________&nbsp;</p><p>B1 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 114 sqm - From Ksh. 13.68M - 14.82M&nbsp;</p><p>B2 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 114 sqm - From Ksh. 13.68M - 14.82M&nbsp;</p><p>B3 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 117 sqm - From Ksh. 14M - 15.2M&nbsp;</p><p>B4 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 117 sqm - From Ksh. 14M - 15.2M&nbsp;</p><p>B5 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 114 sqm - From Ksh. 13.68M - 14.82M&nbsp;</p><p>B6 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 114 sqm - From Ksh. 13.68M - 14.82M&nbsp;</p><p>___________&nbsp;</p><p>C1 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 61 sqm - From Ksh. 7.3M - 7.93M</p><p>C2 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 60 sqm - From Ksh. 7.2M - 7.8M&nbsp;</p><p>C3 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 66 sqm - From Ksh. 7.9M - 8.58M&nbsp;</p><p>C4 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 73 sqm - From Ksh. 8.7M - 9.49M&nbsp;</p><p>C5 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 75 sqm - From Ksh. 9M - 9.75M&nbsp;</p><p>C6 – 1 Bedroom | Size: 81 sqm - From Ksh. 9.7M - 10.53M&nbsp;</p><p>C7 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 84 sqm - From Ksh. 10M - 10.92M&nbsp;</p><p>C8 – 2 Bedroom | Size: 84 sqm - From Ksh. 10M - 10.92M&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Construction is set to begin soon, offering investors an excellent opportunity for flexible payment plans and early equity growth.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>PAYMENT PLAN</p><p>- Minimum deposit of 20%, with the balance payable until March 2029&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(5742,'property',385,'zh','short_description','<p>推出Executive Suites ，这是一个独特的新住宅开发项目，坐落在宁静、著名和备受追捧的街区，提供来自Kshs的1、2和3卧室住宅。7.2米，包括带DSQ的选定单元，以满足不同的生活方式需求和投资策略。&nbsp;</p>'),(5743,'property',386,'zh','property_name','BALKIS RESIDENCE'),(5744,'property',386,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(5745,'property',386,'zh','description','<p>Modern 1, 2 &amp; 3 Bedroom Apartments in Prime Riverside, Nairobi</p><p><br></p><p>Discover elevated urban living at Balkis Residences, an exclusive new development surrounded by embassies, expat communities, corporate offices and new commercial spaces.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities include:</strong></h3><p>* ? Rooftop infinity pool with city views</p><p>* ⁠?️ Restaurant&nbsp;</p><p>* ⁠☕️ Cáfe&nbsp;</p><p>* ⛲️ Landscaped courtyard</p><p>* ?‍♂️‍➡️ Fully equipped gym</p><p>* ? Children’s play area</p><p>* ? Hotel-style lobby</p><p>* ⁠? Rooftop Sauna</p><p>* ⁠? Convenience store</p><p>* ⁠⚡️ Fully back-up generator&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prizes:</strong></h3><p>One-bedroom | 66-69sqm | from 7.9M&nbsp;</p><p>Two-bedroom | 109-114sqm | from 12.7M&nbsp;</p><p>Two-bedroom with DSQ | 128-133sqm | from 15.2M</p><p>Two-bedroom+ Study area +DSQ | 149-155sqm | from 17.25M&nbsp;</p><p>Three-bedroom with DSQ | 200-210sqm| from 23.3M</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Investment Highlights:</strong></h3><p>* High rental demand from expats &amp; embassy staff</p><p>* Attractive rental yields</p><p>* Strong capital appreciation potential</p><p>* Strategic high-value location</p><p>Book your unit today with flexible payment options.</p>'),(6007,'property',387,'zh','property_name','盖亚居住地'),(6008,'property',387,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹布鲁克赛德'),(6009,'property',387,'zh','description','<p>Gaia Brookside Forest is a premier residential development designed for those who seek elegance, comfort, and exclusivity. Situated in one of Westlands’ most sought-after neighborhoods, this development offers meticulously designed&nbsp;<strong>3, 4, and 5-bedroom apartments and penthouses</strong>, blending modern architecture with state-of-the-art amenities.</p><p>Gaia Brookside Forest offers a full suite of amenities designed to enhance your living experience:</p><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Arrival concierge and business center</strong>&nbsp;for a seamless living experience</li><li><strong>Residence lounge</strong>&nbsp;for private gatherings and relaxation</li><li><strong>Fully equipped gym and infinity pool</strong>&nbsp;with a rain shower feature</li><li><strong>Spa, jacuzzi, and yoga center</strong>&nbsp;for wellness and relaxation</li><li><strong>Jogging and walking track</strong>&nbsp;within landscaped gardens</li><li><strong>Cinema and library</strong>&nbsp;for entertainment and quiet study spaces</li><li><strong>Helipad</strong>&nbsp;for premium accessibility</li><li><strong>In-building retail and laundry services</strong>&nbsp;for ultimate convenience</li><li><strong>Sports facilities</strong>&nbsp;including basketball and padel courts</li><li><strong>Children’s daycare and play areas</strong>&nbsp;for a family-friendly environment</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and prizes:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>3-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (192 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 25.3M</strong></li><li><strong>3-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (210 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 27.6M</strong></li><li><strong>3-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (219 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 28.9M</strong></li><li><strong>4-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (275 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 36.3M</strong></li><li><strong>5-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (365 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 45M</strong></li><li><strong>5-Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (387 sqm)</strong>&nbsp;– From&nbsp;<strong>Ksh 51M\\</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6010,'property',387,'zh','short_description','<p>盖亚布鲁克赛德森林（ Gaia Brookside Forest ）是首屈一指的住宅开发项目，专为追求优雅、舒适和独特的人士而设计。该开发项目位于Westlands最受欢迎的街区之一，提供精心设计的<strong>3卧室、4卧室和5卧室公寓和顶层公寓</strong>，将现代建筑与最先进的便利设施融为一体。</p>'),(6011,'property',388,'zh','property_name','联排镇屋'),(6012,'property',388,'zh','detailed_address','Waiyaki'),(6013,'property',388,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Property Overview</p><p>Total of 48 elegant maisonettes</p><p>24 four-bedroom units</p><p>18 five-bedroom units</p><p>6 six-bedroom units</p><p>Four-bedroom units: 240 m² built-up area</p><p>Six-bedroom units: 360 m² built-up area</p><p><br></p><p>Design &amp; Architecture</p><p>Modern design with mono-pitched roofs</p><p>Architecture blends seamlessly with the natural surroundings</p><p><br></p><p>Ground Floor Features</p><p>Entrance lobby</p><p>Spacious lounge with:</p><p>Fireplace</p><p>Double-volume ceiling</p><p>Dining area</p><p>Kitchen with pantry</p><p>Dhobi (laundry area)</p><p>Visitor’s cloakroom</p><p>Ensuite guest bedroom</p><p><br></p><p>First Floor Features</p><p>Entertainment / family lounge</p><p>Three ensuite bedrooms</p><p>Two bedrooms with balconies</p><p>Generously sized master bedroom with a seating area</p><p><br></p><p>Additional Features</p><p>Domestic staff quarter (DSQ) for one</p><p>Parking for two vehicles per unit</p><p>Amenities</p><p>Clubhouse with swimming pool</p><p>Children’s play area</p><p>Jogging track along the river and around the estate</p><p>Ample water storage</p><p>Electric perimeter fence</p><p>24-hour security with a manned gate</p><p><br></p><p>Environment &amp; Views</p><p>Gradual slope towards the river creating a peaceful and serene environment</p><p>Each home enjoys stunning forest views</p><p>Accessibility &amp; Connectivity</p><p>Accessible via three main routes:</p><p>Waiyaki Way</p><p>Southern By-pass via Thogoto Road</p><p>Kikuyu Road from Dagoreti Road (Karen)</p><p>5-minute drive from Waiyaki Way</p><p>Less than 10 minutes to Karen Shopping Centre</p><p><br></p><p>Easy access to:</p><p>Westlands</p><p>Nairobi CBD</p><p>Jomo Kenyatta International Airport (JKIA)</p><p>5-minute drive to the Southern By-pass</p><p>5-minute drive to the Nakuru–Naivasha Highway</p><p>Construction Timeline</p><p><br></p><p>Development under construction in three phases:</p><p>Phase 1: 15 units – completion by August 2025</p><p>Phase 2: 18 units – completion by February 2026</p><p>Phase 3: 15 units – completion by September 2026</p><p>Show house complete and ready for viewing</p><p><br></p><p>Pricing</p><p>4 bedroom KES 25,000,000</p><p>5 bedroom KES 30,000,000</p><p>6 bedroom KES 35,000,000</p>'),(6014,'property',389,'zh','property_name','常春藤公园'),(6015,'property',389,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(6016,'property',389,'zh','description','<p>IVY PARK is a landmark residential development poised to redefine luxury and convenience in the heart of Nairobi\'s most sought-after neighborhood, Kilimani. This project, a testament to modern architectural excellence and sustainable design, is strategically located along Kirichwa Road, offering unparalleled access to the city\'s key hubs while providing a serene and exclusive living environment. With a groundbreaking ceremony set for October 1, 2025, and an ambitious completion date of October 1, 2028, IVY PARK is set to become a beacon of sophisticated urban living.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>World-Class Amenities:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>IVY PARK is designed to offer a holistic and enriching living experience, with a comprehensive suite of amenities that cater to every aspect of modern life. These state-of-the-art facilities are meticulously curated to provide residents with comfort, convenience, and opportunities for relaxation and recreation. The amenities include:</p><p><br></p><p>* Heated Swimming Pool: A luxurious, heated pool perfect for year-round swimming, relaxation, and wellness.</p><p>* Lush Garden: A beautifully landscaped garden offering a tranquil retreat from the urban bustle, ideal for leisurely walks and quiet contemplation.</p><p>* Fully Equipped Gym: A modern fitness center with the latest equipment, providing residents with everything they need for their health and wellness routines.</p><p>* Indoor Children\'s Playground: A safe and engaging space where children can play and socialize in a secure, indoor environment.</p><p>* Co-working Space: A dedicated, professionally designed co-working space that offers a quiet and productive environment for remote work and business activities.</p><p>* Coffee Bar: A stylish on-site coffee bar where residents can enjoy their favorite beverages and socialize with neighbors.</p><p>* Rooftop Garden: A serene rooftop garden with panoramic city views, providing a unique space for relaxation and social gatherings.</p><p>* Rooftop Lounge: An elegant rooftop lounge designed for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the breathtaking skyline.</p><p>* Yoga Studio: A tranquil and well-appointed studio for yoga, meditation, and other mindfulness practices.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></h3><p><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>62 sqm – Cash: KES 6.82M | Installment: KES 7.32M</li><li>66 sqm – Cash: KES 7.26M | Installment: KES 7.76M</li><li>67 sqm – Cash: KES 7.37M | Installment: KES 7.87M</li><li>69 sqm – Cash: KES 7.59M | Installment: KES 8.09M</li><li>73 sqm – Cash: KES 8.03M | Installment: KES 8.53M</li><li>76 sqm – Cash: KES 8.36M | Installment: KES 8.86M</li></ul><p><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong></p><ul><li>98 sqm – Cash: KES 10.78M | Installment: KES 11.28M</li><li>110 sqm – Cash: KES 12.10M | Installment: KES 12.60M</li><li>114 sqm – Cash: KES 12.54M | Installment: KES 13.04M</li><li>115 sqm – Cash: KES 12.65M | Installment: KES 13.15M</li><li>108 sqm + DSQ – Cash: KES 11.88M | Installment: KES 12.38M</li><li>128 sqm + DSQ – Cash: KES 14.08M | Installment: KES 14.58M</li></ul><p><strong>3 Bedroom + DSQ</strong></p><ul><li>142 sqm – Cash: KES 15.62M | Installment: KES 16.12M</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6017,'property',389,'zh','short_description','<p>常春藤公园公寓（ Ivy Park Residence ）由Nandwa&nbsp;<strong>Ivy、Diamond Homes、Diamond Ivy、Blossom Ivy和Luckinn Ivy</strong>等值得信赖的团队开发，不仅仅是一个家，它还是对内罗毕最具活力的街区之一的明智投资。</p>'),(6021,'property',390,'zh','property_name','4间独立卧室'),(6022,'property',390,'zh','detailed_address','Tigoni'),(6023,'property',390,'zh','description','<p>Experience refined countryside living in this beautifully designed 4-bedroom townhouse nestled within an exclusive gated compound in the heart of Tigoni. Surrounded by rolling tea plantations and fresh highland air, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy, security, and modern comfort.</p><p>Thoughtfully crafted with spacious interiors and elegant finishes, the home features a bright, open-plan living and dining area that flows seamlessly into a contemporary fitted kitchen — ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Large windows flood the home with natural light while framing breathtaking green views.</p><p>All four bedrooms are generously sized, with the master suite offering a tranquil retreat complete with ample closet space and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. The private garden provides the perfect setting for family gatherings, quiet relaxation, or outdoor dining.</p><p>Located in a secure, well-managed gated community, residents enjoy peace of mind while remaining conveniently close to top schools, shopping centers, Limuru Road, and Nairobi’s CBD.</p><p>Where serenity meets sophistication — your Tigoni sanctuary awaits.</p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 44, 52);\"> Unique Features</span></h3><p>✔️ Located in an exclusive gated compound with 24/7 security</p><p>✔️ Scenic views of Tigoni’s lush tea plantations</p><p>✔️ Spacious bedrooms</p><p>✔️ Private landscaped garden</p><p>✔️ Expansive windows for natural lighting</p><p>✔️ Modern fitted kitchen with premium finishes</p><p>✔️ Ample parking space</p><p>✔️ High ceilings enhancing light and airflow</p><p>✔️ Quiet, low-density development for enhanced privacy</p><p>✔️ Cool highland climate all year round</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6024,'property',390,'zh','short_description','<p>宁静与精致相遇—您的Tigoni避难所正等着您。</p><p><br></p>'),(6147,'property',391,'zh','property_name','七十七套公寓'),(6148,'property',391,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(6149,'property',391,'zh','description','<p>A modern residential development comprising 2 &amp; 3 Bedroom Apartments, some with DSQ&nbsp;located along Argwings Kodhek Road, Hurlingham.</p><p>Project Overview:</p><p>* 2 Blocks: A &amp; B</p><p>* 20 Floors</p><p>* 4 Units per Floor in Each Block</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>* Spacious Living Lounge</p><p>* Backup Generator</p><p>* Smart Access Control</p><p>* High-Speed Lifts</p><p>* Modern Swimming Pool</p><p>* Ample Parking</p><p>* Masjid</p><p>* Rooftop Terrace</p><p>* Near Masjid Rahma, Hurlingham</p><p>* Segregated Gym for Ladies &amp; Gents</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> Unit Sizes &amp; Prices:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Price (KES)</p><p>2 Bedroom All Ensuite</p><p>116 sqm</p><p>11.6M</p><p><br></p><p>2 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ</p><p>149 sqm</p><p>14.9M</p><p><br></p><p>3 Bedroom All Ensuite</p><p>180 sqm</p><p>18.0M</p><p><br></p><p>3 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ</p><p>185 sqm</p><p>18.5M</p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong> Payment Plan</strong></h3><p>* 30% Deposit</p><p>* 70% Balance payable within 2 years</p>'),(6150,'property',391,'zh','short_description','<p>现代住宅开发项目，包括2卧室和3卧室公寓，其中一些位于Hurlingham的Argwings Kodhek路沿线。</p>'),(6194,'property',392,'zh','property_name','仓库出租'),(6195,'property',392,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(6196,'property',392,'zh','description','<p>The Link is Kenya\'s first SME-focused warehousing and logistics park, situated within Phase 2 of the Tatu Industrial Park. Developed as a KES 2.5 billion joint venture, it is specifically designed to provide high-quality, affordable space for small and medium-sized enterprises.&nbsp;</p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong>Warehousing &amp; Capacity:</strong></h3><p>As of early 2026, the development is nearing its final full-scale capacity following the launch of its second phase in March 2025.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Phase 1: Fully sold out and operational as of 2025, housing companies such as Bakels East Africa and Novis PLC.</p><p>•	Phase 2: Currently in the final stages of development or newly completed (scheduled for completion in late 2025).</p><p>•	Unit Sizes: Flexible spaces ranging from 850 sqm to 10,000 sqm.</p><p>•	Lease Rates: Historically listed from USD 6 per sqm, with some early-bird incentives offering rates as low as USD 5.7 per sqm.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Businesses at The Link benefit from the robust, \"future-proofed\" infrastructure characteristic of Tatu City.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Logistics Design: Wide internal roads (up to 29 metres), generous truck turning radii, and advanced fire safety systems.</p><p>•	Utilities: Guaranteed 24/7 power and water, supported by a 135MVA substation and high-speed fibre optic connectivity.</p><p>•	Integrated Facilities: Units include integrated office spaces and modern ablution facilities.</p><p>•	Security: Features a secure perimeter with an electric fence, CCTV surveillance, and 24-hour access control.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Special Economic Zone (SEZ) Benefits:</strong></h3><p>Companies operating within The Link enjoy significant tax incentives that lower operational costs:&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Corporate Tax: Reduced to 10% for the first 10 years and 15% for the subsequent 10 years (compared to the standard 30%).</p><p>•	Exemptions: VAT zero-rating on goods and services, and exemptions from import duty and stamp duty.</p>'),(6197,'property',392,'zh','short_description','<p>The Link是肯尼亚第一个以中小企业为中心的仓储和物流园区，位于塔图工业园二期。作为一家25亿韩元的合资企业，它专门为中小型企业提供高质量、经济实惠的空间。&nbsp;</p>'),(6206,'property_type',15,'zh','name','仓库'),(6211,'property',393,'zh','property_name','JUJA/KIAMBU待售地块'),(6212,'property',393,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(6213,'property',393,'zh','description','<p>Zuri Springs is an 855-acre mixed-use development located in Juja, Kiambu County. It is developed by Rendeavour, the same owner and developer behind Tatu City and Oaklands. As of early 2026, it is marketed as a satellite development that offers more affordable land options compared to the core Tatu City precinct while maintaining similar master-planning standards.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Types &amp; Pricing (2026)</strong></h3><p>Prices for plots depend on the intended land use and current availability. As of early 2026, standard pricing is as follows:</p><p>Plot Type Size	Starting Price (KES)</p><p>Residential (Legacy)	1/8 Acre	3,000,000</p><p>High Density (Apartments)	1/4 Acre	7,300,000</p><p>Industrial	1/2 Acre	10,900,000</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The development is designed as a \"live-work-play\" community with a focus on natural serenity.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>•	Infrastructure: Includes on-site power (with transformer points), water supply from natural springs, and a picturesque dam fed by the Ndarugo River.</p><p>•	Environment: The site features mature eucalyptus and pine trees, 15km of nature trails, and green open spaces.</p><p>•	Social Amenities: Includes the Kia-Ora Primary School within the development and a planned dispensary, police post, and retail areas.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Location &amp; Accessibility</p><p>•	Proximity: Situated approximately 40km north of Nairobi and 15km from Tatu City.</p><p>•	Access: Located 7–9km from the Thika Superhighway (Exit 15) via the tarmacked Juja-Gatundu Road.</p><p>•	Nearby Hubs: Close to JKUAT University, Juja City Mall, and Gatundu Level 5 Hospital.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Investment &amp; Ownership</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Buyers typically pay a 10% deposit and clear the balance over a flexible 3-year (36-month) period.</p>'),(6214,'property',393,'zh','short_description','<p>Zuri Springs是一个占地855英亩的混合用途开发项目，位于基安布县的Juja。它由Rendeavour开发， Rendeavour是塔图市和奥克兰背后的同一所有者和开发商。截至2026年初，它作为一个卫星开发项目进行营销，与塔图市核心区相比，它提供了更实惠的土地选择，同时保持了类似的总体规划标准。&nbsp;</p>'),(6219,'property',394,'zh','property_name','瑞鲁（经济特区）商业/工业用地'),(6220,'property',394,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru'),(6221,'property',394,'zh','description','<p>Tatu Industrial Park is the largest private light industrial and logistics zone in East Africa. It is a core component of the 5,000-acre Tatu City Special Economic Zone (SEZ), designed to provide a \"live, work, play\" environment that decongests Nairobi.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Project Scope &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p>•	Size: The park is divided into phases; Phase 1 covers 457 acres (over 90% sold), and Phase 2 adds another 450 acres to meet rising demand.</p><p>•	Location: Situated 24km from Nairobi CBD at Exit 11 on the Thika Superhighway and 2km from the Northern/Eastern Bypasses.</p><p>•	Utilities: Features world-class infrastructure including 99.7% power reliability via a dedicated substation, 24/7 water supply with 30 million liters of storage, and 90km of underground fibre optic cable.</p><p>•	Security: Managed by a centralized command center monitoring all infrastructure and security 24/7.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Special Economic Zone (SEZ) Benefits:</strong></h3><p>Businesses operating within the park receive significant fiscal incentives under Kenya\'s SEZ framework:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Corporate Tax: Reduced to 10% for the first 10 years and 15% for the next 10 years (vs. the standard 30%).</p><p>•	Tax Exemptions: Zero-rated VAT on all supplies, and exemptions from import duties, excise duties, and stamp duty on property transfers.</p><p>•	One-Stop Shop: Fast-tracked processing for work permits, business licenses, and construction approvals.&nbsp;</p><p>Major Tenants &amp; Businesses</p><p><br></p><p>Over 100 local and global companies are already operational or under development:&nbsp;</p><p>•	Manufacturing &amp; FMCG: Unilever East Africa, Heineken, Chandaria Industries, Bidco Africa, and Kim-Fay.</p><p>•	Logistics: Africa Logistics Properties (ALP), Emirates Logistics, and Freight Forwarders Solutions.</p><p>•	Tech &amp; Services: CCI Global (Kenya\'s largest contact centre) and Davis &amp; Shirtliff.</p><p>•	Retail &amp; Food: Naivas, Dormans Coffee (global HQ), and the Tamarind Group.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Investment Opportunities:</strong></h3><p>•	Land Sales: Serviced plots are available for purchase, starting at approximately KSh 22.5 million per ¼-acre for commercial/industrial use.</p><p>•	Warehousing: Premium grade-A warehousing is available for lease for businesses not looking to build their own facilities.</p>'),(6222,'property',394,'zh','short_description','<p>塔图工业园是东非最大的私人轻工业和物流区。它是占地5000英亩的塔图市经济特区（ SEZ ）的核心组成部分，旨在提供一个“生活，工作，娱乐”的环境，缓解内罗毕的拥挤。&nbsp;</p>'),(6233,'property',395,'zh','property_name','8卧室家具联排别墅'),(6234,'property',395,'zh','detailed_address','Runda'),(6235,'property',395,'zh','description','<p>Set within the tranquil, tree-lined avenues of Runda, this exceptional 8-bedroom townhouse offers an unmatched blend of space, elegance, and privacy. Designed for refined living, the home delivers expansive interiors and seamless indoor-outdoor flow in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious residential addresses.</p><p>From the moment you step inside, you’re welcomed by grand, light-filled living spaces with high ceilings and sophisticated finishes. The generous lounge opens onto a beautifully landscaped private garden — ideal for entertaining, family gatherings, or simply enjoying peaceful afternoons in a serene setting.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Property Highlights:</strong></h3><p>8 generously sized bedrooms, all en-suite for maximum comfort and privacy</p><p>Lavish master suite with walk-in closet and spa-style bathroom</p><p>Expansive formal lounge and separate family/TV room</p><p>Elegant dining area perfect for hosting</p><p>Contemporary, fully fitted kitchen with ample cabinetry and workspace</p><p>Private landscaped garden ideal for outdoor relaxation</p><p>Domestic staff quarters (DSQ)</p><p>Ample parking and secure compound</p><p><br></p><p>Located in a quiet, secure, and highly sought-after neighborhood</p><p>This residence is perfectly suited for ambassadors, corporate executives, large families, or organizations seeking a prestigious address with generous accommodation capacity.</p>'),(6236,'property',395,'zh','short_description','<p>立即安排观看时间，探索最优质的高端生活。</p>'),(6237,'property',396,'zh','property_name','1英亩配备齐全的待售地块'),(6238,'property',396,'zh','detailed_address','Karen'),(6239,'property',396,'zh','description','<p>Karen Hills is a premier, master-planned gated community developed by Lordship Africa. Located in the lush suburb of Karen, it serves as the company\'s pilot project in Kenya and is designed for high-net-worth individuals seeking a \"signature lifestyle\" in a serene, controlled environment.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3>Development Overview:</h3><p>•	Concept: A low-density residential estate consisting of 60 fully serviced one-acre plots.</p><p>•	Infrastructure: The project features world-class infrastructure that is already completed, including:</p><p>o	Roads: Heavy-duty cabro-paved internal roads with attractive street lighting.</p><p>o	Utilities: Reliable borehole water with a large underground reservoir, electricity, and IT/telecommunications conduits provided to every plot.</p><p>o	Security: A dry-stone perimeter …</p><p><br></p><h3>On-Site Amenities:</h3><p>•	Sports Facilities: Includes a tennis court, basketball court, and a 7-aside football field.</p><p>•	Leisure: A Gazebo club for social gatherings and entertainment, plus dedicated children\'s play areas.</p><p>•	Landscape: Extensive indigenous landscaping designed to preserve the natural \"leafy\" character of Karen.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Pricing &amp; Investment:</strong></p><p>•	Plot Sales: Serviced one-acre plots have been listed starting from KSh 110 million, depending on the location within the estate.</p><p>•	Management: The estate is professionally managed to ensure value preservation and consistent service quality.</p>'),(6240,'property',396,'zh','short_description','<p>Karen Hills是由Lordship Africa开发的首屈一指的总体规划门禁社区。它位于Karen郁郁葱葱的郊区，是该公司在肯尼亚的试点项目，专为在宁静、受控的环境中寻求“标志性生活方式”的高净值人士而设计。&nbsp;</p>'),(6256,'property',397,'zh','property_name','在RUIRU出售的地块。'),(6257,'property',397,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru, Kiambu.'),(6258,'property',397,'zh','description','<p>Oaklands is a 1,400-acre master-planned, mixed-use development located in Ruiru, Kiambu County. It is a sister project to Tatu City, situated just 800 metres from the Tatu City boundary and approximately 7 km from the Thika Superhighway. As of early 2026, it continues to offer serviced plots for residential, commercial, and light industrial use in a controlled environment.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing :</strong></h3><p>Pricing varies by plot size and intended use (e.g., single dwelling vs. high-density apartments).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Plot Type Size	Starting Price (KES)	3-Year Installment Price (KES)</p><p>Residential (1/8 Acre)	50 x 100 ft	2,800,000	~3,700,000</p><p>Residential (1/4 Acre)	100 x 100 ft	4,900,000	~5,600,000</p><p>Apartment Plots (1/4 Acre)	High Density	5,500,000	7,600,000</p><p>Apartment Plots (1/2 Acre)	High Density	10,400,000	12,900,000</p><p>Note: Some premium listings for 1/8-acre plots are priced up to KES 4.3 million depending on location and proximity to amenities.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Sub-Communities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>Oaklands is divided into several distinct gated precincts:</p><p>•	Taratibu: Offers 1/8-acre plots designated for single-dwelling residential homes.</p><p>•	The Springs: An 8-acre gated community featuring 1/4-acre plots and a private 5-acre park.</p><p>•	Utulivu: Features larger 1/4 and 1/2-acre plots situated by a magnificent lake with a jetty and indigenous trees.</p><p>•	Pazuri Park: A 46-acre community with completed infrastructure, including borehole water and elevated storage tanks.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Amenities &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></p><p>•	Education: Home to the Oaklands Primary School and the upcoming Catholic Archdiocese of Nairobi day school.</p><p>•	Utilities: Fully serviced with all-weather murram roads, permanent beacons, piped water, and reliable electricity.</p><p>•	Environment: Includes 15km of nature trails, green open spaces, and a scenic dam fed by the Ndarugo River.</p><p>•	Security: Features perimeter fencing, gated entries, and professional security management.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Payment &amp; Contact Information:</strong></p><p>•	Payment Plan: Requires a 10% deposit, with the balance payable over flexible periods ranging from 3 months to 3 years (36 months).</p><p>•	Title Deeds: Over 1,800 clean title deeds have already been issued for the project.</p>'),(6262,'property',398,'zh','property_name','出售优质住宅用地。'),(6263,'property',398,'zh','detailed_address','Ruiru, Kiambu.'),(6264,'property',398,'zh','description','<p>Kijani Ridge is the flagship residential neighborhood of the Tatu City Special Economic Zone, a 5,000-acre master-planned city in Ruiru. Spanning approximately 350 to 400 acres of undulating land, it is designed for a \"live, work, play\" lifestyle.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Project Scope &amp; Infrastructure:</strong></h3><p>•	Controlled Development: Managed by a Development Control Company to ensure architectural uniformity and protect property value.</p><p>•	Fully Serviced Plots: Every plot includes underground utilities: power, water (from a 10M-litre reservoir), waste management, and ICT fibre.</p><p>•	Current Status: Over 90–95% sold, with hundreds of families already residing in the community.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing:</strong></p><p>Prices vary based on plot location (e.g., proximity to the dam or green areas) and current market rates.&nbsp;</p><p>•	1/4 Acre (approx. 1,000 sqm): Starting from KES 22.4 million.</p><p>•	1/2 Acre (approx. 2,000 sqm): Starting from approximately KES 42 million to 48 million.</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Tatu City typically offers a flexible 24-month payment plan with a booking fee.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Amenities &amp; Lifestyle:</strong></p><p>•	Health &amp; Wellness: Features 15km of exercise trails and jogging tracks designed by Olympian Lornah Kiplagat.</p><p>•	Recreation: Includes a large stunning lake/dam, over 75 acres of green space, and a planned clubhouse.</p><p>•	Education: Within walking distance of international schools like Nova Pioneer and Crawford International School.</p><p>•	Security: A gated community with 24/7 manned security and patrol walkways.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong>House Designs:</strong></p><p>While buyers can bring their own dream home designs for approval, Tatu City provides 12 pre-approved architectural designs for 3-, 4-, and 5-bedroom villas and bungalows.</p>'),(6265,'property',399,'zh','property_name','公寓出售'),(6266,'property',399,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani'),(6267,'property',399,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p><br></p><p>A contemporary, high-return residential development strategically located in Kilimani, ideal for buy-to-let investors seeking strong rental demand and capital growth.</p><p>Welcome to this stylish and modern 1-bedroom apartment located in the heart of the sought-after Kilimani neighborhood. Perfectly blending comfort, convenience and  urban living ,this unit offers an ideal space for investors, couples or singles .</p><p><br></p><p>? Prime Location</p><p>• 1-minute walk to Adlife Plaza</p><p>• 500 metres to Yaya Centre✨ Features &amp; Amenities</p><p>✔ On-site Restaurant</p><p>✔ Fully Equipped Gym</p><p>✔ Controlled Access</p><p>✔ High-Speed Lifts</p><p>✔ Borehole</p><p>✔ Water Purification System</p><p>✔ Backup Generator</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>? Available Unit</p><p>• 1 Bedroom (65 sqm) – KES 7.8M</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6268,'property',399,'zh','short_description','<p>位于Kilimani的战略性现代高回报住宅开发项目，是寻求强劲租赁需求和资本增长的买入出租投资者的理想选择。</p><p><br></p>'),(6292,'property',400,'zh','property_name','37 BY INEZA'),(6293,'property',400,'zh','detailed_address','Runda'),(6294,'property',400,'zh','description','<p>Quietly tucked behind Runda, just off Kiambu Road along Kwaheri Road, and moments from Sabis International School, 37 By Ineza reveals itself the way nature intended unforced, calm, and deeply rooted in its surroundings.</p><p><br></p><p>Set within one of Nairobi’s most prestigious low-density residential neighbourhoods, this exclusive development introduces a new rhythm of life guided by greenery, light, and intentional design.</p><p><br></p><p>Only 37 expansive luxury residences, elegantly positioned across 5 acres of verdant land. Each home sits on approximately 1/8 of an acre, preserving rare openness where nature is not an afterthought, but a constant companion.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Lifestyle &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>* Residents enjoy a carefully curated lifestyle offering:</p><p>* Exclusive Residents’ Clubhouse</p><p>* Heated Swimming Pool</p><p>* Paddle Court</p><p>* Half Basketball Court</p><p>* Landscaped Green Lawns</p><p>* Children’s Play Areas</p><p>* CCTV Surveillance</p><p>* Controlled Entry Gate</p><p>* Perimeter Wall with Electric Fencing</p><p>* Intercom Access</p><p>* Borehole &amp; Mains Water Supply</p><p>* Underground Water Storage</p><p>* Backup Generator</p><p>* Wide Internal Roads</p><p><br></p><p><strong> Prime Location Advantage:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>* Positioned next to Ineza Estate on Kwaheri Road, within a renowned blue-zone neighbourhood reserved for low-density luxury living, the development guarantees privacy, security, exclusivity, and long-term value.</p><p>* Runda</p><p>* Off Kiambu Road</p><p>* Near Sabis International School</p><p>* Easy access to Gigiri, UN Avenue &amp; Westlands</p><p><br></p><h3><strong> Investment Highlights:</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>* 5-Bedroom Ultra-Luxury Villas</p><p>* Prices from Ksh. 69.5 Million</p><p>* Limited to only 37 homes</p><p>* Ideal for owner-occupiers &amp; high-end investors</p><p>* Every residence at 37 BY INEZA is a 5-bedroom, all-ensuite townhouse with DSQ, meticulously planned across approximately 353 sqm.</p>'),(6295,'property',400,'zh','short_description','<p>37 By Ineza安静地藏在Runda后面，位于Kwaheri路沿线的Kiambu路旁，距离Sabis国际学校仅几分钟路程。它揭示了大自然想要非受迫的、平静的、深深植根于周围环境的方式。</p>'),(6296,'property',401,'zh','property_name','ARIA CAPITAL RESIDENC'),(6297,'property',401,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani, Nairobi.'),(6298,'property',401,'zh','description','<p><br></p><p>Located along Nairobi, Kilimani area.</p><p>Consists of 1,2 and 3 bedroom all units ensuite plus an extra guest washroom.</p><p><br></p><p>2 Blocks, A and B</p><p>24 Floors</p><p>2 lifts per block&nbsp;</p><p>2 Basement levels&nbsp;</p><p>5 units per floor</p><p>200 units in total&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>AMENITIES.</strong></p><p>✔️Rooftop heated swimming pool</p><p>✔️Fully equipped gym</p><p>✔️Steam and Sauna</p><p>✔️Children play area</p><p>✔️Ample parking</p><p>✔️Full back up generator</p><p>✔️Shopping Mart</p><p>✔️Public reading room</p><p>✔️CCTV&nbsp;</p><p>✔️2 lifts per block</p><p>✔️Party room</p><p>✔️Inter come</p><p>✔️24hrs security</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Unit sizes and Prices.</strong></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite of size 70sqm</p><p>Price from- 7.9M</p><p><br></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite of size 80sqm</p><p>Price from 9M</p><p><br></p><p>1 bedroom ensuite + study of 92sqm&nbsp;</p><p>Price from 10.4M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 113sqm</p><p>Price from 12.8M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 126sqm</p><p>Price from 14.2M</p><p><br></p><p>2 bedroom all ensuite of size 129.8sqm</p><p>Price from 14.6M</p><p><br></p><p>3 bedroom all ensuite of size 174.83sqm</p><p>Price from 19.8M</p><p><br></p><p>3 bedroom all ensuite + Dsq of size 194.62sqm&nbsp;</p><p>Price from 22M</p><p><br></p><p><strong>PAYMENT PLAN.</strong></p><p>?Installments:- 20% deposit, balance paid in installments. Monthly or quarterly up to completion</p><p><br></p><p>?Cash payment:- 20% deposit,balance shall be done within 2 weeks.</p><p><br></p><p>?Morgage:-at least 20% within 7 days, balance shall be financed and secured by financiers and professional undertakings after completion.</p><p><br></p><p>Completion is December 2027.</p>'),(6324,'property',402,'zh','property_name','宁静的庄园'),(6325,'property',402,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani, Nairobi.'),(6326,'property',402,'zh','description','<p>Serene Manor Apartments&nbsp;is a premium residential development offering&nbsp;modern apartments for sale in Kilimani, Nairobi. Designed for both homeowners and savvy investors, the project blends smart layouts, quality finishes, and lifestyle-enhancing amenities in one of Nairobi’s most desirable neighborhoods.</p><p>Whether you’re buying your first home, upgrading your lifestyle, or investing in a high-demand rental area,&nbsp;Serene Manor Kilimani&nbsp;delivers exceptional value and long-term returns.&nbsp;</p><h2><br></h2><h2>Amenities</h2><ul><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Fully equipped gym</li><li>Landscaped gardens &amp; circular relaxation area</li><li>Children’s play area</li><li>On-site community shop</li><li>High-speed elevators</li><li>Full backup power generator</li><li>Borehole water supply</li><li>CCTV surveillance</li><li>24/7 professional security</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Apartment Options And Pricing</h2><p>Serene Manor offers a diverse range of apartment options to suit different budgets and lifestyle needs:</p><ul><li>1 Bedroom Apartments (56 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 6,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (60 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 7,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (80 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 9,500,000</li><li>2 Bedroom Apartments (98 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 12,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom + Master Ensuite (110 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 13,000,000</li><li>2 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (125 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 13,500,000</li><li>3 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (140 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 15,800,000</li><li>4 Bedroom All Ensuite + DSQ (180 sqm)&nbsp;– From&nbsp;KES 20,000,000.</li></ul><h2><br></h2><h2>Payment Plan.</h2><ul><li>20% deposit on booking</li><li>Balance payable through&nbsp;monthly or quarterly installments&nbsp;up to project completion</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Project Completion and handover is scheduled for December 2027.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6330,'property',403,'zh','property_name','金芒果高地。'),(6331,'property',403,'zh','detailed_address','Kilimani, Nairobi.'),(6332,'property',403,'zh','description','<p>These beautifully designed 1 and 2-bedroom apartments are ideal for both homeowners and investors looking for a luxury lifestyle in a prime location. Located in one of Nairobi’s most prestigious neighborhoods, The Golden Mango Heights offers a blend of modern architecture, spacious living, and top-tier amenities. The apartments are designed to allow maximum natural light and provide optimal space for comfort.</p><p><br></p><h3>Amenities:</h3><ul><li>Two dedicated parking spaces per unit</li><li>Standby backup generator</li><li>Reliable water supply with storage tanks per apartment</li><li>High-speed elevators for all floors</li><li>Intercom system for easy communication</li><li>24/7 manned security gate and electric fencing</li><li>High-speed internet and connectivity</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>Apartment Features:</h3><ul><li>Modern and spacious layouts</li><li>Bright living rooms with large windows</li><li>Stylish open-plan kitchen with pantry</li><li>Dining area with guest washroom</li><li>DSQ (Domestic Servant Quarter) with private entrance through the kitchen</li><li>High-quality fittings and finishes for long-lasting comfort</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Pricing:</h3><ul><li><br></li><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom (55 sqm) – KES 7,000,000</li><li>&nbsp;1 Bedroom (88 sqm) – KES 9,000,000</li><li>&nbsp;2 Bedroom (100 sqm on 8th floor) – KES 11,000,000</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>Flexible Payment Plan</h3><ul><li>Pay just 30% deposit on booking</li><li>Settle the balance on occupation</li></ul><p>This flexible plan makes it easy to own your dream apartment in one of Nairobi’s most desirable locations.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>'),(6333,'property',405,'zh','property_name','待售住宅用地'),(6334,'property',405,'zh','detailed_address','Kiambu'),(6335,'property',405,'zh','description','<p>Kofinaf Tatu Residences is the most exclusive residential neighborhood within Tatu City, specifically designed as a low-density \"legacy\" estate. Launched in January 2023, it spans over 200 acres of mature landscape, including century-old indigenous trees and a 32-acre lake (Comte de Beaumont Dam).&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Unlike other developments in Tatu City that offer apartments, Kofinaf primarily provides serviced plots for buyers to build custom, high-end homes.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><h3><strong>Key Features &amp; Amenities:</strong></h3><p>The estate is defined by its \"lakeside living\" and integrated nature reserve.&nbsp;</p><p>Tatu City</p><p>•	Private Nature Reserve: Exclusive access to the Comte de Beaumont Dam, which serves as a sanctuary for diverse wildlife.</p><p>•	Estate Amenities: Includes gatehouses with 24/7 security, CCTV, electric fencing, private jogging tracks, and picnic sites.</p><p>•	Infrastructure: Fully serviced with reliable power, water, and high-speed fibre optic connectivity.</p><h3><br></h3><p><br></p><h3><strong>Plot Sizes &amp; Pricing:</strong></h3><p>Plots at Kofinaf are significantly larger than those in the neighboring Kijani Ridge, emphasizing privacy and exclusivity.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>•	Plot Sizes: Typically range from 1 to 2 acres (approximately 0.7 to 3.0 acres).</p><p>•	Pricing: Prices are generally available on application. As of early 2026, specific re-sale or premium listings for 4-bedroom luxury residences on smaller nearby parcels (1/4 acre) have been priced around KES 90 million, while the primary large-acreage plots require direct inquiry.</p><p>•	Payment Plans: Tatu City typically offers flexible 2-year payment plans for its residential plots, with financing available through partners like Stanbic Bank.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>Location &amp; Connectivity:</h3><p>•	Proximity: Situated in the \"secluded heart\" of Tatu City, it is minutes away from Tatu Central (the CBD), Grade A offices, and the Business Bay Square (BBS) expansion.</p><p>•	Education: Close to international schools including Crawford International School and Nova Pioneer.</p>'),(6336,'property',405,'zh','short_description','<p>Kofinaf Tatu Residences是塔图市最独特的住宅区，专门设计为低密度的“传统”庄园。它于2023年1月推出，占地200多英亩的成熟景观，包括百年古树和32英亩的湖泊（博蒙特伯爵大坝）。&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>'),(6337,'property',406,'zh','property_name','MOGOTIO OASIS'),(6338,'property',406,'zh','detailed_address','韦斯特兰兹'),(6339,'property',406,'zh','description','<p>Designed for modern urban lifestyles, Mogotio Oasis features&nbsp;<strong>studio, 1, 2, and 3 bedroom luxury apartments</strong>, finished with premium materials and hotel-grade detailing. Every element of the development is crafted to offer comfort, elegance, and long-term value for homeowners and investors alike. </p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Amenities:</strong></h3><p>Mogotio Oasis offers world-class activity facilities designed to enhance everyday living and overall happiness:</p><ul><li>Golf club</li><li>Swimming pool</li><li>Fully equipped gym</li><li>Children’s play area</li><li>Yoga room</li><li>Landscaped relaxation spaces</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Mogotio Oasis Apartments Types &amp; Prices:</h3><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Studio Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 5.8M</strong></li><li><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 7.8M</strong></li><li><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 12.3M</strong></li><li><strong>3 Bedroom Apartments</strong>&nbsp;– from&nbsp;<strong>KES 18.3M</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Prime Westlands Location:</h3><p>Situated in a highly accessible and secure part of Westlands, residents enjoy proximity to:</p><ul><li>Global Trade Centre (GTC)</li><li>Shopping malls, offices, and restaurants</li><li>Top schools and hospitals</li><li>Major roads and business hubs</li></ul><p><br></p><p>The completion is scheduled for&nbsp;<strong>June 2028</strong>, making this project an ideal off-plan investment opportunity in Westlands.</p><p><br></p>'),(6340,'property',406,'zh','short_description','<p>Mogotio Oasis专为现代都市生活方式而设计，设有<strong>单间公寓、1卧室、2卧室和3卧室豪华公寓</strong>，配有优质材料和酒店级细节。该开发项目的每个元素都旨在为房主和投资者提供舒适、优雅和长期价值。</p><p><br></p>');
