INSERT INTO `users` VALUES (9,'ken@afbeke.com','$2a$10$tzhgJAYhuQxeKOYg07LMh.Qtjf/bPI3beizS5Mwlfly.ihCJgrL.a','Ken','Huang','KenHuang','Chief Executive Officer','Leading BEKE Africa with a vision to transform real estate across all 54 African countries.','From the very beginning, BEKE Africa has held a firm belief — to provide the people of Africa with comprehensive, high-quality, and efficient real estate transaction and living services.\n\nToday, we continue to move forward with confidence and determination along the path of pursuing and realizing our dreams. All of our motivation comes from every BEKE team member\'s commitment to the \"Five-Heart\" Service Standard, striving to deliver the best one-stop service experience to our clients. It also comes from the dedication and hard work of every practitioner who upholds BEKE\'s \"family culture.\"\n\nI have always firmly believed that the real estate brokerage industry is a people-oriented industry. Ultimately, competition in this industry is competition for talent — the competition of a company\'s ability to cultivate and empower its people.\n\nAs frontline managers, you are both the core talent of our operational system and the foundation of our talent management structure. The overall capability of department managers determines business competitiveness, which in turn is one of the key elements defining the company\'s overall strength.\n\nThe company will continue to provide guidance and support to help our managers grow in their professional capabilities. By leveraging BEKE\'s years of proven management platforms, I encourage you to keep innovating, stay determined, and strive forward — so that, together, we can achieve our shared dreams and enable you to become the best version of yourselves along the journey.','','','',NULL,' ','https://beke.wecharge.africa/storage/profile/avatar/ceo-photo.jpg','active',1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-10-13 19:42:24','2025-10-31 16:11:36',NULL,NULL,1,'internal_staff',NULL),(10,'Joseph@afbeke.com','$2b$10$IXVqgkpaNOztu4CstPBkcOntnCeGaHO28Qx3C4kSSqqNsFDpG.7Vm','Joseph','Wanguo','Joseph123','General Services Department Head','','BEKE has built and is still building a strong reputation not only for delivering exceptional real estate solutions but also for putting people first, our clients, our partners, and our team, marketing, media, and administration who not only play an essential role in driving the growth and betterment of BEKE but also drive the dedication and integrity that define every transaction, every engagement, and every project we undertake.\n\nOur marketing team continues to be the voice of our brand — creatively presenting BEKE to the world with passion, precision, and a deep understanding of what our clients value most. Through innovative campaigns and strategic outreach, they ensure that BEKE’s name remains synonymous with trust, quality, and modern real estate solutions. Their work builds bridges between our agency and the communities we serve, helping us connect with clients in meaningful and lasting ways.\n\nOur media department strengthens this visibility even further. In today’s digital age, the power of perception cannot be underestimated. Through engaging content, professional branding, and a strong online presence, our media team ensures that BEKE’s image reflects who we truly are — a forward-thinking, client-centered, and dynamic real estate agency. Their creative storytelling brings our home to your own home.\n\nAnd behind all this, we have the administration team — the backbone of our operations. Their diligence and organization keep every process efficient, every record accurate, and every task on schedule. They ensure that our structure supports our growth, providing stability and coordination that allows the rest of us to perform at our best.\n\nThe perspective of this department is that our mission is always to provide the backbone that supports BEKE’s day-to-day excellence, ensuring that our operations run smoothly, our environment is well-maintained, and our teams have the resources they need to perform at their very best. Our commitment to service and efficiency directly contributes to BEKE’s success. Every organized workspace, every logistical arrangement, and every support function reflects our shared pursuit of excellence.\n\nBEKE’s growth story is a testament to what can be achieved when professionalism meets passion — when collaboration towards a common vision of serving clients with honesty and reliability. BEKE continues to operate with the same level of integrity and efficiency that has earned the trust of so many.\nAs we look to the future, let us carry forward BEKE’s values: excellence, innovation, and service. Together, we will continue building not just great engagements, but lasting relationships and a legacy of trust in the real estate world.','','','','https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/160c1bca40931e86aa98665dfdae51b035ff1f24.png','0701730233','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250804/160c1bca40931e86aa98665dfdae51b035ff1f24.png','active',1,0,0,'2025-09-09 07:30:50','197.248.222.197','2025-09-09 07:30:50','2025-07-03 15:03:51','2025-11-01 09:04:57',NULL,NULL,2,'internal_staff',NULL),(11,'carol@afbeke.com','$2b$10$AkEMP4Cwf5AqTOtIMAtbjeEhkn7WJ6IcOn8Qzzdr50L8XBYkmPdBq','Caroline','Gakuya','Carol123',' Head of Sales','Empowering my team to not only meet targets but to exceed client expectations through integrity, creativity, and consistency.','With years of experience in Nairobi’s property market, I’ve learned that real estate is all about relationships, trust, and understanding what truly matters to each client. At Beke, my goal is to make every interaction meaningful and every experience memorable.','Kenyan','','1997-09-13','https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/a4456786f1a131c01af68c766f4e8adeb191acee.png','0723 834963','https://api.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/a4456786f1a131c01af68c766f4e8adeb191acee.png','active',1,