INSERT INTO `work_plans` VALUES (3,13,NULL,'1.upload more projects\n2. Test more functions on the website and adjust where necessary','2025-11-04','pending','2025-11-03 19:26:58','2025-11-03 19:26:58'),(31,27,86,'1. Report writing.\n2. Site visit to KEZA Riruta with two leads.','2025-11-08','pending','2025-11-07 13:47:32','2025-11-07 13:47:32'),(33,24,88,'Will be doing the activation at Village Market.','2025-11-08','pending','2025-11-07 15:15:30','2025-11-07 15:15:30'),(35,11,NULL,'1. Call all Village market clients.\n2. Call the leads that Rashid will share today from the Luminara ad. \n3. Ensure that i have also shared details for Luminara with all the clients that were interested in this project.\n4. Have individual meetings with my team members to plan for the week.\n5. Compile last weeks weekly reports and send them to Ken. \n\n','2025-11-10','pending','2025-11-10 08:53:46','2025-11-10 08:53:46'),(36,27,94,'1. Reaching out to my hot leads and a thorough follow up on their enquiry.\n2. Viewing of the Riara One furnished apartment for my own new lead.','2025-11-11','pending','2025-11-10 14:36:57','2025-11-10 14:36:57'),(37,15,95,'Editing of Karen villas and generating leads ','2025-11-11','pending','2025-11-10 17:45:45','2025-11-10 17:45:45'),(38,13,96,'I am planning to upload more projects for land\nI will be checking project locations confirming if they are correct\nI will be doing follow ups with a previous client via call and update on the CRM\nI will do other office duties where necessary','2025-11-12','completed','2025-11-10 18:00:37','2025-11-12 06:12:22'),(40,12,98,'Waiting for a revisit on site at Azure in syokimau by Ian who viewed over weekend,I should take him there\n\nI will follow up with other clients from Village market ','2025-11-11','pending','2025-11-10 18:58:02','2025-11-10 18:58:02'),(41,23,99,'Still have very many follow ups from village market and also to finalize on pending reports','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 06:10:36','2025-11-11 06:10:36'),(42,22,100,'two clients meeting; A.   For four bed Amallia springs villa.\n                                               B,   For two acres in Cianda Kiambu.\nsourcing clients for Luminara','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 06:22:50','2025-11-11 06:22:50'),(43,23,103,'-Meeting.\n-Pitch by AAD\n-Meeting with Client. To be confirmed tomorrow.\n-Meeting at Luminara','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 14:10:21','2025-11-11 14:10:21'),(44,27,104,'1. Early morning lead\'s follow up.\n2. Later on, sourcing in Two Rivers with Centum Real Estate on their projects as I have a hot lead looking to invest in their Lofts.\n3. Back to the office to meet Kelvin and Lucy and discussing about their need.','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 14:11:41','2025-11-11 14:11:41'),(45,22,105,'1. Take a client to a site visit of 2acre land in Ruiru KAMAKIS by 9:30am.\n2. Take a client in Migaa Estate for viewing by noon.\n3. Sourcing.\n4. Be in the office for training by 4pm.','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 14:31:27','2025-11-11 14:31:27'),(46,19,106,'Office duties \nSourcing \nFollowing up with clients','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 17:06:04','2025-11-11 17:06:04'),(47,13,107,'1. I will be doing other office duties where necessary\n2. I will be doing a follow up with today\'s client\n3.I will be working on the website ','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-11 17:17:02','2025-11-11 17:17:02'),(48,15,108,'Organizing and strategizing with mia interms how how to structure the remaining part of the week .','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 17:53:10','2025-11-11 17:53:10'),(49,12,110,'Tomorrow I have a sourcing appointment at Stellato , concerning their commercial spaces they\'re letting and. Selling \nI will call the pending clients sourced from village market \nI will finish up the remaining clientele updates onto the new CRM \n\nI will follow up with previous clients concerning the 5 br mansionatte in syokimau ','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 18:51:06','2025-11-11 18:51:06'),(50,24,111,'8.35-9.30\nMorning Meeting.\n\n10.00-11.00\nMeeting with the HK Developers and Landowner for 11acres Limuru Road at U-Design, Lavington Mall.\n\n11.30-2.00\nTaking client to view 5acres at Gekambura, Kiambu County.\nSourcing at Kiambu for 10acres.\n\n4.00-5.00\nLuminara Celebrations.\n','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 19:36:21','2025-11-11 19:36:21'),(51,11,112,'	1.	Continue calling my leads, as I didn’t get time to do so today (though I managed to share details with them via WhatsApp).\n	2.	Follow up with my team members on their progress and plans for Luminara.\n	3.	Update my CRM system.\n	4.	Ensure all team members have submitted their daily reports.\n	5.	Send last week’s weekly report.\n','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-11 20:58:27','2025-11-11 20:58:27'),(52,19,115,'Get done with all, Primary responsibilities first\nFollow up with all pending projects. \nFinalize on most of my work \nSend out all reports \n','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 12:11:16','2025-11-12 12:11:16'),(53,19,NULL,'Office duties \nSourcing \nFollowing up with clients','2025-11-12','pending','2025-11-12 12:13:25','2025-11-12 12:13:25'),(54,19,NULL,'Get done with all, Primary responsibilities first\nFollow up with all pending projects. \nFinalize on most of my work \nSend out all reports','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 12:14:13','2025-11-12 12:14:36'),(55,22,116,'A. I\'ll attend the morning office meeting.\nB. Do follow up calls on clients I intend to invite for Luminara project plus all the rest clients and landlords we unfinished business.\n3. Sourcing ','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 16:25:20','2025-11-12 16:25:20'),(56,15,117,'Content preparation for the Cartier villas, purpose for the shoot on Monday making necessary arrangements including drone hiring and site permesions \n\nFinishing on the luminara long form educational video for YouTube and Instagram.\n\nTaking professional photos for domnic and Desmond ','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 16:53:32','2025-11-12 16:53:32'),(57,17,118,'Attend the morning meeting\nAttend the meta class from 9am to 2pm.\ncomplete my research on the best influencers we can use for marketing our properties.','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 18:31:32','2025-11-12 18:31:32'),(58,13,119,'1. I will continue from where I left today as today I wasn\'t able to do all the tasks I had planned to do.\n2.I will continue with my research on the real estate blogs and important topics.','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 18:56:56','2025-11-12 18:56:56'),(59,20,120,'Kilimani at 10 am \nParklands 12am\nUpper Hill 2pm','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 19:26:21','2025-11-12 19:26:21'),(60,12,121,'\nMeeting appointment scheduled with Stellato to discuss their commercial spaces available for sale and rent.\n\nShooting appointment for the Sunstone Penthouse Apartment to create a virtual tour video for a client who had requested it.\n\nConfirmed viewing appointment with Mr. Andrew for Friday as earlier scheduled.\n\n\n\n---\n','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 19:27:27','2025-11-12 19:27:27'),(61,23,122,'Sourcing in Westlands\nFollow up calls\nContact leads assigned','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-12 19:35:41','2025-11-12 19:35:41'),(62,27,123,'I will spend the whole day in the office following up with Luminara, and my other hot leads. In addition, keying in all my leads in the CRM. Following up with all the pending consents from my sourcings.','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-13 06:11:13','2025-11-13 06:11:13'),(63,19,124,'Continue with primary work responsibilities . \nSend out all daily reports on time \nFollow up with client and Previous project mentioned on my reports. \nFollow up with client interested in Westland\'s project\'s','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 13:17:20','2025-11-13 13:17:20'),(64,19,NULL,'Get done with primary responsibilities first \nFocus on trying to close a client for Luminara , Then Cartier Villa\'s and then The Diplomat (InShaAllah ) \n','2025-11-13','pending','2025-11-13 13:18:40','2025-11-13 13:18:40'),(65,27,125,'1. Early morning meeting and then leads\' follow up.\n2. Scheduled meeting with Kelvin and Lucy to go through the various project options we can offer them.\n3. Golden Mansion apartment shooting.\n4. Scheduled viewing with my lead Wilson to check out the ready 1Br apartments in Westlands.\n5. Back to the office to follow up on leads and prepare for Saturday scheduled viewings.','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 14:43:16','2025-11-13 14:43:16'),(66,15,126,'Shooting content at golden Maison to run an ad creative on the ongoing leads campaign.','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 17:26:23','2025-11-13 17:26:23'),(67,13,127,'1.I will be doing my normal work on the website, uploading projects.\n2.Complete some of the tasks that I wasn\'t able to complete today as the training took longer.\n3.Do other office duties as need arises.\n\n','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 17:38:12','2025-11-13 17:38:12'),(68,12,128,'\n\nPlanned Activities for Tomorrow\n\nTomorrow, I have a scheduled viewing appointment at the Azure project in Syokimau with a client interested in purchasing a 1-bedroom apartment with a balcony.\n\nI’ll also be following up with clients who have viewings planned over the weekend — two on Saturday (Luminara and the 5-bedroom maisonette in Syokimau) and one on Sunday (Apple Tree and Mango Tree projects).\n\nAdditionally, I will follow up with Paul and Lynne regarding the Luminara project, which I previously shared with them via WhatsApp.\n\n','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 18:59:19','2025-11-13 18:59:19'),(69,24,129,'Visiting 4th Parklands property with the client,\nVisiting Two Rivers properties with NanChong Team.\nActivation at Village Market with Dominic. ','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 19:05:16','2025-11-13 19:05:16'),(70,11,130,'1. Chair the morning team meeting.\n2. Continue follow-ups with previous and Village Market Expo clients (currently engaging with three serious prospects from the expo).\n3. Meet Eric for Luminara viewing between 12:00 PM and 1:00 PM.\n4. Return to the office for individual meetings with team members to review their weekly progress, discuss challenges, achievements, and ensure alignment on targets.','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 20:06:15','2025-11-13 20:06:15'),(71,22,131,'1. Attend morning office meeting\n2. Activation at  village market.\n3 Sourcing. ','2025-11-14','pending','2025-11-13 20:23:16','2025-11-13 20:23:16'),(72,19,132,'Get done with primary responsibilities. \nSubmit all daily assignments on time. \nFollow up with meetings and clients. ','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 13:45:26','2025-11-14 13:45:26'),(73,27,133,'1. Site visit with my lead at Emaar residence and Sunstone apartments.\n2. In the office following up with more leads.','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 13:51:19','2025-11-14 13:51:19'),(74,13,134,'Tomorrow I will be at village market together with Mia and Rashid.','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 16:54:32','2025-11-14 16:54:32'),(75,22,135,'Going for re-beaconing of 2acre in Cianda with :Land owner, client and a private surveyor by 10am. I will not make it for the office meeting tomorrow. ','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 17:28:18','2025-11-14 17:28:18'),(76,12,136,'Viewing appointment with a client for the 5br mansionatte in syokimau,\n\nI\'ll also be compiling my weekly report ','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 17:36:15','2025-11-14 17:36:15'),(77,23,137,'2 site visits at Luminara tomorrow from mid morning','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 18:10:55','2025-11-14 18:10:55'),(78,17,138,'Heading to village market for activation.','2025-11-15','pending','2025-11-14 19:28:02','2025-11-14 19:28:02'),(79,12,139,'next week’s plan:\n\n\n---\n\nNext Week’s Plan\n\nContinue follow-ups with all pending clients from last week.\n\nSchedule viewing appointments for clients who have confirmed their availability.\n\nActively source additional properties, including villas in Lavington.\n\nFollow up on Letty’s and Andrew’s offer letters for their respective properties to ensure progress.\n\n\n\n---\n\n','2025-11-17','pending','2025-11-16 18:13:32','2025-11-16 18:13:32'),(80,19,142,'Ensure primary office tasks are done. \nFollowed up with clients.','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 12:04:42','2025-11-17 12:04:42'),(81,27,143,'1. More follow up on my Village Market activation leads.\n2. Viewing with two of my leads to Luminara.\n3. Sourcing of more listings.','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 13:33:07','2025-11-17 13:33:07'),(82,17,144,'Attend the morning meeting at the office.\nGo to Luminara for the shoot as planned.\nFollow up on the influencers I had contacted since last week\nCall my clients and do followups.\n','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 16:12:49','2025-11-17 16:12:49'),(83,13,145,'1. I will be looking for better photos for projects that still don\'t have good photos  from other websites.\n2. I will get in touch with my client for today and also those who didn\'t pick up my call.\n3.I will be doing other office duties as they arise.\n4.upload projects received from my colleagues ','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 17:08:44','2025-11-17 17:08:44'),(84,23,146,'Still have leads that need following up to take to Luminara for viewing for this week. \nFollow-up with Jemimah regarding land in Migaa','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 17:45:42','2025-11-17 17:45:42'),(85,15,147,'Shooting at luminara \nLead generation and having atarget of 10 for tomorrow.\n\n And assigning them to various sale team ','2025-11-18','pending','2025-11-17 17:52:48','2025-11-17 17:52:48'),(86,24,148,'Hold a meeting with my team to go through the system and each client they have posted and checkon the progress.\nMake follow up calls and texts to my previous clients updated in the CRM\nSite visit at 2pm with UN Client for a house in Old Muthaiga valued at 320Million and 250Million in Nyari.\nFollow on the offer letters shared last week for the 10acres in Tigoni at 210Million and 1.6acres Hurli